Text:"<s1384>ROHO YA KRISTU</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Roho ya Kristu initakase, mwili wa Kristu uniokoe
Damu ya Kristo  
inichangamshe.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Maji ya ubavu wa Kristu yanioshe.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mateso ya Kristu nguvu yanizidishie.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Yesu mwema, unisikilize.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Katika madonda yako unifiche.
Usikubali nitengane nawe.
Na adui mwovu unikinge.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Saa ya kufa kwangu uniite.
Uniamuru kwako nije, na watakatifu wako
nikutukuze, milele na milele. Amina.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
