Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA NA KANUNI MPYA YA MISA
MWANZO WA       ADHIMISHO</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa jina la Baba, na la Mwana, na la Roho Mtakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Amina</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana awe nanyi</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Na awe rohoni mwako</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Namna nyingine ya kusalimiana:</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>1.Neema ya Bwana wetu yesu Kristo, na upendo wa Mungu Baba, na ushirika wa Roho Mtakatifu viwe nanyi nyote.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Na viwe rohoni mwako</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>2.Neema na amani  kutoka kwa Mungu, Baba yetu, na kwa Bwana Yesu Kristo, viwe nanyi.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Na viwe rohoni mwako</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu, tukiri dhambi zetu, ilitupate kustahilishwa kuadhimisha mafumbo matakatifu</s></f>"},{ID:12,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Namwungamia   Mungu Mwenyezi,  nanyi ndugu zangu, kwani nimekosa mno kwa mawazo,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kwa maneno, kwa matendo, na kwa  kuto timiza wajibu;
Nimekosa mimi, nimekosa mimi, nimekosa sana.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndiyo maana namwomba Maria mwenye heri, Bikira daima, Malaika na Watakatifu wote, nanyi ndugu zangu, niombeeni kwa Bwana Mungu wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utukufu kwa Mungu juu mbinguni na amani duniani kwa watu aliowaridhia. Tunakusifu, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tunakuheshimu, tunakuabudu, tunakutukuza, tunakushukuru kwa ajili ya utukufu wako mkuu, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ee Bwana Mungu, Mfalme wa mbinguni, Mungu Baba mwenyezi.
Ee Bwana Yesu Kristo, Mwana Pekee, ee Bwana Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwana kondoo wa Mungu, Mwanawa Baba, mwenyekuondoadhambi za ulimwengu, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utuhurumie; 
Mwenye  kuondoa dhambi za ulimwengu, pokea ombi letu.  
Mwenye kuketi kuume kwa Baba, utuhurumie.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa kuwa ndiwe uliye peke yako Mtakatifu, peke yako Bwana, peke yakoUliye Juu kabisa, Yesu Kristo, pamoja na Roho Mtakatifu, katika utukufu wa Mungu Baba.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI 
Bwana awe nanyi</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Na awe roho ni mwako</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyo andikwa na (J….)</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Utukufu kwako, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwisho wa Injili:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana. (au: Injiliya Bwana).</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Sifa kwako, ee Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>HOMILIA
KANUNI YA IMANI (NASADIKI)</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Mungu mmoja, Baba Mwenyezi, Muumba mbingu na nchi, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na vitu vyote 
vinavyoonekana na visivyoonekana.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Bwana mmoja Yesu Kristo, 
Mwana wa pekee </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa Mungu, aliyezaliwa kwa Baba tangu milele yote.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu aliyetoka kwa Mungu, mwanga kwa mwanga, Mungu kweli kwa Mungu kweli.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aliyezaliwa  bila kuumbwa, mwenye umungu mmoja na Baba; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ambaye vitu vyote vimeumbwa naye. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alishuka kutoka mbinguni,  kwa ajili </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yetu sisi wanadamu, na kwa ajili ya wokovu wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akapata mwili kwa uwezo wa Roho Mtakatifu </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwake yeye Bikira Maria, akawa mwanadamu.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akasulubiwa  kwa ajili yetu sisi; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa mamlaka  ya Ponsyo Pilato; akateswa, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akafa na akazikwa, siku ya tatu akafufuka,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kadiri ya Maandiko, akapaa mbinguni; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amekaa kuume kwa Baba. Atakuja tena kwa utukufu, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuwa hukumu wazima na wafu, na ufalme wake </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hautakuwa na mwisho.
Nasadiki kwa Roho Mtakatifu, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana mleta uzima, atokaye kwa Baba na Mwana.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Anaye abudiwa na kutukuzwa, pamoja na Baba </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Mwana, aliyenena kwa vinywa vya Manabii.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Kanisa moja, takatifu, katoliki, la Mitume.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naungama ubatizo mmoja kwa maondoleo ya dhambi. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nangojea na ufufuko wawafu. Na uzima wa milele ijayo. Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lituru jia ya Ekaristi</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KUTAYARISHA DHABIHU</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utukuzwe, ee Bwana, Mungu waulimwengu, maana kwa ukarimu wako tumepokea mkate huu tunaokutolea;</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nimazao ya nchi na ya kazi ya mikono ya wanadamu, na uwe kwetu mkate wauzima.
