Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utukuzwe, ee Bwana, Mungu wa ulimwengu, maana kwa ukarimu wako tumepokea divai hii tunayokutolea;</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nitunda la mzabibu na la kazi ya mikono ya wanadamu, na iwe kwetu kinywaji cha kiroho.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Atukuzwe Mungu milele.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Salini, ndugu, ili sadaka yangu na yenu ikubalike kwa Mungu Baba mwenyezi.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>W. Bwana apokee sadaka mikononi mwako kwa sifa na utukufu wajina lake, 
