Text:" Yesu, Mwana wa Mungu"},{Guid:"OmMiO0AZBEu2iSyCuNeU4A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    1 Thesalonika 5:16-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a ithe witũ, kenagai hingo ciothe; hoyagai mũtegũtigithĩria; maũndũ-inĩ mothe-rĩ, cokagĩria Ngai  ngatho;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ ha ũhoro wanyu-rĩ, ũguo noguo Ngai endaga, e thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu. Mũtikanahorie mwaki wa Muoyo; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>mũtikanararie mohoro  marĩa marathagwo; roranagiai maũndũ mothe; mũrũmagie ũndũ o wothe ũrĩa mwega; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na mũthemage ũndũ o wothe ũngĩonwo wĩ mũũru.  Nake Ngai Mwene thayũ we mwene aromwamũra amũtherie kũna. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Namo maroho manyu, na ngoro cianyu, o na mĩĩrĩ yanyu ĩroikario ĩrĩ ngima, na ĩgakorũo ĩtarĩ na ũcuke,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mwathani Yesu Kristũ akoneka.  Ũcio ũmwĩtaga nĩ wa kwĩhokeka, nake nĩakahingia ũhoro ũcio.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Isaia 61,1</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Muoyo  wa Mwathani Ngai arĩ igũrũ rĩakwa, nĩ hunjagĩrie  arĩa athĩni ũhoro ũrĩa mwega.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"rezQ7PbqQEqE5QnActjmCA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                          
1 John 2:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JOHN</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Twana twakwa, ngũmwandĩkĩra maũndũ maya nĩguo mũtikehagie.  Na mũndũ ehia, twĩ na Mũtũcirĩrĩri harĩ Ithe witũ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩwe Yesu Kristũ, ũrĩa mũthingu, nake nĩwe ihaki rĩa mehia maitũ; na to maitũ ithuiki,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ rĩa mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ gĩothe o nakĩo.  Na ũndũ ũrĩa ũtũmaga tũmenye atĩ nĩ tũmũũĩ nĩ atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> twatũũra tũmenyereire maathani make.  Ũrĩa uugaga ũũ: Nĩndĩmũũĩ, na ndamenyagĩrĩra maathani make, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio nĩ wa maheni, na ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma ndarĩ na guo ngoro yake; no rĩrĩ, ũtũire o amenyagĩrĩra ũhoro wake,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> thĩinĩ wa ũcio-rĩ, kwenda Ngai nĩ gũkinyanĩire kũna.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       Luka 24,32</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Yesu, Wee ũtũhotithie kũmenya Mandĩko Mathure; ngoro ciitũ ihĩaga rĩrĩa Wee ũgũtwarĩria.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"KW4x7uNDe0OQayXoijy4+g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ				           Kũguũrĩrio 21:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ John ngĩcoka ngĩona igũrũ rĩerũ o na thĩ njerũ; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>amu igũrũ rĩrĩa rĩa mbere o na thĩ ĩrĩa ya mbere nĩ gũthenga ciathengete igathira; iria rĩrĩa inene narĩo rĩgakĩaga.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Na ngĩona itũũra rĩrĩa itherũ, Jerusalemu ĩrĩa njerũ, rĩgĩikũrũka  rĩkiuma Igũrũ kwĩ Ngai, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>rĩthagathagĩtwo  ta mũhiki agemeirio mũthuri  we.  Na ngĩigua mũgambo mũnene woima gĩtĩ-inĩ kĩrĩa gĩa ũthamaki woiga:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, gĩikaro kĩa Ngai kĩ hamwe na andu, nake  nĩ egukarania nao, nao matuike andu ake  nake Ngai we mwene,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>agiyage ohamwe nao e Ngai wao.  nake ni ekũmagiria maithori mothe mathire maitho mao;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nakĩo gĩkuũ gũtirĩ hingo gĩgacoka  kũgĩa, o na gũtirĩ hingo gũgacoka kũgĩa na kĩeha, kana kĩrĩro, kana ruo; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>maũndũ marĩa ma mbere nĩ mathengu magathira.  Nake ũrĩa ũtũire aikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki akiuga: Nĩ atĩrĩ, maũndũ mothe nĩ kũmerũhia ndĩramerũhia.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI								John 13, 34
	</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>					       
Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: ngũmũhe rĩathani rĩerũ: nĩ atĩ mwendane; o ta ũguo niĩ ndĩmwendete, inyuĩ mwendane o ro ũguo inyuene.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"/qAWCknFYk6wwkpAoWDv1A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ 1 Akorintho 15:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ngũcoka kũmũmenyithia Injiri ndamũhunjĩirie, o ĩrĩa mwetĩkirie na noguo mũtũire mũrũmĩtie;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ nĩguo ũtũmaga mũhonoke, mwakorũo mũgũtũũra mũnyitĩte ciugo iria ndamũhunjĩirie ũhoro ũcio nacio,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> tiga mũkorirũo mwawĩtĩkirie tũhũ.  O mbere-rĩ, ndaambĩrĩirie kũmũhe  ũhoro  o ũrĩa  niĩ ndaamũkĩrire,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩguo atĩ Kristũ nĩ aakuire nĩ ũndũ wa mehia maitũ, o ta ũrĩa Maandĩko moigĩte; na atĩ nĩ aathikirũo: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na atĩ mũthenya wa gatatũ akĩriũkio ta ũrĩa Maandĩko macio maakiugĩte; na atĩ akĩũmĩrĩra Cefa;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> agĩcoka akiũmĩrĩra andũ arĩa ikũmi  na erĩ.  Thutha wa ũguo ningĩ akiumĩrĩra ariũ a Ithe witũ Magana matano na magakira,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> akĩmoimĩrĩra o ihinda rĩmwe othe, nao andũ acio-rĩ, arĩa aingĩ marĩ o ho o na rĩu, no amwe nĩ gũkoma makomete.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Thutha ũcio akiumĩrĩra Jakobu; na thutha wa ũguo akiumĩrĩra atũmwo othe; na thutha wa acio angĩ othe,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> akĩnyũmĩrĩra o na niĩ, ndariĩ ta mũndũ waciarirũo atarĩ mũkinyu.  Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ niĩ ũrĩa mũnyinyi wa atũmwo arĩa angĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> na ndiagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩtagwo mũtũmwo, nĩ ũndũ nĩ ndanyaririre kanitha wa Ngai.  No rĩrĩ, Wega wa Ngai nĩguo ũtũmĩte nduĩke ũũ ndariĩ;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> naguo Wega wake ũcio ndakinyĩirio ndwatuĩkire wa tũhũ, no nĩ ndarutire wĩra ngĩĩnogagia mũno gũkĩra acio angĩ othe;</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> no ti niĩ ndarutaga wĩra ũcio, nĩ Wega wa Ngai ũcio warĩ hamwe na niĩ waũrutaga.  Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>o na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ nĩ niĩ kana nĩ acio, ũhoro  ũcio noguo tũhunjagia, na noguo inyuĩ mwetĩkirie. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 15,16
	</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuga atĩrĩ  Ti inyuĩ mwathurire  niĩ, nĩ niĩ ndamũthurire inyuĩ, ngĩmwamũra, nĩ getha mũthiĩ mũciare maciaro, namo maciaro manyu matũũre.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ 1 Akorintho 15:1-11
"},{Guid:"WDTX+7q8NEGHzqmOq7OEYw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI							Mathayo 28:16-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, arutwo arĩa ikũmi na ũmwe na maathiire Galilea, magĩkinya o kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩrĩa merirũo nĩ Yesu. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nao maamuona, makĩmũturĩria ndu makĩmũgooca: no amwe ao nĩmaathanganagia. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu agĩũka akĩmaarĩria, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Nĩ’heetwo wathani wothe wa na Igũrũ na wa gũkũ thĩ.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, thiĩ mũgatũme andũ a ndũrĩrĩ ciothe matuĩke arutwo akwa,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> mũkĩmabatithagia thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Ithe witũ, na rĩa Mwana, na rĩa Muoyo Mũtheru: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>mũkĩmarutaga kũrũmia maũndũ marĩa mothe ndĩmwathĩte inyuĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na atĩrĩrĩ, niĩ ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ mĩthenya yothe, o nginya ithirĩro rĩa mahinda maya.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"xZBNQLaz3EqB3fgomOge8g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Luka 5:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ gwatwĩkire atĩ hĩndĩ ĩmwe rĩrĩa andũ aingĩ mamũhatĩkaga nĩ getha maigwe mũgambo wa Ngai, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>we nĩ arũgamĩte rũtere-inĩ rũa iria rĩa Jenezareth, Yesu nĩ onire ngarawa igĩrĩ ciikaire rũtere-inĩ rũa iria rĩu;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> no atahi a ciũngũyũ nĩ moimĩte  thĩinĩ wacio, na nĩ gũthambia maathambagia ngara ciao cia ndigi. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩtonya ngarawa ĩmwe yarĩ Simone, akĩmũthaitha amĩtwaratware  hanini, yume  rũtere-inĩ. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Agĩcoka agĩikara thĩ, akĩruta kĩrĩndĩ ũhoro, arĩ ngarawa-inĩ.  Na aatiga kwaria, akĩĩra Simone atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ta twaratwara ngarawa harĩa hariku, mũikũrũkie ngara cianyu cia ndigi iria-inĩ mũtahe ciũngũyũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Simone akĩmũcokeria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwonania, nĩ tũrutĩre wĩra wa hinya ũtukũ wothe,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na tũtinagwatia kĩndũ o na kĩ: no rĩrĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa kiugo kĩu gĩaku nĩ ngũikũrũkia ngara iria cia ndigi.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nao maarĩkia gwĩka ũguo, magĩtaha ciũngũyũ nyingĩ ma; nacio ngara ciao cia ndigi igĩtuĩkatuĩka;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nao makĩheneria arĩa maarutithanagia wĩra nao, marĩ ngarawa-inĩ iria ingĩ, atĩ moke mamateithie. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Magĩgĩũka makĩiyũria ngarawa icio cierĩ ki, nacio ikĩenda kũhorokera maaĩ-inĩ.  Nake Simone Petro ona ũguo,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> akĩinamĩrĩra maru-inĩ  ma Yesu, akiuga atĩrĩ: Ta njeherera, Mwathani, nĩ gũkorũo ndĩ mũndũ mwĩhia. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ we, o na andũ othe arĩa maarĩ hamwe nake, nĩ maagĩĩtwo nĩ kĩgeganio nĩ ũndũ wa ciũngũyũ icio nyingĩ maatahĩte;</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> o na gwata Jakobu na John, ariũ a Zebedeo, arĩa maarutithanagia wĩra na Simone. </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩĩra Simone atĩrĩ: Tiga gwĩtigĩra, nĩ ũndũ kuuma rĩu nĩ ũrĩtahaga andũ. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> Nao maarĩkia gũtwara ngarawa ciao rũtere-inĩ, magĩtiga indo ciao ciothe, makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Luka 5:1-11
"},{Guid:"hEp51TZPN02bq7bnHIPWBw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                        John 10:11-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu nĩ oigire: Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega. Mũrĩithi mwega nĩ arutaga muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wa ng’ondu. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Mũndũ ũheagwo mũcara, na atarĩ mũrĩithi, na ataarĩ we mwene ng’ondu, ũcio onaga hiti igĩũka,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> agatiga ng’ondu, akora, nayo hiti ĩgacihuria na ĩgacihurunja; oraga nĩ ũndũ no wa mũcara,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na ndatindagĩrĩra ũhoro wa ng’ondu.  Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega, na niĩ njũĩ ng’ondu ciakwa mwene,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o nacio ng’ondu  ciakwa nĩ injũĩ, o ta ũrĩa Ithe witũ anjũĩ, na niĩ ngamenya Ithe witũ;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩ kũruta ngũruta muoyo wakwa nĩ ũndũ wa ng’ondu.  Na ndĩ na ng’ondu ingĩ, itarĩ cia kiugũ gĩkĩ; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>icio nacio no ndĩcirehe, nacio nĩ ikaiguaga mũgambo wakwa; igagĩtuĩka rũũru rũmwe rũa mũrĩithi ũmwe. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩkĩo Ithe witũ anyendete, nĩ ũndũ ngũruta muoyo wakwa, nĩ getha njoke ndĩũiyũkie rĩngĩ.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũkũndunya; nĩ niĩ ngũũruta, niĩ mwene. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Ndĩ na rũtha ndĩũrute, na ningĩ ndĩ na rũtha njoke ndĩũiyũkie rĩngĩ.  Nĩ ndaathirũo ũguo nĩ Awa. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"ozGT0PL8mk6bnbnZvazfOQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Mark 1:14-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thutha wa John aarĩkia kũnyitwo, Yesu agĩkinya bũrũri wa Galilea akiumbũraga Injiri ya Ngai, akiugaga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Hingo nĩ ĩhingĩte, naguo ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩ ũkuhĩrĩirie:  wĩrirei, na mwĩtĩkie Injiri. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩa aathiaga rũtere rũa iria rĩa Galilea nĩ onire Simone na Andrea, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩwe mũrũ wa nyina na Simone, akĩmona makĩrekia rũgara rũnene rũa ndigi iria-inĩ;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> amu maarĩ atahi a ciũngũyũ.  Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkai mũnyume thutha, na nĩ ngatũma mũtuĩke atahi a andũ.  Nao magĩtiga ngara ciao cia ndigi o ihinda o rĩu,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmuuma thutha.  Ningĩ aathianga hanini, akĩona Jakobu wa Zebedeo na mũrũ wa nyina wetagwo John,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> marĩ marikabu thĩinĩ o nao, magĩthondeka ngara ciao harĩa ciatuĩkĩte. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> O rĩmwe akĩmeta: nao magĩtiga Ithe wao Zebedeo kũu marikabu thĩinĩ hamwe na ndungata iria cia wĩra, makĩmuuma thutha.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Mark 1:14-20
"},{Guid:"uZKOpSveLESdf3vvBKIo+Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Marko 1:29-39</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu, moima thinagoga, magĩthiĩ na Jakobu na John magĩtonya nyũmba ya Simone na Andrea. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, nyina wa mũtumia wa Simone agĩkorũo akomete e mũrũaru mũrimũ wa kũhiũha mwĩrĩ;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> makĩhe Yesu ũhoro wake ooka; nake agĩthiĩ akĩmũnyita guoko, akĩmũũkĩria; naguo mũrimũ ũkĩmũtiga, agĩitĩka kũmatungatĩra . </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ hwaĩ-inĩ, riũa rĩgĩthũa, akĩreherũo  arĩa maarĩ arũaru othe, o na arĩa maarĩ na ndaimono.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Na andũ othe a itũũra makĩũngana hau mũromo-inĩ wa nyũmba. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akĩhonia andũ aingĩ arĩa maarũarĩte mĩrimũ mĩthemba mĩingĩ, o na ndaimono nacio nyingĩ agĩtũma ciume andũ; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na ndangĩĩtĩkĩria ndaimono ciarie, tondũ nĩ cia mũũĩ.  Ningĩ rũci-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> gũtigairie ihinda  inene gũkĩe, agĩũkĩra akiumagara, agĩthiĩ handũ hataathiagwo nĩ andũ, akĩhoera Ngai ho.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Simone na arĩa angĩ maarĩ nao, makĩmũkinyĩra; makĩmũkora, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Nĩ ũracario nĩ andũ othe. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Nĩ tuume gũkũ tũthiĩ mĩciĩ ĩrĩa ĩngĩ, ngaheane ũhoro o nakuo; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>amu nĩkĩo ndokire.  Agĩthiĩ agĩtonyaga thinagoga ciao kũu Galilea guothe,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> akĩheanaga ũhoro na akĩrutaga andũ ndaimono.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006600"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Marko 1:29-39
"},{Guid:"I7deMov1CkCQu/pMYCRi0g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI John 20:19-31</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthenya  o ũcio wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia, gũkinyĩte hwaĩ-inĩ, na mĩrango ĩkahingwo kũu arutwo maarĩ, </s>"},{ID:4},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi.  Yesu agĩũka akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ, akĩmera atĩrĩ:
 
Gĩai na thayũ.  Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, akĩmonia hĩ ciake o na mbaru.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao arutwo mona Mwathani magĩkena.  Yesu agĩkĩmera rĩngĩ atĩrĩ: Gĩai na thayũ; o ta ũrĩa Ithe witũ aandekirie niĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>noguo ndamũrekia inyuĩ.
Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo akĩmaheherera, akĩmera: Iyũkiai Muoyo Mũtheru;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> andũ arĩa othe mwarekera mehia mao, nĩ maarekerũo; arĩa othe mwarega kũrekera mehia mao, megũikara matarekeirũo. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, ũmwe wa arĩa ikũmi na erĩ, na nĩ Thomas ũrĩa wetagwo Didimo, ũcio ndaarĩ nao  hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu okire.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ ũcio arutwo arĩa angĩ makĩmwĩra: Nĩ tuonete Mwathani.  Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Itonete irema cia micumarĩ hĩ ciake,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ngatonyia kĩara gĩakwa irema-inĩ icio cia mĩcumarĩ na ngatonyia guoko gwakwa mbaru-inĩ ciake-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ndingĩtĩkia o na hanini.
Ningĩ matukũ maathira anana, arutwo ake maarĩ kuo rĩngĩ kũu nyũmba thĩinĩ, na maarĩ na Thomas.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Yesu agĩũka, mĩrango ĩrĩ mĩhinge, akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ, akiuga: Gĩai na thayũ.  Agĩcoka akĩĩra Thomas atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Rehe kĩara gĩaku haha, ũrore hĩ ciakwa; na ũrehe guoko gwaku, ũtonyie mbaru-inĩ ciakwa; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>na ũtige gũtuĩka wa kũrega gwĩtĩkia, ũtuĩke wa gwĩtĩkia.  Thomas agĩcokia akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani wakwa, Ngai wakwa! Nake Yesu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee tondũ nĩ ũnyonete, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>nĩkĩo wĩtĩkĩtie, gũkena-rĩ nĩ arĩa matonete, na no metĩkĩtie.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Gwĩ ciama ingĩ nyingĩ Yesu ekire arutwo me ho, itaandĩkĩtwo mbuku ĩno; </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>no icio nĩ ciandĩkĩtwo nĩ getha mwĩtĩkie atĩ Yesu nĩwe Kristũ, </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Mũrũ wa Ngai, na tondũ wa gwĩtĩkia mũgĩe na muoyo na ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI John 20:19-31
"},{Guid:"VTq4vQ+1Dk6m6Rqb7hjC/w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Atũmwo 2:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na mũthenya wa Pentecoste wakinya-rĩ, acio othe magĩkorũo marĩ o handũ hamwe. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na hĩndĩ o ĩo hagĩũka mũgambo uumĩte Igũrũ, ta wa rũhuho rũnene rũkĩhuhũkania,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ũkĩiyũra nyũmba yothe ĩrĩa maaikaire thĩ; nao makiumĩrĩrũo nĩ nĩmĩ ciatariĩ ta nĩnĩmbĩ cia mwaki igayũkanĩte, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nacio igĩikara igũrũ rĩa mũndũ o mũndũ.  Nao othe makĩiyũrũo nĩ Muoyo Mũtheru,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> magĩitĩka gũthioma thiomi ingĩ o ta ũrĩa Muoyo aamahotithirie kwaria.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Na hĩndĩ ĩo kũu Jerusalemu nĩ gwaikarĩte Ayahudi aigua-Ngai moimĩte ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ ciothe cia thĩ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩa mũgambo ũcio waiguirũo-rĩ, andũ a kĩrĩndĩ  magĩcokanĩrĩra, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>makĩhagaiga tondũ o mũndũ o mũndũ nĩ aamaiguaga makĩaria na mwarĩrie wa kwao kĩũmbe. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nao othe makĩmaka makĩgegeara, makĩĩrana atĩrĩ: Githĩ aya othe maraaria ti a Galilea? Nao makĩaria-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ kĩ gĩgũtũma tũmaigue makĩaria na mĩarĩrie iitũ, o mũndũ na mwarĩrie wake wa kũrĩa aaciarĩirũo?</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Aparti na Amedi na Aelamiti, o na arĩa matũũraga Mesopotamia, na Judea na Kapadocia, na Ponto na Asia, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>na Frijia na Panfilia, na Misri na ndwere cia Lĩbia iria irĩ gũkuhĩ na Cirene, na ageni moimĩte Roma,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> arĩa Ayahudi, o na arĩa megarũrĩte magatuĩka Ayahudi, o na andũ a Creta na Aarabu, ithuothe-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> tũkũigua andũ aya makĩaria na mĩarĩrie iitũ maũndũ marĩa manene mekĩtwo nĩ Ngai.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
"},{Guid:"5RSK5oKq00yxWB7bZP48nA",Verses:[{
