Text:"MUGAMBO WAKU NGAI (NTUKUMIE PG64/213)"},{Guid:"KGldjVhjNk2NM5thJ6Uiig",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                          Ezekiel 17:22-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA KĨRORI EZEKIELI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Ngai oigĩte ũũ: Kũrĩ hingo ĩgoka ngetuĩra kamũtĩ ke mũthia-inĩ wa mũtarakwa o na niĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ndĩkahande; ngagĩtua kahonge ka mũthia-inĩ ga tũhonge twĩthĩ tũrĩa tũrĩ o igũrũ gacũmbĩrĩ-inĩ kaguo,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> njoke ndĩkahande kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩraya na igũrũ, gĩtũgĩru mũno; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nakĩo kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩrĩa gĩtũũgĩru kĩa Israeli nĩkuo ngakahanda; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nako nĩ gakũruta honge gaciare maciaro, na gatuĩke mũtarakwa mwega;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nakĩo kĩruru-inĩ kĩaguo nĩ hagatũũragwo nĩ nyamũ ciothe iria irĩ mathagu cia mĩthemba yothe;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o kũu kĩĩruru-inĩ kĩa honge ciaguo-rĩ, nĩkuo igatũũra.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Nayo mĩtĩ yothe ya werũ nĩ ĩkamenya atĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani hometie mũtĩ ũrĩa mũraihu na igũrũ mũno, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ngatũũgĩria mũtĩ ũrĩa mũnyinyi mũno; ningĩ nĩ niĩ nyũmĩtie mũtĩ ũrĩa mũruru,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> naguo mũtĩ ũrĩa mũũmũ ngatũma ũrure wega; niĩ Mwathani nĩ niĩ njarĩtie ũhoro ũcio na ngawĩka.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GITHOMO KIA MBERE Ezek 17: 22-24"},{Guid:"SIzlmuHVu02PZR1wIOtkaA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					           Jeremiah 17:5-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI JEREMIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, kũgwatwo nĩ kĩrumi-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wĩhokaga andũ a gũkũ thĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana akehotora ehokete hinya  wao, ngoro yake ĩgatirika Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo agatuĩka  o ta kamũtĩ kĩng’ang’ĩtie werũ-inĩ kũrĩa gũtarĩ wega o na ũrĩkũ ũngĩmũkinyĩra,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> no egũtũũra kũndũ kũũmũ kwĩ nyota werũ-inĩ, o rũng’ũrĩ rũa cumbĩ rũtatũũragwo nĩ andũ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  No rĩrĩ, gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wĩhokaga Mwathani, na agatua  Mwathani mwĩhoko wake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ agatuĩka o ta mũtĩ ũhandĩtwo hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia maaĩ, ũrĩa ũtambagia mĩri yaguo gũkuhĩ na rũũĩ; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na rĩrĩa kwagĩa ũrugarĩ wa riũa-rĩ, mũtĩ ũcio ndũngĩhoha, no ithangũ rĩaguo rĩgũtũũra rĩrĩ iruru; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na rĩrĩ, mũtĩ ta ũcio ndũrĩ ũndũ ũgĩũtanga mwaka wa wathima, na ndũngĩtiga gũciara maciaro.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"kO7Bw+OXH0G8qhzKrCVmAg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					           Isaia 6:1-2a,3-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwaka  o ũrĩa mũthamaki Ozia aakuire, nĩguo ndonire Mwathani aikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki kĩigĩtwo igũrũ kũndũ gũtũũgĩru;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nacio nguo ciake ikaiyũra hekarũ nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa ciaraihĩte.  Na igũrũ rĩake hakarũgama Aserafi,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o Serafi ũmwe akagĩa na mathagu matandatũ.  Nao o ũmwe akaanĩrĩra akera ũrĩa ũngĩ atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita, nĩwe mũtheru, ĩĩ, ti itheru, nĩwe mũtheru; thĩ yothe ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ riri wake.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Nacio itina cia hingĩro cia mĩromo ikĩenyenya nĩ ũndũ wa mũgambo wa ũcio waanagĩrĩra,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nayo nyũmba ikĩiyũra ndogo.  Niĩ na niĩ ngĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Hĩ! Kaĩ ndĩ na haaro-ĩ! Nĩ ũndũ ndirĩ ho rĩu;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo ndĩ mũndũ wĩ mĩromo ĩtarĩ mĩtheru, o na ningĩ ndũũraga thĩinĩ wa andũ matarĩ mĩromo mĩtheru; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>amu maitho makwa nĩ monete Mũthamaki, o we Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Serafi ũmwe akĩũmbũka agĩũka harĩ niĩ, anyitĩte ikara rĩa mwaki na guoko,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> arĩrutĩte kĩgongona-inĩ na mĩĩhato; agĩkĩhutia kanua  narĩo, akiuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, rĩrĩ nĩ rĩakũhutia mĩromo, naguo ũũru waku nĩ weherio,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> o namo mehia maku maahoroherio.  Ngĩcoka ngĩigua mũgambo wa Mwathani, akiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Nũ ũngĩrekia, ningĩ-rĩ, nũ ũgũtũthiĩra? Hĩndĩ ĩo ngĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ haha; ta ndekia arĩ niĩ.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GITHOMO KIA MBERE Isaia 6:1-2a,3-8"},{Guid:"iDyXxNTr3EGI8q93y1iojw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Gũcokerithia Maathani 4:32-34,39-40</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Musa agĩgĩta kĩrĩndĩ, akĩmera atĩrĩ: rĩu ta hoya ũhoro wa matukũ marĩa mathiru o marĩa maarĩ mbere yaku,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> gwata mũthenya ũrĩa Ngai ombire mũndũ atũũre gũkũ thĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o na ningĩ kuuma gĩturi kĩmwe kĩa matu-inĩ o nginya gĩturi kĩrĩa kĩngĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũũrie kana hihi nĩ kũrĩ kwoneka ũndũ ta ũyũ mũnene ũũ, kana gũkĩiguwo  ũndũ ũtariĩ ta ũguo?</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ kũrĩ hihi andũ marĩ maaigua, o na rĩ, mũgambo wa Ngai akĩaria e mwaki-inĩ thĩinĩ, o ta ũrĩa wee ũuiguĩte,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na magatũũra muoyo? O na tene-rĩ, kũrĩ kwonwo Ngai athigĩrĩirie gũthiĩ kwĩgwatĩra rũrirĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>arũrute thĩinĩ wa rũrĩrĩ rũngĩ na ũndũ wa magerio, na kũringa ciama, na gwĩka maũndũ ma kũgegania,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na kũhũrana mbaara, na gwĩka maũndũ na njara ĩrĩ hinya, o na guoko gũtambũrũkĩtio,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na gwĩtigĩrithania  mũno, o ta ũrĩa maũndũ mothe maatariĩ marĩa Mwathani Ngai wanyu ekire kũu Misri nĩ ũndũ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mũkĩĩonagĩra na maitho manyu?
Tondũ ũcio menya ũmũthi, o na ũige maũndũ macio ngoro-inĩ yaku,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ Mwathani nĩwe Ngai ũrĩa wĩ kũrĩa igũrũ matu-inĩ, o na gũkũ thĩ mũhuro warĩo; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>gũtirĩ ũngĩ o na ũrĩkũ. Nawe menyagĩrĩra irĩra cia watho wake wothe wa kũrũmĩrĩrũo,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> o na maathani make marĩa ngũgwatha ũmũthĩ, nĩ getha wonage wega wee mwene, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>o na ciana ciaku iria irĩũkaga thutha waku, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>na ningĩ nĩ getha matukũ maku maingĩhe wĩ bũrũri  ũrĩa Mwathani Ngai waku akũheete ũtuĩke waku tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:" GITHOMO KIA MBERE"},{Guid:"0R5+cKo3+0yJjMqSG1x31A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE  						Sirach 3: 2-6; 12-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA GĨTABU KĨA SIRACH (“ŨGĨ WA JOSHUA BIN SIRA”)</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ akwenda ithe atĩo nĩ ciana; na akũnengera nyina kĩhooto igũrũ rĩa ciana ciake. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ũrĩa ũtĩaga ithe nĩ arĩhaga mawĩhia; na ũrĩa ũkumagia nyina nĩ ta ũrĩa ũnganagia mĩthithũ.  Ũrĩa ũtĩaga ithe nĩ agakenio nĩ ciana ciake we mwene,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na rĩrĩa ahoyaga nĩ agwĩtĩkĩrio.  Ũrĩa ũkumagia ithe nĩ akongererũo matukũ make; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa wĩtĩkagia Mwathani nĩ agakenia nyina.  Mwana wakwa, teithia  thoguo rĩrĩa akũrĩte;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na ndũkae kũmũiguithia ũru kinya arĩ muoyo. O na angĩte gĩtaranio, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ũmũiguĩre tha na ndũkamũconokithie rĩrĩa wee ũrĩ na hinya.  Amu tha gwa thoguo  itikariganĩra, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na igatarũo ithenya-inĩ rĩa thĩnjo ya mawĩhia.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"GITHOMO KIA MBERE "},{Guid:"qoBq5VtkBkyJ9UmlyduXeA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 
Kĩambĩrĩria 15:5-12. 17-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨAMBĨRĨRIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ macio Ngai agĩcoka akiumia nja Abraham na akiuga atĩrĩ: Rĩu ta tiira maitho, ũbare igũrũ, ũtare njata, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>okorũo wakĩhota gũcitara; ningĩ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ũguo noguo mbeũ yaku ĩkaigana. Nake akĩĩhoka Mwathani; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>naguo ũndũũcio Mwathani akĩmũtuĩra ta arĩ ũthingu e naguo.  Agĩcoka akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani ũrĩa wakũrutire bũrũri wa Ur wa Akaldei, nĩ getha ngũhe bũrũri ũyũ ũtuĩke igai rĩaku.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nake akĩũria atĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai, ngũmenyithio nĩ kĩ atĩ nĩ ũgatuĩka igai rĩakwa? Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ta njoera mori ya mĩaka ĩtatũ, na harika ya mĩaka ĩtatũ, na ndũrũme ya mĩaka ĩtatũ, na ndirahugi</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na kĩana kĩa ndutura.  Nake agĩkĩmũoera icio ciothe,  agĩciatũranga na gatagatĩ njatũ igĩrĩ igĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nacio njatũ icio agĩciara mĩhari, akĩringanagia a rũatũ na rũrĩa rũngĩ; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>no rĩrĩ, nyamũ icio cia njoya ndaigana gũciatũranga.  Nacio nderi igĩitĩka gũcuhũkĩra nyamũ icio thĩnje, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nake Abraham agaciũmbũra.  Na rĩrĩa riũa rĩatuire gũthũa, Abraham akĩgwatwo nĩ toro mũnene; na atĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>agĩtebeba nĩ ũndũ wa gũtũmanĩrũo nĩ nduma nene.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ  riũa rĩathũa, na kwagĩa nduma-rĩ, atĩrĩrĩ, gũkĩgĩa na kĩmwaki kĩnene gũgũtoga ndogo,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> o na gĩcinga gĩkũrĩrĩmbũka, nakĩo gĩkĩhĩtũkĩra gatagatĩ-inĩ ka njatũ icio cia nyama.  </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya o ro ũcio Mwathani agĩĩkĩra kĩrĩkanĩro na Abraham, akiuga atĩrĩ: Bũrũri ũyũ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ‘heete mbeũ yaku, warũma rũũĩ rũa Misri o nginya rũũĩ rũrĩa rũnene rũĩtagwo Eufrate.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE Kĩambĩrĩria 15:5-12. 17-18
	"},{Guid:"WJz9j32pqUmG23cLtgCy1g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>KWAMBATA IGŨRŨ KWA MWATHANI</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE						Atũmwo 1:1-11</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO :</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Theofilo, nĩ ndaandĩkire ũhoro ũrĩa wa mbere ngwĩre maũndũ mothe marĩa Yesu</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> aambĩrĩirie gwĩka na kũrutana kinya mũthenya ũrĩa aatwarirũo Igũrũ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>arĩkĩtie gwatha na Muoyo Mũtheru atũmwo ake arĩa ethurĩire. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ nĩ eonanirie kũrĩ o arĩ muoyo, thutha wa kũnyamarĩka gwake, na imenyithia nyingĩ itangĩkararĩka, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>akamonekagĩra ihinda rĩa matukũ mĩrongo ĩna, akaaragia mohoro ma ũthamaki wa Ngai. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Na arĩ hamwe nao monganĩte-rĩ, akĩmaatha atĩ matikoime Jerusalemu, no meterere kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa gĩa Ithe witũ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>akiuga atĩrĩ: Kĩĩranĩro kĩu nĩ kĩrĩa ndamwĩrire ũhoro wakĩo: amu ti-itherũ John aabatithanagia na maaĩ; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>no inyuĩ nĩ mũrĩbatithio na Muoyo Mũtheru matukũ maingĩ matanathira.  Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> maakorũo monganĩte hamwe, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Mwathani, ihinda rĩrĩ nĩrĩo ũgũcokeria Aisraeli ũthamaki wao? </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nake akĩmera: Ti ũhoro wanyu kũmenya ciathĩ o na kana mahinda marĩa Ithe witũ atuĩte na wathani wake mwene. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> No nĩ mũrĩheo hinya, Muoyo Mũtheru aarĩkia gũkinya igũrũ rĩanyu: </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>na mũtuĩke aira akwa a Jerusalemu na Judea guothe, na Samaria, o na kinya ituri ciothe cia thĩ. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Na aarĩkia kuuga maũndũ macio, o mamũcũthĩrĩirie-rĩ, akĩambatio Igũrũ, na itu rĩkĩmũiyũkia, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>matige kũmuona rĩngĩ.  Na rĩrĩa maaikaire marorete mũno Igũrũ agĩthiĩ-rĩ, arũme erĩ makĩrũgama harĩ o,</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> mehumbĩte nguo njerũ; makĩmoria atĩrĩ: Inyuĩ andũ a Galilea, nĩ kĩ gĩtũmĩte mũrũgame mũcũthĩrĩirie Igũrũ? </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu, o ro ũcio watwarũo Igũrũ oime harĩ inyuĩ, nĩ agacoka rĩngĩ o ro ũguo mwamũona agĩthiĩ Igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GITHOMO KIA MBERE		"},{Guid:"y4fHpEyNrEG9hfh2zR4Klw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GOSPEL</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the holy Gospel according to Mark   		     Mark 1:14-20</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>After John was arrested, Jesus came into Galilee, preaching the Gospel of God, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>and saying, “The time is fulfilled, and the kingdom of God is at hand;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> repent, and believe in the Gospel.”
And passing along by the Sea of Galilee,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> he saw Simon and Andrew the brother of Simon casting a net in the sea;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> for they were fishermen.
And Jesus said to them, “Follow me and I will make you become fishers of men.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> And immediately they left their nets and followed him.  And going on a little farther,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> he saw James the son of Zebedee and John his brother, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>who were in their boat mending the nets.  And immediately he called them;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> and they left their father Zebedee in the boat with the hired servants, and followed him.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>The Gospel of the Lord.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GOSPEL
"},{Guid:"E0zqryKgK0mlqZFT6zfimw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>INJILI									Yohane 1:6-8,19-28</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Palitokea mtu, ametumwa na Mungu, jina lake Yohane. Huyo alikuja kutoa ushuhuda,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> apate kuushuhudia mwanga ili wote wasadiki kwa sababu yake. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Yeye hakuwa ule mwanga, ila wajibu wake ulikuwa  kuushuhudia ule mwanga.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Huu ndio ushuhuda wa Yohane.  Wayahudi walipowatuma makuhani na Walawi kutoka Yerusalemu waende  kwake na kumwuliza,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> “Wewe u nani?”Naye alikiri, wala hakukana; basi akakiri akajibu, “Mimi si Kristo.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Wakamwuliza, “Wewe u nani basi? Wewe u Eliya?”Akasema, “Hapana,”“Wewe u nabii yule?”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Akajibu, “La!”Basi, wakamwambia, “U  nani wewe? Tupate kuwapa majibu wale waliotutuma.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Wewe mwenyewe wajisema kuwa nani?”
Akasema, “Mimi, ni kama alivyonena nabii Isaya –</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ‘ndiyo sauti ya mtu aliaye nyikani, inyosheni njia ya Bwana.’”
Nao wajumbe  walikuwa wa jamii ya Mafarisayo. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Wakaendelea  kumhoji na kumwambia, “Mbona basi, wabatiza, ikiwa wewe si Kristo, wala Eliya, wala nabii yule?”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Yohane akawajibu, 
“Mimi nabatiza kwa maji.  Katikati yenu amesimama yeye msiyemjua ninyi,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> yeye ndiye anayekuja nyuma yangu, ambaye sistahili kufungua ukanda wa kiatu chake.”</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Mambo hayo yalitendeka Bethania, ng’ambo ya Yordani, alikobatiza Yohane.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Injili ya Bwana</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Somo la Injili Yohane 1:6-8,19-28	"},{Guid:"em/GRTMxwk6ALYNm53QgqA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SECOND READING				                     1Corinthians 15:12, 16-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the first Letter of Saint Paul to the Corinthians</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Brethren</s> 
<s1384>If Christ is preached as raised from the dead, how can some of you say that there is no resurrection of the dead?</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>For if the dead are not raised, then Christ has not been raised.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> If Christ has not been raised, your faith is futile and you are still in your sins. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Then those also who have fallen asleep in Christ have perished. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> If for this life only we have hoped in Christ, we are of all men most to be pitied.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>But in fact Christ has been raised from the dead, the first fruits of those who have fallen asleep.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Word of the Lord</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia, Alleluia 													               </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Rejoice and leap for joy, says the Lord, for behold, your reward is great in heaven.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"SECOND READING	"},{Guid:"bGyJKSirLUyYeQl+Ya8b3g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA 
Danieli 12:1-3</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Danieli</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Wakati huo, Mikaeli atasimama, yule mkuu anayewasimamia wana wa taifa lako;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>kutakuwa na wakati wa taabu, isivyowahi kutokea tangu walipoanza kuwako mataifa, mpaka sasa. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Lakini wakati ule taifa lako litaokolewa, ndio wote walioandikwa katika kitabu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Wengi sana wa wale wanaolala katika nchi ya mavumbi wataamka; baadhi kwa uzima wa milele, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>wengine kwa dharau ya milele. Wenye hekima watang'ara kama mwangaza wa anga,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nao waliowaongoza wengi katika njia ya haki watamulika kama nyota, milele na milele.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA Danieli 12:1-3
"},{Guid:"jeXVjrrjNUKqk112xJ/sKQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA PILI 
Waebrania 10:11-14, 18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika barua kwa Waebrania</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kila kuhani husimama altareni kila siku atimize huduma yake na kutoa sadaka zile zile mara nyingi, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ingawa haziwezi kuondoa dhambi hata mara moja. Lakini huyo alitoa sadaka moja tu kwa ajili ya dhambi, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>akaenda kukaa daima kulia kwa Mungu. Tangu hapo anangojea mpaka adui zake wawekwe chini ya miguu yake. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Maana kwa nguvu ya sadaka moja amewapatia wanaotakaswa wote ukamilifu wa milele. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Lakini palipo na msamaha, sadaka kwa ajili ya dhambi haipo tena.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>SHANGILIO LA INJILI 							Luka 21:36</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya.   Aleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Kesheni na kusali daima, mpate nguvu ya kusimama wima mbele ya Mwana wa Mtu.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"SOMO LA PILI Waebrania 10:11-14, 18
"},{Guid:"gJtUKDjkJ02tF31EUUvtGw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA 							Yeremia 23:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Yeremia</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ole wao wachungaji, wanaowaacha kondoo wa malisho yangu kutawanyika na kupotea - asema Bwana.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Ndiyo maana Bwana, Mungu wa Israeli, amesema hivi juu ya wachungaji wanaowalisha watu wa taifa langu:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> mmewatawanya na kuwasambaza kondoo wa kundi langu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Hamkuwaangalia, lakini sasa mimi nawaangalia ninyi  sababu ya matendo yenu maovu, asema Bwana. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nami nitawakusanya kondoo wangu waliobaki, kutoka nchi zote nilikowasambaza.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nitawarudisha katika malisho yao, hapo watazaa tena na kuongezeka. Nitaweka juu yao wachungaji wenye kuwalisha,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nao hawataona tena woga wala hofu,
wala hatapotea hata mmoja wao, asema Bwana. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Tazama, siku zitakuja -  asema Bwana- nitakapomwoteshea Daudi chipukizi takatifu, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>mfalme atakayetawala na kutenda kwa hekima, na kufanya hukumu na haki katika nchi.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zake, Yuda ataokolewa, na Israeli atakaa salama, naye ataitwa jina hili:
\"Bwana ndiye haki yetu.\"</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA Yere23:1-6	"},{Guid:"Dsno4tvfQ0aFmscdOXAC3g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 138:1-2a;2b-3;4-5;7b-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.	Nĩ ngũgũcokeria ngatho na ngoro yakwa yothe, ngũkũinĩra ngĩkũgoocaga ngai ciothe irĩ o ho.  Ngũinamĩrĩra  njerekeire  hekarũ yaku theru.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Njokerie rĩĩtwa rĩaku ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa ũtugi waku, na tondũ wa wĩhokeku waku o naguo,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> amu nĩ kũnenehia ũnenehetie uuge waku kũrĩ maũndũ marĩa mangĩ ma rĩĩtwa rĩaku mothe.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthĩ o ũrĩa ndetanire, wee nĩ wanyamũkĩire; nĩ wanyũmĩrĩirie nĩ kũnjĩkĩra hinya ngoro.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Athamaki othe a thĩ nĩ ngatho  magagũcokeria, wee Mwathani, rĩrĩa magakorũo  maiguĩte ciugo iria kanua gaku kaanoiga. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩĩ-ni, nĩ kũina makaina, magane ikĩro cia Mwathani, nĩ gũkorũo riri wa Mwathani nĩ mũnene.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Guoko gwaku kwa ũrĩo nĩkuo gũkahonokia, Mwathani-rĩ, maũndũ makwa nĩ akamakindĩra: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>ũtugi waku, Mwathani, nĩ wa tene na tene; wĩra wa moko maku-rĩ, ndũkanaũtiganĩrie.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"lYmxEb7ZF0mHXUKJd4c5Aw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                 Thaburi 104: 1. 24; 29,30; 31. 34.</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ muoyo waku.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani.  Ĩ Mwathani, Ngai wakwa, wee ũrĩ mũnene mũno; wĩguĩkĩte ũtĩĩku,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na ũkaru.  Ĩ Mwathani, nĩ maingĩ atĩa mawĩra marĩa ũrutĩte! O mothe ũmarutĩte na wara; thĩ nĩ kũiyũra ĩiyũire ũrĩmi waku.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ muoyo waku.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ ũkahitha ũthiũ, cio igagĩcanjama; ũcokagĩra mĩheehũ yacio, igakua, igacoka rũkũngũ-inĩ gwacio. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Gũtũma ũtũmaga muoyo waku, nacio igakĩgĩa; ũthiũ wa thĩ ũgakĩwanakahia.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ muoyo waku.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Riri wa Mwathani ũrotũũra tene o na tene; Mwathani arokenagĩra mawĩra marĩa arutĩte.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Macũrania makwa marogĩa na mũrĩo harĩ we: niĩ-rĩ, nĩ Mwathani ndĩrĩkenaga nĩ ũndũ wake.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ muoyo waku.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO "},{Guid:"GDRpHAbatUyYiUMau5JObw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO   Thaburi 33:4-5;18-19;20,22</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, uuge wa Mwathani nĩ mwerekereru; wĩra wake wothe nĩ wa kwĩhokwo.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũndũ ũrĩa enda nĩ ũthingu, o na kĩhooto: thĩ ĩiyũire ũtugi wa Mwathani o kũiyũra.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ; riitho rĩa Mwathani rĩerekeire harĩ arĩa amwĩtigĩri, rĩgakĩerekera harĩ andũ arĩa merĩgagĩrĩra o ũtugi wake; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩguo ateithũrage ũtũũro wao gĩkuũ-inĩ, gwata hingo ya ng’aragu amaikaragie na muoyo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩoyo itũ-rĩ, ĩkirĩrĩrie yetereire o Mwathani: we nowe ũteithio witũ o na ngo iitũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũtugi waku, Mwathani, tũma ũikarage na ithuĩ, kũringana o na ũrĩa tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO   Thaburi 33:4-5;18-19;20,22
"},{Guid:"HqDe8/1UyUS3rHWmnrTbRQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                               Thaburi 107:23-24;25-26;28-29;30-31</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ arĩa maikũrũkaga magathiĩ na iria me thĩinĩ wa marikabu, arĩa mathiaga wonjoria  kũu maaĩ-inĩ maingĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> acio nĩ monaga mawĩko ma Mwathani; maũndũ make me magegania magakĩmeonera me maaĩ-inĩ macio mariku.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Amu rĩrĩa oiga, rũhuho nĩ rũarahũkaga, rũrĩa rũa kĩhuhũkanio, naruo rũkaiyũkĩrĩria makũmbĩ ma maaĩ, macio ma iria, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>andũ makoyũo na igũrũ o nginya matu-inĩ, ningĩ magacoka na thĩ o mũriko-inĩ; ngoro ciao ĩgakĩregera nĩ ũũru ũrĩa marona.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Magagĩkaĩra Mwathani tondũ wa ũrĩa mathĩnĩkĩte, nake akamaruta mĩnyamaro-inĩ ĩo marĩ nayo. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Atũmaga kĩhuhũkanio gĩcoke kũhorera, makumbĩ macio moima kuo magagĩkira ngiria.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nao magakena nĩ ũndũ rĩu mo nĩ mahorerete, agakĩmakinyia rĩingĩrĩro-inĩ o rĩrĩa merirĩirie makinye;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o, ta nĩ macokerie Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa ũtugi wake, na maũndũ ma magegania marĩa ekaga ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ!</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GUCOKERWO Thaburi 107:23-24;25-26;28-29;30-31 "},{Guid:"fluQPNQJmECA5xXpkeXGNg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                         
Thaburi  15:2-3a;3b-4;5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Arĩa athaka ngoro magaikara mũciĩ-inĩ wa Ngai</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, nĩ ũrĩa wĩna mĩthiĩre mĩkinyanĩru, ũrĩa wĩkaga o maũndũ ma ũthingu, na kwaria aaragia o ũhoro-wa-ma,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o ũrĩa wa ngoro yake; mũndũ ũtarĩ na njambanio rũrĩmĩ-inĩ rwake.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Arĩa athaka ngoro magaikara mũciĩ-inĩ wa Ngai</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ndekaga mũthiritũwe ũũru, kana akoya kiugo gĩa kũmenereria  mũndũ ũngĩ wa itũũra</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>.  Maitho-inĩ make mũũra-huhu  nĩ gĩthemba kĩrurũke; no arĩa etigĩri Mwathani nĩo ekĩrĩire.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  O na aakorũo ehĩtĩte mwĩhĩtwa ũngĩmũnũha ndangĩgarũrĩra.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Arĩa athaka ngoro magaikara mũciĩ-inĩ wa Ngai</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ndohoranagĩra mbia ciake nĩ getha one nyongeri, na ndangĩiyũkia ihaki rĩa gũtũma amene mũndũ ũtarĩ mwĩhia.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ũrĩa ũrũmagĩrĩra mĩtugo ĩyo ndarĩ hingo angĩenyenyeka.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Arĩa athaka ngoro magaikara mũciĩ-inĩ wa Ngai</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO "},{Guid:"s2gHucBVW0ejbxCkhK0hFQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                   Thaburi 103:1-2;3-4 8 na 10;12-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani; gwata kĩrĩa o gĩothe gĩĩ thĩinĩ wakwa nĩ kĩgathe rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩamũre. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ngoro yakwa, kĩgathe Mwathani, na ndũkariganĩrũo nĩ wega o na ũmwe marĩa agwĩkaga. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩ we ũkuohagĩra waganu waku wothe, ndũari ciaku ciothe o nacio nowe mũkũhonia; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o we mũkũũri muoyo waku harĩ irima rĩa gĩkuũ, na nowe mũgwĩki maũndũ ma ũtugi na ma matha maingĩ, ta arĩ thũmbĩ aragwĩkĩra ya ũnene.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ nĩ muuma-andũ mũno; ndahiũhaga kũrakara, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na e na ũtugi mũingĩ.  Ndatwĩkĩte ta ũrĩa mahĩtia maitũ maagĩrĩirũo, kana agatũcokeria kũringana na ũrĩa waganu witũ ũigana.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>O ta ũrĩa irathĩro kũraihanĩrĩirie na ithũĩro, no taguo atũthengeirie mehia maitũ matũraihĩrĩrie.  </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> O ũrĩa mũthuri aiguagĩra ciana ciake tha, noguo Mwathani aiguagĩra arĩa mamwĩtigĩrĩte.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"THABURI YA GUCOKERWO Thaburi 103:1-2;3-4 8 na 10;12-13"},{Guid:"TsJSqG7A/0aqft/Uaw0XEA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                           Thaburi 27:1;7-8;9ab;13-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa, o gwata ũhonokio wakwa; ingĩgĩĩtigĩra ũ? </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩwe hinya ũrĩa ũgitĩire muoyo wakwa; ũrĩa ũngĩ’makia nũ?</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ĩ Mwathani, igua mũgambo wakwa ngĩkaya; kĩnginyĩrie wega waku, ũnyamũkĩrie.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Harĩa woigire, rongoriani ũthiũ wakwa-rĩ, ngoro yakwa ĩkwĩrĩte ũũ: Ũthiũ  waku, Mwathani, nĩ ndĩrĩũrongoragia.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Tiga kwĩĩ’hithĩra ũthiũ; tiga gũkĩingata ndungata yaku na marakara: nĩwe ũtũire ũndeithagia.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Gũca njĩtĩkĩtie atĩ nĩ ngeyonera wega wa Mwathani ndĩ bũrũri wa arĩa me muoyo, ingĩrĩ kũhooteka.  </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Eterera O Mwathani gĩa na hinya, na wĩũmĩrĩrie ngoro; ĩĩ-ni, no gĩeterere Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO "},{Guid:"zQelqwDUKk2KLIpFMwLNHg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 84: 1-2,4-5,8-10(K)1</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Hekaarũ yaku, Mwathani Mwene Hinya Wothe, kaĩ nĩ ndĩmĩendeete-ĩ!</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hekaarũ yaku, Mwathani Mwene Hinya Wothe, kaĩ nĩ ndĩmĩendeete-ĩ! 
Nĩndĩrerirĩria mũno gũkorwo ndĩ Hekaarũinĩ ya Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ndĩrainĩra Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ muoyo na ngoro yakwa yothe ngeneete.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Hekaarũ yaku, Mwathani Mwene Hinya Wothe, kaĩ nĩ ndĩmĩendeete-ĩ!</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa maikaraga Hekaarũinĩ yaku, mainaga magĩkũgoocaga hingo ciothe.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ arĩa maheagwo hinya  nĩ we, arĩa makoragwo merirĩirie gũthiĩ gũgũthaathaiya kĩrĩmainĩ gĩa Zayuni.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Hekaarũ yaku, Mwathani Mwene Hinya Wothe, kaĩ nĩ ndĩmĩendeete-ĩ!</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Igua ihooya rĩakwa, Mwathani Ngai Mwene Hinya Wothe; tega matũ, wee Ngai wa Jakubu! </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai, raathima mũthamaki witũ, ũrĩa wee ũitĩrĩirie maguta ũkamwamũra.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Hekaarũ yaku, Mwathani Mwene Hinya Wothe, kaĩ nĩ ndĩmĩendeete-ĩ!</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Gũtinda mũthenya ũmwe hekarũinĩ yaku nĩ kwega gũkĩra gũikara handũ hangĩ o hoothe mĩthenya ngiri.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ kaba ndũũgame kĩhingoinĩ kĩa nyũmba ya Ngai  handũ ha gũtũũra mĩciĩ ya andũ arĩa aaganu.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Hekaarũ yaku, Mwathani Mwene Hinya Wothe, kaĩ nĩ ndĩmĩendeete-ĩ!</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO   "},{Guid:"qZD+MNI1ck63+duQdVLxtQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Zaburi ya Kuitikizana					                
Zab. 96:1 2</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>K: Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwimbieni Mungu, wimbo mpya!
Mwimbieni Mungu, ulimwengu wote!
Mwimbieni Mungu na kulisifu jina lake!</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>K: Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Tangazeni kila siku habari njema kwamba 
Ametuokoa. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Yatangazieni mataifa utukufu wake,na matendo yake makuu kwa watu wote.(K)</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>K: Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mpeni Mungu heshima, enyi jamii zote za watu;sifuni utukufu na enzi yake.
Lisifuni jina tukufu la Mungu!(K) </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>K: Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Leteni sadaka na kuingia Hekaluni
Mwake.  Mwabuduni Mungu anapotokea,
tetemeka mbele yake, ee dunia nzima.(K)</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Yaambieni mataifa: “Mwenyezi ni Mfalme! 
Ameufanya ulimwengu imara, hautatikisika,Atawahukumu watu kwa haki(K)</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>K: Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
