 96
"},{Guid:"T8fUHdZ3MEyGZjPlgXh2wQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA			Zaburi 54:3-4, 5, 6 na 8 (K. tazama 6b)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Mungu, kwa jina lako unisalimishe.Kwa nguvu yako unifanyie haki.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Mungu, usikie sala yangu,
uyasikilize maneno ya kinywa changu. (K)</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa maana wageni wamenishambulia;watu wakatili wanaitafuta nafsi yangu;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>hawakumweka Mungu mbele ya macho yao. (K)</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Tazama, Mungu ananisaidia,
Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa moyo mkunjufu nitakutolea sadaka,
nitalisifu jina lako, ee Bwana, maana ni jema. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
