Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 
(Zab. 89: 2-3, 4-5, 27na29 (K 2a)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Fadhili zako nitaziimba milele, ee Bwana.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Fadhili za Bwana nitaziimba milele, kwa kinywa  changu nitavijulisha vizazi  vyote uaminifu wako.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Maana ulisema: Wema wangu wadumu milele; 
uaminifu wangu umesimikwa katika mbingu (K)</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Fadhili zako nitaziimba milele, ee Bwana</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nimefunga agano na mteule wangu, 
nimemwapia Daudi, mtumishi wangu: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nitawasimika wazao wako hata milele, 
nitaimarisha kiti cha ufalme wako kwa vizazi vyote. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Fadhili zako nitaziimba milele, ee Bwana</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Yeye ataniita, ‘Wewe ni Baba yangu, 
Mungu wangu na mwamba wa wokovu wangu!’</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nitamhifadhia fadhili zangu hata milele,
na agano langu kwake litadumu imara milele. (K)</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Fadhili zako nitaziimba milele, ee Bwana</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF7F00FF"}}},
