Text:"<s1384>Heri mtu yule aliyesamehewa kosa,
aliyesitiriwa dhambi yake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Heri mtu yule ambaye Bwana hamhesabii kosa,wala moyoni mwake hamna hila. (K)</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nilikujulisha dhambi yangu;
wala sikuficha kosa langu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nikasema, \"Nitamwungamia Bwana uovu wangu,\"nawe ukaondoa ubaya wa dhambi yangu. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mfurahieni Bwana, shangilieni, enyi waadilifu;
shangilieni, enyi nyote wanyofu wa moyo. (K)</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
