Text:"CONSOLATA CATHEDRAL"},{Guid:"BIftTgxpkUWdr9VagjfzLg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>I believe in one God, the Father almighty,</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384> maker of heaven and earth, of all things visible and invisible.</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>I believe in one Lord Jesus Christ, the Only Begotten Son of God, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>born of the Father before all ages.  </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>God from God, Light from Light, true God from true God, begotten,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> not made, consubstantial with the Father;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> through him all things were made. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> For us men and for our salvation he came down from heaven,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and by the Holy Spirit was incarnate of the Virgin Mary, and became man.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>For our sake he was crucified under Pontius Pilate,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> he suffered death and was buried,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and rose again on the third day in accordance with the Scriptures.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  He ascended into heaven and is seated at the right hand of the Father.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>He will come again in glory to judge the living and the dead and his kingdom will have no end.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>I believe in the Holy Spirit, the Lord, the giver of life, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>who proceeds from the Father and the Son, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>who with the Father and the Son is adored and glorified,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> who has spoken through the prophets.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>I believe in one, holy, catholic and apostolic Church. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> I confess one baptism for the forgiveness of sins and I look forward to the resurrection of the dead and the life of the world to come.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Amen.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
