Text:"<s1384>7	
1.Ding dong merrily on high,
In heav'n the bells are ringing:</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Ding dong! verily the sky
Is riv'n with angel singing.
	
Gloria, Hosanna in excelsis!</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>2.	E'en so here below, below,
Let steeple bells be swungen,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And \"io, io, io!\"
By priest and people sungen.
Gloria, Hosanna in excelsis!</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>3.Pray you, dutifully prime
Your matin chime, ye ringers;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>May you beautifully rime
Your evetime song, ye singers.
Gloria, Hosanna in excelsis!</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
