Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord to his anointed, to Cyrus, whose right hand I have grasped,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> to subdue nations before him and uncover the loins of kings, to open doors before him that gates may not be closed:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>“For the sake of my servant Jacob, and Israel my chosen, I call you by your name, I surname you, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>though you do not know me.  I am the LORD,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> and there is no other, besides me there is no God;I  clothe you,  though you do not know me, that men may know, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>from the rising of the sun and from the west, that there is none besides me; I am the LORD, and there is no other.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"first reading"},{Guid:"cnA5CcUDiU2xycRiHEAYDQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						            Wisdom 6:12-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Wisdom</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Wisdom is radiant and unfading, and she is easily discerned by those who love her, and is found by those who seek her. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>She hastens to make herself known to those who desire her.  He who rises early to seek her will have no difficulty, for he will find her sitting at his gates. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> To fix one’s thought on her is perfect understanding, and he who is vigilant on her account will soon be free from care, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>because she goes about seeking those worthy of her, and she graciously appears to them in their paths,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and meets them in every thought.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"++hRsRz9b06UmGKtNK9SVQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		        Acts. 10:25-26,34-35,44-48</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>When Peter entered, Cornelius met him and fell down at his feet and worshipped him. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> But Peter lifted him up, saying, “Stand up; I too am a man. “</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And Peter opened his mouth and said: “Truly I perceive that God shows no partiality,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> but in every nation any one who fears him and does what is right is acceptable to him.”</s>"},{ID:6},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>While Peter was still speaking, the Holy Spirit fell on all who heard the word. 
 
And the believers from among the circumcised who came with Peter were amazed,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> because the gift of the Holy Spirit had been poured out even on the Gentiles. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> For they heard them speaking in tongues and extolling God.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Then Peter declared, “Can any one forbid water for baptizing </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>these people who have received the Holy Spirit just as we have?”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>And he commanded them to be baptized in the name of Jesus Christ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Then they asked him to remain for some days.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"w09wtTL6wU+slNnjO8a6Nw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                       Isaiah 40:1-5,9-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Comfort, comfort my people, says your God.  Speak tenderly to Jerusalem, and cry to her that her warfare is ended,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> that her iniquity is pardoned, that she has received from the Lord’s hand double for all her sins. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>A voice cries:  “In the wilderness prepare the way of the Lord, make straight in the desert a highway for our God. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Every valley shall be lifted up, and every mountain and hill be made low; the uneven ground  shall become level,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and the rough places a plain.  And the glory of the Lord shall be revealed, and all flesh shall see it together, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>for the mouth of the Lord has spoken.” Get you up to a high mountain, O Zion, herald of good tidings; lift up your voice with strength, O Jerusalem, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>herald of good tidings, lift it up, fear not; say to the cities of Judah, “Behold your God!” Behold, the Lord God comes with might, and his arm rules for him;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> behold, his reward is with him, and his recompense before him. He will feed his flock like a shepherd, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>he will gather the lambs in his arms, he will carry them in his bosom, and gently lead those that are with young.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"P+faL7FxtUmQqs8odLhsgQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						    Isaiah 63:16d-17;64:1,3b-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>You, O Lord, are our Father, our Redeemer from old is your name.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>O Lord, why do you make us err from your ways and harden our heart, so that we do not fear you?
Return for the sake of your servants,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> the tribes of your heritage.
O that you would tear the heavens and come down, that the mountains might quake at your presence!</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>You came down, the mountains quaked at your presence. From of old no one has heard or perceived by the ear, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>no eye has seen a God besides you, who works for those who wait for him.  You meet him that joyfully works righteousness,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> those that remember you in your ways. Behold, you were angry, and we sinned; in our sins we have been a long time, and shall we be saved?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> We have all become like one who is unclean, and all our righteous deeds are like a polluted garment.  We all fade like a leaf,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> and our iniquities, like the wind, take us away. There is no one that calls upon your name, that bestirs himself to take hold of you;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> for you have hidden your face from us, and have delivered us into the hand of our iniquities.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Yet, O Lord, you are our Father; we are the clay, and you are our potter; we are all the work of your hand.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"3o6iNslUH0i+1yGd3YULfQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						
A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>On this mountain the Lord of hosts will make for all peoples a feast of fat things,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> a feast of choice wines-of fat things full of marrow, of choice wines well refined.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And he will destroy on this mountain the covering that is cast over all peoples, the veil that is spread over all nations.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> He will swallow up death for ever, and the Lord God will wipe away tears from all faces, and the reproach of his people he will take away from all the earth, for the Lord has spoken.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>It will be said on that day, “Behold, this is our God; we have waited for him, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>that he might save us.  This is the Lord; we have waited for him; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>let us be glad and rejoice in his salvation.” For the hand of the Lord will rest on this mountain.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"JjD9zGNfmkWJtxPh4+ecIQ",Verses:[],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"h4j2tz80yEiQN4PQs8SR/w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						              Job 7:1-4, 6-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Job</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Job spoke, saying: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>“Has not man a hard service upon earth, and are not his days like the days of a hireling? </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Like a slave who longs for the  shadow, and like a hireling who looks for his wages,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> so I am allotted months of emptiness, and nights of misery are apportioned to me.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>When I lie down I say, ‘When shall I arise?’
But the night is long, and I am full of tossing till the dawn.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>“My days are swifter than a weaver’s shuttle, and come to their end without hope. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> “Remember that my life is a breath; my eye will never again see good.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"0NsQDs0RIESQAcLUce6Xmg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Nehemiah 8:2-4a,5-6,8-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Nehemiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Ezra the priest brought the law before the assembly, both men and women and all who could hear with understanding, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>on the first day of the seventh month.  And he read from it facing the square before the Water Gate from early morning until midday, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>in the presence of the men and the women and those who could understand;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> and the ears of all the people were attentive to the book of the law.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> And Ezra the scribe stood on a wooden pulpit which they had made for the purpose.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> And Ezra opened the book in the sight of all the people, for he was above all the people;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and when he opened it all the people stood. And Ezra blessed the Lord, the great God; and all the people answered,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> “Amen, Amen,” lifting up their hands; and they bowed their heads and worshipped the Lord with their faces to the ground.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>And Ezra and the Levites read from the book, from the law of God, clearly; and they gave the sense, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>so that the people understood the reading. And Nehemiah, who was the governor, and Ezra the priest and scribe, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>and the Levites who taught the people said to all the people, “This day is holy to the Lord your God; do not mourn or weep.”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>For all the people wept when they heard the words of the law. Then he said to them, “Go your way,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> eat the fat and drink sweet wine and send portions to him for whom nothing is prepared; for this day is holy to our Lord; </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>and do not be grieved, for the joy of the Lord is your strength.”</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"Fw1ocl8WQE+bpCMxHW1xrg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                               1Kings 17:10-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Kings                                  </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Elijah (the prophet) arose and went to Zarephath; and when he came to the gate of the city, behold, a widow was there gathering sticks;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and he called to her and said, “Bring me a little water in a vessel, that I may drink.”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And as she was going to bring it, he called to her and said, “Bring me a morsel of bread in your hand.”
And she said “As the Lord your God lives,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> I have nothing baked, only a handful of meal in a jar, and a little oil in a pitcher; and now, I am gathering a couple of sticks, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>that I may go in and prepare it for myself and my son, that we may eat it, and die.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>And Elijah said to her, “Fear not; go and do as you have said; but first make me a little cake of it and bring it to me, and afterward make for yourself and your son. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>For thus says the Lord the God of Israel, ‘The jar of meal shall not be spent, and the pitcher of oil shall not fail, until the day that the Lord sends rain upon the earth.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>’
And she went and did as Elijah said; and she, and he, and her household ate for many days.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>The jar of meal was not spent, neither did the pitcher of oil fail, according to the word of the Lord which he spoke by Elijah.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"PQv+xp3nHU2Y4tlSOqJK/A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                Exodus 20:1-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Exodus</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>God spoke all these words, saying,
“I am the Lord your God, who brought you out of the land of Egypt, out of the house of bondage.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>“You shall have no other gods before me.  You shall not make for yourself a graven image, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>or any likeness of anything that is in heaven above, or that is in the earth beneath, or that is in the water under the earth; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>you shall not bow down to them or serve them; for I the Lord your God am a jealous God, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>visiting the iniquity of the fathers upon the children to the third and the fourth generation of those who hate me, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>but showing mercy to thousands of those who love me and keep my commandments.
“You shall not take the name of the Lord your God in vain; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>for the Lord will not hold him guiltless who takes his name in vain.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>“Remember the Sabbath day, to keep it holy.  Six days you shall labour, and do all your work; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>but the seventh day is a Sabbath to the Lord your God; in it you shall not do any work, you, or your son, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>or your daughter, your manservant, or your maidservant, or your cattle, or the sojourner who is within your gates; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>for in six days the Lord made heaven and earth, the sea, and all that is in them, and rested the seventh day; </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>therefore the Lord blessed the Sabbath day and hallowed it.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>“Honour your father and your mother, that your days may be long in the land which the Lord your God gives you.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> “You shall not kill. “You shall not commit adultery. “You shall not steal.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>  “You shall not bear false witness against your neighbor. </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>“You shall not covet your neighbor’s house; you shall not covet your neighbour’s wife,</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384> or his manservant, or his maidservant, or his ox, or his donkey, or anything that is your neighbour’s.”</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"EdoSxYpIqEq2G/m89DP8uw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Genesis</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						   Genesis 22:1-2.9a.10-13,15-18</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
God tested Abraham, and said to him, “Abraham!” and he said, “Here am I.” </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>He said, “Take your son, your only-begotten son Isaac, whom you love, and go to the land of Moriah,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and offer him there as a burnt offering upon one of the mountains of which I shall tell you”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>When they came to the place of which God had told him, Abraham built an altar there, and laid the wood in order.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Then Abraham put forth his hand, and took the knife to slay his son. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>But the angel of the Lord called to him from heaven, and said, “Abraham, Abraham!”
And he said, “Here am I.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>He said, “Do not lay your hand on the lad or do anything to him; for now I know that you fear God, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>seeing you have not withheld your son, your only-begotten son, from me.”</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>And Abraham lifted up his eyes and looked, and behold, behind him was a ram, caught in a thicket by his horns; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>and Abraham went and took the ram, and offered it up as a burnt offering instead of his son.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>And the angel of the Lord called to Abraham a second time from heaven, and said, “By myself I have sworn, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>says the Lord, because you have done this, and have not withheld your son, your only-begotten son, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>I will indeed bless you, and I will multiply your descendants as the stars of heaven and as the sand which is on the seashore.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>And your descendants shall possess the gate of their enemies, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>and by your descendants shall all the nations of the earth bless themselves, because you have obeyed my voice.”</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"kW7knL4sQk6D8Jateb+7Cg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>First Reading						                         Isaiah 55:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Thus says the Lord: “Ho, every one who thirsts, come to the waters; and he who has no money,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>  come, buy and eat! 
Come, buy wine and milk without money and without price. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> Why do you spend your money for that which is not bread, and your labour for that which does not satisfy? </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Listen diligently to me, and eat what is good, and delight yourselves in rich food.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>  Incline your ear, and come to me; hear, that your soul may live;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>and I will make with you an everlasting covenant, my steadfast, merciful love for David.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> Behold, I made him a witness to the peoples, a leader and commander for the peoples. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> 
Behold, you shall call nations that you know not, and nations that knew you not shall run to you,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> because of the Lord your God, and of the Holy One of Israel, for he has glorified you.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>“Seek the Lord while he may be found, call upon him while he is near; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>let the wicked forsake his way, and the unrighteous man his thoughts;</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> let him return to the Lord, that he may have mercy on him, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>and to our God, for he will abundantly pardon.  For my thoughts are not your thoughts,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> neither are your ways my ways, says the Lord.
For as the heavens are higher than the earth, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>so are my ways higher than your ways and my thoughts than your thoughts.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>“For as the rain and the snow come down from heaven, </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>and do not return there but water the earth, making it bring forth and sprout,</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> giving seed to the sower and bread to the eater, </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>so shall my word be that goes forth from my mouth; </s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>it shall not return to me empty, but it shall accomplish that which I intend, and prosper in the thing for which I sent it.”</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"Y/cqQemQYEaNRhclLpyaiQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                   Isaiah 61:1-2a,10-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Spirit of the Lord God is upon me, because the Lord has anointed me to bring good tidings to the afflicted; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>he has sent me to bind up the brokenhearted, to proclaim liberty to the captives, and the opening of the prison to those who are bound;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> to proclaim the year of the Lord’s favour.
I will greatly rejoice in the Lord, my soul shall exult in my God;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> for he has clothed me with the garments of salvation, he has covered me with the robe of righteousness,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> as a bridegroom decks himself with a garland, and as a bride adorns herself with her jewels.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> For as the earth brings forth its shoots, and as a garden causes what is sown in it to spring up, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> so the Lord God will cause righteousness and praise to spring forth before all the nations.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"TXo/WS7rd0ak7s5CeHeNNg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						  Proverbs 31:10-13,19-20,30-31</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Proverbs </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Who can find a good wife?
She is far more precious than jewels.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>The heart of her husband trusts in her, and he will have no lack of gain.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  She does him good, and not harm, all the days of her life.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> She seeks wool and flax, and works with willing hands.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  
She puts her hands to the distaff, and her hands hold the spindle. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> She opens her hand to the poor,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and reaches out her hands to the needy.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Charm is deceitful, and beauty is vain,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> but a woman who fears the Lord is to be praised.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Give her of the fruit of her hands, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and let her works praise her in the gates.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"Pe9sEyYN9kelLRkx2m+87Q",Verses:[{
Text:"First Reading						                       Isaiah 45:1,4-6"},{ID:2,
Text:"A reading from the Book of Isaiah"},{ID:3,
Text:"Thus says the Lord to his anointed, to Cyrus, whose right had I have grasped, to subdue nations before him and uncover the loins of kings, "},{ID:4,
Text:"to open doors before him that gates may not be closed:"},{ID:5,
Text:"“For the sake of my servant Jacob, and Israel my chosen, I call you by your name, I surname you, though you do not know me."},{ID:6,
Text:"  I am the LORD, and there is no other, besides me there is no God; "},{ID:7,
Text:"O clothe you,  though you do not know me, that men may know, from the rising of the sun and from the west, that there is none besides me; "},{ID:8,
Text:"I am the LORD, and there is no other."},{ID:9,
Text:"Word of the Lord"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"Z93g3RBvwEeEMEQXoFg6rw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		               Acts. 5:27b-32,40b-41</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
The high priest questioned the apostles, saying, “We strictly charged you not to teach in this name,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> yet here you have filled Jerusalem with your teaching and you intend to bring this man’s blood upon us.”</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> But Peter and the apostles answered, “We must obey God rather than men. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> The God of our fathers raised Jesus whom you killed by hanging him on a tree.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  God exalted him at his right hand as Leader and Saviour, to give repentance to Israel and forgiveness of sins. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And we are witnesses to these things, and so is the Holy Spirit whom God has given to those who obey him.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> And they charged the apostles not to speak in the name of Jesus, and let them go. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Then they left the presence of the council, rejoicing that they were counted worthy to suffer dishonor for the name.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"VoAHP1LLT0WSNQyoyZiJKA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>First Reading						             Malachi 1:14b-2:2b,8-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Malachi</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>“I am a great King, says the Lord of hosts, and my name is feared among the nations.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846>“And now, O priests, this command is for you. If you will not listen, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846>if you will not lay it to heart to give glory to my name, says the Lord of hosts, then I will send the curse upon you.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846>“You have turned aside from the way; you have caused man to stumble by your instruction;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846> you have corrupted the covenant of Levi, says the LORD of hosts, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846>and so I make you despised and abased before all the people,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1846> inasmuch as you have not kept my ways but have shown partiality in your instruction.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1846>Have we not all one father?
Has not one God created us?</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1846>Why then are we faithless to one another, profaning the covenant of our fathers?</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1846>Word of the Lord</s>"}],
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"lrPiD45sI0Km4PIJ/UVX2A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		               Acts. 5:12-16</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Many signs and wonders were done among the people by the hands of the apostles.
And they were all together in Solomon’s Portico.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>None of the rest dared join them, but the people held them in high honour. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> And more than ever believers were added to the Lord, multitudes both of men and women,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> so that they even carried out the sick into the streets, and laid them on beds and pallets,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> that as Peter came by at least his shadow might fall on some of them. The people also gathered from the towns around Jerusalem,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> bringing the sick and those afflicted with unclean spirits, and they were all healed.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"Qtw+i4GuNEmAdOfgUM6IcQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                   Ezek. 34:11-12,15-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Ezekiel</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>“Thus says the Lord God: 
Behold, I, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>I myself will search for my sheep, and will seek them out. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> As a shepherd seeks out his flock when some of his sheep</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> have been scattered abroad, so will I seek out my sheep;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and I will rescue them from all places where they have</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> been scattered on a day of clouds and thick darkness.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“I myself will be the shepherd of my sheep, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and I will make them lie down, says the Lord God.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  I will seek the lost, and I will bring back the strayed, and I will bind up the crippled,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and I will strengthen the weak, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and the fat and the strong I will watch over; I will feed them in justice.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>“As for you, my flock, thus says the Lord God: Behold, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>I judge between sheep and sheep, rams and he-goats.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"rdwo1MV3uUSz5LOyS8DQBQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		               Acts. 13:14, 43-52</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
Paul and Barnabas passed on from Perga and came to Antioch of Pisidia.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  And on the Sabbath day they went into the synagogue and sat down. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And many Jews and devout converts to Judaism followed Paul and Barnabas, who spoke to them and urged them to continue in the grace of God.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>The next Sabbath almost the whole city gathered together to hear the word of God.  But when the Jews saw the multitudes,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> they were filled with jealousy, and contradicted what was spoken by Paul, and reviled him.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>And Paul and Barnabas spoke out boldly, saying, “It was necessary that the word of God should be spoken first to you. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Since you thrust it from you, and judge yourselves unworthy of eternal life, behold, we turn to the Gentiles. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> For so the Lord has commanded us, saying, ‘I have set you to be a light for the Gentiles, that you may bring salvation to the uttermost parts of the earth.’”</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>And when the Gentiles heard this, they were glad and glorified the word of God; and as many as were ordained to eternal life believed. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> And the word of the Lord spread throughout all the region.  But the Jews incited the devout women of high standing and the leading men of the city, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>and stirred up persecution against Paul and Barnabas, and drove them out of their district.  But they shook off the dust from their feet against them, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>and went to Iconium.  And the disciples were filled with joy and with the Holy Spirit.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"9O5NuN6va0aJgQcMOsrDvA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                         Sirach 3:2-6,12-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Sirach </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord honoured the father above the children, and he confirmed the right of the mother over her sons. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Whoever honours  his father  atones for sins, and preserves himself from them. When he prays, he is heard; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>and whoever glorifies his mother is like one who lays up treasure.
Whoever honours his father will be gladdened by his own children, and when he prays he will be heard.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Whoever glorifies his father will have long life, and whoever obeys the Lord will refresh his mother.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>O son, help your father in his old age, and do not grieve him as long as he lives; even if he is lacking in understanding,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> show forbearance; and do not despise him all the days of his life. For kindness to a father will not be forgotten, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and against your sins it will be credited to you – a house raised in justice to you.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Copyright:"SECOND SUNDAY OF ADVENT
",Guid:"eFUOHHFhuUObh5QEDr0p+Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                        Isaiah 40:1-5,9-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Comfort, comfort my people, says your God.  Speak tenderly to Jerusalem, and cry to her that her warfare is ended,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> that her iniquity is pardoned, that she has received from the Lord’s hand double for all her sins. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>A voice cries: 
“In the wilderness prepare the way of the Lord, make straight in the desert a highway for our God. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Every valley shall be lifted up, and every mountain and hill be made low; the uneven ground shall become level,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and the rough places a plain.  And the glory of the Lord shall be revealed, and all flesh shall see it together, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>for the mouth of the Lord has spoken.”
Get you up to a high mountain, O Zion, herald of good tidings;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> lift up your voice with strength, O Jerusalem, herald of good tidings, lift it up, fear not;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> say to the cities of Judah, “Behold you God!”
Behold, the Lord God comes with might, and his arm rules for him;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> behold, his reward is with him; behold, his reward is with him, and his recompense before him.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> He will feed his flock like a shepherd, he will gather the lambs in his arms, he will carry them in his bosom, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>and gently lead those that are with young.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"gA81ECE7s0qSa/ggMeBAPQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                Genesis 9:8-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Genesis</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>God said to Noah and to his sons with him, “Behold, I establish my covenant with you and your descendants after you,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and with every living creature that is with you, the birds, the cattle, and every beast of the earth with you,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> as many as came out of the ark. I establish my covenant with you, that never again shall all flesh be cut off by the waters of a flood, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>and never again shall there be a flood to destroy the earth.” And God said, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“This is the sign of the covenant which I make between me and you and every living creature that is with you,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> for all future generations: I set my bow in the cloud, and it shall be a sign of the covenant between me and the earth.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> When I bring clouds over the earth and the bow is seen in the clouds, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>I will remember my covenant which is between me and you and every living creature of all flesh; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>and the waters shall never again become a flood to destroy all flesh.”</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"w9Xqx+jAyUGe+sXIdrxrIQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Kings                                             1Kings 19:4-8</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
Elijah went a day’s journey into the wilderness, and came and sat down under a broom tree;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and he asked that he might die, saying, “It is enough; now, O Lord, take away my life; for I am no better than my fathers.”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And he lay down and slept under a broom tree; and behold, an angel touched him, and said to him, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“Arise and eat.” And he looked and behold, there was at his head a cake baked on hot stones and a jar of water. 
 </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And he ate and drank, and lay down again. And the angel of the Lord came again a second time, and touched him, and said, “Arise and eat,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> else the journey will be too great for you.” And he arose, and ate and drank, and walked in the strength of that food forty days and forty nights to Horeb the mount of God.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"RaPfNGH88k+b+Av2QUe18w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THE ASCENSION  OF THE LORD</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>First Reading								Acts 1:1-11</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The beginning of the Acts of the Apostles</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>In the first book, O Theophilus, I have dealt with all that Jesus began to do and  teach, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>until the day when he was taken up, after he had given commandment through the Holy Spirit to the apostles whom he had chosen. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> To them he presented himself alive after his passion by many proofs, appearing to them during forty days, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and speaking of the kingdom of God.  And while staying with them he charged them not to depart from Jerusalem,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> but to wait for the promise of the Father, which, he said, “you heard from me, for John baptized with water,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> but before many days you shall be baptized with the Holy Spirit.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>So when they had come together, they asked him, “Lord, will you at this time restore the kingdom to Israel?”</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>He said to them, “It is not for you to know times or seasons which the Father has fixed by his own authority. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> But you shall receive power when the Holy Spirit has come upon you;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> and you shall be my witnesses in Jerusalem and in all Judea and Samaria and to the end of the earth.”</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>And when he had said this, as they were looking on, he was lifted up, and a cloud took him out of their sight.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>  And while they were gazing into heaven as he went, behold, two men stood by them in white robes, and said, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>“Men of Galilee, why do you stand looking into heaven? This Jesus, who was taken up from you into heaven, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>will come in the same way as you saw him go into heaven.”</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"fQz8tZ8/mE2a0R1fKj4ZFQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Genesis 2:18-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Genesis                                    </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord God said,
“It is not good that the man should be alone; I will make him a helper fit for him.”</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>So out of the ground the Lord God formed every beast of the field and every  beast of the field and every bird of the air,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and brought them to the man to see what he would call them; and whatever the man called every living creature, that was its name.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>The man gave names to all cattle, and to the birds of the air, and to every beast of the field; but for the man there was not found a helper fit for him.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> So the Lord God caused a deep sleep to fall upon the man, and while he slept took one of his ribs and closed up its place with flesh;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and the rib which the Lord God had taken from the man he made into a woman and brought her to the man.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Then the man said, “This at last is bone of my bones and flesh of my flesh; she shall be called Woman, because she was taken out of Man.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Therefore a man leaves his father and his mother and clings to his wife, and they become one flesh.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"ZyZUeYeiXECSRUqI7XWvNQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						   Isaiah 50:4-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord God has given me the tongue of those who are taught,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> that I may know how to sustain with a word him that is weary. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Morning by morning he wakens, he wakens my ear to hear as those who are taught. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> The Lord God has opened my ear, and I was not rebellious, I turned not backward.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  I gave my back to those who struck me, and my cheeks to those who pulled out the beard; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>I hid not my face from shame and spitting.
For the Lord God helps me;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> therefore I have not been confounded; therefore I have set my face like a flint,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> and I know that I shall not be put to shame.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"QAnRFE0uHUasnfUJ0r/q9Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                         Isaiah 60:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Arise, shine; for your light has come, and the glory of the Lord has risen upon you. For behold, darkness shall cover the earth, and thick darkness the peoples;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> but the Lord will arise upon you, and his glory will be seen upon you.  And nations shall walk by your light,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and kings in the brightness of your rising. Lift up your eyes round about, and see; they all gather together,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> they come to you; your sons shall come from far, and your daughters shall be carried in the arms. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Then you shall see and be radiant, your heart shall thrill and rejoice; because the abundance of the sea shall be turned to you. the wealth of the nations shall come to you </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>A multitude of camels shall cover you, the young camels of Midian and Ephah; all those from Sheba shall come. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> They shall bring gold and frankincense, and shall proclaim the praise of the Lord.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"r1KqGcUZJkyqUy742D+ApQ",Verses:[{},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						      2 Samuel 7:1-5,8b-12,14a,16</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the second Book of Samuel</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>When King David dwelt in his house, and the Lord had given him rest from all his enemies round about,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> the king said to Nathan the prophet, “See now, I dwell in a house of cedar, but the ark of God dwells in a tent.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And Nathan said to the king, “Go, do all that is in your heart; for the Lord is with you.”</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>But that same night the word of the Lord came to Nathan, “Go and tell my servant David, ‘Thus says the Lord: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Would you build me a house to dwell in? I took you from the pasture, from following the sheep, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>that you should be prince over my people Israel; and I have been with you wherever you went, and have cut off all your enemies from before you;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> and I will make for you a great name, like the name of the great ones of the earth. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>And I will appoint a place for my people Israel,  and will plant them, that they may dwell in their own place, and be disturbed no more; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>and violent men shall afflict them no more, as formerly, from the time that I appointed judges over my people Israel;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> and I will give you rest from all your enemies.  Moreover the Lord declares to you that the Lord will make you a house.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>  When your days are fulfilled and you lie down with your fathers, I will raise up your offspring after you, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>who shall come forth from your body, and I will establish his kingdom.  I will be his father, and he shall be my son.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>“ ‘And your house and your kingdom shall be made sure for ever before me; your throne shall be established for ever.’”</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"rEG+ZPx3TUqqW7o8ckK9dA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						 2nd Chronicles 36:14-16,19-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Chronicles</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>All the leading priests and the people were exceedingly unfaithful,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> following all the abomination of the nations; and they polluted the house of the Lord which he had hallowed in Jerusalem.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord, the God of their fathers, sent persistently to them by his messengers,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> because he had compassion on his people and on his dwelling place; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>but they kept mocking the messengers of God, despising his words, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and scoffing at his prophets, till the wrath of the Lord rose against his people, till there was no remedy.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And the Chaldeans burned the house of God, and broke down the wall of Jerusalem,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and burned all its palaces with fire, and destroyed all its precious vessels. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> The king of the Chaldeans took into exile in Babylon those who had escaped from the sword,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> and they became servants to him and to his sons until the establishment of the kingdom of Persia,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> to fulfil the word of the Lord by the mouth of Jeremiah, until the land had enjoyed its Sabbaths. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> All the days that it lay desolate it kept Sabbath, to fulfil seventy years.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Now in the first year of Cyrus king of Persia,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> that the word of the Lord by the mouth of Jeremiah might be accomplished, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>the Lord stirred up the spirit of Cyrus king of Persia so that he made a proclamation throughout all </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>his kingdom and also put it in writing: 
“Thus says Cyrus king of Persia, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>‘ The Lord, the God of heaven, has given me all the kingdoms of the earth,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> and he has charged me to build him a house at Jerusalem, which is in Judah.  </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Whoever is among you of all his people, may the Lord his God be with him.  Let him go up”’</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"UKwMpB2STEi9gF/R89BJrQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading					         Deuteronomy 4:32-34,39-40</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Deuteronomy</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Moses spoke to the people, saying, “Ask now of the days that are past, which were before you, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>since the day that God created man upon the earth, and ask from one end of heaven to the other,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> whether such a great thing as this has ever happened or was ever heard of.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Did any people ever hear the voice of God speaking out of the midst of the fire, as you have heard, and still live?</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Or has God ever attempted to go and take a nation for himself from the midst of another nation, by trials, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>by signs, by wonders, and by war, by a mighty hand and an outstretched arm, and by great terrors,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> according to all that the Lord your God did for you in Egypt before your eyes?
“Know therefore this day,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> and lay it to your heart, that the Lord is God in heaven above and on the earth beneath; there is no other.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Therefore you shall keep his statutes and his commandments, which I command you this day, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>that it may go well with you, and with your children after you and that you may prolong your days in the land which the Lord your God gives you for ever.”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"Cmrh2U7mOU+ukSV4LZ/VcA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						         Jeremiah 31:31-34</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>“Behold, the days are coming, says the Lord, when I will make a new covenant with the house of Israel and the house of Judah,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> not like the covenant which I made with their fathers when I took them by the hand to bring them out of the land of Egypt,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> my covenant which they broke, and I showed myself their Master, says the Lord.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  
But this is the covenant which I will make with the house of Israel after those days, says the Lord:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> 
I will put my law within them, and I will write it upon their hearts: and I will be their God, and they shall be my people.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And no longer shall each man teach his neighbor and each his brother, saying, ‘Know the Lord,’</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> for they shall all know me, from the least of them to the greatest, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>says the Lord; for I will forgive their iniquity,
 and I will remember their sin no more.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"nhr1TY+pgkeRgBdq6vK4PQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading								Acts 2:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>When the day of Pentecost had come, they were all together in one place. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> And suddenly a sound came from heaven like the rush of a mighty wind, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>and it filled all the house where they were sitting.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  And there appeared to them tongues as of fire, distributed and resting on each one of them. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> And they were all filled with the Holy Spirit and began to speak in other tongues, as the Spirit gave them utterance.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Now there were dwelling in Jerusalem Jews, devout men from every nation under heaven.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  And at this sound the multitude came together, and they were bewildered, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>because each one heard them speaking in his own language.  And they were amazed and wondered, saying, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>“Are not all these who are speaking Galileans? And how is it that we hear, each of us in his own native language?</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Parthians and Medes and Elamites and residents of Mesopotamia, Judea and Cappadocia, Pontus and Asia,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Phrygia and Pamphylia, Egypt and the parts of Libya belonging to Cyrene, and visitors from Rome, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>both Jews and proselytes, Cretans and Arabians, we hear them telling in our own tongues the mighty works of God.”</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"wRSJ0M/DKkSvrOivbMwO8Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                Leviticus 13:1-2,44-46</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Leviticus</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord said to Moses and Aaron, “When a man has on the skin of his body a swelling or an eruption or a spot,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and it turns into a leprous disease on the skin of his body,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> then he shall be brought to Aaron the priest or to one of his sons the priests.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“He is a leprous man, he is unclean; the priest must pronounce him unclean; his disease is on his head.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“The leper who has the disease shall wear torn clothes and let the hair of his head hang loose,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and he shall cover his upper lip and cry, ‘Unclean, unclean.’ </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>He shall remain unclean as long as he has  the disease; he is unclean; he shall dwell alone in a habitation outside the camp.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"ca+OLzB550e4b+DWLinrgw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						              Deuteronomy 18:15-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Deuteronomy</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>“Moses spoke to the people, saying,
“The Lord your God will raise up for you a prophet like me from among you,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> from your brethren – him you shall heed – just as you desired of the Lord your God at Horeb on the day of the assembly, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>when you said, ‘Let me not hear again the voice of the Lord my God, or see this great fire any more, lest I die.’</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“And the Lord said to me, ‘They have rightly said all that they have spoken.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>I will raise up for them a prophet like you from among their brethren; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>and I will put my words in his mouth, and he shall speak to them all that I command him.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> And whoever will not give heed to my words which he shall speak in my name, I myself will require it of him.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>But the prophet who presumes to speak a word in my name which I have not commanded him to speak, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>or who speaks in the name of other gods, that same prophet shall die.”’</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"TKkwfWMMhU+ArmSCut2BlA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                           Joshua  5: 9,10-12
A reading from the Book of Joshua                               </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
The Lord said to Joshua, “This day I have rolled away the reproach of Egypt from you.” </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>While the sons of Israel were encamped in Gilgal they kept the Passover on the fourteenth day of the month at evening in the plains of Jericho. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And on the next day after the Passover, on that very day, they ate of the produce of the land, unleavened cakes and parched grain. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And the manna ceased on the next day, when they ate of the produce of the land; and the sons of Israel had manna no more, but ate of the fruit of the land of Canaan that year.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"58n8S/6XaEqR3SQL64wIwg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Numbers 11:25-29</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Numbers                                    </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord came down in the cloud and spoke to Moses, and took some of the spirit that was upon him and put it upon the seventy elders; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>and when the spirit rested upon them, they prophesied. But they did so no more.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Now two men remained in the camp, one named Eldad, and the other named Medad, and the spirit rested upon them;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> they were among those registered, but they had not gone out to the tent, and so they prophesied in the camp.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>And a young man ran and told Moses, “Eldad and Medad are prophesying in the camp.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>And Joshua the son of Nun, the minister of Moses, one of his chosen men, said “My lord Moses, forbid them.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>But Moses said to him, “Are you jealous for my sake? Would that all the Lord’s people were prophets, that the Lord would put his spirit upon them!”</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"ezoFJAkkoE6LMXxbWEPsmQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                           Deuteronomy 26:4-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Deuteronomy                                </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Moses said to the people, “The priest shall take the basket of first fruits[of first fruits] from your hand, and set it down before the altar of the Lord your God.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And you shall make response before the Lord your God, ‘A wandering  Aramean was my father;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and he went down into Egypt and sojourned there, few in number; and there he became a nation, great, mighty, and populous.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And the Egyptians treated us harshly, and afflicted us, and laid upon us hard bondage.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Then we cried to the Lord the God of our fathers, and the Lord heard our voice, and saw our affliction, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>our toil, and our oppression; and the Lord brought us out of Egypt with a mighty hand and an outstreached arm, with great terror,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> with signs and wonders; and he brought us into this place and gave us this land, a land flowing with milk and honey. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> And behold, now I bring the first of the fruit of the ground, wich you, O Lord, have given me.’ </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>And you shall set it down before the Lord your God, and worship before the Lord your God.”</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"2Pc+5IKO4kaLq9MyLczZTw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THE HOLY FAMILY OF JESUS, MARY, AND JOSEPH</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                         1 Samuel 1:20-22.24-28</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Samuel </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And in due time Hannah conceived and bore a son, and she called his name Samuel, for she said, “I have asked him of the LORD.”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  And the man Elkanah and all his house went up to offer to the Lord the yearly sacrifice, and to pay his vow.  But Hannah did not go up,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> for she  said to her husband, “ As soon as the child  is weaned, I will bring him, that he may appear in the presence of the Lord, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and abide there for ever.” And when she had weaned him, she took him up with her, along with a three-year-old bull,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> an ephah of flour, and a skin of wine; and she brought him to the house of the Lord at Shiloh; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and the child was young. Then they slew the bull, and they brought the child  to Eli.  And she said,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> “Oh, my lord!  As you live, my lord.  I am the woman who was standing here in your presence, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>praying to the Lord.  For this child I prayed; and the Lord has granted me my petition which I made to him.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Therefore I have lent him to the Lord; as long as he lives, he is lent to the Lord.”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"ZNoAuoUgBkmvB4iszZvc+Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                           Exodus 3:1-8a,13-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Exodus                               </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Moses was keeping the flock of his father-in-law,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Jethro, the priest of Midian; and he led his flock to the west side of the wilderness,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and came to Horeb, the mountain of God.
And the angel of the Lord appeared to him in a flame of fire out of the midist of a bush;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and he looked, and behold, the bush was burning, yet it was not consumed.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And Moses said, “I will turn aside and see this great sight, why the bush is not burnt.” 
When the Lord saw that he turned aside to see, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>God called to him out of the bush, “Moses, Moses! “ And he said, “Here am I.” Then he said, “Do not come near; put off your shoes from your feet,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> for the place on which you are standing is holy ground.”
And he said, “I am the God of your father, the God of Abraham, the God of Isaac, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and the God of Jacob.” And Moses hid his face, for he was afraid to look at God. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Then the Lord said, “I have seen the affliction of my people who are in Egypt, and have heard their cry  because of their taskmasters; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>I know their sufferings, and I have come down to deliver them out of the hand of the Egyptians,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  and to bring them up out of that land to a good and broad land, a land flowing with milk and honey.”
Then Moses said to God, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>“If I come to the sons of Israel and say to them, ‘The God of your fathers has sent me to you,’ and they ask me, ‘What is his name? </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>What shall I say to them? God said to Moses, “I AM WHO I AM.” And he said, “Say this to the sons of Israel, I AM has sent me to you.’”</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> God also said to Moses, Say this to the sons of Israel,  The Lord, the God of your fathers, the God of Abraham, the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> has sent me to you’: this is my name for ever, and thus I am to be remembered throughout all generations.” </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"iYISkNsjlEyZ6DPnwyd3BQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                           Isaiah 43:16-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah                               </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord, who makes a way in the sea, a path in the mighty waters, who brings forth chariot and horse,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> army and warrior; they lie down, they cannot rise, they are extinguished, quenched like a wick: “Remember not the former things,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nor consider the things of old.
Behold, I am doing a new thing; now it springs forth, do you not perceive it? </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>I will make a way in the wilderness and rivers in the desert. The wild beasts will honour me, the jackals and the ostriches; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>for I give water in the wilderness, rivers in the desert, to give drink to my chosen people, the people whom I formed for myself that they might declare my praise.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"20qjZ2gkdEqwxPlf8/Gvrg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                      1 Sam. 3:3b-10,19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the first Book of Samuel </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Samuel was lying down within the temple of the Lord, where the ark of God was.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Then the Lord called, “Samuel! Samuel!” and he said, “Here I am!”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and ran to Eli, and said, “Here I am, for you called me.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>But he said, “I did not call; lie down again.” 
So he went and lay down.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  And the Lord called again, “Samuel!” 
And Samuel arose and went to Eli, and said, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>“Here I am, for you called me!” But he said, “I did not call, my son; lie down again.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Now Samuel did not yet know the Lord, and the word of the Lord had not yet been revealed to him.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  And the Lord called Samuel again the third time.  And he arose and went to Eli,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> and said, “Here I am, for you called me.”
Then Eli perceived that the Lord was calling the boy. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Therefore Eli said to Samuel, “Go, lie down; and if he calls you, you shall say, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>‘Speak, Lord, for your servant hears.’” So Samuel went and lay down in his place.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>And the Lord came and stood forth, calling as at other times, “Samuel! Samuel!”</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>And Samuel said, “Speak, for your servant hears.”</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>And Samuel grew, and the Lord was with him and let none of his words fall to the ground.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"2kRuOs/AXkq+roj59l3YTg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                            Exodus 24:3-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Exodus</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
Moses came and told the people all the words of the Lord and all the ordinances;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and all the people answered with one voice, and said, “All the words which the Lord has spoken we will do”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And Moses wrote all the words of the Lord.  And he rose early in the morning, and built an altar at the foot of the mountain, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>and twelve pillars, according to the twelve tribes of Israel. And he sent young men of the people of Israel,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> who offered burnt offerings and sacrificed peace offerings of oxen to the Lord. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>And Moses took half of the blood and put it in basins, and half of the blood he threw against the altar.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Then he took the book of the covenant, and read it in the hearing of the people; and they said, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>“All that the Lord has spoken we will do, and we will be obedient.” And Moses took the blood and threw it upon the people,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> and said, “Behold the blood of the covenant  which the Lord has made with you in accordance with all these words.”</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"50oLnp1dyk+KcnptRBNaFQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THIRD SUNDAY IN ORDINARY TIME</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                   Jonah 3:1-5,10</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Jonah</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>The word of the Lord came to Jonah saying, “Arise, go to Nineveh, that great city,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and proclaim to it the message that I tell you.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>So Jonah arose and went to Nineveh, according to the word of the Lord. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Now Nineveh was an exceedingly great city, three days’ journey in breadth.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Jonah began to go into the city, going a day’s journey.  And he cried, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>“Yet forty days, and Nineveh shall be overthrown!” </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>And the people of Nineveh believed God; they proclaimed a fast, and put on sackcloth, from the greatest of them to the least of them.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>When God saw what they did, how they turned from their evil way, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>God repented of the evil which he had said he would do to them; and he did not do it. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"3778cm4LYEOTpMVg9NEz/g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						   Isaiah 50:4-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord God has given me the tongue of those who are taught, that I may know how to sustain with a word him that is weary.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Morning by morning he wakens, he wakens my ear to hear as those who are taught.  The Lord God has opened my ear, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>and I was not rebellious, I turned not backward.  I gave my back to those who struck me, and my cheeks to those who pulled out the beard;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> I hid not my face from shame and spitting.
For the Lord God helps me; therefore I have not been confounded;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> therefore I have set my face like a flint, and I know that I shall not be put to shame.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF990000"}}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"vgQYOqKzrkSnfO7o/NcpkQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading						                         Isaiah 60:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Arise, shine; for your light has come, and the glory of the Lord has risen upon you.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> For behold, darkness shall cover the earth, and thick darkness the peoples;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> but the Lord will arise upon you, and his glory will be seen upon you. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> And nations shall walk by your light, and kings in the brightness of your rising. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Lift up your eyes round about, and see; they all gather together,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> they come to you; your sons shall come from far, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and your daughters shall be carried in the arms.  Then you shall see and be radiant,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> your heart shall thrill and rejoice; because the abundance of the sea shall be turned to you.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>The wealth of the nations shall come to you.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>A multitude of camels shall cover you, the young camels of Midian and Ephah;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> all those from Sheba shall come.  They shall bring gold and frankincense, and shall proclaim the praise of the Lord.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"gjFmBOdxlEiYdWGORLnq2A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		               Acts. 14:21b-27</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
Paul and Barnabas returned to Lystra and to Iconium and to Antioch, strengthening the souls of the disciples,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> exhorting them to continue in the faith, and saying that through many tribulations we must enter the kingdom of God. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> And when they had appointed elders for them in every church, with prayer and fasting, they committed them to the Lord in whom they believed.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Then they passed through Pisidia, and came to Pamphylia.  And when they had spoken the word in Perga, they went down to Attalia; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>and from there they sailed to Antioch, where they had been commended to the grace of God for the work which they had fulfilled. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> And when they arrived, they gathered the Church together and declared all that God had done with them, and how he had opened a door of faith to the Gentiles.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading"},{Guid:"8rAN8dO1iEOCKLmbsMZf3Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                              	Isaiah 62:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>For Zion’s sake I will not keep silent, and for Jerusalem’s sake I will not rest until her vindication goes forth as brightness, and her salvation as a burning torch.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>The nations shall see your vindication, and all the kings your glory; and you shall be called by a new name which the mouth of the Lord will give.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>You shall be a crown of beauty in the hand of the Lord, and a royal diadem in the hand of your God.
You shall no more be termed Forsaken,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> and your land shall no more be termed Desolate; but you shall be called My delight is in her, and your land Married; for the Lord delights in you, and your land shall be married.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>For as a young man marries a virgin, so shall your sons marry you, and as the bridegroom rejoices over the bride, so shall your God rejoice over you.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"kLid9MI52U2SNRJ8RcR9Zw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                              	Micah 5:2-5a</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Prophet Micah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord:
You, O Bethlehem Ephrathah, who are little to be among the clans of Judah, from you shall come forth for me one who is to be ruler in Israel, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>whose origin is from of old, from ancient days.
Therefore he shall give them up until the time when she who has labour pains has brought forth;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> then the rest of his brethren shall return to the sons of Israel.
And he shall stand and feed his flock in the strength of the Lord, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>in the majesty of the name of the Lord his God.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And they shall dwell secure, for now he shall be great to the ends of the earth.  And this shall be peace.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"AkVoek1OnE6CFSLMTyyakA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Wisdom 2: 12, 17-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Wisdom                                     </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>(Ungodly men said:) 
“Let us lie in wait for the righteous man, because he is inconvenient to us and opposes our actions; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>he reproaches us for sins against the law, and accuses us of sins against our training.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>“Let us see if his words are true, and let us test what will happen at the end of his life; for if the righteous man is God’s son, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>he will help him, and will deliver him from the hand of his adversaries.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Let us test him with insult and torture, that we may find out how gently he is, and make trial of his forbearance. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Let us condemn him to a shameful death, for, according to what he says, he will be protected.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"nQs6BJ/+vUaZAgEMToUfcg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					             1 Samuel 26:2,7-9,12-13,22-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the first Book of Samuel                                    </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
Saul arose and went down to the wilderness of Ziph,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> with three thousand chosen men of Israel, to seek David in the wilderness of Ziph.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>So David and Abishai went to the army by night; and there lay Saul sleeping within the encampment, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>with his spear stuck in the ground at his head; and Abner and the army lay around him.  Then said Abishai to David,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> “God has given your enemy into your hand this day; now therefore let me pin him to the earth with one stroke of the spear,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and I will not strike him twice.” But David said to Abishai, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>“Do not destroy him; for who can put forth his hand against the Lord’s anointed,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and be guiltless?”
So David took the spear and the jar of water from Saul’s head; and they went away.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>No  man saw it, or knew it, nor did any awake; for they were all asleep, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>because a deep sleep from the Lord had fallen upon them. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Then David went over to the other side, and stood afar off on the top of the mountain,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> with a great space between them. And David said,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> “Here is the spear, O king! Let one of the young men come over and fetch it. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord rewards every man for his righteousness and his faithfulness;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> for the Lord gave you into my hand today, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>and I would not put forth my hand against the Lord’s anointed.”</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"DtZO334Y702l0W01eSWqBQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					         Revelation 11:19a; 12:1-6a,10ab</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Revelation                                      </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>God’s temple in heaven was opened.  And a great sign appeared in heaven, a woman clothed with the sun, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>with the moon under her feet, and on her head a crown of twelve stars; she was with child and she cried out in her pangs of birth, in anguish for delivery. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> And another sign appeared in heaven; behold, a great red dragon, with seven heads and ten horns, and seven diadems upon his heads.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  His tail swept down a third of the stars of heaven, and cast them to the earth.  And the dragon stood before the woman who was about to bear a child,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> that he might devour her child when she brought it forth;  she brought forth a male child, one who is to rule all the nations with a rod of iron,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> but her child was caught up to God and to his throne,  and the woman fled into the wilderness, where she has a place prepared by God.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>And I heard a loud voice in heaven, saying, “Now the salvation  and the power and kingdom of our God and the authority of his Christ have come.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"VwP+tvjRZ0yig42WtwBHPw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                           Genesis 15:5-12,17-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Genesis                                </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
God brought Abraham outside and said, “Look toward heaven, and number the stars, if you are able to number them.” </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Then he said to him, “So shall your descendants be.” And he believed the Lord; and he reckoned it to him as righteousness.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And he said to him, I am the Lord who brought you from ur of the Chaldeans, to give you this land to possess.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> But he said “O Lord God how am I to know that I shall possess it?” He said to him, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“Bring me a heifer three years old, a she-goat three years old, a ram three years old, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>a turtledove, and a young pigeon.” 
And he brought him all these, cut them in two,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> and laid each half over against the other; but he did not cut the birds in two. And when birds of prey came down upon the carcasses, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Abram drove them away. As the sun was going down, a deep sleep fell on Abram; and behold, a dread and great darkness fell upon him.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>When the sun had gone down and it was dark, behold, a smoking fire pot and a flaming torch passed  between these pieces.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  On that day the Lord made a covenant with Abram, saying, “To your descendants I give this land,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> from the river of Egypt to the great river, the river Euphrates.”</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"yWKhx8hg2UG3Hdbs5oqqYw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Jeremiah 17:5-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord: “Cursed is the man who trusts in man and makes flesh his arm, whose heart turns away from the Lord.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>He is like a shrub in the desert, and shall not see any good come.  He shall dwell in the parched placed of the wilderness, in an uninhabited salt land.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>“Blessed is the man who trusts in the Lord, whose trust is the Lord. He is like a tree planted by water,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> that sends out its roots by the stream, and does not fear when heat comes for its leaves remain green, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and is not anxious in the year of drought, for it does not cease to bear fruit.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"unU89EukWESyAcxKORE4gw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Isaiah 50:5-9a</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah                                     </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord God has opened my ear, and I was not rebellious, I turned not backward. I gave my back to those who struck me,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and my cheeks to those who pulled out the beard; I hid not my face from shame and spitting.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>For the Lord God helps me; therefore I have not been confounded; therefore I have set my face like a flint, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>and I know that I shall not be put to shame; he who vindicates me is near.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Who will contend with me? Let us stand up together.  Who is my adversary? Let him come near to me. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Behold, the Lord God helps me; who will declare me guilty?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"B0TsnF1qZkS1DUpC6YPuBg",Verses:[{
Text:"First<s1384> Reading 					                     Isaiah 35:4-7a</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah                                     </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Say to those who are of a fearful heart, “Be strong, fear not! Behold, your God will come with vengeance, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>with the recompense of God.  He will come and save you.”</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Then the eyes of the blind shall be opened, and the ears of the deaf unstopped: then shall the lame man leap like a deer, and the tongue of the mute sing for joy.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>For waters shall break forth in the wilderness, and streams in the desert; the burning sand shall become a pool, and the thirsty ground springs of water.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"LbjC/qHg7kGcpNYrX4W/LA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                              	Baruch 5:1-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book Baruch </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Take  off the garment of your sorrow and affliction, O Jerusalem, and put on for ever the beauty of the glory from God.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> 
Put on the robe of the righteousness from God; put on your head the diadem of the glory of the Everlasting. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> For God will show your splendor everywhere under heaven.  For your name will for ever be called by God,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> “Peace of righteousness and glory of godliness.” 
Arise, O Jerusalem, stand upon the height and look toward the east, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and see your children gathered from west and east, at the word of the Holy One, rejoicing that God has remembered them.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  For they went forth from you on foot, led away by their enemies; but God will bring them back to you,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> carried in glory, as on a royal throne.  For God has ordered that every high mountain and the everlasting  hills be made low and the valleys filled up,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> to make  level ground, so that Israel may walk safely in the glory of God.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> The woods and every fragrant tree have shaded Israel at God’s command.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>For God will lead Israel with joy, in the light of his glory, with the mercy and righteousness that come from him.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"o3KcEnIKm0qxJJWWrOgCJg",Verses:[],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"zkP/+BUZzkSdnxGe9XAe1Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Jeremiah 31:7-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah                                   </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord: “Sing aloud with gladness for Jacob, and raise shouts for the chief of the nations;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> proclaim, give praise, and say, “The Lord has saved his people, the remnant of Israel.’</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Behold, I will bring them from the north country, and gather them from the farthest parts of the earth, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>among them the blind and the lame, the woman with child and her who is in travail, together;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> a great company , they shall return here.  With weeping they shall come, and with consolations I will lead them back,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> I will make them walk by brooks of water, in a straight path in which they shall not stumble;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> for I am a father to Israel, and Ephraim is my first-born.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"smaVl48dzkKWcs7rtGL/GQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                               Jeremiah 33:14-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>“Behold, the days are coming, says the Lord, when I will fulfill the promise I made to the house of Israel and the house of Judah. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>In those days and at that time I will cause a righteous Branch to spring forth for David;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and he shall execute justice and righteousness in the land. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> In those days Judah will be saved and Jerusalem will dwell securely.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And this is the name by which it will be called: ‘The Lord is our righteousness.’”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"MFSiJaxJe0q3O2yzbB2jLQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>FIFTH SUNDAY IN ORDINARY TIME</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Isaiah 6:1-2a, 3-8</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>In the year that King Uzziah died I saw the Lord sitting upon a throne, high and lifted up; and his train filled the temple. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Above him stood the seraphim; each had six wings. And one called to another and said: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“Holy,holy,holy is the Lord of hosts; the whole earth is full of his glory” </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And the foundations of the thresholds shook at the voice of him who called, and the house was filled with smoke. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>And I said: “Woe is me! For I am lost; for I am a man of unclean lips, and I dwell in the midst of a people of unclean lips;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> for my eyes have seen the King, the Lord of hosts!”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Then flew one of the seraphim to me, having in his hand a burning coal which he had taken with tongs from the altar. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> And he touched my mouth, and said: “Behold, this has touched your lips; your guilt is taken away, and your sin forgiven.” </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>And I heard the voice of the Lord says, “Whom shall I send, and who will go for us?” 
Then I said, “Here am I! Send me.”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord
 </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"+zOen1L8ZEOYwZnwUrllIg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                               Daniel 12:1-3</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Daniel                                  </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>At that time shall arise Michael, the great prince who has charge of your people.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> And there shall be a time of trouble, such as never has been since there was a nation till that time;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> but at that time your people shall be delivered, every one whose name shall be found written in the book. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> 
And many of those who sleep in the dust of the earth shall awake, some to everlasting life, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and some to shame and everlasting contempt.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> And those who are wise shall shine like the brightness of the firmament; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and those who turn many to righteousness, like the stars for ever and ever.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"Ndai4slZ7ki4IYAoBqm2Sw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                         Numbers 6:22-27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Numbers  </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord said to Moses, “Say to Aaron and his sons, Thus you shall bless the sons of Israel: you shall say to them, The Lord bless you and keep you:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> The Lord make his face to shine upon you, and be gracious to you: The Lord lift up his countenance upon you, and give you peace.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>“So shall they put my name upon the sons of Israel, and I will bless them.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"98rzaQ2inkq4R7ziY1liiA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Wisdom 7:7-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Wisdom                                   </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>I prayed and understanding was given me; I called upon God, and the spirit of wisdom came to me. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> I preferred her to scepters and thrones, and I accounted wealth as nothing in comparison with her. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Neither did I liken to her any priceless gem, because all gold is but a little sand in her sight, and silver will be accounted as clay before her.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  
I loved her more than health and beauty, and I chose to have her rather than light, because her radiance never ceases.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  All good things came to me along with her, and in her hands uncounted wealth.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"0NhTtxQBzEK/0IKBaffDyw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                               Daniel 7:13-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Daniel                                  </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>I saw in the night visions, and behold, with the clouds of heaven there came one like a son of man,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and he came to the Ancient of Days and was presented before him.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>And to him was given dominion and glory and kingdom, that all peoples, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nations, and languages should serve him; his dominion is an everlasting dominion, which shall not pass away,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> and his kingdom one that shall not be destroyed.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"LsbI3lGyakiT6OOoe7o5YQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                                      Sirach 27:4-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the first Book of Sirach                                    </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>When a sieve is shaken, the refuse remain; so a man’s filth remains in his thoughts. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> The kiln tests the potter’s vessels; so the test of just men is in tribulation.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>The fruit discloses the cultivation of a tree; so the expression of a thought discloses the cultivation of a man’s mind.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Do not praise a man before you hear him speak, for this is the test of men.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"LWMx1gIy80Ow/Q2tv5FRLw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                               Deuteronomy 6:2-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Deuteronomy                                   </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Moses spoke to the people, saying, “Fear the Lord your God, you and son and your son’s son,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> by keeping all his statutes and his commandments, which I command you, all the days of your life; that your days may be prolonged.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Hear therefore, O Israel, and be careful to do them; that it may go well with you, and that you,   may multiply greatly, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>as the Lord, the God of your fathers, has promised you, in a land flowing with milk and honey.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“Hear, O Israel:
The Lord our God is one Lord; and you shall love the Lord your God with all your heart, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>and with all your soul, and with all your might.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>And these words which I command you this day shall be upon your heart.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"1EuWLehzxUCYDmnl99OXDg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Isaiah 53:10-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Isaiah                                   </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>It was the will of the Lord to bruise him; he has put him to grief; when he makes himself an offering for sin,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> he shall see his offspring, he shall prolong his days; the will of the Lord shall prosper in his hand;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> he shall see the fruit of the travail of his soul and be satisfied; by his knowledge shall the righteous one,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> my servant, make many to be accounted righteous; and he shall bear their iniquities.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"WWQq0S25zEWZyMQU84KnPw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                              	Zephania 3:14-18a</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Prophet Zephaniah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Sing aloud, O daughter of Zion; shout, O Israel!
Rejoice and exult with all your heart, O daughter of Jerusalem! </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord has taken away the judgements against you, he has cast out your enemies.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>The King of Israel, the Lord, is in your midst; you shall fear evil no more.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>On that day it shall be said to Jerusalem: “Do not fear, O Zion;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> let not your hands grow weak.  The Lord your God is in your midst, a warrior who gives victory; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>he will rejoice over you with gladness, he will renew you in his love; he will exult over you with loud singing as a day of festival.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"tc0QiGMj+UOlDYU5xGUp0g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Deuteronomy 4:1-2,6-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Deuteronomy                                      </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Moses spoke to the people, saying, “Now, O Israel, give heed to the statutes and the ordinances which I teach  you,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and do them; that you may live, and go in and take possession of the land which the Lord, the God of your fathers, gives you.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  You shall not add to the word which I command you, nor take from it; that you may keep the commandments of the Lord your God which I command you.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“Keep them and do them; for that will be your wisdom and your understanding in the sight of the peoples, who, when they hear all these statutes,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> will say, ‘Surely this great nation is a wise and understanding people.’ For what great nation is there that has a god so near to it as the Lord our God is to us,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> whenever we call upon him? And what great nation is there, that has statutes and ordinances so righteous as all this law which I set before you this day?”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"KKFoCOrkCUqYafG0Bq/X6A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Jeremiah 17:5-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord: “Cursed is the man who trusts in man and makes flesh his arm, whose heart turns away from the Lord.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>He is like a shrub in the desert, and shall not see any good come. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> He shall dwell in the parched placed of the wilderness, in an uninhabited salt land.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“Blessed is the man who trusts in the Lord, whose trust is the Lord. He is like a tree planted by water, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>that sends out its roots by the stream, and does not fear when heat comes for its leaves remain green,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> and is not anxious in the year of drought, for it does not cease to bear fruit.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading "},{Guid:"OnK9u+Jeg06v4jgYH3UGiw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 					                     Jeremiah 1:4-5,17-19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In the days of Josiah the word of the Lord came to me saying, “Before I formed you in the womb I knew you, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>and before you were born I consecrated you; I appointed you  a prophet to the nations.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>“But you, gird up your loins; arise, and say to them everything that I command you.   Do not be dismayed by them, lest I dismay you before them. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And I, behold, I make you this day a fortified city, an iron pillar, and bronze walls, against the whole land, against the kings of Judah, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>its princes, its priests and the people of the land.  They will fight against you; but they shall not prevail against you, for I am with you, says the Lord, to deliver you.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading 					First Reading             "},{Guid:"pS2e/OMR1UKN00Ab9SLLbQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		               Acts. 10:34a,37-43</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Peter opened his mouth and said, “You know the word which was proclaimed throughout all Judea, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>beginning from Galilee after the baptism with John preached: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>how God anointed Jesus of Nazareth with the Holy Spirit and with power; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>how he went about doing good and healing all that were oppressed by the devil, for God was with him.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And we are witnesses to all that he did both in the country of the Jews and in Jerusalem.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  They put him to death by hanging him on a tree; but God raised him on the third day and made him manifest;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> not to all the people but to us who were chosen by God as witnesses, who ate and drank with him after he rose from the dead.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  And he commanded us to preach to the people,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> and to testify that he is the one ordained by God to be judge of the living and the dead. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>To him all the prophets bear witness that every one who believes in him receives forgiveness of sins through his name.”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"IfFy0vS0UketAtbqZnVFgQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Ezekiel	                     Ezekiel 2:2-5</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
The Spirit entered into me and set me upon my feet; and I heard him speaking to me.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And he said to me, “Son of man, I send you to the sons of Israel, to a nation of rebels, who have rebelled against me; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>they and their fathers have transgressed against me to this very day.  
The people also are impudent and stubborn:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> I send you to them; and you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the Lord God.’</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>And whether they hear or refuse to hear (for they are a rebellious house) they will know that there has been a prophet among them.”</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"ZJMONcjLK0avNEsdZnf9cw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Job	                              Job 38:1,8-11</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord answered Job out of the whirlwind: “Who shut in the sea with doors, when it burst forth from the womb;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> when I made clouds its garment, and thick darkness its swaddling band; and prescribed bounds for it,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and set bars and doors, and said, ‘Thus far shall you come, and no farther, and here shall your proud waves be stayed’?”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"oV814sUT2UmZkkQauvq81A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		                      Acts. 4:32-35</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The company of those who believed were of one heart and soul,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and no none said that any of the things which he possessed was his own, but they had everything in common. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> And with great power the apostles gave their testimony to the resurrection of the Lord Jesus, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>and great grace was upon them all.  There was not any one needy among them,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> for as many as were possessors of lands or houses sold them, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>and brought the proceeds of what was sold and laid it at the apostles’ feet; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and distribution was made to each as any had need.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"C+EyNWltr0WPM/2gisteGg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Genesis		Genesis 1:26-2:3</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>God said, “Let us make man in our image, after our likeness; and let them have dominion over the fish of the sea, and over the birds of the air,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and over the cattle, and over all the earth, and over every creeping thing that creeps upon the earth.”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> So God created man in his own image, in the image of God he created him; male and female he created them. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> And God blessed them, and God said to them, “Be fruitful and multiply, and fill the earth and subdue it; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and have dominion over the fish of the sea and over the birds of the air and over every living thing that moves upon the earth.” And God said, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>“Behold, I have given you every plant yielding seed which is upon the face of all the earth, and every tree with seed in its fruits; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>you shall have them for food. And to every beast of the earth, and to every bird of the air, and to everything that creeps on the earth, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>everything that has the breath of life,  I have given every green plant for food.” And it was so. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>And God saw everything that he had made, and behold, it was very good.  And there was evening and there was morning, a sixth day.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Thus the heavens and the earth were finished, and all the host of them.  And on the seventh day God finished his work which he had done, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>and he rested on the seventh day from all his works which he had done.  </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>So God blessed the seventh day and hallowed it, because on it God rested from  all his work which he had done in creation.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"Yd5HF8RBMUaY1YKz0B7nRQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading 
2 Kings 4:42-44
Verse 2</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Second Book of Kings                               </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>A man came from Baal-shalishah, bringing the man of God bread of the first fruits, twenty loaves of barley,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and fresh ears of grain in his sack.  And Elisha said, “Give to the men, that they may eat.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>But his servant said, “How am I to set this before a hundred men?”
So he repeated,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> “Give them to the men, that they may eat, for thus says the Lord, “They shall eat and have some left.” So he set it before them.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>And they ate, and had some left, according to the word of the Lord.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"CEsdiv90+kKL9mwBhXScjw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		                Acts. 3:13-15,17-19ab</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Peter said to the people, “The God of Abraham and of Isaac and of Jacob, the God of our fathers,</s>"},{ID:4},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> glorified his servant Jesus, whom you delivered up and denied in the presence of Pilate when he had decided to release him.
  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>But you denied the Holy and Righteous One, and asked for a murderer to be granted to you,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> and killed the Author of life, whom God raised from the dead.
To this we are witnesses.</s>"},{ID:6},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“And now, brethren, 
I know that you acted in ignorance, as did also your rulers.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>But what God foretold by the mouth of all the prophets, that his Christ should suffer, he thus fulfilled.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Repent therefore, and turn again, that your sins may be blotted out.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"N8IPe0+fGU6NpypbT4PykA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		                Acts. 4:8-12</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Peter, filled with the Holy spirit, said, “Rulers of the people and elders,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> if we are being examined today concerning a good deed done to a cripple, by what means this man has been healed,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> be it known to you all, and to all the people of Israel, that by the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>whom you crucified, whom God raised from the dead, by him this man is standing before you well. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> This is the stone which was rejected by you builders, but which has become the cornerstone. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> And there is salvation in no one else, for there is no other name under heaven given among men by which we must be saved.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"1RXvJA7TK0OuWojSDtAnhQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Acts of the Apostles		               Acts. 10:34a,37-43</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Peter opened his mouth and said, “You know the word which was proclaimed throughout all Judea,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> beginning from Galilee after the baptism which John preached: how God anointed Jesus of Nazareth with the Holy Spirit and with power;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> how he went about doing good and healing all that were oppressed by the devil, for God was with him.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And we are witnesses to all that he did both in the country of the Jews and in Jerusalem.  They put him to death by hanging him on a tree; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>but God raised him on the third day and made him manifest;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> not to all the people but to us who were chosen by God as witnesses, who ate and drank with him after he rose from the dead.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>And he commanded us to preach to the people, and to testify that he is the one ordained by God to be judge of the living and the dead. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>To him all the prophets bear witness that every one who believes in him receives forgiveness of sins through his name.”</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"sYcQFJv1pEmEKXNKy56dLw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Exodus                                   Exodus. 16:2-4,12-15</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>At that time: 
The whole congregation of the sons of Israel murmured against Moses and Aaron in the wilderness and said to them,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> “Would that we had died by the hand of the Lord in the land of Egypt, when we sat by the fleshpots and ate bread to the full;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> for you have brought us out into this wilderness to kill this whole assembly with hunger.”</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Then the Lord said to Moses, “Behold, I will rain bread from heaven for you; and the people shall go out and gather a day’s portion every day, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>that I may test them, whether they will walk in my law or not.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>“I have heard the murmurings of the sons of Israel; say to them, ‘At twilight you shall eat flesh, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>and in the morning you shall be filled with bread; then you shall know that I am the Lord your God.’”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>In the evening quails came up and covered the camp; and in the morning dew lay round about the camp. And when the dew had gone up, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>there was on the face of the wilderness a fine, flake-like thing, fine as hoarfrost on the ground. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>When the sons of Israel saw it, they said to one another, “What is it?” for they did not know what it was.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>And Moses said to them, “It is the bread which the Lord has given you to eat.”</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"my81TmgqjkCqVuJo2nIwYA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Wisdom	                     Wisdom 1:13-15;2:23-24</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>God did not make death, and he does not delight in the death of the living. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> 
For he created all things that they might exist, and the creatures of the world are wholesome,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and there is no destructive poison in them; and the dominion of Hades is not on earth. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>For righteousness is immortal. For God created man for incorruption, and made him in the image of his own eternity, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>but through the devil’s envy death entered the world, and those who belong to his party experience it.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"dsDZa47yVEeaqs6kfnloHg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Prophet Ezekiel	                             Ezekiel 17:22-24</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord God:
“I myself will take a sprig from the lofty top of the cedar, and will set it out; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>I will break off from the topmost of its young twigs a tender one, and I myself will plant it upon a high and lofty mountain; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>on the mountain height of Israel will I plant it, that it may bring forth boughs and bear fruit,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> and become a noble cedar; and under it will dwell all kinds of beasts;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> in the shade of its branches birds of every sort will nest.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  And all the trees of the field shall know that I the Lord bring low the high tree, and make high the low tree, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>dry up the green tree, and make the dry tree flourish.  I the Lord have spoken, and I will do it.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"3lILxanXtk2nbdj8M24A+g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Joshua                                        Joshua 24:1-2a, 15-18b</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Joshua gathered all the tribes of Israel to Shechem, and summoned the elders, the heads, the judges, and the officers of Israel; and they presented themselves before God. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> 
And Joshua said to all the people, “If you be unwilling to serve the Lord, choose this day whom you will serve,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> whether the gods your fathers served in the region beyond the River, or the gods of the Amorites in whose land you dwell;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> but as for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.”Then the people answered,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> “Far be it from us that we should forsake the Lord, to serve other gods; for it is the Lord our God who brought us and our fathers up from the land of Egypt, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>out of the house of bondage, and who did those great signs in our sight, and preserved us in all the way that we went,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> and among all the peoples through whom we passed; therefore we also will serve the Lord.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"t3pS9krQyk2xzSAKHgCSJQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Jeremiah  	                            Jeremiah 23:1-6</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>“Woe to the shepherds who destroy and scatter the sheep of my pasture!” says the Lord.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Therefore thus says the Lord, the God of Israel, concerning the shepherds who care for my people; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>“You have scattered my flock, and have driven them away, and you have not attended to them.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Behold, I will attend to you for your evil doings, says the Lord.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Then I will gather the remnant of my flock out of all the countries where I have driven them, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>and I will bring them back to their fold, and they shall be fruitful and multiply.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> I will set shepherds over them who will care for them, and they shall fear no more, nor be dismayed, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>neither shall any be missing, says the Lord.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>“Behold, the days are coming, says the Lord, when I will raise up for David a righteous Branch, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>and he shall reign as king and deal wisely, and shall execute justice and righteousness in the land. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> 
In his days Judah will be saved, and Israel will dwell securely. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> And this is the name by which he will be called: ‘The Lord is our righteousness.’”</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"vR6/xvWJU0KExaSoym4glQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Amos 	                            Amos 7:12-15</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>In those days: 
Amaziah the priest of Bethel said to Amos, “O seer, go, flee away to the land of Judah, and eat bread there,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> and prophesy there; but never again prophesy at Bethel, for it is the king’s sanctuary, and it is a temple of the kingdom.”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Then Amos answered Amaziah, “I am no prophet, nor a prophet’s son; but I am a herdsman, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>and a dresser of sycamore trees, and the Lord took me from following the flock, and the Lord said to me, ‘Go, prophesy to my people Israel.”</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading 
"},{Guid:"Qen6LTV08EuyXw32TRAyAw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>First Reading			Exodus 22:21-27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of Exodus</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord:
“You shall not wrong stranger or oppress him, for you were strangers in the land of Egypt.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> You shall not afflict any widow or orphan.  If you do afflict them, and they cry out to me,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> I will surely hear their cry; and my wrath will burn, and I will kill you with the sword, and your wives shall become widows and your children fatherless.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>“If you lend money to any of my people with you who is poor, you shall not be to him as a creditor, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>and you shall not exact interest from him.  If ever you take your neighbour’s garment in pledge, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>you shall restore it to him before the sun goes down; for that is his only covering, it is his mantle for his body; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>in what else shall be sleep? And if he cries to me, I will hear, for I am compassionate.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"First Reading						                First Reading"},{Guid:"tJ5RA5USCEODZh6vyQS5UA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>1st reading</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>A reading from the Book of Revelation </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>I, John, saw another angel ascend from the rising of the sun,
 </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>with the seal of the living God, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846>and he called with a loud voice to the four 
angels who had been given power to harm earth and sea,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846>saying, \" Do not harm the earth or the sea or the trees.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846>till we have sealed the servants of our God upon their foreheads.\"</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846>And I heard the number of the sealed, a hundred and forty-four thousand sealed,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846>out of every tribe of the sons of Israel.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846>After this I looked, and behold, a great multitude which
no man could number, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846>from every nation, from all tribes
and peoples and tongues, standing before the throne and before
the Lamb, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846>clothed in white robes, with palm branches in their hands,
and crying out with a loud voice, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1846>\"Salvation belongs to our God who sits upon the throne, and to the Lamb!\"</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1846>And all the angels stood round the throne and round the elders and the four living creatures,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1846> and they
fell on their faces before the throne and 
worshiped God, saying, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1846>\"Amen! Blessing and glory and wisdom
and thanksgiving and honour and power and might be to
our God for ever and ever!Amen.\"</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1846>Then one of the elders addressed me saying, \"Who are
these, clothed in white robes, and from where have 
they come?\"</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1846> I said to him, \"Sir, you know.\" And
he said to me, \" These are they who have come
out of the great tribulation; </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1846>they have washed their 
robes and made them white in the blood of the Lamb.\" </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1846>The word of the Lord.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"first reading
"},{Guid:"MJtfmPd7AkCEHhbLxsQDOQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>FIRST READING</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>A reading from the Book of the Prophet Ezekiel</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Thus says the Lord God:
“Behold, I will take the sons of Israel
From the nations among which they have gone,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>And will gather them from all sides, 
And bring them to their own land;
And I will make them one nation in the Land,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Upon the mountains of Israel;
 And one king shall be king over them all;
And they shall be no longer two nations, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>And no longer divided into two kingdoms.
They shall not defile themselves any more with their idols and their detestable things,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Or with any of their detestable things,
Or with any of their transgressions;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>But I will save them from all the backslidings 
In which they have sinned, and will cleansed them;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>And they shall be my people and I will be their God.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>“My servant David shall be king over them;
And they shall all have one shepherd.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>They shall follow my ordinances
And be careful to observe my status.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>They shall dwell in the land where your fathers dweltThat I gave to my servant Jacob;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>They and their children and their children’s childrenShall dwell there forever;
And David my servant shall be their prince forever.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> I will make a covenant of peace with them;
It shall be an everlasting covenant with them;
And I will bless them and multiply them;</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>And I will bless them and multiply them
And will set my sanctuary in the midst of them for evermore.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>My dwelling place shall be with them;
And I will be their God,And they shall be my peopleThen the nations will know that I the Lord sanctify Israel,</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>When my sanctuary is in the midst of them for evermore.”</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>The word of the Lord.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"FIRST READING
"},{Guid:"J2+jvsxYvkq4CZv00oSsQg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>A reading  from the second Book of Maccabees		2 Maccabees 12:43-45</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>In those days:
Judas (the leader of Israel) also took up a collection, man by man, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>to the amount of two thousand drachmas  of silver and sent it to Jerusalem to provide for a sin offering.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  In doing this he acted very well and honourably, taking account of the resurrection.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>For if he were not expecting that those who had fallen would rise again, it would have been superfluous and foolish to pray for the dead. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> But if he was looking to the splendid reward that is laid up for those who fall asleep in godliness, it was a holy and pious thought.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Therefore he made atonement for the dead, that they might be delivered from their sin.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Word of the Lord</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
Text:"first readings"},{Guid:"IIHnRQgjyUWs3EwtA4u8qw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Githomo gia mbere </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Mwiciragiei tha cia Ngai' ariu a ithe witu ndamuthaitha ni undu wa uria Ngai aanamwiguira tha,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>ati mwirute miiri yanyu ituike ihaki ria kumuhakira igongona nario riri muoyo na riri itheru, o riria ringitiikirika ni Ngai, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ariguo uungati wa uuhingu uria mwagiriru. Na mutika hananie uhoro wanyu na wa andu a guku thi,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> no riri mugaruruke undu ungi ni undu wa ngoro cianyu guthondeko mechiria machio makeruhio,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>niguo muhotage kwimenyerera kuna maundu maria Ngai endaga mekwo, namo no maria mega maria mangitikirika o maria makinyaniru kuna.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>wendani wanyu ni utuikage o uria utari na uhinga. Undu uria muuru uthuuragei; naguo uria mwega, mukiurumagie.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>He kwendana na ariu aria angi a ithe witu-ri, mundu niendage uria ungi na ngoro ya uuma-andu; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na ha uhoro wa gitio, mundu niendage kaba uria ungi atio mbere yake. Ningi ha uhoro ubatie kiyo, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>menyai gukaugutarira; rekei ngoro cianyu ihiahiagire thiinii na mutungatagire Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Kenagai ni undu wa uria muri na kirigiriro; na hindi ya thina, kiragiririai; nakuo kuhoya,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>rumanagiriai kuhoya na kiyo. Teithagiai anu aria amure mabataroini mao, na muture mugwatanaga ugeni.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Andu aria mamnyariraga-ri marathimagei; rathimagai na mutikanarumane. Aria megukena,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>kenagai hamwe nao, na aria mekurira, murirage hamwe nao. Iguanagai o mundu na mundu uria ungi; </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>tigagai kugia na meciria ma mwitiio, no mwitikire kuiuanwo ni maundu maria manyinyi; </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>tigagai kwiyona ta muri ogi.  Menyai gugathukira mundu ona uriku uuruni undu wa uuru uia amwikite; </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>mwichiragiei gwika maundu o maria mangiono magiriire ni andu othe; inyui hanyu-ri, kungihoteka, geragiai guikarania na andu othe mwina thayu. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Twatuura twendaine, Ngai niatuuraga thiinii witu. O naguo wendo wake ugagikinyanira thiini witu.</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Githomo gia mbere"},{Guid:"eG2pUW1G90GfLrJb9NO1Aw",Verses:[{}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"teUP2GRvxEeWHJZK2t+FjA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 Aefeso 2:13-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, rĩu, thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu-rĩ, inyuĩ arĩa mwaraihĩrĩirie nĩ mũreharehetwo hakuhĩ nĩ ũndũ wa thakame ya Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Amu nĩwe thayũ witũ, o we watũmire ithuĩ twarĩ erĩ tũtuĩke o ro ũmwe, agĩgĩtharia rũhĩrĩgo rũrĩa rũatũhakanĩtie;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> naguo ũthũ-rĩ, akĩũnina na ũndũ wa mwĩrĩ wake, naguo  ũguo nĩta kuuga atĩ nĩ aaninire watho ũrĩa wa maathani marĩa maatuĩtwo.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Agĩgĩĩka ũguo nĩ getha ombe thĩinĩ wake mwene mũndũ ũmwe mwerũ uumĩte harĩ acio erĩ, na amaciarithanie ũguo;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ nĩ getha atũme matuĩke mwĩrĩ ũmwe, amaiguithanie na Ngai na ũndũ wa mũtharaba,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ wa ũrĩa aaninĩte ũthũ naguo.  Agĩgĩũka akĩhunjanĩria ũhoro wa thayũ, thayũ kũrĩ inyuĩ arĩa mwaraihĩrĩirie, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o na thayũ kũrĩ arĩa maakuhĩrĩirie o nao, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ tondũ wake we ithuĩ a irũka icio cierĩ twĩtĩkagĩrio tũkinye harĩ Ithe witũ, tũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Muoyo o ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 10,27
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Ng’ondu ciakwa-rĩ, nĩ ciiguaga mũgambo wakwa, na niĩ nĩ ndĩciũĩ, nacio ikanũmĩrĩra.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"fSJERnRlXEKkBkbV/TwgAQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ				 Kũguũrĩrio 1:9-11. 12-13.17-19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ John, mũrũ wa ithe wanyu na mũgwatanĩri na inyuĩ mĩnyamaro na ũthamaki na ũkirĩrĩria, iria ii na Yesu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ndakorirũo ndĩ gĩthama kĩrĩa gĩĩtagwo Patmos nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro wa Ngai na ũira wa Yesu.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ngĩkorũo ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Muoyo mũthenya wa Mwathani, na ngĩigua mũgambo mũnene na thutha wakwa, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o ta wa coro, ũkiuga atĩrĩ: Ũrĩa ũkuona-rĩ, andĩka mbuku-inĩ, ũcoke ũtũmĩre makanitha marĩa mũgwanja. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ngĩkĩĩhũgũra nyone mũgambo ũcio wanjarĩria.  Ndehũgũra, ngĩona mĩtĩ mũgwanja ya kũhangĩrũo matawa, ya thahabu; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na mĩtĩ-inĩ ĩo ya kũhangĩrũo matawa gatagatĩ ngĩona kũrĩ wĩ ho ahaana ta mũrũ wa mũndũ, ekĩrĩte nguo ĩmũkinyĩte o nyarĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na akeoha mũcibi wa thahabu gĩthũri-inĩ.  Ndamuona, ngĩgũa magũrũ-inĩ make ngĩikara ta mũndũ mũkuũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake akĩnjigĩrĩra guoko kwa ũrĩo, akiuga: Tiga gwĩtigĩra; nĩ niĩ wa mbere o na wa kũrigĩrĩria, nĩ niĩ Ũrĩa-wĩ-muoyo; na nĩ ndakuĩte, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ niĩ ũyũ, ngũtũũra muoyo kinya o tene na tene, nacio ihingũro nĩ niĩ ndĩ nacio cia gĩkuũ na cia kwa-ngoma.  Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> kĩandĩke maũndũ macio wona, o namo maũndũ marĩa me kuo rĩu, na marĩa magakinya thutha.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       John 20,29</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Wee, Thomas, tondũ nĩ ũnyonete, nĩkĩo wĩtĩkĩtie; gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matonete na no metĩkĩtie.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"Az5NT2NKgE+E89oLf3xe6w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						Ahibirania 9:11-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAŨL KŨRĨ AHIBIRANIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ĩndĩ rĩrĩa Kristũ okire, arĩ mũruti  igongona cia maũndũ marĩa mega makiriĩ gũũka-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ aahungurire hema ĩrĩa nene na njagĩrĩru makĩria, o ĩrĩa ĩtarĩ thondeke na moko, ũguo nĩ ta kuuga  ndĩũmbĩtwo mĩũmbĩre ya thĩ ĩno. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Agĩgĩtonya handũ harĩa hatheru ihinda o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, atakuuĩte thakame ya mbũri na ya njaũ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>no akuuĩte thakame yake mwene; agĩgĩkorũo akũũrĩte andũ ũguo na ũkũũri  ũrĩa ũtagathira.  Tondũ kũngĩkorũo atĩ thakame cia mbũri na cia ndegwa,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o na mũhu wa mori icinĩtwo, ciaminjaminjĩrio andũ arĩa me na thahu, nĩ ihotaga kũmatheria, mĩĩrĩ yao ithahũke-rĩ, githĩ thakame ya Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> o we werutĩire Ngai, atarĩ na kaũũgũ, na ũndũ wa Muoyo ũrĩa ũtũũraga tene na tene-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ndĩngĩkĩria mũno kũmũtheria thamiri cianyu nĩguo mũtigane na ciĩko iria irehage gĩkuũ, na mũtũngatagĩre Ngai ũrĩa wĩ muoyo?</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Na tondũ ũcio nĩwe mũiguithania wa kĩrĩkanĩro kĩngĩ kĩerũ, nĩ getha yarĩa metĩtwo makagaĩrũo igai rĩtagathira,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> o rĩrĩa merĩirũo, kuona atĩ nĩ harĩ na gĩkuũ gĩkuĩtwo  kĩrĩa kĩmakũũrĩte mahĩtia-inĩ marĩa maahĩtirie hingo ya kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩa mbere.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"dY2dBsM/90+yWQTyrCXftg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					Aroma 8:31-34</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRI ANDŨ A ROMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, tũkiuge atĩa tondũ wa maũndũ macio? Akorũo Ngai arĩ mwena witũ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nũ ũngĩkĩhota gũtũtuma ũthũ? Ũcio ũtaigana gũcaira Mũriũ wake mwene-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>tiga o kũmũruta aamũrutire nĩ ũndũ witũ ithuothe-rĩ, agĩtũheete Ũcio,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> angĩkĩrega atĩa gũtũtugaga na indo iria ingĩ ciothe? Atĩrĩrĩ, andũ arĩa Ngai ethũrĩire-rĩ, nũ ũngĩona ũndũ ũngĩ angĩmathitangĩra? </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Githĩ ti Ngai mũmatui athingu? Nũ ũngĩhota kũmatua ehia? Githĩ ti Kristũ Yesu wakuire, o na makĩria akĩriũkio oime kũrĩ aria akuũ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩu atũire guoko-inĩ  kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai, o na nĩwe ũtũthaithanagĩrĩra?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Marko 9. 7					   
	</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco  na gitio gwaku, Mwathani Yesu! </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Thiini wa itu gũkiuma mũgambo  wa Ithe: “Ũyũ niwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno: mũiguagei”. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco na gitio gwaku, Mwathani Yesu!</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"kAH9bH4owUebJbAojuf+fQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ				           Kũguũrĩrio 5:11-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ John ngĩcoka ngĩrora, ngĩigua mũgambo wa araika aingĩ mathiũrũrũkĩirie gĩtĩ kĩrĩa gĩa ũthamaki na ciũmbe icio ii muoyo o na athuri, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na ũrĩa maaiganaga nĩ ngiri ikũmi, na ngiri cia ngiri; makoigaga atĩrĩ na mũgambo mũnene,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Gatũrũme karĩa gaathĩnjirũo nĩwe mwagĩrĩru wa kũgwata ũhoti, o na ũtonga, na ũũgĩ, na hinya, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na gĩtĩo, na riri o na kĩrathimo.  Na kĩndũ kĩũmbe o gĩothe, kĩrĩa kĩĩ Igũrũ, na kĩrĩa kĩrĩ thĩ, na kĩrĩa kĩrĩ ruungu rũa thĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na kĩrĩa kĩrĩ iria rĩrĩa inene igũrũ, o na indo ciothe iria irĩ kuo, ngĩigua ikiuga atĩrĩ: Ũcio ũikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o nake Gatũrũme, marotũũra na kĩrathimo, o na gĩtĩo, na riri, o na wathani, nginya tene na tene.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nacio ciũmbe icio inya ii muoyo ikiuga: Amen.  Nao athuri makĩĩgũithia thĩ magĩthathaiya.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
			
			       
Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Kristũ nĩ ariũkĩte We ũrĩa  wombire thĩ na ahonokirie andũ thĩinĩ wa tha ciake.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"VzPEo4xwCk2QpG2VgDIlcQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                Afilipi 4:4-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ikaragai mũkenete nĩ ũndũ wa Mwathani hĩndĩ ciothe: o na nguuga o rĩngĩ atĩ mũikarage mũkenete.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Tũmagai gũkiranĩrĩria kwanyu kũmenyũo nĩ andũ othe.  Mwathani akiriĩ gũũka.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Tigagai gwĩtanga nĩ ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ: no rĩrĩ, menyithagiai Ngai maũndũ marĩa mothe mwendaga,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> mũkĩmũhoyaga na mũkĩmũthaithaga, hamwe na kũmũcokeria ngatho.  Naguo thayũ wa Ngai,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa ũtangĩmenyeka ũrĩa ũtariĩ, nĩ ũrĩikaragia ngoro cianyu o na gwĩciria kwanyu nakuo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI			
	</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Muoyo wa Mwathani arĩ Igũrũ rĩakwa, nĩ getha hunjagĩrie arĩa athĩni ũhoro ũrĩa mwega.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"0Ci1deEEAUmGR3TwBWTEqQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					         Jakobu 1:17-18, 21b-22.27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, inyuĩ nyenda mũno, ũheani o wothe wa maũndũ mega, o na kĩheo o gĩothe kĩrĩa kĩagĩrĩire kũna, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ciumanaga Igũrũ, igaikũrũka ciumĩte kũrĩ ithe witũ, mwene motheri ma igũrũ, ũrĩa ũtagariũkaga, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na ndarĩ kĩĩruru gĩa kũgarũrũka.  Nĩwe watũciarire na mũgambo wa ma, kũringana na ũrĩa eyendeire we mwene,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha tũtuĩke ta mũtũrio wa indo iria ombire. Nyitani na ngoro ũhoreri mũgambo ũrĩa ũhandĩtwo thĩinĩ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o ũrĩa ũngĩhota kũhonokia mĩoyo yanyu.  Ĩndĩ tuĩkai andũ a gwĩkaga ũhoro ũrĩa mũiguĩte,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na mũtigatuĩke o a kũũiguaga mũtekũwĩka, mũkĩĩhenagia inyuĩ ene. Ũndini ũrĩa wonagwo nĩ Ngai,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o we Ithe witũ, wĩ mũtheru, na ũtarĩ mũthũku nĩguo ũyũ atĩrĩ, nĩ gũthiaga kũrora ciana cia ngoriai na atumia a ndigwa hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mathĩnĩkĩte,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ atĩ mũndũ eikaragie gũkũ thĩ ategũthũkio nĩ imeni iria njũru ciakuo.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Thaburi 27:11</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nyonagĩrĩria njĩra yaku, Mwathani, ndwaraga o na ũthiĩro mwaraganu.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"gh81dAyoukGdG6y2jJoGRQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ			1 Athesalonike 1:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKE MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ithuĩ, Paolo na Silvano na Timotheo, twatũma marũa maya kũrĩ kanitha wa Athesalonike,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa ũtũire thĩinĩ wa Ngai Ithe witũ o na Mwathani Yesu Kristũ. Mũrogĩa na Wega wa Ngai, o na thayũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ tũcokagĩria Ngai ngatho hĩndĩ ciothe nĩ ũndũ wanyu inyuothe, tũkĩmũgwetaga mahoya-inĩ maitũ; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na rĩrĩa tũmũhoyagĩra twĩ mbere ya Ngai Ithe witũ, nĩ tũririkanaga ciĩko cianyu tũtegũtigithĩria, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o iria ciumanaga na wĩtĩkio wanyu, o na mawĩra manyu ma kwĩnogia marĩa mũrutaga nĩ ũndũ wa wendani, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na ningĩ ũrĩa mũkiragĩrĩria mũkĩĩrĩgagĩrĩra Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Ariũ a Ithe witũ, inyuĩ mwendetwo nĩ Ngai-rĩ nĩ tũũĩ atĩ nĩ mwathurirũo nĩwe,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega twahunjagia ndwakinyire kũrĩ inyuĩ ta arĩ a ciugo theri,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> no gũkinya wakinyire wĩna hinya, na wĩna Muoyo Mũtheru, na wĩna ihoooto itangĩthanganio</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Afilipi 2:15-16			
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Inyuĩ mũkengaga ta ũtheri wa gũkũ thĩ, mũkĩonanagia mũgambo wa ũtũũro.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"P2zBlsHij0KCUphLZOkB8g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					1 Akorintho 10:31-11,1</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, tondũ ũcio-rĩ, rĩrĩa mũkũrĩa, kana rĩrĩa mũkũnyua,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana ũndũ ũngĩ o ũrĩkũ ũrĩa mwĩkaga-rĩ, ĩkagai maũndũ mothe mũkĩendaga, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>kũgoocithia, Ngai namo.  Tigagai gwĩka ũndũ ũngĩhĩngithia Ayahudi, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>kana Ayunani, o na kana kanitha wa Ngai, o ta ũrĩa niĩ na niĩ ngeragia gũkenia andũ othe na maũndũ mothe,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> itegwĩcarĩria ũndũ wa kwĩguna niĩ mwene, tiga o ũrĩa ũngĩguna andũ arĩa aingĩ, nĩ getha mahonoke.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Inyuĩ tuĩkai a kwĩgerekania na niĩ, o ta ũrĩa niĩ na niĩ ndĩĩgerekanagia na Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							   
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Andũ agima matibataragio nĩ mũthondekani niĩ njũkĩte  gwĩta andũ arĩa ehia.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"h9FjDodluUybb2Gnpp7QDA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						1 Akorintho 15:20-26,28</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna aitũ, Kristũ nĩ ariũkĩtio akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, agagĩtuĩka mũtũrio wa andũ arĩa makomete.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Amu kuona atĩ nĩ mũndũ watũmire gũũke gĩkuũ, o ũguo ningĩ nĩ mũndũ watũmire kũriũka kwa andũ arĩa akuũ gũũke o nakuo.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa andũ othe makuaga nĩ ũndũ wa Adamu, no taguo andũ othe magacokio muoyo nĩ ũndũ wa Kristũ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, o mũndũ itarĩri-inĩ rĩake: mũtũrio nĩ Kristũ na thutha nĩ andũ a Kristũ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa agoka</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>.  Thutha ũcio ihinda rĩkinye rĩrĩa rĩa mũrigĩrĩrio, rĩrĩa akane Ngai, Ithe, ũthamaki; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o rĩrĩa agakorũo eheretie wathani ũngĩ o wothe, na ũnene o wothe, o gwata hinya ũngĩ o ũrĩkũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ we ndarĩ hingo atarĩthamakaga o nginya agakorũo aigĩte thũ ciake ciothe ruungu rũa makinya make. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, thũ iria ikarigĩrĩria kũninwo nĩyo gĩkuũ.  Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa indo ciothe igakorũo irĩkĩtie gũtuĩka cia gwathagwo nĩwe,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> hĩndĩ ĩo Mũriũ o nake we mwene agatuĩka wa gwathagwo nĩ Ũcio watuire indo ciothe cia gwathagwo nĩwe,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha Ngai agĩtuĩke nĩwe maũndũ mothe biũ kũrĩ andũ o othe biũ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI					      Kũguũrĩrio 1,8. 2,25	</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ niĩ Alfa o na Omega, ũrĩa ũrĩ ho, na nowe warĩ ho, na nowe ũgũũka: maũndũ marĩa mwĩ namo, magwatagĩriei kinya o rĩrĩa ngoka.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"/Q6dt5n2mEW2HdES3rY1YA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						1 Athesalonike 4:13-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKE MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna aitũ, tũtikwenda mũikare mũrigĩtwo nĩ ũhoro wa andũ arĩa makomete</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mũtikae kũgĩa na kĩeha, ta andũ arĩa angĩ matarĩ na ũndũ merĩgĩrĩire.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ tũngĩkorũo nĩ twĩtĩkĩtie atĩ Yesu nĩ aakuire na agĩcoka kũriũka,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> no twĩtĩkie atĩ ũguo noguo Ngai akarehanĩria hamwe na Yesu arĩa makomete me thĩinĩ wake. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩkĩo twamwĩra na ũhoro wa Mwathani atĩrĩ, atĩ ithuĩ arĩa tũgakorũo tũtũire muoyo, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o ithuĩ tũtigaire o nginya rĩrĩa Mwathani akoneka, tũtikahĩta arĩa makomete o na hanini. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani we mwene nĩ agaikũrũka oime Igũrũ agĩĩtanaga na kayũ, o na mũgambo wa mũraika ũrĩa mũnene,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> naguo coro wa Ngai ũkĩhuhagwo: nao andũ arĩa makuĩte me thĩinĩ wa Kristũ nĩo makaamba kũriũka:</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na thutha wa ũguo, ithuĩ arĩa tũgakorũo tũrĩ muoyo, ithuĩ tũtigaire-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ tũkoyanĩrio hamwe nao tũtwarũo matu-inĩ, nĩguo tũgacemanie na Mwathani o kũu rĩera-inĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>tũgagĩtũũrania ũguo na Mwathani o nginya tene. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Hakĩrĩ ũguo, ũmanagĩrĩria o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ na ciugo icio.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani. 
RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Kũguũrĩrio 2, 10	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani akuuga ũũ: We ikaraga wĩ mwĩhokeku kinya o gũkua, na nĩ ngakũhe ngerenwa ya muoyo.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"9YDhDVyfKUi/kTLJfFmO7w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                1 Akorintho 12:4-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, iheo iria iheanagwo ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, no rĩrĩ, Muoyo mwene cio no ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Mĩtungatĩre o nayo nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, na Mwathani mwene yo no ũmwe.  O nayo mĩĩkĩre ya maũndũ nĩ ĩtiganĩte mĩthemba,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ĩndĩ Ngai no ũmwe, ũcio wĩkithagia maũndũ macio mothe thĩinĩ wa andũ  othe. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ aheagwo ũndũ wake ũrĩa wonanagia atĩ arĩ na Muoyo nĩ getha </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ũndũ ũcio ũgune andũ othe.  Tondũ wa kũheo nĩ Muoyo-rĩ, mũndũ ũmwe agĩaga na ũhoro wa kwaria ũrĩ ũũgĩ; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ũngĩ akagĩa na ũhoro ũrĩ ũmenyi mũkinyanĩru werekanĩrĩire na wa Muoyo  o ro ũcio; nake ũngĩ akaheo wĩtĩkio , </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o oro ũcio; ũngĩ akaheo ũhoti wa kũhonania mĩrimũ, no ũndũ wa Muoyo o ũcio  ũmwe; ũngĩ nake akaheo ũhoti wa kũringa ciama,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> ũngĩ ũrathi, ũngĩ ũhoti wa gũkũũrana mioyo; ũngĩ gũthioma thiomi, na ũngĩ ũtaũri ahote gũtaũra thiomi icio.  No rĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>maũndũ macio mothe no wĩra wa Muoyo o ro ũcio ũmwe, akĩgayagĩra andũ o ta ũrĩa ekwenda, o mũndũ mwanya, o mũndũ mwanya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 2:11</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu nĩ ekire ũguo kũu Kana ya Galilea, akĩambĩrĩria ciama ciake, agĩkĩonania ũnene wake; nao arutwo ake makĩya kũmwĩhoka.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"hZzCOi0rekedqBb5Q4Pvyg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					1 Akorintho 9:16-19. 22-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, nĩ gũkorũo o na ndatuĩka nĩ hunjagia Injiri –rĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ũcio ti ũndũ ingĩhota kwĩrahĩra, amu niĩ ndirĩ hĩndĩ itabatairio nĩ kũũhunjia, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na ingĩtiga kũhunjia Injiri, kaĩ ndagĩa na haaro-Ĩ! tondũ ingĩrutaga wĩra ũcio na kwĩendera, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ndaheo ngerenwa; no ingĩkorũo ti kwĩendera gwakwa-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩo no gũtuĩke nĩ ũramati ndĩĩhokeirũo.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, ngerenwa yakwa nĩ kĩ? Nĩ atĩrĩ, atĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ngũhunjia  Injiri, ngũmĩhunjia hatarĩ kĩndũ ĩkũrutĩrũo,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ngakĩrega kũrandũra  kĩrĩa ndĩ na kĩhooto gĩa kũheagwo ndĩ mũhunjia wa Injiri. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Amu-rĩ, o na itarĩ ngombo ya mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ, nĩ  ndetuire ngombo ya andũ othe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha nyone aingĩ makĩria magarũrũkĩte.  Kũrĩ andũ arĩa manyihĩtie hinya ngoro ngĩgĩikara ta itarĩ na hinya o na niĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha nyone acio manyihĩtie hinya magarũrũkĩte. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Ndanehaanania na  andũ othe na maũndũ mao mũthemba  o mũthemba, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>nĩguo ngeragie na njĩra ciothe gũtũma amwe mahonoke. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Na maũndũ macio mothe ndĩmekaga nĩ ũndũ wa Injiri, nĩ getha nduĩke ũmwe wa kũgwatanĩra ũguni wayo.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							    John 6:63,68</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩgambo yaku, Mwathani, nĩ muoyo na ũtũũro; wee wĩ na ndeto cia muoyo wa tene na tene</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006600"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"V2GPCPjly0em2w45fnWFNw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 Aefeso 4:30 – 5:2</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũtikanaiguithie Muoyo Mutheru wa Ngai ũũru, o we ũrĩa mwekĩrirwo rũũri nĩwe o nginya mũthenya ũrĩa wa gũkũũrwo ũgakinya. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Eheriai kũrĩ inyuĩ ũhoro wothe wa gũtũũranĩria ũũru ngoro,  o na mang’ũrĩka na marakara na kũrumana, na ningĩ mweherie muku wothe. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Tuganagai o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ, na mũkĩohanagĩra mehia o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa Ngai nake amuoheire mehia manyu, arĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ.Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, rũmanagĩrĩrai kwĩgerekania na Ngai,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ta ciana ciendetwo mũno; na mũtũũre mwendaine, o ta ũrĩa Kristũ nake aamwedire inyuĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> agĩkĩruta nĩ ũndũ witũ, nĩ getha atuĩke ihaki o na igongona rĩa kũrutĩrwo Ngai, rĩĩ na mũtararĩko ũnungĩte wega.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 6,51</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu ekuuga atĩ; Nĩniĩ mũgate ũrĩa waikũrũkire uumĩte Igũrũ, wĩ muoyo: mũndũ aarĩa mũgate ũyũ, agatũũra tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"JvIZC9ZdO0Gaa1YbYedzNg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                Aheberea 10:11-14,18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũruti o wothe wa igongona nĩ arũgamaga o mũthenya o mũthenya  agĩtungatagĩra Ngai,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na akĩrutaga magongona o ro macio kaingĩ, namo matingĩhota kweheria mehia o na rĩ.  Ĩndĩ ũyũ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> aarĩkia kũruta igongona o rĩmwe rĩa kweheria mehia rĩa kũigana nginya tene na tene, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>agĩikara thĩ guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai, eterere o nginya rĩrĩa thũ ciake igatuwo gaturua ka makinya make.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ-rĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa kwĩruta o ihinda rĩmwe, nĩ aatũmire andũ arĩa aamũre maagĩrĩre kũna o nginya tene.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩ, macio maarĩkia kũrekanĩrũo, gũtingĩcoka kurutwo ihaki rĩa mehia.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 24:42
	</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Wĩbarĩrĩreni, nĩ gũkorũo mũtiũĩ mũthenya ũrĩa Mwathani wanyu agoka.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"4VS9cwaS+Uicy9L3EwlnfQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					            2 Akorintho 8:7. 9. 13-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, na rĩrĩ, o ta ũrĩa mũingĩhĩtie maũndũ mothe-rĩ, wĩtĩkio, na kũhota kwaria,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na ũmenyo, o na kĩyo gĩtangĩnyihia, ningĩ wendani ũrĩa mũtwendete naguo-rĩ, kĩingĩhiei wega ũndũ ũyũ wa gũtugana o naguo.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Amu nĩ mũũĩ Wega ũrĩa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ aarĩ naguo, mũgakĩmenya atĩ o na aarĩ gĩtonga, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ aatuĩkire ngĩa nĩ ũndũ wanyu, nĩ getha inyuĩ mũtuĩke itonga nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa we aakĩarĩte.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Ndikuuga ũguo nĩguo andũ angĩ mehererio thĩna, na inyuĩ mũthĩne, no rĩrĩ, nĩ getha kũigananio maũndũ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ihinda rĩrĩ ũrĩa  inyuĩ mũingĩhĩtie indo ũtuĩke wa gũteithia wagi wao, nĩ getha rĩrĩa acio makaingĩhia indo,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o nao magateithia wagi wanyu; nĩguo maũndũ maigananio.  O ta ũrĩa haandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Mũndũ ũrĩa wacokereirie nyingĩ ndaarĩ kĩndũ o na kĩ aatigarĩirio, o nake ũrĩa wacokereirie tũnini ndaanyihirie.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						John 6: 63. 68</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo ciaku, wee Mwathani, nĩcio muoyo na ũtũũro: wee nĩwe wĩna ciugo cia ũtũũro wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"hNRvPfhiC0i3Ebok2RJotw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                    Aefeso. 5:21-32</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũkĩĩnyihanagĩria o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa mwĩtigĩrĩte Kristũ Inyuĩ atumia, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>athĩkagĩrai athuri anyu inyuĩ ene, o ta ũrĩa mũngĩathĩkagĩra Mwathani.  Tondũ mũndũ mũrũme nĩwe mũtwe wa mũtumia,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa Kristũ nake arĩ we mũtwe wa Kanitha, akĩrĩ o we muhonokia wa mwĩrĩ ucio.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na rĩrĩ ota o rĩa kanitha wathikagira Kristu ouguo noguo  kwagĩrĩire atĩ  atumia nao maathĩkagĩre athuri ao maũndũ-inĩ mothe.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Inyuĩ athuri-rĩ, endagai atumia anyu o ta ũrĩa Kristũ nake endire Kanitha, akĩaya kwĩneana nĩ ũndũ waguo;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha awamũre aũtherie, nĩ kũũthambia, gũthambia kũrĩa kwa maaĩ hamwe na Ũhoro, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha ahote kwĩrehere Kanitha wĩ riri, ũtarĩ na kĩmeni, kana handũ hagũtharu, kana ũndũ o na ũmwe ta ũcio; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> no ũtuĩke mũtheru na ũtarĩ gĩko. o uguo noguo athuri magĩrĩrwo nĩkwedaga atumia ao ene na o ta rĩ o mĩĩrĩ yao ene. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Mũndũ ũrĩa wendaga mũtumia wake, nĩwe wĩendaga:  nĩ ũndũ gũtirĩ kwonwo mũndũ ũthũire mwĩrĩ wake mwene; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>no nĩ kũũhe aũheaga irio na akaũikaragia wega, o ta ũrĩa Kristũ nake ekaga Kanitha: nĩ ũndũ tũrĩ ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ wake. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ nĩ atigane na ithe na nyina, agwatanio na mũtumia; nao erĩ matuĩke mwĩrĩ ũmwe.  </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ũcio nĩ ũhoro wa hitho, wĩ bata o ma; no ngiuga ũguo-rĩ, nĩ ũhoro wa Kristũ na Kanitha ndĩragweta.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 6:63;68
	</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:15},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩgambo yaku, Mwathani, ĩrĩ muoyo na ũtũũro; Wee wĩna ndeto cia muoyo wa tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"xS4BdQMcOEakmds1ZMyECg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Aheberea 9:24-28</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kristũ ndaatonyire handũ hatheru hathondeketwo nĩ moko, harĩa hahaananĩtio na harĩa ha ma; nĩ gũtonya aatonyire o igũrũ kuo kwene,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha rĩu onekage mbere-inĩ ya Ngai nĩ ũndũ witũ. Ningĩ ti getha erutage kaingĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ta ũrĩa mũthacerdoti mũnene atonyaga Handũ Harĩa Hatheru o mwaka o mwaka akuuĩte thakame ĩtarĩ yake mwene; amu kũngĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> no mũhaka angĩtũire anyariragwo kaingĩ kuuma o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa thĩ yaambĩrĩirie kũũmbwo.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩndĩ rĩu, o mahinda maya ma kũrigĩrĩria-rĩ, nĩ aguũranĩirio ihinda o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, nĩguo athengie wĩhia o gũthengia nĩ kwĩruta atuĩke wa igongona we mwene.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Na ta ũrĩa gũtuĩtwo atĩ andũ makue gĩkuũ o kĩmwe, na thutha ũcio matuĩrũo cira-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ũguo no taguo Kristũ nake, tondũ nĩ arĩkĩtie kũrutwo arĩ wa igongona ihinda rĩmwe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha akuue mehia ma andũ aingĩ, nĩ agacoka kuoneka ihinda rĩa kerĩ, gũtarĩ na mehia, nĩguo akahonokie andũ arĩa mamwetagĩrĩra.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 25:34</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Ũkani, inyuĩ mũrathimĩtwo nĩ Awa, gwatai igai rĩa ũthamaki ũrĩa mwathondekeirũo gwata rĩrĩa thĩ yombirũo.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"IxobFU3fREWCWvX9Gzlrfg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna aitũ, nĩ menyerete gũikara ndĩ mũkĩaru, na ngamenyera gũikara ndĩ mũtongu:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kũndũ guothe o na maũndũ-inĩ mothe nĩ ndutĩtwo kũhũna o na kũhũta, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na ningĩ gũtonga o na kwaga.  Nĩ hotaga gwĩka maũndũ mothe na ũndũ wake we ũrĩa ũheaga hinya. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ĩndĩ nĩ mwekire wega nĩ kũgwatanĩra na niĩ thĩna wakwa.  Nake Ngai wakwa nĩ arĩkiragĩrĩria kũmũhe kĩrĩa o gĩothe mũngĩkorũo mwagĩte, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>akĩmũtanahagĩra na ũtonga wake ũrĩa wĩna Kristũ Yesu kũrĩa kwĩ na riri.  Nake Ngai, o we Ithe witũ, arogoocagwo tene na tene. Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				
						
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai Ithe wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ atũhe muoyo wa ũũgĩ nĩ getha tũmenye wega ũtarie atĩa wetereri wa rĩĩtana rĩaku.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"xDiQzHoN7UmvGjoCRRQh+Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					              1 Athesalonike 3,12-4,2</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Mwathani aromuongerera na amũkĩrĩrĩrie wendani wa kwendana o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na wa kwendaga andũ othe, o ta ũrĩa na ithuĩ tũmwendete inyuĩ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha agatũma ngoro cianyu ciikarage irũmĩte wega, na ikorũo itarĩ na ũcuke na ii na ũtheru mbere ya Ngai, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o we Ithe witũ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa Mwathani witũ Yesu akoneka me hamwe na andũ ake othe aamũre.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Naguo ũhoro wa kũrigĩrĩria nĩ atĩrĩ, ariũ a Ithe witũ, twamũthaitha na twamũringĩrĩria thĩinĩ wa Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>atĩ o ta ũrĩa mwarutirũo nĩ ithuĩ ũhoro wa mĩthiĩre ĩrĩa mwagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũthiaga nayo nĩguo mũkenagie Ngai, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na noguo mwĩkaga-rĩ, mũkiragĩrĩrie gwĩka ũguo mũno.  Tondũ nĩ mũũĩ maũndũ marĩa twamũtaarire namo nĩ ũndũ wa Mwathani Yesu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Thaburi 85,7
	</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie  ũhonokio waku.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"a5imKXCfXEmvl2TOFkQcZQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                     Aefeso 2:4-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KURĨ ANDU A EFESO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Ngai-rĩ, tondũ wa ũrĩa tha ciake ciingĩhĩte,  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o na tondũ wa wendani ũrĩa mũnene atwendete naguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twakorirũo tũrĩ akuũ nĩ ũndũ wa mehia maitũ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ aatũmire tũcoke kũgĩa na muoyo hamwe na Kristũ na riri,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ wega wa Ngai watũmire mũhonokio, na agĩtũriũkanĩria hamwe nake,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> agĩtũikaria hamwe nake kũrĩa igũrũ, twĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mahinda-inĩ marĩa magoka akamenyithania ũrĩa Wega wa Ngai  watũmire mũhonokio, na agĩtũriũkanĩria hamwe nake,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> agĩtũikaria hamwe nake kũrĩa Igũrũ, twĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mahinda-inĩ marĩa magoka akamenyithania ũrĩa Wega wake ũingĩhĩte mũno kũrĩ ithuĩ, nĩ ũrĩa atũire atũtugaga thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, nĩ Wega wa Ngai watũmire mũhonokio nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia; naguo ũndũ ũcio ndwoimanire na inyuĩ ene: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>no kũheo mwaheirwo nĩ Ngai: na ndwakiumanire na mawĩra marĩa mwanaruta , </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mũndũ o wothe ndakanegooce.  Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ ithuĩ wĩra wa moko make, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>tũũmbĩtwo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu nĩguo twĩkage ciĩko njega.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  O iria Ngai aathondekire o mbere nĩguo atĩ tũtũũre tũciĩkaga.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI								John 3:16	</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>			   
Ngai , tondũ wa ũrĩa endete kĩrĩndĩ gĩa gũkũ thĩ, nĩ aarutire Mũrũ wake wa mũmwe,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩhokete ndakore, no agĩe muoyo wa tene na tene.  </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"uAF87WwcYE6Rx5Pgz2qyqw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    1 Akorintho 7:32-35</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, inyuĩ-rĩ, ndenda mũikare mũtegũtangĩka nĩ mĩhang’o.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Mũndũ ũtahikanĩtie ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma Mwathani, amenyage ũrĩa angĩkenia Mwathani; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>no ũrĩa ũhikanĩtie ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma thĩ, amenyage ũrĩa angĩkenia mũtumia wake. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ ũhoro wa mũtumia wĩ na mũrũme wake nĩ ũtiganĩte na wa mũirĩtu.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ũcio ũtarĩ aahika ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma Mwathani, ahotage gũikara emwamũre mwĩrĩ o na muoyo; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>no ũrĩa ũhikĩte ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma thĩ, amenyage ũrĩa angĩkenia mũthuri we. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Naguo ũhoro ũcio ndawaria nĩ getha mũgunĩke inyuĩ ene,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> ti ndĩmwĩkĩre mũhĩndo ngingo, no nĩ getha ndĩmuonie maũndũ marĩa maagĩrĩire, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ getha mũikarage mwĩheanĩte kwĩ Mwathani mũtekũgucĩrĩrio nĩ maũndũ mangĩ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							    Aefeso 1:17-18		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Kaĩ gwitũ nĩ gũũkĩrĩte mũnabii mũnene-ĩ: Ngai nĩ acereire andũ ake</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"ZwKpoukT7k2nNbTyfAz89Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					         Agalatia 5:16-25</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A GALATIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na ningĩ nguuga atĩrĩ, thiagai mũtongoretio nĩ Roho, na mũtigeka maũndũ marĩa meriragĩrio nĩ mwĩrĩ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ mwĩrĩ nĩwĩriragĩria maũndũ marĩa matangĩendwo nĩ Roho; nake Roho akenda maũndũ marĩa matangĩendwo nĩ mwĩrĩ;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ maũndũ macio merĩ nĩmahĩtanĩtie; na nĩkĩo mũtahotaga gwĩka ũrĩa mwĩendeire inyuĩ ene. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No akorũo mũtongoragio nĩ Roho, mũtiathagwo nĩ watho.  Na rĩrĩ, maũndũ ma kĩĩmwĩrĩ marĩa mekagwo nĩmoĩo o wega, namo nĩ maya:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũmaraya, na merirĩria mathũku, na ũũra-thoni, na kũhoya mĩhianano, na kũrogana, na ũthũ na kũũgitana, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na ũiru, na marakara, na ngarari, na  kwamũkana, na morutani mahĩtanu, ningĩ gũcumĩkĩra, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na kũrĩwo, na maruga marĩa mainagĩrũo nyĩmbo itaagĩrĩire, o na maũndũ mangĩ ta macio: naho ha ũhoro wamo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> ngũmwĩra na ma, o ta ũrĩa ndamwĩrire na ma rĩa mbere, atĩ andũ arĩa mekaga maũndũ ta macio,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> matikagaĩrũo ũthamaki wa Ngai.  No maciaro ma Roho nĩmo maya, nĩ wendani, na gĩkeno, na thayũ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> na gũkirĩrĩria, na gũtugana, na gwĩkana wega, na kwĩhokeka, na kũhorera, na kwĩgirĩrĩria merirĩria ma mwĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>macio-rĩ, gũtirĩ watho wa kũgiria mekagwo. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Nao andũ arĩa a Kristo Jesu nĩmarĩkĩtie kwamba mĩĩrĩ yao mũtĩ igũrũ hamwe na thuti ciayo o na merirĩria mayo.  </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Tũngĩkorũo tũtũire muoyo nĩ ũndũ wa Roho, nĩtũthiage  o tũtongoretio nĩ Roho mĩthiĩre-inĩ iitũ.  </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI					    
		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ũkĩra Muoyo Mũtheru, ũiyũrie ngoro cia etĩkĩa aku na ũmagwatie thĩinĩ wao mwaki wa rũendo rũaku.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"1O20iDA2MkGw7qr/dthIiw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Kũguũrĩrio 1:5-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu Kristũ, mũira ũrĩa mwĩhokeku, o we irigithathi rĩa arĩa akuũ, na nowe mwathi wa athamaki a thĩ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  O we ũcio ũtwenda, na watuohorire na thakame yake tuume mehia-inĩ maitũ, na agĩtũtua kĩrĩndĩ kĩa mũthamaki,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> tũtuĩke athĩnjĩri Ngai wake, o we Ithe-rĩ, ũgoocwo na Mwathani arogĩaga kũrĩ we nginya tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.  Atĩrĩrĩi, nĩ gũũka egũũka na matu, na gũtirĩ riitho rĩtakamuona, o na arĩa maamũthecire o nao mamuone; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na ndũrĩrĩ ciothe cia thĩ nĩ gũcakaya nĩ ũndũ wake.  Noguo gũgatuĩka, Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ niĩ Alfa o na Omega, nĩguo Mwathani Ngai ekuuga, ũrĩa ũrĩ ho, na nowe warĩ ho, na nowe ũgũũka, o we Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mark 11,10</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ ũrĩa ũgũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani! Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ ũthamakĩ ũrĩa ũgũũka.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"35f5Rcy7XECLtrBVUTwAPw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Aheberea 2:9-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨIRŨO  KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Yesu, tũkamuona ekĩrĩtwo thũmbĩ ya riri o na ũkaru tondũ wa ũrĩa onire thĩna wa gũkua, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha atĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa Wega wa Ngai, atuĩke wa gũcama gĩkuũ ithenya rĩa andũ othe.  Nĩ ũndũ nĩ kwamwagĩrĩire, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>We Ngai, ũrĩa indo ciothe ciombirũo ituĩke ciake, o na we waciũmbire-rĩ, akĩrehithie ciana nyingĩ kũrĩa kwĩ riri,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> atũme Mũtongoria ũrĩa wa kũmatongoria magĩe na ũhonokio aagĩrĩre o kwagĩrĩra nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa aanyamarĩkire.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ rĩrĩ, we ũtheragia andũ, nao andũ arĩa matheragio, othe hamwe moimĩte o kĩhumo kĩmwe; na nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndaconokaga akĩmeta ariũ a Ithe witũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              1 John 4,12</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Twatũũra twendaine, Ngai nĩ atũũraga thĩinĩ witũ, o naguo wendo wake ũgagĩkinyanĩra thĩinĩ witũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"1TX91WbZZEGzYlAZ/cXPyg",Verses:[],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"},Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"HJ/7M9BaskOsGlJKILSAww",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                1 Akorintho 12:12-31</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, o ta ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa mũndũ ũrĩ na ciĩga nyingĩ, na mwĩrĩ ũcio no ũmwe, nacio ciĩga ciothe ciaguo, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o na ciatuĩka nĩ nyingĩ, no mwĩrĩ o ũmwe-rĩ, ũguo no taguo ũhoro wa Kristũ ũtariĩ. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo ithuĩ twabatithirio ithuothe  nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o  ũmwe tũtuĩke mwĩrĩ o ũmwe, tũrĩ Ayahudi, kana tũrĩ Ayunani, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana twĩ ngombo kana tũtarĩ ngombo; na ithuothe tũgĩkĩnyuithio  Muoyo o ũmwe.  Amu mwĩrĩ ti wa kĩĩga kĩmwe, nĩ wa ciĩga nyingĩ.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Kũgũrũ kũngiuga: Tondũ ti niĩ guoko-rĩ, niĩ ndikĩrĩ wa mwĩrĩ ũyũ, ũguo ndũngĩtũma kwage gũtuĩka kwaguo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Nakuo gũtũ kũngiuga: Na niĩ, tondũ ti niĩ riitho-rĩ, niĩ ndikĩrĩ wa mwĩrĩ  ũyũ, ũguo ndũngĩtũma kwage gũtuĩka kwaguo.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Mwĩrĩ wothe ũngĩtuĩka na riitho itheri, kũigua twakĩiguaga na kĩ? </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ mwĩrĩ wothe ũngĩtuĩka no gũtũ gũtheri gwa kũigua nakuo-rĩ, ĩ kũnungĩra twakĩnungagĩra na kĩ?</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ nĩ atĩ Ngai nĩ ekĩrire o kĩĩga thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ o harĩa endete gĩikare.  Na rĩrĩ, ciothe ingĩtuĩka no kĩĩga kĩmwe-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mwĩrĩ naguo wakĩgĩa ha? No ũrĩa kũrĩ, nĩ atĩ ciĩga nĩ nyingĩ, no  mwĩrĩ nĩ ũmwe.  Narĩo riitho rĩtingĩhota kwĩra guoko atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ ndirĩ na bata nawe; kana mũtwe naguo wĩre magũrũ, Niĩ ndirĩ na bata na inyuĩ.  No makĩria mũno,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ iria cionagũo ii njacu kũrĩ iria ingĩ-rĩ, nĩcio itangĩtigĩka; na mĩĩrĩ iitũ kũrĩa tuonaga na gũtarĩ gwa gũtĩwo mũno, kũu nĩkuo tũheaga gĩtĩo kĩnene makĩria,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> harĩa honagwo ta harĩ thoni hagagĩtuwo haagĩrĩru gũkĩra kũrĩa kũngĩ; ĩndĩ harĩa hathaka hatirĩ ũndũ habataire gwĩkwo. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Mwĩrĩ-rĩ, Ngai nĩ kũũiguithania aũiguithanĩtie, harĩa hatingiarĩtie agakĩhahe gĩtĩo makĩria ma harĩa hangĩ, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mwĩrĩ ndũkagĩe na ũndũ ũngĩwamũkania, no atĩ ciĩga ciaguo imenyanagĩrĩre, </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>o kĩĩga na kĩrĩa kĩngĩ.  Na kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩngĩkorũo gĩkĩnyarirĩka, ciĩga iria ingĩ ciothe nĩ inyarirĩkaga hamwe nakĩo.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>  Na kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩngĩkorũo kĩheetwo gĩtĩo-rĩ, ciĩga iria ingĩ ciothe igagĩkenanĩra hamwe nakĩo. </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩu-rĩ, inyuĩ nĩ inyuĩ mwĩrĩ wa Kristũ, nake mũndũ o mũndũ wanyu nĩ kĩĩga kĩaguo.
O na thĩinĩ wa kanitha, </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai nĩ ekĩrĩte andũ amwe matuĩke o mbere atũmwo, a kerĩ anabii, a gatatũ arutani; na thutha wa ũguo kũgĩe na ũringi wa ciama,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ iheo cia ũhonokia wa mĩrimũ, na maũndũ ma ũteithania, na ma ũtabarĩri, o na ũhoro wa gũthioma thiomi. </s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384> No anga andũ othe marĩ atũmwo? No anga othe marĩ anabii? No anga othe marĩ arutani? Othe nĩ aringi a ciama?</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384> Othe nĩ ahe iheo cia ũhonania? Othe nĩ magĩthiomaga thiomi? Othe nĩ makĩhotaga gũtaũranĩra thiomi icio? </s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, wĩriragĩriei kũheo iheo ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai iria ikĩrĩte iria ingĩ. </s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384> Na hamwe na ũguo-rĩ, nĩ ngũcoka kũmuonia njĩra ĩngĩ, ĩrĩa njega makĩria. </s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Luka 4,18</s>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ andũmĩte ‘hunjagĩrie arĩa athĩĩni Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, na njohorithie arĩa mahinyĩrĩirio.</s>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"8gd9jf7qoke1Te91Pxxueg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					         1 Akorintho 15:20-26</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Kristũ nĩ ariũkĩtio akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, agagĩtuĩka mũtũrio wa andũ arĩa makomete. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Amu kuona  atĩ nĩ mũndũ watũmire gũũke gĩkuũ, o ũguo ningĩ nĩ mũndũ watũmire kũriũka kwa andũ arĩa akuũ gũũke o nakuo.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa andũ othe makuaga nĩ ũndũ wa Adamu-rĩ, no ta guo andũ othe magacokio mũoyo nĩ ũndũ wa Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, o mũndũ itariri-inĩ rĩake: mũtũrio  nĩ Kristũ, na thutha nĩ andũ a Kristũ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa agoka. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Thutha ũcio ihinda rĩkinye rĩrĩa rĩa mũrigĩrĩrio, rĩrĩa akane Ngai, Ithe, ũthamaki;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> o rĩrĩa agakorũo  eheretie  wathani ũngĩ o wothe, na ũnene o wothe, o gwata hinya ũngĩ o ũrĩkũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ we ndarĩ hingo atarĩthamakaga o nginya agakorũo aigĩte thũ ciake ciothe ruungu rũa makinya make.  Na rĩrĩ, thũ ĩrĩa ĩkarigĩrĩria kũninwo nĩyo gĩkuũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Maria nĩ ambatĩtio Ikenero, na mbũtũ cia aini cia Araika nĩ maramũkũngũĩra.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"vpE/BgCHIUiI5/Quq3dcGQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    Efeso 3:2-3,5-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a ithe witũ, mũngĩgĩkorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũhoro wa ũramati wa wega wa Ngai ũrĩa heetwo nĩ ũndũ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na mũgakorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũrĩa ndamenyithirio ũhoro ũrĩa wa hitho nĩ ũndũ wa kũguũrĩrio nĩ Ngai, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o ta ũrĩa ndamwandĩkĩire o kabere na ciugo itarĩ nyingĩ.  O ũcio ũtonirio ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ hĩndĩ ya njiaro ingĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ta ũrĩa rĩu ũrĩkĩtie kũguũrĩrio atũmwo ake atheru o na anabii nĩ muoyo. Naguo nĩ ũyũ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>atĩ andũ a ndũrĩrĩ nĩ matuĩkĩte agai hamwe na ithuĩ na ningĩ a mwĩrĩ ũmwe na ithuĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> magagĩtuĩka a ngwatanĩro ĩmwe na ithuĩ ũhoro-inĩ wa kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa kĩarehirũo nĩ Kristũ Yesu na ũndũ wa kũhunjanĩria ũhoro-ũrĩa mwega.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Mathayo2,2 		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ twonire njata yake kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ na nĩ tũũkĩte tũmũturĩrie ndu tũgooce Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"KEL3xGzmPE+zndast0U2Vw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                          Akolosai 3:1-4</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRI ANDŨ A KOLOSAI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, mũngĩkorũo nĩ mwariũkire hamwe na Kristũ </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>no kĩmathagei maũndũ marĩa ma igũrũ kũrĩa Kristũ arĩ aikaire guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Rũmbũyagiai maũndũ marĩa marĩ igũrũ na mũtigage kũrũmbũyia marĩa marĩ thĩ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ nĩ mwakuire naguo muoyo wanyu nĩ mũhithe hamwe na Kristũ thĩinĩ wa Ngai.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩa Kristũ, o we ũrĩ muoyo witũ rĩrĩa akonanio, hĩndĩ ĩo o na inyuĩ nĩmũkonanio hamwe nake mwĩ na riri.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>SEQUENCE</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska
Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Kristũ Atarĩ na wĩhia – Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ikua na ũtũũro igĩcemanio ikĩrũa
Mũnene wa ũtũũro arĩ mũkuũ agĩathana arĩ muoyo</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska
Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Twĩre Marĩa wonire kĩ njĩra-inĩ?
Nĩ ndonire mbĩrĩra ya Kristũ arĩ muoyo – na ngĩona ũkumio wa mũriũku.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Araika marĩ aira, matama ma nguo
Kristũ mwĩhoko wakwa, nĩ ariũkĩte. Nĩ akamatongoria Galilea</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska
Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ithuĩ nĩ tũĩ Kristũ ti itherũ Nĩ ariũkĩte kuuma kũrĩ akuũ </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Wee mũnene mũcindani, ũtũigwĩre tha.  Nĩ gũtuĩke guo</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska
Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       1 Akorintho 5:7-8</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu Paska iitũ nĩ athĩnjĩtwo.  Rekei tũgĩe na thigũkũ thĩinĩ wa Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"uZxNCObCPkexJci/WVey1w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Aheberea 7:23-28</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, (andũ a Israeli) a mbere nĩ aingĩ ao maatuagwo  aruti igongona, tondũ nĩ maagiragio gũtũũra wĩra-inĩ ũcio nĩ ũndũ wa gũkua:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ĩndĩ we rĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa atũũraga muoyo nginya tene,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> aikaraga arĩ mũruti igongona atarĩ hingo agatigĩra mũndũ ũngĩ wĩra ũcio.  Ningĩ nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ahotaga kũhonokia kũna kũna andũ arĩa makũhagĩrĩria Ngai mathiĩrĩire harĩ we,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> kũona atĩ atũũraga muoyo hĩndĩ ciothe nĩguo amahoyagĩre.  Tondũ rĩrĩ, nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũgĩe na mũruti igongona  mũnene ta ũcio,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> mũtheru na ũtarĩ na ũũru, kana ũũgũ, na mwamũre kũrĩ ehia , o na agatũũgĩrio o igũrũ rĩa matu-inĩ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Ndarĩ na bata wa kũrutaga magongna o mũthenya o mũthenya ta aruti igongona anene acio angĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>rĩa mbere nĩ ũndũ wa mehia make mwene, na thutha ũcio nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ  nĩ ekire ũguo  ihinda o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, rĩrĩa erutiire we mwene.  Tondũ watho-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũtuaga andũ matarĩ hinya  aruti igongona anene: ĩndĩ kiugo kĩrĩa kĩa mwĩhĩtwa,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> ũcio wokire thutha wa watho-rĩ, nĩ gĩtuĩte Mũriũ mũruti igongona mũnene, o we ũtuĩtwo mwagĩrĩru kũna o nginya tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 14,23</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: mũndũ aakorũo nĩ anyenda, arĩmenyagĩrĩra uuge wakwa; nake Awa nĩ arĩmwendaga, na nĩ tũrĩũka kũrĩ we.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"wolrTXbdgUqwgQ/Ktcwxnw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						Aroma 8:14-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHŨRE PAŨL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A ROMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, andũ arĩa othe matongoragio nĩ Muoyo wa Ngai, acio nĩo ciana cia Ngai. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Amu mũtiaheirũo muoyo wa gũtũma mũcoke kũigua ta mũrĩ ngombo, mwĩtigagĩre;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> mwaheirũo muoyo wa gũtũma mũmenye atĩ mũrĩ ciana ciake cia kwĩrererũo, na nĩguo ũtũmaga twanĩrĩre tũkiuga:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Abba, Baba! Muoyo Mũtheru we mwene nĩwe mũira, hamwe na muoyo witũ, wa gũtũmenyithia atĩ tũrĩ ciana cia Ngai: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na  rĩrĩ, akorũo tũrĩ ciana ciake, ningĩ tũrĩ agai, o agai a Ngai tũgagĩtuĩka tũrĩ a gũkayanĩrio hamwe  na Kristũ; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ũguo nĩguo tũtariĩ kũngĩgĩtuĩka atĩ nĩ tũnyamarĩkanagĩra nake, nĩ getha tũkahota o na kũgwatanĩra riri nake.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨIMBO RWA INJIRI							Kũguũrĩrio 1, 8			</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Arokumio Ithe, na Mwana, na Muoyo Mũtheru: Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ ho, na nowe warĩ ho, na nowe ũgũũka.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"sEgeSP55PkeEdaI2R6CWKg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                         Ef. 5: 21-32,6:1-4</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AEFESO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũkĩĩnyihanagĩria o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa mwĩtigĩrĩte Kristo.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Inyuĩ atumia, athĩkagĩrai athuri anyu inyuene, o ta ũrĩa mũngĩathĩkagĩra Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ mũndũ mũrũme nĩwe mũtwe wa mũtumia, o ta ũrĩa Kristo anake arĩ we mũtwe wa kanitha,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> akĩrĩ o we mũhonokia wa mwĩrĩ ũcio. Na rĩrĩ, o ta ũrĩa kanitha wathĩkagĩra Kristo,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũguo noguo kwagĩrĩire atĩ atumia nao maathĩkagĩre athuri ao maũndũ-inĩ mothe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Inyuĩ athuri-rĩ, endagai atumia anyu o ta ũrĩa Kristũ nake endire kanitha, akĩya kwĩneana nĩ ũndũ waguo;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha awamũre aũtherie, nĩ kũũthambia gũthambia kũrĩa kwa maĩ hamwe na Ũhoro, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ahote kwĩrehere kanitha  wĩ riri, ũtarĩ na kĩmeni, kana handũ hagũtharu, kana ũndũ o na ũmwe ta ũcio;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> no ũtuĩke mũtheru, na ũkaaga kaũũgũ.  O ũguo noguo athuri nao maagĩrĩirũo nĩ kwendaga atumia ao ene,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o ta arĩ o mĩĩrĩ yao ene.  Mũndũ ũrĩa wendaga mũtumia wake, nĩwe wĩendaga:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ gũtirĩ kwonwo mũndũ ũthũire mwĩrĩ wake mwene; no nĩ kũũhe aũheaga irio na akaũikaragia wega,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa Kristo nake ekaga kanitha: nĩ ũndũ tũrĩ ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ wake.  Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ nĩatigane na ithe na nyina, agwatanio na mũtumia;</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> nao erĩ matuĩke mwĩrĩ ũmwe.  Ũcio nĩ ũhoro wa hitho, wĩ bata o ma; no ngiuga ũguo-rĩ, nĩ ũhoro wa Kristo na kanitha ndĩragweta.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Inyuĩ ciana-rĩ, athĩkagĩrai aciari anyu mwĩ thĩinĩ wa Mwathani: nĩ gũkorũo gwĩka ũguo nĩkuo kwagĩrĩire. </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Tĩa thoguo na nyũkwa, (rĩu nĩrĩo rĩathani rĩa mbere rĩrĩa rĩĩ na kĩĩranĩro) nĩ getha maũndũ maku magaacĩre,</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> na ũtũũre hĩndĩ ndaya gũkũ thĩ.  Na inyuĩ maithe-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>mũtikanarakarie ciana cianyu, no kũrera mũcirerage na mũrutanĩre o na mũtaarĩre ũrĩa wa Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"wtw9FDkLb0yXBbtr5RbfeA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          1 Akorintho 12, 31-13,13.</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, wĩriragĩriei kũheo iheo ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai iria ikĩrĩte iria ingĩ.  Na hamwe na ũguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ngũcoka kũmũonia njĩra ingĩ, iria njega makĩria.  
Atĩrĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o na ingĩtuĩka atĩ nĩ thiomaga thiomi cia andũ o na cia araika, na ngorũo itarĩ na wendani-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>no njikare ta ndĩ o kĩndũ kĩa rũthuku kĩrĩa kĩnegenaga kĩaringwo, kana ta thani iria ihũrithanagio ikagamba karagaca! </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> O na ingĩkorũo nĩ menyaga kũratha mohoro, na ngamenya maũndũ mothe ma hitho o na maũndũ mothe marĩa mangĩmenyeka,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na ngorũo ndĩ na wĩtĩkio o ũrĩa mũthũngĩru kinya ngahota gũthamia irĩma, no rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nduĩke ndirĩ na wendani-rĩ, ndirĩ bata o na hanini.  O na ingĩtũũra ndutaga indo ciakwa ciothe cia gũtuga athĩni, o na ingĩheana mwĩrĩ wakwa ũcinwo,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ngorũo ndirĩ na wendani-rĩ, ndirĩ harĩa ingĩgunwo.
Wendani-rĩ, nĩ gũkiranĩrĩria ũkiranagĩrĩria na nĩ ũtuganaga; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ wendani ndũrĩ ũiru; wendani ndwĩgathaga, na ndũrĩ mwĩtĩo, na ningĩ ndũrĩ rũtũrĩko, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na ndũcaragia ũrĩa ũngĩĩguna guo mwene, o na ndũrĩ marakara, na ndwĩcokagia; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ ndũkenagĩra maũndũ marĩa matarĩ ma ũthingu, no ũhoro ũrĩa ũkenanagĩra naguo no ũrĩa wa ma. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Wendani-rĩ,  nĩ wĩtiiragĩrĩria maũndũ mothe, na ũgetĩkia maũndũ mothe, o na ũgakirĩrĩria maũndũ mothe. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Wendani ndũrĩ hĩndĩ ũngĩng’atĩka; no korũo nĩ ũrathi-rĩ, ũcio nĩ ũkeherio ũthire; na korũo nĩ gũthioma thiomi,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> icio nĩ igatiga gũthiomwo; na korũo nĩ ũmenyi wa maũndũ, ũcio o naguo no kweherio ũkeherio ũthire.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ rĩu tũmenyaga maũndũ icunjĩ-icunjĩ, o na kũratha tũkaratha ũhoro o gĩcunjĩ: </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>no hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro ũgakorũo ũũkĩte ũrĩa mũkinyanĩru, ũhoro ũcio mũtingiaru nĩ kweherio ũkeherio ũthire.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>  Rĩrĩa ndarĩ kaana-rĩ, ndaaragia ta kaana, mũiguĩre wakwa wa ũhoro naguo warĩ o wa kaana, </s>"},{ID:20,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<s1384>o na gũtarania ndaũtaranagia ta kaana: no rĩu ndanatuĩka mũndũ mũgima-rĩ, nĩ ndĩkĩtie gũte maũndũ ma wana. </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384> Amu rĩu tuonaga maũndũ na mairia, ta kuona na gĩcicio; no hĩndĩ ĩo-rĩ, tũkonaga ta andũ makĩonana ũthiũ na ũthiũ;</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384> rĩu njũĩ ũhoro o gĩcunjĩ, no hĩndĩ ĩo ngakorũo  ngĩũmenya o kũũmenya, o ta ũrĩa  niĩ ndũire menyetwo o kũmenyũo.</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩu maũndũ maya, gwĩtĩkia, na kwĩrĩgĩrĩra, na kwendana, mo matatũ-rĩ,nĩmo megũtũũra o ho; na ũrĩa mũnene wamo-rĩ, nĩguo kwendana.</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				
                              Mathayo 11,25
	</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>Awa, Mwathani wa Igũrũ o na thĩ, ndakũgatha nĩ ũndũ nĩ ũkaimbũrĩra hitho ya Ũthamaki wa Igũrũ andũ arĩa anini.</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"1Sp6c7wDFkeKhLkBzqw9/Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    Efeso 3:2-3,5-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a ithe witũ, mũngĩgĩkorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũhoro wa ũramati wa wega wa Ngai ũrĩa heetwo nĩ ũndũ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na mũgakorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũrĩa ndamenyithirio ũhoro ũrĩa wa hitho nĩ ũndũ wa kũguũrĩrio nĩ Ngai, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o ta ũrĩa ndamwandĩkĩire o kabere na ciugo itarĩ nyingĩ.  O ũcio ũtonirio ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ hĩndĩ ya njiaro ingĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ta ũrĩa rĩu ũrĩkĩtie kũguũrĩrio atũmwo ake atheru o na irori nĩ muoyo. Naguo nĩ ũyũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ andũ a ndũrĩrĩ nĩ matuĩkĩte agai hamwe na ithuĩ na ningĩ a mwĩrĩ ũmwe na ithuĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> magagĩtuĩka a ngwatanĩro ĩmwe na ithuĩ ũhoro-inĩ wa kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa kĩarehirũo nĩ Kristũ Yesu na ũndũ wa kũhunjanĩria ũhoro-ũrĩa mwega.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Mathayo2,2 		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ twonire njata ya kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ na nĩ tũũkĩte tũmũturĩrie ndu tũmũgooce Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"FplDZzavxEmXPVr4mh8Zxw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						1 Athesalonike 2:7-9.13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKE MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna aitũ, twatũũrainie na inyuĩ  tũrĩ ahoreri, o ta ũrĩa mũreri amenyagĩrĩra ciana ciake mwene. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ũguo no taguo, tondũ wa ũrĩa twamwĩriragĩria twĩna wendo-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>twakenire nĩ kũmũgaĩra Injiri ya Ngai, na to Ũhoro wiki, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>no makĩria  o na mĩoyo iitũ nayo, nĩ ũndũ nĩ mwatuĩkĩte andũ ende mũno nĩ ithuĩ.  Amu no mũkũririkana,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ariũ a Ithe witũ, ũrĩa twarutaga wĩra wa hinya o tũkĩĩnogagia, na tũkarutaga wĩra ũtukũ na mũthenya,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twamũhunjagĩria Injiri ya Ngai, nĩ getha tũtikae kũritũhĩra mũndũ o na ũmwe wanyu.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ nĩ tũcokagĩria Ngai ngatho tũtegũtigithĩria nĩ ũndũ wa rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwetĩkĩrire mũgambo wa Ngai ũrĩa mwaiguire na ithuĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>mũtiawamũkĩrire ta arĩ ũhoro wa andũ, no ta arĩ mũgambo wa Ngai-na nĩ ma-,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo ũtariĩ; na nĩguo ũrutaga wĩra waguo thĩinĩ wanyu inyuĩ mwĩtĩkĩtie.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Luka:21,36		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ta ndungata arĩa mĩhokekete, ikaragai mwĩiguĩte mahinda mothe, mũkĩhoyaga Ngai nĩ getha mũhote kũrũgama mbere ya Mũrũ wa mũndũ.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"YOPe6IjuMEabRD7dlKF4kg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					         Jakobu 3:16 - 4:3</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, nĩ ũndũ harĩa harĩ ũiru na mĩamũkano, nĩĩho harĩ ngũĩ na ciĩko ciothe cia waganu. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ĩndĩ ũũgĩ  uumaga Igũrũ o mbere nĩ mũtheru, na ningĩ wenda ũiguano, na nĩ ũcayanagĩra, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na ndũrĩ ngarari, ningĩ ũkaiyũrũo nĩ tha  o na maciaro  mega, na ndũrĩ ngariũko o na kana ũhinga. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Namo maciaro ma ũthingu nĩmo moimanaga na mahanda ma ũiguano marĩa mahandagwo nĩ arĩa ateithũrani.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  
Rĩu-rĩ, mbaara na kũhũrana -rĩ, ciumaga kũ thĩinĩ  wanyu? Githĩ itiumaga o thuti-inĩ cianyu iria irũaga ciĩga-inĩ  cianyu thĩinĩ? Mwĩriragĩria na mũkaaga kuona: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ mũũraganaga, mũkagĩa na rũitho, na mũtione kĩndũ: na ningĩ mũhũranaga na mũkarũa mbaara,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> mũgakĩaga kuona kĩndũ tondũ wa kwaga kũhoya.  Mũhoyaga, na mũtiheo, nĩ ũndũ mũhoyaga na mũhoere ũrĩa ũtaagĩrĩire,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> no getha mũitangage kĩrĩa mũngĩheo na maũndũ marĩa mwendaga gwĩkenia namo.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 11,25
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Awa, Mwathani wa igũrũ o na wa thĩ, ndakũgatha  nĩ ũndũ nĩ ũhithĩte andũ arĩa ogĩ na imenyi maũndũ macio, ũkamaguũrĩria tũkenge.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"CVzqJ5LdzkCvoeCG0jZUUA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					1 Akorintho 6:13-15,17-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mwĩrĩ-rĩ, ti wa gũtuwo wa ũmaraya, tiga ũtuĩke wa Mwathani, nake Mwathani aathage mwĩrĩ ũcio.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Na Ngai nĩ aariũkirie Mwathani, na ithuĩ o na ithuĩ nĩ gũtũriũkia agatũriũkia na ũhoti wake. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Kaĩ mũtoĩ atĩ mĩĩrĩ yanyu nĩ ciĩga cia Kristũ? Na kuona  atĩ atariĩ ũguo-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>mũgũkĩenda njoe ciĩga cia Kristũ ndĩcitue ciĩga cia mũka wa maraya? Kũroaga gũtuĩka ũguo! Na rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> mũndũ ũrĩa ũgwataine na Mwathani-rĩ, ũcio nĩ maatuĩka muoyo ũmwe nake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũragĩrai ũmaraya.  Rĩĩhia rĩngĩ o rĩothe rĩrĩa mũndũ ehagia, kĩhumo kĩarĩo kĩĩ na nja ya mwĩrĩ;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> no rĩrĩ, mũndũ wa kũhũra maraya, nĩ mwĩrĩ wake mwene ekwĩhia.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Kana hihi mũtikĩmenya atĩ mĩĩrĩ yanyu nĩ hekarũ ya Muoyo Mũtheru ũrĩa ũikaraga thĩinĩ wanyu, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa mwaheirũo nĩ Ngai? Inyuĩ-rĩ, mwene inyuĩ ti inyuĩ, nĩ ũndũ nĩ kũgũrũo mwagũrirũo,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mũgĩkĩrutĩrũo kĩndũ kĩa goro; tondũ ũcio-rĩ, maũndũ ma mĩĩrĩ yanyu, goocithagiai Ngai namo.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						1 Samuel 3:9; John 6,68 
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Aria Mwathani, nĩ ũndũ ndungata yaku nĩ ĩraigua.  Wee wĩna ndeto cia muoyo wa tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"OBN/oRqT1EanKq4ymSRYPg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                Afilipi 1:4-6;8-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ndĩmũthaithanagĩrĩra, nĩ kũhoya ndĩmũhoyagĩra ngenete,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa tũgwatanĩire na inyuĩ kũhunjanĩria Ũhoro-ũrĩa-mwega,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> kuuma o mũthenya ũrĩa wa kwambĩrĩria o nginya rĩu. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na ngakĩmenya ũndũ ũyũ na ma, atĩ we ũrĩa waambĩrĩirie wĩra mwega thĩinĩ wanyu nĩ akaũrĩkia o nginya Mũthenya ũrĩa wa Yesu Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ Ngai nĩwe mũira wakwa wa ũrĩa ndĩmwĩriragĩria inyuothe ndĩ na tha o iria ii na Yesu Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Na ũrĩa ‘hoyaga nĩ atĩrĩ, atĩ wendani wanyu ũingĩhage o kũingĩha makĩria, mũkĩongagĩrĩrũo ũmenyi o na ũkuũku wothe, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mũhotage gũkũũrana maũndũ mũgĩthuraga marĩa maagĩrĩire kũrĩ marĩa mangĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na mũtũũre mũtarĩ na ũhinga, na mũtarĩ ũndũ ũngĩmũhĩtithia, o nginya rĩrĩa Mũthenya wa Kristũ ũgakinya;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ atĩ mũtũũre mũiyũrĩtwo nĩ maciaro ma ũthingu, marĩa monekaga na ũndũ wa Yesu Kristũ, nĩ getha Ngai agoocagwo na akumagio.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Luka 3:4,6
	</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Thondekai kĩng’aratua kĩa Mwathani, rũngariai njĩra ciake.  O na andũ othe nĩ makona kũhonokania kũrĩa kwa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"C1Gip3uyPE+vHpuzlY6B8w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					1 Akorintho 12:3-7. 12-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kuuga atĩ Yesu nĩwe Mwathani atarĩ na Muoyo Mũtheru. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, iheo iria iheanagwo ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, no rĩrĩ, Muoyo mwene cio no ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Mĩtungatĩre o nayo nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, na Mwathani mwene yo no ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> O nayo mĩĩkĩre ya maũndũ nĩ ĩtiganĩte mĩthemba, ĩndĩ Ngai no ũmwe, ũcio wĩkithagia maũndũ macio mothe thĩinĩ wa andũ othe.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ aheagwo ũndũ wake ũrĩa wonanagia atĩ arĩ na Muoyo nĩ getha ũndũ ũcio ũgune andũ othe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Amu – rĩ, o ta ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa mũndũ ũrĩ na ciĩga nyingĩ, na mwĩrĩ ũcio no ũmwe, nacio ciĩga ciothe ciaguo,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o na ciatuĩka nĩ nyingĩ, no mwĩrĩ o ũmwe-rĩ, ũguo no taguo ũhoro wa Kristũ ũtariĩ. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo ithuĩ twabatithirio ithuothe nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o ũmwe tũtuĩke mwĩrĩ o ũmwe, tũrĩ Ayahudi,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> kana tũrĩ Ayunani, o na kana twĩ ngombo kana tũtarĩ ngombo; na ithuothe tũgĩkĩnyuithio Muoyo o ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"B5EAnHdW4EKbsOv8esA0cA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					1 Akorintho1:22-25</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, amu Ayahudi metagia ciama, nao Agirĩki macaragia ũũgĩ, no ithuĩ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>tũhunjagia ũhoro wa Kristũ arĩ mwambe mũtĩ-igũrũ: naguo ũcio naguo uhoro ocio nĩ mũhĩnga harĩ Ayahudi, na harĩ andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ no ũrimũ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>no kũrĩ andũ arĩa metĩtwo, Ayahudi na Agirĩki, Kristũ nĩwe hinya wa Ngai  na nĩwe ũũgĩ wa Ngai.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũkorũo ũrimũ wa Ngai ũrĩ ũũgĩ gũkĩra andũ, o naguo ũhũthũ wa Ngai nĩ ũrĩ hinya gũkĩra andũ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI								John 3:16				   
Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai , tondũ wa ũrĩa endete kĩrĩndĩ gĩa gũkũ thĩ, nĩ aarutire Mũrũ wake wa mũmwe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩhokete ndakore, no agĩe muoyo wa tene na tene.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"lNkHng9N7UqWNh2l1VtReg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    Efeso 3:2-3,5-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a ithe witũ, mũngĩgĩkorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũhoro wa ũramati wa wega wa Ngai ũrĩa heetwo nĩ ũndũ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na mũgakorũo nĩ mũiguĩte ũrĩa ndamenyithirio ũhoro ũrĩa wa hitho nĩ ũndũ wa kũguũrĩrio nĩ Ngai,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa ndamwandĩkĩire o kabere na ciugo itarĩ nyingĩ.  O ũcio ũtonirio ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ hĩndĩ ya njiaro ingĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ta ũrĩa rĩu ũrĩkĩtie kũguũrĩrio atũmwo ake atheru o na irori nĩ muoyo. Naguo nĩ ũyũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ andũ a ndũrĩrĩ nĩ matuĩkĩte agai hamwe na ithuĩ na ningĩ a mwĩrĩ ũmwe na ithuĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>magagĩtuĩka a ngwatanĩro ĩmwe na ithuĩ ũhoro-inĩ wa kĩĩranĩro kĩrĩa kĩarehirũo nĩ Kristũ Yesu na ũndũ wa kũhunjanĩria ũhoro-ũrĩa mwega.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Mathayo2,2
 		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ twonire njata yake kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ na nĩ tũũkĩte tũmũturĩrie ndu tũmũgooce Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"9cY8e0pCJkKNa4v54hv2VA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                  2 Akorintho 5:6-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ,  ũcio-rĩ, tũikaraga hingo ciothe twĩting’ũrĩtie, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>tũkĩmenyaga atĩ hĩndĩ ĩno tũtũũraga thĩinĩ  wa mwĩrĩ ta arĩ guo mũciĩ witũ, tũikaraga tũtarĩ hamwe na Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo mĩthiĩre-ĩno iitũ tũthiaga na ũhoro wa gwĩtĩkia, ti ũhoro wa kuona na maitho. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nguuga rĩngĩ atĩ tũtũũraga twĩting’ũrĩtie, na ũrĩa tũngĩenda makĩria nĩ kaba gũikara tũtarĩ thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo tũtũũranie na Mwathani ta arĩ kuo gwitũ.  Na tondũ ũcio ningĩ tũgeragia na kĩyo gũtũma akenage nĩ ũndũ witũ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o na twaakorũo tũrĩ o gũkũ mĩĩrĩ-inĩ iitũ, o na kana tũkoretwo tũthamĩte kuo. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ-rĩ, no mũhaka ithuothe tũkoneka ũrĩa tũtariĩ tũrĩ mbere ya gĩtĩ gĩa Kristũ kĩrĩa gĩa ituĩro, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha o mũndũ akaheo kĩrĩa aagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũheo nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ marĩa aaneka arĩ na mwĩrĩ, makorũo marĩ mega kana marĩ moru.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						Atũmwo 16:14</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Wee Mwathani hingũra ngoro ciitũ, na nĩ tũrĩ hunguraga ciugo cia Mwana waku.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"7E3dAMS2LUi4EF5QIFelIA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						1 Athesalonike 5:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKE MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>Aruna aitũ, ha ũhoro wa mahinda na ciathĩ-rĩ, mũtirĩ na bata mũtĩnde mũkĩandĩkĩrũo.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846>  Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũũĩ wega inyuene atĩ mũthenya wa Mwathani nĩ ũgoka o ta ũrĩa mũici okaga ũtukũ. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ moigaga atĩ: Nĩ kũrĩ thayũ, na gũtirĩ mburuga, o hĩndĩ ĩo nĩyo makahobanĩrio nĩ kwanangwo  kwa narua,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846> o ta ũrĩa mũtumia wĩna ihu akoragĩrĩrũo nĩ ruo rũa kũrũmwo;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846> nao matikahonoka o na atĩa.  No inyuĩ , ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũtikĩrĩ nduma-inĩ, atĩ mũthenya ũcio ũmũkorerere ta mũici;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846> nĩ gũkorũo inyuothe mũrĩ ciana cia ũtheri na ciana cia mũthenya.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1846>Tũtikĩrĩ a ũtukũ kana a nduma; nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩ tũtigei gũkoma toro ta acio angĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1846>no makĩria nĩ tũikarage twĩiguite na tũtahotetwo nĩ ũkoroku.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Mathayo 24,42	</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1846>Wĩhũgagei na ikaragai mwĩigwĩte, nĩ gũkorũo mũtiũĩ mũthenya ũrĩa Mwathani agoka.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1846>Alleluia
 </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"0btbzuVI10GeEcmfsLpsvg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                          1 John 3:1-2</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JOHN</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, onei wendani ũrĩa ũkĩnenehete, ũrĩa Ithe witũ atwendete naguo, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>atĩ tũtuwo ciana cia Ngai; na nĩguo tũtuĩkĩte.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ ũcio andũ a gũkũ thĩ matitũũĩ, nĩ ũndũ o nake matiamũmenyire.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Endwa akwa, rĩu tũrĩ ciana cia Ngai, na gũtirĩ kũramenyithanio ũrĩa tũgaikara thutha. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ tũũĩ atĩ o rĩrĩa we akonithanio, tũkahaanana nake; nĩ gũkorũo tũkamũona o ũrĩa atariĩ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       John 10:14</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga: Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega; nĩ njũĩ ng’ondu ciakwa mwene, o nacio ng’ondu ciakwa nĩ injũĩ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"RvkS0E3kbkiR4ubwDLELwA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                  Akolosai 3:12-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KOLOSI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, kuona atĩ mũrĩ athure nĩ Ngai, mũgagĩtuĩka  andũ atheru mendetwo nĩwe, wĩhumbei  mwĩhumbĩre  wa ngoro ũrĩa wa kũiguanĩra tha,  na wa gũtugana, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na kwĩnyihia, na kũhorera, o na gũkirĩrĩria, mũgĩkiranagĩrĩria  na mũkĩohanagĩra o mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, angĩkorũo nĩ harĩ mũndũ matetanĩtie na ũrĩa ũngĩ-rĩ;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> kĩohanagĩrei inyuene o ta ũrĩa Mwathani nake aamũoheire inyuĩ.  Ningĩ gũkĩra maũndũ macio  mothe-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>gĩagai na wendani, na nĩguo wohanagia  maũndũ mothe hamwe nĩguo maagĩrĩre kũna.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Rekei thayũ wa Kristũ ũteithũranage maũndũ mothe ngoro-inĩ  cianyu; na nĩguo mwetĩirũo mwathagwo  nĩguo, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>kuona atĩ mũrĩ a mwĩrĩ ũmwe; ningĩ mũgĩage na ngatho. Rekei Ũge Kristũ ũikarage ũngĩhĩte mũno thĩinĩ wanyu, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ũkĩmũũhĩgagia na ũũgĩ wothe; na mũrutanage inyuĩ ene, mũgĩtaaranaga na thaburi, na nyĩmbo cia Ngai,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o na nyĩmbo cia  kũguna maroho ma andũ, mũkĩinagĩra Ngai mũrĩ na Wega wake thĩinĩ wa ngoro cianyu.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Na ningĩ atĩrĩ: maũndũ marĩa mothe mũrĩĩkaga, mũkĩaria o na kana mũgĩĩka ũndũ o ũrĩkũ-rĩ, mekagei na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani Yesu, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>mũgĩcokagĩria Ngai Ithe witũ ngatho na ũndũ wake.  Inyuĩ atumia-rĩ, athĩkagĩrai athuri anyu o ta ũrĩa kwagĩrĩire andũ arĩa maikaraga thĩinĩ wa Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Na inyuĩ athuri-rĩ, endagai atumia anyu, na tigagai kũmakũũma.  O na inyuĩ ciana,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> iguagai aciari anyu maũndũ-inĩ mothe, nĩ ũndũ ũguo nĩguo ũkenagia Mwathani.  Na inyuĩ maithe-rĩ, tigagai kũrakaria ciana cianyu, mũtigatũme igĩe na kĩnyiria.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Akolosai 3:15-16	</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya. </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Thayũ wa Kristũ  ũteithũranage maũndũ mothe ngoro-inĩ cianyu; Mũgambo wa Kristũ ũikarage ũingĩhĩte mũno thĩinĩ wanyu. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"43xhls+t2EKOyEDXPiZgIg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                          1 John 4:7-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JOHN</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Endwa akwa, nĩ twendanagei, amu kwendana nĩ kwa Ngai, na mũndũ o wothe wendanaga aciarĩtwo nĩ Ngai,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na nĩ oĩ Ngai.  Ũrĩa ũtendanaga ndoĩ Ngai; amu Ngai nĩwe wendani.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũhoro ũrĩa wendani wa Ngai wonanirio naguo harĩ ithuĩ nĩ ũyũ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ Ngai nĩ aarekirie Mũriũ wake wa mũmwe oke gũkũ thĩ, nĩ getha tũgĩe muoyo nĩ ũndũ wake. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Wendani nĩ ũũ; ti atĩ nĩ ithuĩ twendaga Ngai; ĩndĩ nĩwe watwendaga ithuĩ, agĩkĩrekia Mũriũ oke atuĩke ihaki rĩa mehia maitũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       John 14:23</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			    </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Mũndũ aakorũo nĩ anyenda, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>arĩmenyagĩrĩra uuge wakwa; nake Awa nĩ arĩmwendaga, na nĩ tũrĩũka kũrĩ we.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"BAJYwhqSYkyUfdPkTPm/4g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 Aefeso 1:3-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai arogoocwo, o we Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na nowe Ithe, ũrĩa ũtũrathimĩte thĩinĩ  wa Kristũ  na irathimo ciothe cia muoyo, iria ciumaga igũrũ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>kũringana na ũrĩa aatũthurire thĩinĩ  wake thĩ ĩtanombwo, nĩ getha tũtuĩke atheru  na twage  kaũgũ agĩtuona.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na tondu wagũtwenda-rĩ getha tũtuĩke atheru  na twage  kaũgũ agĩtuona.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ni atũorereire o mbere niguo tutuike ciana ciake na ũndũ wa Yesu Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> agĩgĩĩka ũguo no ũndũ wa ũrĩa endete gũtũguna, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ getha Wega ũcio aatũitũrũrĩire na ũtana thĩinĩ wake we ũrĩa endete mũno. Na nĩ thĩinĩ wake twakũũrirũo, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ wa thakame yake, o na  tũkoherũo mehia maitũ kũringana na ũrĩa Wega wake ũingĩhĩte, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o Wega ũcio aatũingĩhĩirie na  ũndũ wa ũũgĩ wake, o na ũtaũku wake, aarĩkia gũtũmenyithia ũndũ ũrĩa wa hitho aatanyĩte gwĩka thĩinĩ wa Kristũ;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> naguo nĩguo atĩ, rĩrĩa hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njagĩrĩru ĩgakorũo ĩkinyĩte-rĩ, nĩ agacokanĩrĩria maũndũ mothe thĩinĩ wa Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> o marĩa marĩ igũrũ na marĩa marĩ gũkũ thĩ; ĩĩ-ni, o thĩinĩ wake we.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ nĩ thĩinĩ wake ithuĩ twatuirũo ũgai wa kũgayũo nĩwe, tondũ wa ũrĩa tworereirũo o mbere tũtuĩke ũguo, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>kũringana na kwenda gwake, we wĩkaga maũndũ mothe o ta ũrĩa aciragĩra gwĩka.  Ningĩ ekire ũguo nĩ getha ithuĩ tũtuĩke a gũtũma riri wake ũkumagio,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> o ithuĩ arĩa twambire kwĩrĩgĩrĩra Kristũ.  Na rĩrĩ, nĩ thĩinĩ wake o na inyuĩ, mwarĩkia kũigua ũhoro-ũrĩa –wa-ma,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo ũhoro-ũrĩa-mwega watũmire mũhonokio-rĩ, o na ningĩ mwarĩkia kũmwĩhoka-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> mũgĩĩkĩrũo rũũri nĩ kũheo Muoyo Mũtheru ũũrĩa weranĩirũo:</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> Na kũheo Muoyo Mũtheru ũguo nĩ mũtũrio wa mbere na kũonania na ma atĩ nĩ tũkagaĩrũo igai riitũ rĩothe,</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> rĩarĩkia gũkũũrũo nĩ Ngai rĩtuĩke rĩake kĩũmbe; ũguo noguo twekirũo nĩ getha riri wake ũkumagio.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              1  Athesalonike 2,13</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthikĩrĩrie Mũgambo wa Ngai ti ta rĩ mũgambo wa andũ, no ta arĩ mũgambo wa Ngai, na nĩ ma. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"6rP04bT6b0+mQ7IDkup9Pg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 Aroma 4:13.16-18;22</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MUTHURE PAŨLŨ KŨRI ANDŨ A ROMA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna akwa, kĩĩrĩro gĩkĩ gĩa atĩ Iburahimu agatuĩka mũgai wa kũgaĩrũo thĩ yothe, nderĩirũo we mwene, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o na kana arĩa a mbeũ yake, nĩ ũndũ wa gwathĩkĩra watho, no nĩ ũndũ wa ũthingu ũrĩa uumanaga na wĩtĩkio.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũguo, ũthingu ũcio uumanaga na wĩtĩkio, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha wonekage no ũndũ wa Wega wa Ngai; nĩguo ũndũ ũrĩa mwĩranĩre wonekage </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>hatarĩ nganja nĩ andũ othe a mbeũ ya Iburahimu, to arĩa maaheirũo ũhoro wa watho oiki, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>no ningĩ arĩa o nao metĩkĩtie wĩtĩkio ta ũcio wake.  Amu iburahimu ũcio-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa ũhoro wake wandĩkĩtwo, atĩ, Nĩngũtũite ithe wa ndũrĩrĩ nyingĩ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> maitho-inĩ ma ũcio etĩkĩtie nĩwe ithe witũ ithuothe, o maitho-inĩ ma Ngai, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>we ũriũkagia arĩa makuĩte, na aaragia ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa matarĩ ho o ta marĩ ho.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Iburahimu, o na kũngĩtuĩka ũndũ ũcio erĩirũo ndũngĩĩrigĩrĩrĩka-rĩ,
 </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>nĩaawĩtĩkĩtie, agĩgĩtũũra erĩgĩrĩire atĩ nĩagatuĩka ithe wa ndũrĩrĩ nyingĩ, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>kũringana o na ũhoro ũrĩa aaheirũo akĩĩrũo ũũ, Ũguo noguo a mbeũ yaku makaigana.
 
 Naguo ũhoro ũcio agĩgĩtuĩrũo ta arĩ ũthingu e naguo</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani arĩgathagwo hĩndĩ ciothe, o we Mũrungu mwene ũhonokio witũ.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"DTHm+1WO/UKAVf5bF98SgA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Aheberea 4:14-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, kuona atĩ twĩ na mũruti igongona na mũnene ũrĩa wĩ bata ma, na ũhungurĩte agakinya o Igũrũ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩwe Yesu Mũrũ wa Ngai, nĩ tũrũmieni ũhoro ũrĩa tũtũire tuumbũraga. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Amu tũtirĩ na mũruti  igongona mũnene ũtangĩhota gũtũiguĩra tha maũndũ-inĩ maitũ ma kwaga hinya; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa twĩ nake aanagerio maũndũ-inĩ mothe o ta ithuĩ, tiga atĩ ndaigana kwĩhia o na atĩa.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ ũcio nĩ tũthengerei gĩtĩ-inĩ gĩa ũthamaki kĩrĩa kĩa Wega wa Ngai tũmĩrĩirie, nĩ getha tũkaiguĩrũo tha, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na tuone Wega wake wa gũtũteithagia hĩndĩ ĩrĩa tũbataire.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Marko 10,45</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu Kristũ ndokire atungatanĩre, na arute muoyo wake ũtuĩke wa gũkũũra andũ aingĩ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"T258KYClK0O9lb8KiOY1Ow",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Aheberea 5:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũruti mũnene o wothe aathurũo kũrĩ andũ, nĩ atuagwo wa kũrũgamagĩrĩra andũ maũndũ-inĩ marĩa makoniĩ Ngai,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha arutage maruta o na magongona nĩ ũndũ wa mehia. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake nĩ ahotaga gũkirĩrĩria arĩa matarĩ ogĩ na arĩa mahĩtagia, ahoreire, kuona atĩ we mwene nĩ atangĩkaga nĩ kwaga hinya.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Na tondũ ũcio nĩ abatairio nĩ kũrutaga horohio nĩ ũndũ wa mehia make mwene, o ta ũrĩa amĩrutaga nĩ ũndũ wa mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Na gũtirĩ mũndũ wĩheaga gĩtĩo kĩu we mwene, tiga o akorirũo etĩtwo nĩ Ngai o ta ũrĩa Harũni etirũo. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũguo no taguo Kristũ nake ataigana gwĩkumia we mwene atĩ atuwo mũruti mũnene wa igongona, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũtuwo aatuirũo nĩ ũrĩa wamwĩrire atĩrĩ: Wee nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa, niĩ ũmũthĩ nĩ ndagũciara:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ta ũrĩa oigire handũ hangĩ, atĩrĩ: We wĩ mũruti igongona o nginya tene, o ta ũrĩa Melkisedeki aatariĩ.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 8,12
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩ: nĩ Niĩ ũtheri wa thĩ: mũndũ aanũmĩrĩra niĩ arĩgĩaga na ũtheri wa muoyo</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"dD677G9fjEaPDZgpKWFqQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 Aefeso 4:17. 20-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, niĩ ni nguuga atiri, na ngamuumburĩra ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Mwathani, atĩ mũtigacoke gũthiaga na mĩthiĩre ĩrĩa andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ mathiaga nayo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> marũmanĩrĩire na uungumania wa meciria mao.  No inyuĩ-rĩ, ũguo tiguo mwĩrutĩte ũhoro wa Kristũ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>mũngĩkorũo ti-itherũ nĩ mũiguĩte mũgambo wake, na mũkarutwo ũhoro mwĩ thĩinĩ wake, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o ũhoro-wa-ma ũrĩa wĩ na Yesu.  Ha ũhoro wa mĩthiĩre yanyu yambere-rĩ, ĩaũrei mũndũ ũrĩa wa tene,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa ũthũkĩte nĩ ũndũ wa kũrũmĩrĩra merirĩria ma kũhenania; na merũhio ma muoyo o na meciria manyu, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na mwĩhumbe mũndũ ũrĩa mwerũ, o ũrĩa wombirũo ahanaaine na Ngai, e na ũthingu, na ũtheru ũrĩa uumanĩte na ũhoro-wa-ma.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 4,4
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ti mũgate wiki ũtũũragia mũndũ muoyo, no kiugo o gĩothe kĩrĩa kiumaga kanua ka Ngai.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"R87Pk+VUnECwj7XpOxJq6g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						       2 Pet. 3:8-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PETER: MARĨA MA KEERĨ:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, endwa akwa, mũtikanariganĩrũo nĩ ũndũ ũyũ ũmwe, atĩ kũrĩ Mwathani mũthĩ ũmwe no ta mĩaka ngiri  o na mĩaka ngiri no ta mũthenya ũmwe. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ha ũhoro wa kũhingia kĩĩranĩro gĩake-rĩ, mwathethũka, nĩ ũndũ ndendaga mũndũ o na ũmwe ore,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> no atĩ othe matuĩke a kwĩrira.  No rĩrĩ, mũthenya ũrĩa wa Mwathani nĩ ũgũka o ta mũici;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> naguo mũthenya ũcio-rĩ nĩguo Igũrũ rĩkarindũka na mũrurumo mũnene,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nacio ciũmbe  iria itũire igũrũ nĩ ikahĩa nĩ mwaki mũnene ithire, nayo thĩ o na indo ciothe iria ithondeketwo kuo nĩ igacinwo biũ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Kũona atĩ indo icio ciothe itirĩ hingo itagathira ũguo-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>inyuĩ  mwagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũikara namĩikarĩre Itariĩ atĩa, ũhoro-inĩ wa mĩtũũrĩre ya ũtheru, na ya kwĩyamũrĩra Ngai, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>mũgĩtanyaga na mũkĩĩriragĩria mũno mũthenya ũcio wa Ngai ũgĩgakinya? </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Naguo wakinya-rĩ nĩrĩo Igũrũ rĩkagwatio mwaki rĩthire, nacio ciumbe iria itũire igũrũ ihĩe nĩ mwaki mũnene itweke.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Ĩndĩ kũringana na ũrĩa eranĩire, nĩ gũtanyaga kũona igũrũ rĩerũ o na thĩ njerũ, o kuo kũrĩa gũtũũraga ũthingu. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, endwa akwa, kuona atĩ no mũtanyaga kuona maũndũ macio,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> ĩkagĩrai kĩyo nĩ getha mũgakorũo mũrĩ na thayũ, na mũtarĩ na kĩmeni ngoro o na kana ũcuke mũkĩonagwo nĩwe.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Luka 3:4-6		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Thondekai kĩng’aratua kĩa Mwathani, rũngariani njĩra ciake.  Andũ othe nĩ makona kũhonokio kũrĩa kwa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"UVs2AqUJyk6xLpugnZTCHQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ	1 John 3: 1-3</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JOHN MARĨA MA MBERE</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, onei wendani ũrĩa ũkĩnenehete, ũrĩa Ithe witũ atwendete naguo, atĩ tũtuwo ciana cia Ngai;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩguo tũtuĩkĩte.  Tondũ ũcio andũ a gũkũ thĩ matitũũĩ, nĩ ũndũ  o nake matiamũmenyire.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Endwa akwa, rĩu tũrĩ ciana cia Ngai, na gũtirĩ kũramenyithanio ũrĩa tugaikara thutha.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nitui ati oriria we akonithanio tukahanana nake ;nigukorwo tukamuona o uria atariĩ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Na mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũmwĩrĩgĩrĩire ũguo nĩ gwĩtheria etheragia, o ta ũrĩa we nake atherete.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"I8ORf5yc9Uad/6fuJPiCyg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF7F00FF"}}},
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    Aroma 16:25-27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AROMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a ithe witũ, na rĩrĩ, Ngai nĩwe ũhotaga kũmwĩkĩra hinya na njĩra ĩrĩa nyonanie nĩ ũhoro ũrĩa mwega hunjagia,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o ũrĩa wa kwanĩrĩra ũhoro wa Yesu Kristũ, na nĩguo ũringaine na kũguũranĩrio kwa ũhoro wa hitho</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa watũire ũhithĩtwo ũgaikara o ũguo ngiri mahinda marĩa ma mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>naguo rĩu nĩ kuumĩrio uumĩrĩtio, na kũringana na ũrĩa Ngai, we ũtũũraga tene na tene aathanire-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũmenyithagio andũ a ndũrĩrĩ ciothe na Maandĩko marĩa ma anabii, nĩ getha matuĩke aathĩku ũhoro-inĩ wa wĩtĩkio.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake we Ngai, o we wiki mũũgĩ-rĩ, arotũũra agoocagwo na njĩra ya Yesu Kristũ nginya tene na tene. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Luka 1,38</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>One ndungata ya Mwathani, nĩ njĩkwo o ta ũrĩa woiga.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"ueVEye+UiE6TIXiTinRXaQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>					                          
GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AGALATIA</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>	
Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũndũ angĩkorũo ahĩtĩtie ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ-rĩ, inyuĩ mũkoragwo mwĩ na Roho mũcokagĩrĩriei mũhoreire ngoro. </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> Wĩmenyagĩrĩre wee mwene ndũkae kũgerio o nawe.  Hũthanagĩriai o mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ maũndũ marĩa  mamũritũhagĩra,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha, mũgĩĩka ũguo, mũhingagie watho wa Kristo.  Nĩ gũkorũo mũndũ o wothe angĩĩtua  atĩ nĩ mũndũ ma,  rĩrĩa arĩ mũndũ hatarĩ-rĩ, nĩ kwĩhenia ekwĩhenia.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ kaba o mũndũ aroragie wĩra wake mwene; na hĩndĩ ĩo-rĩ, ũndũ wake wa kwĩrahĩra nĩũgakorũo wĩ wake we mwene, na ti wa mũndũ ũngĩ.  Tondũ-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe nĩarĩĩkuuagĩra o mũrigo wake mwene.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, nĩ wega mũndũ ũrĩa ũkũrutwo  Ũhoro wa Ngai magayanagĩre na mũmũruti indo ciothe njega.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Mũtikanahenio; Ngai ndangĩnyũrũrio; amu kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩrĩa  mũndũ  ekũhanda nokĩo akagetha. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, mũndũ ũrĩa ũkũhanda o maũndũ ma kũguna mwĩrĩ wake mwene-rĩ, ũcio nĩ kũgetha akagetha ũhoro wa kũbutha uumanĩte na mwĩrĩ ũcio wake; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>no ũrĩa ũkahanda maũndũ ma gũkenia Roho-rĩ, ũcio nĩakagetha muoyo ũtagathira, uumĩte kwĩ Roho ũcio. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ tũtikananogio nĩ gwĩkaga wega; nĩ ũndũ twaaga kũũrũo nĩ hinya, nĩtũkagetha hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yerekereire  yakinya.  Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> o rĩrĩa rĩothe  twona ihinda  rĩagĩrĩru, nĩtwĩkage andũ othe wega, na makĩria nĩ andũ a nyũmba ya arĩa metĩkĩtie.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI									
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ gũkĩra maũndũ macio mothe-rĩ, gĩagai na wendani, na nĩguo wahanagia maũndũ mothe hamwe nĩguo maagĩrĩre kũna.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>		</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"4Vyo5zrMY0SYiyFvm2pblA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                  1Jn. 3:1-2, 21-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA RĨA MA MBERE MA JOHANA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Onei wendo ũrĩa Ngai Ithe witũ agĩtwendeete naguo kinya tũgeetagwo ciana ciake! Hatirĩ nganja tũrĩ ciana ciake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Kĩrĩa gĩtũmĩĩte andũ a thĩ maage gũtũmenya, nĩ tondũ nĩmaagire kũmũmenya we.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Eendwa aakwa, ithuĩ rĩũ twĩ ciana cia Ngai, na gũtirĩ kũramenyeka wega biũ ũrĩa  tũgaakorwo tũhaana thuthainĩ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No nĩtũũĩ atĩ rĩrĩa Kristũ akoonekana tũgaakorwo tũhaana taake, tondũ nĩtũkaamuona o ta ũrĩa ahaana kũna.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Kwoguo eendwa aakwa, angĩkorwo thamiri ciitũ itiratũtuĩra, nĩtũrĩkoragwo na ũũmĩrĩru mbere ya Ngai. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ngai nĩatũheaga kĩrĩa twamũhooya nĩ tondũ nĩtũrũmagĩrĩra maathani make na nĩtwĩkaga maũndũ marĩa mamũkenagia. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩathani rĩake nĩ atĩ twĩtĩkie Mũũriũ wake Jesũ Kristũ, na twendanage mũno na ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa Kristũ aatwathire. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Andũ othe arĩa maathĩkagĩra maathani ma Ngai matũũraga thĩinĩ wa Ngai, naake agatũũra thĩinĩ wao.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩĩrĩ, tũmenyaga atĩ Ngai aikaraga thĩinĩ witũ na ũndũ wa Roho ũrĩa atũheete.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              
	
Akolosai 3:15-16		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Thayũ wa Kristũ ũteithũranage maũndũ mothe ngoro-inĩ cianyu: Mũgambo wa Kristũ ũikarage ũingĩhĩte mũno thĩinĩ wanyu. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"DBNQxdsp7USdQZp0JpfxOw",Verses:[{
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                  1Jn. 3:1-2, 21-24"},{ID:2,
Text:"GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA RĨA MA MBERE MA JOHANA:"},{ID:3,
Text:"Onei wendo ũrĩa Ngai Ithe witũ agĩtwendeete naguo kinya tũgeetagwo ciana ciake! Hatirĩ nganja tũrĩ ciana ciake."},{ID:4,
Text:"  Kĩrĩa gĩtũmĩĩte andũ a thĩ maage gũtũmenya, nĩ tondũ nĩmaagire kũmũmenya we.  "},{ID:5,
Text:"Eendwa aakwa, ithuĩ rĩũ twĩ ciana cia Ngai, na gũtirĩ kũramenyeka wega biũ ũrĩa  tũgaakorwo tũhaana thuthainĩ. "},{ID:6,
Text:" No nĩtũũĩ atĩ rĩrĩa Kristũ akoonekana tũgaakorwo tũhaana taake, tondũ nĩtũkaamuona o ta ũrĩa ahaana kũna.  "},{ID:7,
Text:"Kwoguo eendwa aakwa, angĩkorwo thamiri ciitũ itiratũtuĩra, nĩtũrĩkoragwo na ũũmĩrĩru mbere ya Ngai. "},{ID:8,
Text:" Ngai nĩatũheaga kĩrĩa twamũhooya nĩ tondũ nĩtũrũmagĩrĩra maathani make na nĩtwĩkaga maũndũ marĩa mamũkenagia. "},{ID:9,
Text:"Rĩathani rĩake nĩ atĩ twĩtĩkie Mũũriũ wake Jesũ Kristũ, na twendanage mũno na ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa Kristũ aatwathire. "},{ID:10,
Text:" Andũ othe arĩa maathĩkagĩra maathani ma Ngai matũũraga thĩinĩ wa Ngai, naake agatũũra thĩinĩ wao.  "},{ID:11,
Text:"Na rĩĩrĩ, tũmenyaga atĩ Ngai aikaraga thĩinĩ witũ na ũndũ wa Roho ũrĩa atũheete."},{ID:12,
Text:"Ciugo cia Mwathani"},{ID:13,
Text:"RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              
	
Akolosai 3:15-16		
Alleluya. Alleluya."},{ID:14,
Text:"Thayũ wa Kristũ ũteithũranage maũndũ mothe ngoro-inĩ cianyu: Mũgambo wa Kristũ ũikarage ũingĩhĩte mũno thĩinĩ wanyu. "},{ID:15,
Text:"Alleluia"}],
Text:"GITHOMO KIA IGIRI"},{Guid:"Mg8N8QdF5kyw6VuE3OYpTQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          1 Akorintho 15:45-49</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũndũ ũrĩa wa mbere wetagwo Adamu aatuĩkire mũndũ wĩ muoyo.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Adamu ũrĩa wa kũrigĩrĩria-rĩ, nĩ muoyo wa gwĩkanagĩra muoyo.  No rĩrĩ, mwĩrĩ ũcio wa muoyo tiguo ũgĩaga mbere,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> no nĩ ũrĩa wa ndũire; na thutha waguo gũgoka ũcio wa muoyo.  Mũndũ wa mbere nĩ wa na thĩ ĩno, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o wa tĩri-inĩ; ĩndĩ mũndũ wa kerĩ nĩ wa na Igũrũ.  O ta ũguo ũcio wa tĩri aatariĩ, noguo arĩa a tĩri nao matariĩ; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na ta ũguo ũcio wa Igũrũ atariĩ, noguo arĩa a Igũrũ nao matariĩ.  Na ta ũrĩa twagĩire na mũhianĩre wa ũcio wa tĩri-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> no taguo tũkagĩa na mũhianĩre wa ũcio wa Igũrũ o naguo.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              John 13,34
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Ngũmũhe rĩathani rĩerũ, nĩ atĩ mwendane, o ta ũguo niĩ ndĩmwendete.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"8NLM7pn8DkS9OicRlL8IXw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          1 Akorintho 15:12.16-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ũhoro wa Kristũ ũngĩkorũo ũhunjagio atĩ nĩ kũriũkio aariũkirio-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>kaĩ anyu amwe magĩcokaga kuuga atĩ gũtirĩ kũriũka kwa arĩa akuũ atĩa? Amu korũo andũ arĩa akuũ matiriũkagio-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Kristũ o nake ndakĩigana kũriũkio; na korũo Kristũ ndaigana kũriũkio, gwĩtĩkia kwanyu gũtikĩrĩ kĩene; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>mehia manyu  o na rĩu mũgĩtũire o namo.  O na ningĩ andũ arĩa marĩkĩtie gũkoma me thĩinĩ wa Kristũ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o nao nĩ kũũra makĩũrĩte.  Kũngĩgĩkorũo kwĩrĩgĩrĩĩra kũrĩa twĩrĩgĩrĩire Kristũ gũkoniĩ o muoyo  ũyũ tũtũire-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ithuĩ tũrĩ a kũũmĩrũo tha gũkĩra andũ arĩa angĩ othe. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ, nĩ atĩ Kristũ nĩ ariũkĩtio akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, agagĩtuĩka mũtũrio wa andũ arĩa makomete.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Luk 6,23</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Kenai na mũtũhatũhe; nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, igai rĩanyu nĩ rĩnene o Igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"jSPjcjOcG0C7EMhHuV5YuA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Aheberea 4:12-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨIRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũgambo wa Ngai ũrĩ muoyo, na ũrĩ hinya, na nĩ mũgĩ kũrũga rũhiũ o ruothe rũnoretwo mĩena yerĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ũgatheca ũgakĩgayũkania muoyo na ũtũũro, o na ũgaatĩa mĩthimo na ũkagayũkania mahĩndĩ ma maguta,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ nĩ ũhiũhaga gũkũũrana meciria ma ngoro o na ũrĩa icirĩire gwĩka.  Na gũtirĩ kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩũmbe gĩtonekete mbere yake; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>no rĩrĩ, indo ciothe ciikaraga itarĩ humbĩre, no iguũrĩtio maitho-inĩ make, we mwene ũhoro witũ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Aefeso 1:17-18</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ atũhe o mũndũ muoyo wa ũũgĩ, nĩ getha tũmenye ũtarii atia wetereri wa rĩĩtana riitũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"p+MtnmidbEyNcyFcmpUPew",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ							Aefeso 1:17-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ, o we Ithe witũ mwene riri, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>amũhe o mũndũ muoyo wa kũmũũhĩgia na wa kũmũguũrĩria maũndũ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>muongererũo ũmenyi wa kũmenyana nake; ningĩ atĩ maitho manyu ma ngoro mathererũo nĩ ũtheri,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha mũmenye wega kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩa mwĩtĩirũo nĩwe mũgĩe nakĩo; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o na mũmenye ũrĩa igai rĩake rĩĩ na riri rĩingĩhĩte ta arĩ ũtonga mũnene, na rĩo nĩrĩo rĩa andũ ake aamũre;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ mũmenye ũrĩa ũhoti wake ũnenehete hatarĩ mũhaka, o ũcio aatũkinyĩirie ithuĩ arĩa twĩtĩkĩtie,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> kũringana na ũrĩa arutaga wĩra na hinya wake mũnene, o hinya ũcio onanirie akĩrutaga wĩra wake thĩinĩ wa Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> rĩrĩa aamũriũkirie oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, akĩmũikaria guoko-inĩ gwake kwa ũrĩo kũrĩa Igũrũ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> atũũgĩrĩtio mũno igũrũ rĩa wathani o wothe, na ũthamaki, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na ũhoti, na ũnene, na igũrũ rĩa marĩĩtwa mothe marĩa magwetagwo, to mahinda maya moiki, no ningĩ o na mahinda marĩa magoka.  </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Na ningĩ akĩiga maũndũ mothe ruungu rũa magũrũ make maathagwo nĩwe, agĩkĩmũtua mũnene wa gwathaga maũndũ mothe harĩ kanitha; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>naguo nĩguo mwĩrĩ wake, o ũiyũru wake, we ũiyũrĩte maũndũ mothe o na kũndũ guothe.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076>RŨIMBO RWA INJIRI							Mathayo 28:19-</s>20	
		
<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Thiĩi na mũgatũme andũ a ndũrĩrĩ ciothe.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>  One: niĩ ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ mĩthenya yothe, o nginya ithirĩro rĩa mahinda maya</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"rgah5MR5dEekMtG+RRG7Xw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          2 Akorintho 5: 17-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA KEERĨ:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ angĩkorũo arĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ, nĩ agarũrũkĩte agatuĩka mũndũ ũngĩ mwerũ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> maũndũ marĩa ma tene nĩ mathirĩte; nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ matuĩkĩte mangĩ merũ.  Namo maũndũ mothe moimaga kũrĩ Ngai,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o we watũiguithanirie nake we mwene thĩinĩ wa Kristũ, na agĩtũtua ndungata cia gũtungatĩra ũhoro ũcio wa ũiguithanio;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo wa atĩ Ngai aarĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ, agaikara akĩiguithanagĩria kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ nake we mwene,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> agĩtigaga gũtarĩra andu mahĩtia mao, na atĩ ũhoro ũcio wa ũiguithanio nĩ aũigĩte kũrĩ ithuĩ tũũheanage.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ wa ũguo, tũkĩrĩ arekio mareketio a kwarĩrĩria Kristũ, o ta arĩ Ngai ũrathaithana na tũnua twitũ; twamũthaitha ithenya rĩa Kristũ atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> ĩtĩkĩrai kũiguithanio  na Ngai.  Ngai nĩ aatũmire ũcio ũtarĩ hingo aamenyire wĩhia atuĩke o wĩhĩa arĩ we ithenya riitũ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha ithuĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa twĩ thĩinĩ wake, tũtuĩke o ũthingu wa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Luka 15,18</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>	
Nĩ ngũũkĩra ‘thiĩ kũrĩ Awa, ngamwĩre atĩrĩ: Awa, nĩ njĩhĩtie Igũrũ, o na ngakwĩhia wee.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"0NZMBHWo0Ey86xFXlv/bEg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          1 Akorintho 10: 1-6,10-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Amu rĩrĩ, ariũ a Ithe witũ ndikwenda mwage kũmenya atĩ maithe maitũ arĩa a tene, othe maaikaraga mahumbĩirũo nĩ itu rĩrĩa, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na magĩtuĩkania othe maaĩ-inĩ ma iria rĩrĩa; othe magĩgĩtuĩka ta makĩbatithĩtio matuĩke andũ a Musa, marĩ itu-inĩ rĩu o na iria-inĩ rĩu; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na magĩtũũra marĩaga irio o imwe othe, iria cia muoyo, na makanyuaga gĩa kũnyua o kĩmwe othe, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o kĩrĩa gĩa muoyo; nĩ gũkorũo maanyuaga maaĩ moimĩte ndũmba-inĩ ya ihiga yarĩ ya muoyo ĩrĩa yarũmanagĩrĩra  nao, nayo ndũmba ĩo ya ihiga nĩ Kristũ.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, arĩa aingĩ mũno-rĩ, Ngai ndaigana gũkenio nĩo; amu nĩ kũng’aũranio mang’aũranĩirio nĩwe werũ-inĩ.  Rĩu-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> maũndũ macio maatuĩkire ta igerekanio cia ũhoro witũ, nĩ getha ithuĩ tũtikanatuĩke  erirĩria a maũndũ moru ta ũrĩa andũ acio maameriragĩria.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>O na mũtigatete, ta ũrĩa andũ acio amwe maatetire, na magĩkĩninwo nĩ ũrĩa mũninani.  Na rĩrĩ, maũndũ macio mothe monĩre maarĩ ta igerekanio,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na makĩandĩkwo matuĩke ma gũtũtaara ithuĩ, o ithuĩ tũkinyĩrĩirũo nĩ marigĩrĩrio ma mahinda maya ma ndũire.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ ũkwĩĩra atĩ nĩ ehandĩte ki, nĩ emenyagĩrĩre ndakae kũgũa.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 4,17
	</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani akiuga atĩ: Wĩrirei; tondũ ũthamaki wa Igũrũ nĩ ũkuhĩhĩirie.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"5GB7NLt1l0a3MeuMqv902g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 2 Akorintho 12:7-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, na rĩrĩ, tondũ wa ũrĩa maũndũ macio ndanaguũrĩrio maarĩ manene ũũ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo ndikae gwĩtũũgĩria nĩ ũndũ wamo gũkĩra kwaagĩra, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ndarehithirio ũndũ ũhaaana ta mũigua mũnene ũthecete mwĩrĩ wakwa, ũikarage ũrĩ ũrekio wa Chaitani a’tũũkũrage, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ndikae gwĩtũũgĩria gũkĩra kwagĩra.  Naho ha ũhoro wa ũndũ ũcio, nĩ ndathaithire Mwathani mahinda matatũ atĩ aũnjehererie.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake ũrĩa aanjĩrire nĩ atĩrĩ: Wega wakwa nĩguo ũkũiganĩte, nĩ gũkorũo ũhoti wakwa ũiganagĩra harĩa harĩ ũhinyaru. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ ũcio-ri, ndirĩ hingo itarĩĩrahaga nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ marĩa njagĩte hinya nĩ ũndũ wamo, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ngenete mũno, nĩ getha ũhoti wa Kristũ ũikarage na niĩ.  Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, rĩrĩa ngwaga hinya, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na rĩrĩa ngũrurũkwo, na rĩrĩa nyamarĩkĩte, na rĩrĩa ngũnyarirũo, o na rĩrĩa ngũtuurio nĩ ũndũ wa Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nĩrĩo njiguaga o wega, tondũ-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa hinyarĩte, nĩyo ngoragwo ndĩ na ũhoti.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							    John 1:14.12
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Uuge  ũgĩgĩtuĩka mũndũ na agĩtũũra thĩinĩ witũ.  No arĩa othe maamwĩtĩkĩrire acio akĩmahotithia gũtuĩka ciana cia Ngai.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"b+M1NXy73EKsQ2K3YVsEKA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    Atumwo  10:34-38</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Peter agĩitĩka kwaria akiuga atĩrĩ: Ti-itherũ ndĩ kuona atĩ Ngai ndatĩagĩra andũ maũthĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>no thĩinĩ wa ndũrĩrĩ ciothe mũndũ ũrĩa ũmwĩtigagĩra na ageka maũndũ ma ũthingu nĩ etĩkagĩrũo nĩwe. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ: Ũhoro ũrĩa aarekeirie ciana cia Israeli, o ũrĩa wa kũhunjanĩria ndeto njega cia thayũ ũrĩa wonekaga na Yesu Kristũ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nake nĩwe Mwathani wa guothe.  Ũhoro ũcio-rĩ, inyuĩ nĩ mũũĩ, naguo nĩguo wahunjanĩirio Judea guothe wambĩrĩirio  o Galilea,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> thutha wa rĩrĩa John aaheanire ũhoro wa atĩ andũ mabatithio.  Naguo nĩ wa Yesu wa Nazareth,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa Ngai aamũitĩrĩirie Muoyo Mũtheru o na hinya; nake agĩcamba agĩĩkaga maũndũ mega, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na akĩhonagia andũ arĩa othe maatũire manyariragwo nĩ mũcukani: nĩ gũkorũo Ngai aarĩ hamwe nake.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Marko 9,7 </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Thĩinĩ wa itu gũkiuma mũgambo wa Ithe akiuga atĩrĩ: “Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa, nyendete mũno: mũiguagei”.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"dFu5mo0c6E2OiUqkjH2FDA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                  2 Akorintho 5:14-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, wendani ũrĩa Kristũ atwendete naguo nĩguo ũtũhatagĩrĩria, nĩ ũndũ tũonaga atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ mũndũ ũmwe nĩ aakuire ithenya rĩa andũ othe, na tondũ ũcio gũkua nĩ maagĩkuire othe.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Ningĩ atĩrĩ, aakuire ithenya rĩa andũ othe, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha arĩa matũũraga muoyo matigacoke gũtũũra nĩ ũndũ wa bata wao ene, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>no matũre nĩ ũndũ wa bata wa ũcio wakuire ithenya rĩao, agĩcoka akĩriũka.
Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> kuuma rĩu tũticoka gũtarania ũhoro wa mũndũ na njĩra ya ũmwĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o na gwagĩtuĩka kwĩ hingo twataranagia ũhoro wa Kristũ na njĩra ya ũmwĩrĩ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>rĩu tũtigĩte gũtarania ũhoro wake na njĩra ĩo.  Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ angĩkorũo arĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ agarũrũkĩte agatuĩka mũndũ ũngĩ mwerũ: maũndũ marĩa ma tene nĩ mathirĩte; nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ matuĩkĩte mangĩ merũ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						Thaburi 148:12,15</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Wee Jerusalem, kumia Ngai waku ũrĩa ũtũmaga Mũgambo wake guo Mwene gũkũ thĩ.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"V0L364IYKkq0u4EhleYSqg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                            Aroma 10:8-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A ROMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ũhoro ũcio uugaga atĩa? Uugaga atĩrĩ, atĩ uuge ũrĩa mũreheirũo-rĩ, ũrĩ o hakuhĩ nawe,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o kanua-inĩ gaku na ngoro-inĩ yaku.  Naguo uuge ũcio nĩ ũrĩa wa wĩtĩkio, o ũrĩa ithuĩ tũhunjagia. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ-rĩ, ũngiumbũra na kanua gaku atĩ Yesu nĩwa Mwathani, o na gwĩtĩkia wĩtĩkie na ngoro yaku atĩ Ngai nĩ aamũriũkirie oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, no ũhonoke:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ ngoro mũndũ etĩkagia nayo agagĩtuwo mũthingu, na nĩ kanua oimbũraga  nako agakĩhonoka.  Tondũ Maandĩko mekuuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩhokete rĩ, ndarĩ hĩndĩ agaconorithio.  Amu ũhoro wa gũthurania Mũyahudi na Mũyunani gũtirĩ:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani o ro ũcio nowe Mwathani wa andũ othe, na aikaraga o agĩtanahagĩra othe arĩa mamũkayagĩra.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ nĩ haandĩke atĩrĩ: Mũndũ o wothe ũgakaĩra rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani nĩ akahonoka.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 4:4
	</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco gwaku, Mwathani, Mũnene wa ũkumio ũtarĩ mũhaka. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Ti mũgate wiki ũtũũragia mũndũ muoyo, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>no kiugo o gĩothe kĩrĩa kiumaga kanua ka Ngai.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>  Rũgoco gwaku, Mwathani, Mũnene wa ũkumio ũtarĩ mũhaka.</s>"},{ID:14}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"KiMZ02FrY0GEq20gAuLPVg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                          Akolosai 3:1-4</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRI AKOLOSAI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, mũngĩkorũo nĩ mwariũkire hamwe na Kristũ no kĩmathagei maũndũ marĩa ma Igũrũ, kũrĩa Kristũ arĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> aikaire guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai.  Rũmbũyagiai maũndũ marĩa marĩ Igũrũ, na mũtigage kũrũmbũyia marĩa marĩ thĩ. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ nĩ mwakwire, naguo muoyo wanyu nĩ mũhithe hamwe na Kristũ thĩinĩ wa Ngai.  Na rĩrĩ Kristũ, o we ũrĩ muoyo witũ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> rĩrĩa akonanio, hĩndĩ ĩo o na inyuĩ nĩ mũkonanio hamwe nake mwĩ na riri.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>		   </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"/AomovbTik6+OxmqWwsYfA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          Afilipi 3:8-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ĩĩ-ni, o na maũndũ mothe-rĩ ndĩmatuaga ma tũhũ,</s>"},{ID:4,Style:{Body:{TextAlignment:2}},
Text:"<s1384> kuona atĩ rĩu nĩ menyete Yesu Kristũ Mwathani wakwa na ũmenyi ũrĩa ũkĩrĩte kũna maũndũ macio mangĩ mothe.  Nĩ tondũ wake ndorĩirũo nĩ indo ciothe, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na ngacitua o ta mahuti ma gũteo, nĩ getha ndĩigĩĩre na Kristũ na ngoragwo ndĩ thĩinĩ wake, itakĩrĩ na ũthingu wakwa mwene, o wa mũthemba ũcio uumanaga na watho,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> tiga o ũrĩa uumanaga na ũhoro wa gwĩtĩkia Kristũ, o ũthingu ũrĩa uumaga kũrĩ Ngai nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia. Na ningĩ nĩ getha ndĩmũmenye we,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o na menye hinya ũrĩa uumanaga na kũriũka gwake, na tũgwatanĩre nake mĩnyamaro yake, na haananio nake ũhoro-inĩ wake wa gũkua, nĩguo atĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>kũngĩkĩhoteka, ngakinyĩrĩra ũhoro wa kũriũkio nyume kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. Ngiuga ũguo-rĩ, ti ta kuuga atĩ nĩ ndĩkĩtie gũkinya hau, o na kana ngarĩkia kwagĩrĩra kũna:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> ĩndĩ nĩ kwĩrutanĩria ndĩĩrutanagĩria gũthiĩ na mbere, nĩguo atĩ, kwahoteka, ndĩĩnyitĩre ũndũ o ũrĩa ndanyitĩirũo nĩ Kristũ Yesu. Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ndikwĩona ta ndĩkĩtie kũũnyita:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> no ũndũ ũrĩa njĩkaga no ũmwe, atĩrĩ, nĩ ndiganĩirũo nĩ maũndũ marĩa ndigĩte na thutha, ngatambũrũka ‘nyite maũndũ marĩa  marĩ mbere yakwa-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ngerutanĩria gũthiĩ o na mbere, nĩ getha ngakinya handũ harĩa hakinyagwo, na ngaheo kĩheo kĩrĩa kĩheanagwo, nakĩo nĩkio gwĩtwo nĩ Ngai thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu, nĩguo ‘thiĩ Igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Ezekieli 33,11</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>	
Niĩ ndũũraga muoyo-rĩ, ndikenaga nĩ ũndũ wa gĩkuũ kĩa mũndũ mwaganu;</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> no rĩrĩ, nĩ kaba mũndũ ũcio mwaganu agarũrũke atigane na mĩthiĩre ĩo yake nĩguo atũũre muoyo.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"CsXQ+MlxA0qOyIzC7FqGIw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                     Ahibirania 5:7-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KURĨ ANDU A HEBEREA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kristũ, o matukũ marĩa atũire arĩ na mwĩrĩ, nĩ aahoire na agĩthaitha Ngai, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>agĩkayaga mũno na agĩitaga maithori, o we ũngĩhota kũmũhonokia amũrute gĩkuũ-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> agĩkĩiguwo tondũ nĩ amwĩtigĩrĩte akamũtĩa.  Nake o na aarĩ Mũriũ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ erutire gwathĩka nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa aanyamarĩkire.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Na aakĩrĩkia gũtuo mwagĩrĩru kũna, agĩtuĩka kĩhumo kĩa ũhonokio ũrĩa ũtagathira kũrĩ arĩa othe mamũiguaga.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI								John 12:26</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>	
			   
Mũndũ aatuĩka wa kũndungatagĩra, nĩ anũmagĩrĩre; na kũu ndĩ, nĩkuo ndungata yakwa nayo ĩrĩgĩkoragwo ĩrĩ.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"MOyg0pm0dUybrZwpzelj1w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						1 Kor. 1:3-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũrogĩa na wega, o na thayũ, ciumĩte kwĩ Ngai Ithe witũ na Mwathani Yesu Kristũ. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ nĩ njokagĩria Ngai wakwa ngatho hingo ciothe nĩ ũndũ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ wa wega wa Ngai ũrĩa mwaheirũo mwanyitanio na Kristũ Yesu; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ nĩ mwatongirio na maũndũ mothe thĩinĩ wake, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mũgĩgĩtongio ũhoro-inĩ wothe wa kũheana ũhoro o na wa kũmenya maũndũ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>kũringana na ũrĩa ũhoro wa Kristũ ũrĩa woimbũrirũo wekĩrirũo hinya thĩinĩ wanyu;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> mũgagĩtuĩka atĩ iheo iria Ngai aheanaga na Wega wake gũtirĩ o na kĩmwe mũtingiarĩtie,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na mũgaikara o mũgĩtanyaga kũguũranĩrio kwa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nake nĩ arĩmũtũũragia mwĩ na hinya o nginya hĩndĩ ya kũrigĩrĩria, nĩguo mũgakorũo mũtarĩ na ũcuke rĩrĩa</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mũthenya ũrĩa wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ ũgakinya.  </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai nĩ wa kwĩhokeka, o we mwetirũo nĩwe mũtonye ngwatanĩro-inĩ ya Mũrũ wake Yesu Kristũ Mwathani witũ.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							       Thaburi. 85:7			
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"CIbuPOO7f0mq9MzHleJVag",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          1 Akorintho 15:54-58</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, rĩrĩa mwĩrĩ ũyũ wa kũbutha ũgakorũo wĩĩkĩrĩte mũthemba ũcio ũtarĩ wa kũbutha,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> mwĩrĩ o ũyũ wa gũkua ũgĩkorũo wĩĩkĩrĩte mũthemba ũcio ũtarĩ wa gũkua-rĩ, nĩrĩo ũhoro ũgakinya ũrĩa wandĩkĩtwo ũũ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Gĩkuũ nĩ kũng’ario kĩng’arĩtio, gĩgatorio biũ.  Wee gĩkuũ gĩkĩ-rĩ, gũtorania gwaku gũkĩrĩ ha? Ĩ wee gĩkuũ gĩkĩ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> rũbora rũaku naruo rũkĩrĩ ha? Rũbora rũa gĩkuũ nĩruo wĩhia, naguo hinya wa wĩhia uumanaga na watho; no rĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai arogathwo, arĩ we ũtũmaga tũtoranie na ũndũ wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ! Hakĩrĩ ũguo, ariũ a Baba arĩa nyenda mũno-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ikaragai mwĩrũmĩtie, mũtegũgĩthengeka, na mũtũũre hingo ciothe mũrutaga wĩra wa Mwathani mũgakĩrĩrĩria,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ wa kũmenya atĩ wĩra ũrĩa mwĩnogagia naguo ti wa tũhũ mũkĩũrutaga mũnyitaine na Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Atumwo 16,14</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani hingũra ngoro iitũ, na tũkamenya mĩgambo ya mwana waku.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"a2pFiC7vGk2elzFAaNzxUw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ				           Kũguũrĩrio 7:9. 14-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ John ndonire ngĩona kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ mũno, gĩtangĩgereka nĩ mũndũ, kĩa andũ moimĩte ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ ciothe,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na marĩ a mĩhĩrĩga yothe na nduka ciothe o na mĩario yothe, marũgamĩte mbere-inĩ ya gĩtĩ kĩrĩa gĩa ũthamaki na mbere ya Gatũrũme,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> mehumbĩte nguo njerũ ndaya, na me na makĩndũ moko.  Na niĩ ngĩmwĩra, Mũthuri ũyũ, nĩwe ũũĩ.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nake akĩnjĩra atĩrĩ: Acio nĩo arĩa moimĩte mĩnyamaro-inĩ ĩrĩa mĩnene, na nĩ maathambirie nguo ciao,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> magĩgĩcierũhia na thakame ya Gatũrũme.  Nĩkĩo rĩu maikaraga mbere-inĩ ya gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki kĩa Ngai; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ kũmũtungatagĩra mũthenya na ũtukũ thĩinĩ wa hekarũ yake; nake ũcio ũikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki egũtũũra  aarĩte hema yake igũrũ rĩao.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nao matirĩ hingo magacoka kũhũta, kana macoke kũnyota; o narĩo riũa rĩtirĩ hingo rĩkamacina, kana ũrugarĩ mũnene o na ũrĩkũ; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo Gatũrũme karĩa ge gĩtĩ-inĩ gĩa ũthamaki gatagatĩ egũtũũra arĩ o mũrĩithi wao, amatongoragie amakinyagie ithima-inĩ cia maaĩ marĩa ma muoyo; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nake Ngai nĩ ekũmagiria maithori mothe mathire maitho mao.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI								John 10, 14</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>						       
Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga: Niĩ nĩ niĩ mũrĩithi ũrĩa mwega; nĩ njũĩ ng’ondu ciakwa mwene, o nacio ng’ondu ciakwa nĩ injũĩ.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"NoY0v2/9uEa7q1/8Do0NFA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                          1 John 5:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JOHN</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩtie atĩ Yesu nĩwe Kristũ, nĩ aciarĩtwo nĩ Ngai;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na mũndũ o wothe wendete mũciari, endete ũrĩa ũciarĩtwo nĩwe o nake. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Ũndũ ũrĩa tũmenyaga naguo atĩ nĩ twendete ciana cia Ngai nĩ ũyũ: twakorũo twendete Ngai,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na tũgekaga maathani make.  Amu kwenda Ngai nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ tũmenyagĩrĩre maathani make;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> namo maathani make matirĩ thĩna.  Nĩ gũkorũo kĩrĩa gĩothe gĩciarĩtwo nĩ Ngai nĩ gĩtoragia ũhoro wa gũkũ thĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>naguo ũtoria ũrĩa ũtoretie ũhoro wa thĩ nĩ atĩrĩrĩ, nĩ gwĩtĩkia gwitũ.  Ũrĩa ũtoragia ũhoro wa gũkũ thĩ nũ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> tiga ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩtie atĩ Yesu nĩwe Mũriũ wa Ngai? We nĩwe wokire ũhoro-inĩ wa maaĩ na thakame, o we Yesu Kristũ; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ndokĩire ũhoro-inĩ wa maaĩ moiki, okĩire ũhoro-inĩ wa maaĩ O na thakame.  No Muoyo nĩwe mũira, nĩ gũtuĩka Muoyo nĩwe ũhoro-ũrĩa wa ma.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       John 20:29</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Wee, Thomas, tondũ nĩ ũnyonete, nĩkĩo wĩtĩkĩtie; gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matonete, na no metĩkĩtie.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"kFd+KxzIIk+cKbzjQ79QdA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                            Afilipi 3:17-4,1</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, wĩgerekanagiei na niĩ, ningĩ mũbarage wega andũ arĩa mathiaga na mĩthiĩre o ĩrĩa twamũonagĩrĩria. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ nĩ kũrĩ andũ aingĩ mathiaga na mĩthiĩre ya kũonania atĩ nĩ thũ cia Mũtharaba wa Kristũ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o arĩa ndanamwĩra ũhoro wao kaingĩ, o na rĩu ngũmwĩra ũhoro wao ngĩitaga maithori. Andũ acio-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> kũrigĩrĩria kwao nĩ gũtoma magatoma; ngai yao nĩyo nda; naguo ũndũ ũrĩa wa kũmaconora, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩguo megoocaga nĩ ũndũ waguo; ningĩ metaranagia maũndũ o ma gũkũ thĩ.  Nĩ gũkorũo bũrũri ũrĩa tũrĩ aguo kĩũmbe nĩ kũrĩa Igũrũ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na twetagĩrĩra  Mũhonokia ũrĩa ũkoima kuo, nĩwe Mwathani Yesu Kristũ, ũrĩa ũkagarũra mwĩrĩ ũyũ witũ ũhinyaraga,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> ũhaananio na mwĩrĩ wake wĩna riri, nĩ ũndũ wa hinya ũrĩa arĩ naguo wa gũtũma o maũndũ mothe maathĩkage nĩwe.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Hakĩrĩ ũguo, ariũ a Ithe witũ-rĩ, inyuĩ nyendete na ngamwĩriragĩria, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o inyuĩ mũhaana ta gĩkeno gĩakwa o na thũmbĩ yakwa-rĩ, ikaragai mũrũmĩte wega, endwa akwa, thĩinĩ wa Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Marko 9,7
	</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Thĩinĩ wa itu gũkiuma mũgambo wa Ithe: “Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno: mũiguagei”.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"Npm0dTlFQUK6HwaMnBVj6A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						    1 Akorintho 7:29-31</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ũrĩa nguuga, ariũ a Ithe witũ, nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ atĩ hingo nĩ ĩnyihĩte; kuuma rĩu, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>andũ arĩa me na atumia nĩ maikarage ta matarĩ nao, na andũ arĩa marĩraga maikarage ta matekũrĩra, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na arĩa makenaga maikarage ta mategũkena; nao arĩa megũragĩra indo maikarage ta matagĩĩte nacio,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na arĩa mahũthagĩra maũndũ ma gũkũ thĩ maikarage ta matekũmahũthĩra mũno;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo mũtabarĩre wa thĩ ĩno nĩ gũthira ũrathira.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							    Aefeso 1:17-18		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ, o we Ithe witũ mwene riri, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>amũhe o mũndũ muoyo wa kũmũũhĩgia, nĩ getha mũmenye wega kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩa mwĩtĩirũo nĩwe mũgĩe nakĩo.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ	"},{Guid:"rhiqdMzSy0SXt0xrynrWfg",Verses:[{Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1}},
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                Aheberea 10:5-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA RĨA MAANDĨKĨIRUO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Kristũ, agĩũka gũkũ thĩ, ekuuga atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, ti magongona na mahaki wendaga,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> no nĩ mwĩrĩ ũthondekeire; mahaki ma gũcinwo, na ma kũrutwo nĩ ũndũ wa mehia-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>timo ũkenagĩra.  Hĩndĩ  ĩo ngĩuga  atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ! Ndĩ gũũka, thĩinĩ wa ibuku o rĩo rĩa gĩkũnjo, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>uhoro wakwa nĩho wandĩkĩtwo gwĩkaga o ũrĩa wendaga, wee Ngai.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nake oiga hau mbere atĩ magongona ma mahaki, na mahaki ma gũcinwo, na marĩa ma kũrutwo nĩ ũndũ wa mehia timo wendaga kana ũkamakenera-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> namo nĩmo marutagwo ta ũrĩa gwathanĩtwo watho-inĩ, agacoka akoiga : Atĩrĩ, ndĩ gũũka gwĩkaga o ũrĩa wee wendaga. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ kweheria ekweheria ũhoro ũcio wa mbere, nĩ getha arũmie ũcio wa kerĩ.  Nakuo kwenda kũu nĩkuo gũtũmaga tũtherio, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa Yesu Kristũ warutirũo o ihinda rĩmwe rĩa kũigana.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Luka 1,38
	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>One ndungata ya Mwathani, nĩ njĩkũo ta ũrĩa woiga.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ	"},{Guid:"qaGJNoNaW0e3WEu4O/rJIg",Verses:[{
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                Aheberea 10:5-10"},{ID:2,
Text:"GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA RĨA MAANDĨKĨIRUO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA:"},{ID:3,
Text:"Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Kristũ, agĩũka gũkũ thĩ, ekuuga atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, ti magongona na mahaki wendaga,"},{ID:4,
Text:" no nĩ mwĩrĩ ũthondekeire; mahaki ma gũcinwo, na ma kũrutwo nĩ ũndũ wa mehia-rĩ, "},{ID:5,
Text:"timo ũkenagĩra.  Hĩndĩ  ĩo ngĩuga  atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ! Ndĩ gũũka, thĩinĩ wa ibuku o rĩo rĩa gĩkũnjo, "},{ID:6,
Text:"uhoro wakwa nĩho wandĩkĩtwo gwĩkaga o ũrĩa wendaga, wee Ngai."},{ID:7,
Text:"Nake oiga hau mbere atĩ magongona ma mahaki, na mahaki ma gũcinwo, na marĩa ma kũrutwo nĩ ũndũ wa mehia timo wendaga kana ũkamakenera-rĩ,"},{ID:8,
Text:" namo nĩmo marutagwo ta ũrĩa gwathanĩtwo watho-inĩ, agacoka akoiga : Atĩrĩ, ndĩ gũũka gwĩkaga o ũrĩa wee wendaga. "},{ID:9,
Text:" Nĩ kweheria ekweheria ũhoro ũcio wa mbere, nĩ getha arũmie ũcio wa kerĩ.  Nakuo kwenda kũu nĩkuo gũtũmaga tũtherio, "},{ID:10,
Text:"nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa Yesu Kristũ warutirũo o ihinda rĩmwe rĩa kũigana."},{ID:11,
Text:"Ciugo cia Mwathani"},{ID:12,
Text:"RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Luka 1,38
	
Alleluya. Alleluya."},{ID:13,
Text:"One ndungata ya Mwathani, nĩ njĩkũo ta ũrĩa woiga."},{ID:14,
Text:"Alleluia"}],
Text:"Githomo kia igiri"},{Guid:"SeVPavdCSUGq05OfypNZhA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Jakobu 5:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩu-rĩ, ta thikĩrĩriai, itonga ici, rĩrai mũkĩanũkaga  nĩ ũndũ wa mĩthĩnĩko  ĩrĩa ĩkamũkora. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ũtonga wanyu nĩ ũbuthĩte, nacio nguo cianyu nĩ ndĩĩku nĩ memenyi.  Nayo thahabu yanyu o na betha yanyu nĩ ĩrotete,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nakuo kũrota gwacio nĩkuo gũkamuumbũra ũrĩa mũtariĩ, na nĩ gũkamumuthũra nyama cia mĩĩrĩ yaanyu  o ta mwaki. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ mwĩĩigĩire mũthithũ o matukũ-inĩ marĩa ma ithirĩro.  Atĩrĩrĩ, mũcara wa aruti wĩra arĩa maamũgetheire irio mĩgũnda yanyu,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa mwamaimire na wogogani-rĩ, mũcara ũcio nĩ wanagĩrĩra: naguo mũkayo wa agethi acio </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũkinyĩte matũ-inĩ ma Mwathani mũnene wa ita.  Inyuĩ-rĩ, mũtũire gũkũ thĩ mwĩgangarĩte na mũgĩkenagia na indo iria ciothe muonaga,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nacio ngoro cianyu-rĩ, mũtũire mũcituagĩra ta irĩ gĩcegũ, o nginya mũthenya wa gũthĩnjwo. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Nake mũndũ ũrĩa mũthingu-rĩ, nĩ mũmũtuĩrĩire cira hatarĩ kĩhooto, na mũkamũũragithia; nowe ndamũgiaga.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI		                             
	</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgambo waku, Mwathani, nĩ ũma: ũtũũmĩrĩrie thĩinĩ wa rwendo rwaku.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ	"},{Guid:"bYGwoQHjO0W8KU83+ygftg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ						1 Athesalonike 1:5-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A THESALONIKE MARĨA MA MBERE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna aitũ, inyuĩ nĩ mũũĩ mĩthiĩre ĩrĩa twonekaga nĩ inyuĩ tũgĩthiĩ nayo nĩ ũndũ wanyu. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na inyuĩ mũgĩgĩtuĩka a kwĩgerekanagia na ithuĩ o na Mwathani, mwarĩkia gwĩtĩkĩra Ũhoro wake</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> mwĩ na mathĩna maingĩ o hamwe na gĩkeno kĩrĩa kiumaga kwĩ Muoyo Mũtheru.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Mũgĩgĩtuĩka kĩonereria kũrĩ andũ arĩa othe metĩkĩtie o kũrĩa Macedonia na Akaia.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ rĩrĩ, mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ ũmemerekete uumĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na to Macedonia na Akaia gwiki, no rĩrĩ, ngumo ya ũrĩa mwĩtĩkĩtie Ngai nĩ Ihurunjũkĩire kũndũ guothe;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> tũgakĩaga bata wa kwaria kiugo kĩngĩ o na kĩrĩkũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Amu ha ũhoro witũ-rĩ, andũ acio nĩ maheanaga o ene ũhoro wa mũkinyĩre ũrĩa twakinyire naguo kwanyu;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na wa ũrĩa mwagarũrũkĩire Ngai, mũgĩtigana na mĩhianano, nĩ getha mũtungatagĩre Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ muoyo,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩwe wa ma, na mwetagĩrĩre Mũriũ oime igũrũ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>o ũcio aariũkirie kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, nake nĩwe Yesu, ũrĩa ũtũhonokagia harĩ marakara marĩa magoka.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							Mathayo 11,25
	
		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Awa, Mwathani wa Igũrũ o na thĩ, ndakũgatha nĩ ũndũ nĩ ũguũrĩirie tũkenge maũndũ ma Ũthamaki waku.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ	"},{Guid:"ajIj2FE2Lk6P57sTRF1OfA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					         Jakobu 2:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ha ũhoro wa wĩtĩkio ũrĩa wa gwĩtĩkia Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ, o we mwene riri-rĩ, tigai kũwĩtĩkia mũgĩtĩagĩra andũ maũthĩ.  Tondũ rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kũngĩũka thinagoga yanyu mũndũ wĩ na gĩcũhĩ gĩa thahabu na ehumbĩte nguo thaka-rĩ, na ningĩ gũcoke gũũke mũndũ mũthĩni wĩhumbĩte nguo thũku-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na inyuĩ mũtĩe ũcio wĩhumbĩte nguo ĩrĩa thaka, mũmwĩre atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, ikara thĩ handũ haha hega; na mwĩre ũcio mũthĩni atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ,  rũgama harĩa; kana rĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ikara thĩ haha magũrũ-inĩ makwa-rĩ; githĩ mũtikoragwo mwĩ  na ngũũrani thĩinĩ wanyu, na mũgatuĩka atuĩri andũ, mũkĩrĩ na meciria moru? Ariũ a Ithe witũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> inyuĩ nyenda mũno, ta thikĩrĩriai: githĩ Ngai ndaagĩthurire andũ arĩa marĩ athĩni gũkũ thĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>matuĩke itonga ũhoro-inĩ wa wĩtĩkio, na matuĩke a kũgaĩrũo ũthamaki ũrĩa erĩire arĩa mamwendaga?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Thaburi 7:37</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ekĩte maũndũ mothe wega: arĩa mataiguaga nĩ atũmaga maigue, nao arĩa matahotaga kwaria agatũma maarie.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ Jakobu 2:1-5	"},{Guid:"R8m0UKrs7UGLJCL0+uh46w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					         Jakobu 2:14-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, gũkĩrĩ  na uumithio ũrĩkũ, mũndũ angiuga atĩ arĩ na wĩtĩkio, no ndarĩ na ciĩko njega ekaga?</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ĩ, wĩtĩkio ũcio wakĩhota kũmũhonokia? Mũrũ wa Ithe witũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ angĩkorũo arĩ njaga,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na aagĩte irio cia kũrĩa o mũthenya-rĩ, na ũmwe wanyu amere atĩrĩ: Thiĩi na ũhoro, mũgote mwaki na mũkarĩe, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>mũhũne; na ndamahe indo iria mabatairio nĩcio cia mwĩrĩ, gwĩka ũguo-rĩ, kwĩ na uumithio ũrĩkũ?</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ũguo na taguo wĩtĩkio, ũtarĩ na ciĩko njega, nĩ mũkuũ guo mwene.  Ĩndĩ hihi mũndũ no kuuga atĩrĩ: wee-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>wĩ na wĩtĩkio, na niĩ-rĩ, ndĩ na ciĩko njega; rĩu-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ta kĩnyonie wĩtĩkio waku hatarĩ ciĩko njega, na niĩ-rĩ, nĩ ngũkuonia wĩtĩkio wakwa nĩ ũrĩa njĩkaga ciĩko njega.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Agalatia 6,14
	</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩroaga kwĩgooca  na ũndũ o wothe, tiga o ndĩĩgocire nĩ ũndũ wa mũtharaba wa Kristũ, nĩ ũndũ waguo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> maũndũ ma gũkũ thĩ nĩ maambĩtwo mũtharaba nĩguo ma’thengere, na niĩ ngaambwo mũtharaba nĩguo ndĩmathengere.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ	"},{Guid:"Yjj1PYtpxEGnwm5wYTf4NA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 21:1-19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ-ĩo Yesu nĩ eonithirie arutwo ake rĩngĩ iria-inĩ rĩa Tiberiade; na ũrĩa eonithanirie nĩ ũũ: Simone Petro,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na Thomas ũrĩa wetagwo Didimo, na Nathanaeli wa na kũrĩa Kana ya Galilea, na ariũ a Zebedei, o na arutwo angĩ ake erĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>andũ acio maarĩ hamwe.  Nake Simone Petro akĩmera atĩrĩ: Niĩ ndathiĩ gũtega ciũngũyũ.  Makĩmwĩra: O na ithuĩ nĩ tũgũthiĩ nawe.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Magĩkiumagara magĩtonya marikabu; na ũtukũ ũcio matiigana kũgwatia kĩndũ.  Na rũcinĩ gũgĩkĩa Yesu agĩkorũo arũngiĩ rũtere-inĩ rũa iria;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nao arutwo matiamenyaga nĩwe Yesu.  Nake Yesu agĩkĩmoria atĩrĩ: ciana, mwĩ na kanyamũ ga kũrĩa? Makĩmũcokeria:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Aca, tũtirĩ.  Akĩmera: Ikiai rũgara mwena wa ũrĩo wa marikabu na nĩ mũkuona. Magĩgĩikia, na hĩndĩ ĩo rũkĩrema kũgucĩka nĩ ũrĩa ciũngũyũ ciingĩhĩte. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ ũcio mũrutwo ũrĩa wendetwo nĩ Yesu akĩĩra Petro atĩrĩ: Nĩ Mwathani.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Simone Petro aakĩigua atĩ nĩ Mwathani, akĩĩoha nguo yake, tondũ aarĩ ũtheri, akĩrũũga maaĩ-inĩ.  Nao arutwo arĩa angĩ magĩũka na macua ĩrĩa nyinyi,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ matiarĩ haraya na rũtere, no ta itĩĩna rĩa makinya igana, magĩũka, makĩgucagia rũgara rũiyũire ciũngũyũ.  Maakĩrĩkia kuumĩra rũteere-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>makĩona mwaki wa Makara wakĩtio ho, na ciũngũyũ ii njĩkĩre riiko, o na mũgate.  Nake Yesu akĩmera; Rehei ciũngũyũ imwe icio mwanyita.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Simone Petro agĩkĩhaica  macua akĩgucia rũgara akĩruumĩria rũtere rũiyũire ciũngũyũ iria nene, igana rĩa mĩrongo ĩtano na ciũngũyũ ithatũ; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ o na harĩa ciarĩ  nyingĩ ũũ, rũgara rũtiigana gũtuĩka.  Nake Yesu akĩmera: Ũkai mwĩgagũre.  Nao arutwo gũtirĩ wetire kũmũũria: Nĩwe ũ?,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ kũmenya nĩwe Mwathani.  Nake Yesu agĩthiĩ, akĩoya mũgate, akĩmahe, o na ciũngũyũ nacio.  Rĩu nĩrĩo rĩa gatatũ Yesu eonithirie arutwo ake, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>arĩkĩtie kũriũka akoima  kwĩ arĩa akuũ.  Ningĩ maakĩrĩkia  kwĩgagũra, Yesu akĩũria Simone Petro  atĩrĩ: Simone wa Jona, wee-rĩ, nĩ ũnyendete kũrĩ aya angĩ?</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> Akĩmwĩra: Ĩĩ-nĩ, Mwathani, wee nĩ ũũĩ nĩ ngwendete. Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Heaga tũgondu twakwa gĩa kũrĩa.  Akĩmũũria rĩngĩ hingo ya kerĩ, atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Simone wa Jona, nĩ ũnyendete? Akĩmwĩra: Ĩĩ-ni, Mwathani, wee nĩ ũũĩ nĩ ngwendete.  Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ:  Rĩithagia ng’ondu ciakwa. </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Agĩcoka akĩmũũria  hingo ya gatatũ, atĩrĩ:  Simone wa Jona, nĩ ũnyendete? Nake Petro akĩigua ũũru nĩ ũndũ aamũria hingo ya gatatũ: </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũnyendete? Agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwathani, wee nĩ ũũĩ maũndũ mothe; no ũkuona atĩ nĩ ngwendete.  Nake Yesu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Heaga ng’ondu ciakwa gĩa kũrĩa. </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384> Ndakwĩra atĩrĩ, o ma, ma; Rĩrĩa warĩ mũnyinyi, nĩ weohaga, ũgetwara o handũ wendaga gũthiĩ; rĩrĩa ũgakũra-rĩ, ũgatambũrũkia moko,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384> mũndũ ũngĩ akuohe, agũtware handũ ũtangĩenda gũthiĩ.  Na rĩrĩ, oigire ũguo akĩorota  gũkua kũrĩa ũcio agakua  agoocithie Ngai nakuo.  Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo agĩcoka akĩmwĩra: Nũmĩrĩra.</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"Qx0xNfJRb0W6dbkittVCag",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 22:34-40</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩyo, Afarisai, rĩrĩa maaiguire atĩ nĩ aahootire Asadukai, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846>magĩkĩũngana hamwe.  Na ũmwe wao, wĩ mũrutani wa mawatho, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ, nĩguo amũgerie: Mũrutani,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846> rĩathani rĩrĩa inene watho-inĩ nĩ rĩrĩkũ? Nake akĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846>Enda Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku yothe, na muoyo waku wothe, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846>na gwĩciria gwaku guothe.  Rĩu nĩrĩo rĩathani rĩrĩa inene, na rĩa mbere.  Narĩo rĩa keerĩ, rĩhaana o ta rĩu, nĩ rĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846>Enda mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩendete wee mwene. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1846> Maathani macio merĩ nĩmo gatũũrũ ka watho, o na ka mohoro mothe ma Arathi.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"2pEuRIT2qUq2W3JRsnP1MA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 9:30-37</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu na arũmĩrĩri ake makiuma kũu, makĩhungura bũrũri wa Galilea; na ndendaga mũndũ amenye. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ nĩ kũruta aarutaga arutwo ake ũhoro, akamera atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa mũndũ nĩ wa kũneanwo  moko-inĩ ma andũ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nao nĩ kũmũũraga makamũũraga; nake aarĩkia kũũragwo, thuutha wa mĩthenya ĩtatũ nĩ agacoka kũriũka. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nao matiigana gũtaũkĩrũo nĩ kiugo kĩu, na nĩ metigĩrire kũmũũria.  Magĩkinya Kafarnao:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na aakorũo e nyũmba thĩinĩ akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Nĩ ũhoro ũrĩkũ  mũgũciraga twĩ njĩra? Nao  magĩkira: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ nĩ maakararanagia me njĩra atĩ nĩ ũrĩkũ mũnene  kũrĩ arĩa angĩ.  Nake agĩikara thĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>agĩĩta arĩa ikũmi na erĩ; akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũndũ angĩenda gũtuĩka mbere, nĩ atuĩke wa thutha  wa arĩa angĩ othe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na atuĩke ndungata yao othe.  Akĩrehe kaana, agĩkĩrũgamia gatagatĩ-inĩ kao: na aarĩkia gũkarigicĩria moko make, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũndũ o wothe wa gwĩtĩkĩra  kaana kamwe ta gaka nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩ niĩ etĩkĩra:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> na mũndũ o wothe wanjĩtĩkĩra niĩ, to niĩ etĩkĩra, nĩ etĩkĩra  ũrĩa wandekirie.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"9VB7DSWtukyp0LJIyd8/Zw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 25:1-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩmahe ũhoro rĩngĩ na ngerekano akiuga: ũthamaki wa Igũrũ ũkahananio na airĩtu ikũmi,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> arĩa moire matawa mao, magĩthiĩ magathaganie mũhikania.  Na atano ao maarĩ akĩgu, na atano maarĩ ogĩ. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ arĩa akĩgu rĩrĩa moire matawa mao, matiigana gũkuua maguta:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> no arĩa ogĩ nĩ maakuuire maguta thĩinĩ wa macuba mao, o hamwe na matawa mao. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩa mũhikania aaikarire, magĩcũnga othe magĩkoma.  Na ũtukũ gatagatĩ gũkĩanĩrĩrũo atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mũhikania  nĩ mũũku! Umai mũmũthaganie.  Hĩndĩ ĩo airĩtu acio othe magĩũkĩra, magĩthondeka matawa mao.  Na arĩa akĩgu makĩĩra arĩa angĩ atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Tũhei maguta mamwe manyu: nĩ ũndũ matawa maitũ nĩ marahora.  No acio ogĩ magĩcokia makiuga: Aca, nĩ ũndũ hihi matitũigana na mamũigane: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ kaba mũthiĩ kũrĩ arĩa mendagia, mũkegũrĩre manyu.  Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maathiĩte kũgũra,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> mũhikania agĩũka; na arĩa methagathagĩte magĩtonyania nake iruga-inĩ rĩa kĩhikanio: naguo mũrango ũkĩhingwo. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Thutha ũcio airĩtu arĩa angĩ magĩũka o nao, makiuga atĩrĩ: Mwathani, Mwathani, tũhingũrĩre. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩcokia akĩmera: Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: Ndimũũĩ.  Nĩ ũndũ ũcio wĩhũgagei, nĩ gũkorũo mũtiũĩ mũthenya kana thaa.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"LXb1qKN4V0O1+1qJ1AChPQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Luka 3:10-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo andũ a kĩrĩndĩ makĩmũũria John atĩrĩ: Korũo nĩ ũguo-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩkaga atĩa? Nake agĩcokia akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ũrĩa wĩna nguo igĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ahe ũrĩa ũtarĩ; nake ũrĩa wĩna irio-rĩ, nĩ ekage ũguo.  Ningĩ gũgĩũka etia mbia cia igoti  makabatithio, nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Mũrutani, ithuĩ twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩkaga atĩa? Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mũtigetie andũ kĩndũ tiga o kĩrĩa mwathĩtwo mwĩtagie. Nao athigari makĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Na ithuĩ-rĩ, twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩkaga atĩa? Akĩmera atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Mũtikananyarire mũndũ, o na kana mũtunye mũndũ kĩndũ nĩ kũmũigĩrĩra; na ningĩ mũiganagwo nĩ mũcara wanyu.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ gĩatanyaga, gĩgĩthanganagia, nao andũ othe mageciragia ngoro-inĩ ciao ũhoro wa John,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> kana hihi nĩwe Kristũ-rĩ, John agĩcokia akĩmera othe atĩrĩ: Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩmũbatithagia na maĩ; no rĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũgoka ũngĩ wĩna hinya kũrĩ niĩ, nayo mĩkwa ya iratũ ciake, niĩ-rĩ, ndiigaine  wa kũmĩohora;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ũcio nĩwe ũkamũbatithagia  na Muoyo Mũtheru o na mwaki: gĩtarũrũ gĩake  arĩ nakĩo guoko, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha  atherie wega kĩhuhĩro gĩake, nacio ngano acokererie aciite ikũmbĩ rĩake; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>no acine mũũngũ na mwaki ũrĩa ũtangĩhoreka.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ũguo noguo aahunjagia Ũhoro ũrĩa Mwega, agĩtaaraga andũ na maũndũ mangĩ maingĩ.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"0/qQ0TtDikmaCnrFV3PmwQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                        John 18:33b-37</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Pilato akĩũria Yesu: Wee nĩwe Mũthamaki wa Ayahudi? Nake Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkũũria ũguo wĩrĩtwo nĩ ngoro yaku mwene, kana nĩ andũ angĩ makwĩrire ũhoro wakwa? </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Pilato agĩcokia atĩrĩ: Kaĩ ndĩ mũyahudi niĩ? Anga ti rũrĩrĩ rũanyu na athacerdoti arĩa anene maakũneana kũrĩ niĩ; nĩ atĩa wĩkĩte? </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: Ũthamaki wakwa ti wana gũkũ thĩ; ũthamaki wakwa ũngĩrĩ wa gũkũ thĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>andũ akwa mangĩrĩ kũruta mbaara, ndikaneo Ayahudi; no rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ, ũthamaki wakwa ti wana gũkũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ ũcio Pilato  akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Anga ũkĩrĩ o mũthamaki, wee? Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: wee nĩ woiga, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>amu ndĩ mũthamaki.  Nĩkĩo ndaciarirũo, na nĩkĩo njũkĩte gũkũ thĩ, atĩ nduĩke  mũira wa ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe waguo nĩ aiguaga mũgambo wakwa.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"wQ/7r6jWgECFqyGHgBNWEA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Marko 6:7-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩcoka agĩĩta arĩa ikũmi na erĩ, akĩrika kũmatũma o erĩ erĩ; akĩmahe wathani wa gwatha ngoma thũku; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na akĩmera, matigakuue kĩndũ kĩa njĩra, no mũtirima wiki; matigathiĩ na irio, kana mburungo,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> kana makuue mbia ndoho-inĩ ciao; na mathiĩ mekĩrĩte  iratũ: akĩmera ningĩ; Na mũtikehumbe  nguo igĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Agĩcoka akĩmera atĩrĩ: O kũndũ mwatonya mũciĩ raaragai kũu nginya mũkoima kuo.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Na kũrĩa andũ matakamũgwata ũgeni, na marege kũmũigua-rĩ, mũkiuma kuo, thukiai magũrũ manyu rũkũngũ rũitĩke,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> rũtuĩke ũira kũrĩ o.  Nao magĩthiĩ, makĩhunjia ũhoro atĩ andũ merire.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Na magĩtũma ndaimono nyingĩ ciume andũ, na magĩitĩrĩria andũ aingĩ maguta, arĩa maarĩ arũaru, makĩmahonia.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"1SGszY9760Wfajwe8XBqvw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Marko 9:2-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩtwara Petro na Jakobu na Johana akĩmakinyia kĩrĩma kĩraya igũrũ o oiki hatarĩ mũndũ ũngĩ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> akĩgarũrũka ũrĩa aahanaga o hau maarĩ. Nguo ciake igĩkenga, igĩtuĩka njerũ cua; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>gũtirĩ mũthambia wa nguo gũkũ thĩ ũngĩhota gũcierũhia ũguo.  Na makiumĩrĩrũo nĩ Elia me na Musa nao makĩaranĩria na Yesu. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Petro agĩcokia ũhoro, akĩĩra Yesu atĩrĩ: Mwonania, nĩ twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũikara gũkũ: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ twake ithũnũ ithatũ, kĩmwe gĩaku, na kĩmwe kĩa Musa, na kĩmwe kĩa Elia.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Amu nĩ aarigĩtwo nĩ ũrĩa angĩcokia; tondũ nĩ maagwatĩtwo nĩ guoya mũnene.  Ningĩ gũgĩũka itu rĩkĩmahumbĩra:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na thĩinĩ wa itu gũkiuma mũgambo ũkiuga atĩrĩ: Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno: mũiguagei.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Na kahinda o kanini, maacoka kũroranga, makĩaga gũcoka kuona mũndũ, tiga o Yesu wiki e hamwe nao.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩa maaikũrũkaga kĩrĩma, akĩmakaania matikere  mũndũ maũndũ macio monete,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> tiga o rĩrĩa Mũrũ wa mũndũ agakorũo arĩkĩtie kũriũka oimĩte kwĩ arĩa akuũ. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Nao magĩtũũra mamenyereire kiugo kĩu, makoranagia o ene nĩ atĩa ũguo, kũriũka kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"B5NmHLYXe02r6gJJ7hY8jg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 9:38-43. 45,47-48</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, John akĩmwĩra: Mwonania, tũronire mũndũ akĩruta andũ ndaimono na rĩĩtwa rĩaku:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na tũramũkaania, nĩ gũkorũo ndatwaranaga na ithuĩ.  Nake Yesu akiuga atĩrĩ: Mũtikamũkaanie:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩĩka wĩko wa hinya na rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, na ahote gũcoka kũmenereria narua. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Amu-rĩ, ũrĩa ũtarĩ ũthũ na ithuĩ no witũ.  Amu mũndũ o wothe ũkamũhe gĩkombe kĩa maaĩ mũnyue, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ mũrĩ a Kristũ, ngũmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ na ma, ũcio ndarĩ ũndũ ũgatũma aage ũtungati wake. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Na mũndũ o wothe ũgatũma twana tũtũ twĩĩhokete kamwe gatuo kahĩtie, wega wake no aharũkio ihiga inene rĩa gĩthĩi ngingo na aikio iria thĩinĩ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ guoko gwaku nĩ gwa gũkũhĩngithia, gũtinie;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> kaba gũtonya muoyo –inĩ wĩ kĩonje gwĩ gũtonya jeena wĩna moko merĩ, ũtonye mwaki-inĩ ũrĩa ũtangĩhoreka. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ kũgũrũ gwaku nĩ gũkũhĩngithia, gũtinie; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ kaba gũtonya muoyo-inĩ wĩ gĩthua gwĩ gũikio Jeena wĩ na magũrũ merĩ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>  O na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ riitho rĩaku nĩ rĩa gũkũhĩngithia, rĩkũũre ũrĩte: </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ kaba gũtonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai wĩna riitho rĩmwe gwĩ gũikio Jeena wĩna maitho merĩ; </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>kũrĩa kĩgunyũ kĩao gĩtakuaga, naguo mwaki ũtahoraga.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"VUMwa9C0o0KPyHMM+DzN+g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 10:46-52</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, rĩrĩa Yesu oimaga kũu Jeriko, me na arutwo ake o na kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ, mũrũ wa Timeo, ũrĩa wetagwo Bartimeo, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>mũndũ mũtumumu watũire ahoyaga thendi-rĩ, nĩ aakorirũo aikaire thĩ mũkĩra-inĩ wa njĩra.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake aaigua atĩ nĩ Yesu ũrĩa wa Nazareth, agĩitĩka kwanĩrĩra, akiugaga: Yesu, mũrũ wa Davide,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> njiguĩra tha.  Na andũ aingĩ makĩmũkaania, makĩmwĩra atĩ akire; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nake no kwanĩrĩra aacokire kwanagĩrĩra o mũno.  Mũrũ wa Davide, njiguĩra tha.  Nake Yesu akĩrũgama, Mwĩtei. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Magĩgĩĩta mũndũ ũcio mũtumumu, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wĩũmĩrĩrie: Ũkĩra, nĩ egũgwĩta. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩtiga aateania nguo, akĩguthũka, agĩthiĩ harĩ Yesu.  Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria ũhoro akĩmũũria: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ũkwenda ngwĩke atĩa? Nake mũndũ ũcio mũtumumu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwonania, ngwenda o njoke kuona. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wĩthiĩre: gwĩtĩkia gwaku nĩkuo gwatũma ũhone.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Na kahinda o kaũ agĩcoka kuona, akĩmũrũmĩrĩra o na njĩra.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"2w8MyLKNFkCLZltGztxyNQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Mk. 1:1-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kĩambĩrĩria kĩa Injiri ya Yesu Kristũ, Mũrũ wa Ngai.  Ota ũrĩa ũhoro wandĩkĩtwo marũa-inĩ ma Isaia ũrĩa mũnabii,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> atĩrĩ: Onei, ngũtũma mũrekio wakwa athiĩ mbere yaku, athondeke kĩng’aratua gĩaku wega; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>mũgambo wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra werũ-inĩ, akoiga, thondekai kĩng’aratua  kĩa Mwathani, rũngariani njĩra ciake; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>noguo John okire, ũrĩa wabatithanagĩria werũ-inĩ, na akaheanaga ũhoro atĩ kũbatithagio arĩa merirĩte nĩguo marekerũo mehia mao.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Na kĩrĩndĩ gĩothe kĩa Judea kĩoimagaraga gĩgathiĩ kũrĩ we, o na andũ othe a Jerusalemu,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na makabatithio nĩwe thĩinĩ wa rũũĩ rũa Jordani, makiumbũraga mehia mao.  Nake John nĩ ehumbaga nguo ya guoya wa ngamĩra, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na akeyoha kamũkwa njohero, na akarĩaga ngigĩ na ũũkĩ wa hako.  Na nĩ aheanaga ũhoro, akoiga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ kũrĩ ũgũũka thutha wakwa ũrĩa wĩ na hinya kũrĩ niĩ, itaigaine niĩ nyinamĩrĩre njohore mĩkwa ya iratũ ciake. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ ndĩmũbatithĩtie na maaĩ; ũcio akamũbatithia  na muoyo Mũtheru.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"Tt98c6TXHU2GYOkK4pKIXg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         John 1:35-42</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthenya ũyũ ũngĩ John agĩkorũo arũngiĩ,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> me na arutwo ake erĩ; agĩcũthĩrĩria  Yesu agĩceera, akiuga:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Onei Gatũrũme ka Ngai! Na arutwo acio erĩ nĩ maaiguire ũguo aaria, magĩkĩrũmĩrĩra Yesu. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩhũgũka, akĩmona mamuumĩte thutha, akĩmoria: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ atĩa mũkwenda? Nao makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Rabbi (ũguo naguo wataũrũo nĩta kuuga: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Mwonania), ũraraga kũ? Akĩmera: Ũkai; nĩ mũkuona.  Magĩgĩthiĩ makĩona kũrĩa araraga; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na magĩikara nake mũthenya ũcio: kwarĩ ta thaa ikũmi.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Andũ acio erĩ maaiguire John aaria na makĩmũrũmĩrĩra, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ũmwe nĩ Andrea, mũrũ wa nyina na Simone Petro.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>We akĩamba gũkora mũrũ wa nyina Simone, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Tũrĩ kuona Messia (narĩo rĩĩtwa rĩu rĩataũrũo, nĩ atĩrĩ, Kristũ).  Akĩmũtwara kwĩ Yesu.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Yesu akĩmũroora, akiuga atĩrĩrĩ: wee tiwe Simone, mũrũ wa Jona?</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Ũgũtuwo Cefa (rĩu narĩo rĩataũrũo nĩ Petro; na noguo Ihiga).</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"JkjjQVJbIEGuvynEwFbVEg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI 		Mathayo 5:  1-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MATHAYO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu ona mĩrũrũngano ya andũ akĩambata kĩrĩma-inĩ; na aarĩkia gũikara thĩ, arutwo ake magĩũka  kũrĩ we; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>agĩtumũra kanua akĩmaruta, akiuga atĩrĩ: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa Igũrũ nĩ wao. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa marĩ na kĩeha, nĩ gũkorũo nĩmakaninĩrũo kĩeha.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa ahoreri, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ makagaya thĩ.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa mahũtagĩra maũndũ marĩa ma ũthingu,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na makamanyotera, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ makahũnio.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa maiguagĩra andũ tha,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ makaiguĩrũo tha.  Gũkena-rĩ,  nĩ arĩa  mateciragia ũũru ngoro, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ makona Ngai. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ ateithũrani, nĩ ũndũ nĩ  magetagwo ariũ a Ngai.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa manyarirĩtwo nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ marĩa ma ũthingu,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa Igũrũ nĩ wao.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ  hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ makamũruma, na mamũnyarire,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na mamũigĩrĩre maũndũ moru ma mĩthemba yothe nĩ ũndũ wakwa.  Kenai na mũcanjamũke, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ  igai rĩanyu nĩ rĩnene kũrĩa Igũrũ; nĩ ũndũ ũguo no taguo irori iria maarĩ mbere yanyu maanyariragwo.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"ohiLss9P8UyyM3l2cG34RA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Marko 1:40-45</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, mũndũ wamũkorire warũarĩte mangũ: agĩũka akĩmũthaithaga, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>agĩturĩria Yesu ndu na akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ũngĩenda-rĩ, wahota kũ’honia ‘there. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩkĩringwo nĩ tha, agĩtambũrũkia guoko, akĩmũhutia, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩngwenda; gũtherio.  Na o kahinda o kau agĩthirũo nĩ mangũ, agĩthera. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akĩmũkaania na hinya, agĩcoka o hĩndĩ ĩo akĩmwĩra oime, ningĩ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Menya ũkera mũndũ: no wĩthiĩre, ũkeyonanie kwĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na ũrute indo cia ũguo watherio, o iria Musa aathanire, ituĩke kĩmenyithia kũrĩ andũ. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> No we agĩĩthiĩra akĩrika kuumbũra mũno na kũmemerekia ũhoro ũcio,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Yesu agĩkĩremwo nĩ gũcoka gũtonya itũũra thĩinĩ akĩonagwo nĩ andũ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>agaikaraga o kũrĩa gũtaarĩ mĩciĩ, kũrĩa gũtaathiagwo: nao andũ makamũkora kuo moimĩte o kũndũ guothe. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"a3x+DOIYm0mCWcxI0TGhTw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 20:1-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthenya wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia Maria wa Magdala akĩroka mbĩrĩra-inĩ rũci-inĩ tene, kũrĩ o nduma, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>akĩona ihiga rĩĩ ithengie muungu-inĩ.  Agĩgĩteng’era agĩthiĩ gwĩ Simeone Petro, na kwĩ mũrutwo ũrĩa ũngĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa Yesu endete, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Nĩ marutĩte mwathani muungu-inĩ, tũtiũĩ harĩa mamũigĩte.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Petro akiumagara o na mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ, magĩthiĩ marorete mbĩrĩra-inĩ mbere: Makĩgwata gũteng’era o erĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nake mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ agĩkĩria Petro ihenya agĩkinya muungu-inĩ mbere ainamĩrĩra arora </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>thĩinĩ akĩona matama marĩa ma gatani me maige thĩ na ndatonye. Simone Petro nake agĩgĩũka amũrũmĩrĩire,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> agĩtonya mungu-inĩ thĩinĩ nake akĩona matama macio ma gatani me maige thĩ  o na gĩtambaya </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nakĩo kĩrĩa kĩarĩ mũtwe wake gĩtaigĩtwo hamwe na matama macio ma gatani nĩ gũkũnjwo  gĩakũnjĩtwo gĩkaigwo</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> handũ mwanya.  Hĩndĩ ĩo mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ nake agĩtonya ũcio waambire gũkinya muungu-inĩ nake akĩona agĩĩtĩkia.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Amu nginya hĩndĩ ĩo matiamenyete wega ũhoro ũcio wandĩkĩtwo atĩ no mũhaka acoke ariũke  oime kwĩ arĩa akuũ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"QYo/SXKGGUGMogs2MCCfVg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 6:17,20-26</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu, agĩikũrũka kĩrĩma nao, akĩrũgama handũ haaraganu, me na arutwo ake gĩkundi kĩnene,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na andũ aingĩ arĩa moimĩte Judea guothe, na Jerusalemu, o na ndere-inĩ cia iria rĩrĩa rĩnene  o kũrĩa Tiro na Sidone.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩtiirĩra arutwo ake maitho, akiuga atĩrĩ: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ athĩni, nĩ gũkorũo Ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩ wanyu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ mũhũtaga rĩu, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka kũhũnio.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ onyuĩ  mũrĩraga rĩu, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka gũtheka.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ rĩrĩa andũ makamũmena,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na  meamũre kũrĩ inyuĩ, na mamũcambie, na mathũkĩrĩrie rĩĩtwa rĩanyu nĩ ũndũ wa Mũrũ wa mũndũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Mũthenya ũcio kenai na mũtũhatũhe; nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, igai rĩanyu nĩ rĩnene o Igũrũ, nĩ gũkorũo ũguo noguo maithe mao mekaga Irori. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ itonga, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũrĩkĩtie kuona kũnyamarũrũo kwanyu. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ mũhũnaga rĩu nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka kũhũta.  Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> inyuĩ mũthekaga rĩu, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka gwĩthikĩra na kũrĩra.  Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, o inyuĩ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>rĩrĩa andũ othe makamũgathagĩrĩria, nĩ gũkorũo ũguo noguo maithe mao mekaga Irori cia maheni.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"o8aNkQzfdU+fK62C9xiODA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 12:38-44</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩra kĩrĩndĩ gĩake, akĩrutana: Wĩmenyagĩrĩrei aandĩki marũa arĩa mendaga gũceera mehumbĩte nguo ndaya, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na makenda kũgeithagio ing’ang’a-inĩ, na gũikaragĩra itĩ cia  mbere me thinagoga, na kũgĩaga harĩa ha gũtĩo maruga-inĩ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na no-o manyamaragia nyũmba cia atumia a ndigwa, o makĩhoyaga mahoya maraya nĩ ũndũ wa ũhinga; acio nĩo magatuĩrũo ituĩro rĩũru makĩria. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ agĩikara thĩ ang’etheire harĩa hekagĩrũo kĩgĩĩna, akĩĩrorera ũrĩa kĩrĩndĩ gĩekagĩra mbia kĩgĩĩna-inĩ kĩu: na andũ aingĩ arĩa maarĩ itonga magĩĩkĩra mbia nyingĩ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Na gũgĩũka mũtumia wa ndigwa mũthĩni, nake agĩĩkĩra tũthendi twĩrĩ, tũrĩa tũiganaga mbeca ĩmwe.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩĩta arutwo ake, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ na ma, mũtumia ũyũ wa ndigwa mũthĩni nĩ ekĩra nyingĩ kũrĩa andũ othe arĩa marekĩra mbia kĩgĩĩna-inĩ: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ acio othe nĩ mekĩra mbia nĩ ũrĩa maingĩhĩtie; nake nĩ ekĩra indo ciake iria oima nacio ciothe, nĩ ũrĩa akĩarĩte, na nĩcio mũthithũ wake wothe.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"sjjYcg9740WwZDDaBiETww",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Luka 2:41-52</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nao aciari ake nĩ maathiaga Jerusalemu, o mwaka, hĩndĩ ya gĩathĩ kĩa Paska.  Na rĩrĩa Yesu aahingirie mĩaka ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> makĩambata nake gĩathĩ-inĩ kĩu kũringana na mũtugo.  Nao maanina matukũ ma gĩathĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>rĩrĩa maainũkaga kwao, kamwana kau, Yesu, gagĩikara kũu Jerusalemu; nao aciari ake matimenye ũguo.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nao magĩthiĩ rũgendo rũa mũthenya mũgima, makĩĩgeragĩria atĩ e gĩkundi-inĩ kĩa andũ a kwao; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>thutha wa ũguo makĩmũcaria kũrĩ andũ a mũhĩrĩga wao o na arĩa maamenyanĩte nao: nao maamwaga-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>makĩhũndũka Jerusalemu, makĩmũcaragia.  Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, matukũ matatũ maathira,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmũkora hekarũ ya Ngai thĩinĩ aikarĩte thĩ kũrĩ arutani, agĩthikagĩrĩria ũrĩa moigaga, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o na akĩmoragia maũndũ. Na andũ arĩa othe maamũiguaga makĩgega nĩ ũndũ wa ũũgĩ wake, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o na ũrĩa aacokagia ũhoro orĩo maũndũ.  Nao aciari ake maamuona makĩgega nĩ ũndũ wa ũũgĩ wake,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o na ũrĩa aacokagia ũhoro orĩo maũndũ.  Nake nyina akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wakwa, ũtwĩkĩte ũũ nĩ kĩ?</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> rĩu-rĩ, ithuĩ na thoguo tũgũcarĩtie twĩ na kĩeha ma. Nake akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Nĩ kĩ gĩtũmĩte mũnjarie? </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Kaĩ mũtoĩ atĩ ndirĩ hingo itarĩkoragwo ndĩ nyũmba  ya Baba? Nao matiamenyire gĩtũmi gĩa ciugo icio aamerire. Nake agĩtherera…</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"OacJq7PAFku424Ebw/jBUQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 2:13-25</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, Paska ya Ayahudi nĩ yatuĩte gũkinya, nake Yesu akĩambata Jerusalem. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na kũu hekarũ-inĩ agĩkora andũ arĩa mendagia ng’ombe na ng’ondu  na ndutura,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ona arĩa maakũũranagĩria  andũ mbia maikaire thĩ kuo: agĩthondeka mũcarica  na mĩkanda, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>akĩmarutũrũra kũu hekarũ othe,  o na ng’ondu na ng’ombe;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o nacio mbeca cia arĩa maahunjithagia mbia agĩciita thĩ, na akĩgũithia metha ciao; akĩĩra arĩa mendagia ndutura atĩrĩ;: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Umiai ici gũkũ; tigai gũtua nyũmba ya Awa nyũmba ya thogora.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao arutwo ake makĩririkana atĩ nĩ haandĩke atĩrĩ: Nĩ kĩyo kĩrĩa ndĩ nakĩo kĩa nyũmba yaku gĩkandĩa.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao Ayahundi magĩgĩcokia makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Rĩu-rĩ tondũ ũreka maũndũ maya-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> kĩmenyithia nĩ kĩrĩkũ ũgũtuonia? Nake Yesu agĩcokia ũhoro akĩmera: </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Thariai hekarũ ĩno, na mĩthenya ĩtatũ nĩ ngamĩcokia igũrũ. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Nao Ayahundi magĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Nyũmba ĩno-rĩ, ĩninĩte mĩaka mĩrongo ĩna na ĩtandatũ ĩgĩakwo</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>nawe gĩthiĩ ũkamĩcokia igũrũ mĩthenya  ĩtatũ ĩrĩĩke? No we nĩ hekarũ ya mwĩrĩ wake aagwetaga. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Na tondũ ũcio aarĩkia kũriũkio akoima kwĩ arĩa akuũ, arutwo  ake magĩkĩririkana atĩ nĩ oigire ũguo; </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> magĩgĩĩtĩkia ũhoro ũrĩa mwandĩke, o na kiugo kĩu Yesu oigire. </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩo aarĩ kũu Jerusalem Paska-inĩ hĩndĩ ya gĩathĩ, </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>andũ aingĩ makĩaga kwĩhoka rĩĩtwa rĩake mona ciama ciake iria ekaga. </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384> No Yesu we ndaigana kwĩhoka ũhoro wao, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ oĩ andũ othe, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>na tondũ ndaabataragio nĩ kuumbũrĩrũo ũhoro wa mũndũ; amu we mwene nĩ oĩ ngoro ciao.</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"HScuneHso0GeQVdE5kWq0A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 10:27-30</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu nĩ  oigire: Ng’ondu ciakwa-rĩ, nĩ ciiguaga mũgambo wakwa, na niĩ nĩ ndĩciũĩ, nacio ikanũmĩrĩra; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na niĩ ngacihe muoyo wa tene na tene, na itirĩ hingo ikora, o rĩ, o rĩ, na gũtirĩ ũngĩgacihuria ciume moko-inĩ makwa. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Awa, ũrĩa ũheete cio, nĩ mũnene kũrĩ othe; na gũtirĩ ũngĩhota gũcihuria  ciume moko-inĩ ma Ithe witũ.  Niĩ na Ithe witũ tũrĩ ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"AUGhDExbwEuOcJyUnNOYGw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩmahe ũhoro rĩngĩ na ngerekano, akiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> Ũthamaki wa Igũrũ nĩ wa kũhaananio na mũthamaki mũna warugire iruga mũriũ akĩhikania,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>agĩtũma ngombo ciake igete arĩa metĩtwo, nĩ getha moke iruga-inĩ rĩu rĩa kĩhikanio: nao makĩrega gũũka. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩcoka agĩtũma ngombo ingĩ, agĩciĩra atĩrĩ: Ĩrai acio metĩtwo: Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩ thondekete irio ciakwa: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ndegwa ciakwa o na ngoima nĩ ithĩnjĩtwo, na indo ciothe nĩ thondeke: ũkani iruga-inĩ rĩa kĩhikanio.  No rĩrĩ, andũ acio makĩaria ũndũ ũcio, magĩĩthiĩra; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ũmwe agĩthiĩ mũgũnda wake, na ũngĩ agĩthiĩ wonjoria-inĩ wake: na arĩa angĩ makĩnyita ngombo ciake,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> magĩciĩka ũũru na magĩciũraga.  Nake mũthamaki ũcio akĩrakara; akĩrekia mbũtũ ciake, akĩnina oragani acio, agĩcina itũũra rĩao. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Hĩndĩ ĩo akĩĩra ngombo ciake atĩrĩ: Iruga rĩa kĩhikanio nĩ rĩthondeke, no rĩrĩ, arĩa metĩtwo matiagĩrĩire kũrĩa.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio thiĩi magomano –inĩ ma ing’aratua, na arĩa othe mũrĩona, metei moke iruga-inĩ rĩa kĩhikanio. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Na ngombo icio ikiumagara, igĩthiĩ ing’aratua-inĩ, ikĩũngania arĩa othe cionire, arĩa oru o na arĩa ega:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nakĩo kĩhikanio gĩkĩiyũra ageni. No rĩrĩa mũthamaki ũcio aatonyire arore ageni acio, akĩona ho mũndũ ũtehumbĩte nguo ya kĩhikanio: akĩmũũria atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Mũrata wakwa, ũtonyire atĩa haha ũtarĩ na nguo ya kĩhikanio? Nake agĩkira ki.  Hĩndĩ ĩo mũthamaki akĩĩra ngombo ciake: Muohei moko na magũrũ, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>mũmũikie na nja, kũrĩa kwĩ nduma; kũu nĩkuo gũkagĩa kĩrĩro na kũhagarania magego.  </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ arĩa metĩtwo nĩ aingĩ, no arĩa athure nĩ anyinyi.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"WSjrWOMRSE2LmFhNZyCqgQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Luka 1:1-4; 4:14-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kuona atĩ andũ aingĩ maanagwata kwandĩka marũa ma maũndũ marĩa tũhingĩirio, o ta ũrĩa twaheirũo ũhoro wamo nĩ aira arĩa mameoneire,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kuuma o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maambĩrĩirie gwĩkĩka; nao nĩo maarĩ ndungata cia ũhoro ũcio; kuona ũguo-rĩ, niĩ o na niĩ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ nĩ nduĩrĩtie wega maũndũ macio kuuma o rĩrĩa maambĩrĩirie gwĩkwo, nĩ nyonete arĩ wega ngwandĩkĩre marũa, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>wee Theofilo, mũnene mũgathe, ma gũthingatania maũndũ macio wega o ta ũrĩa mekĩkire, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ũmenye na ma maũndũ marĩa warutirũo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu agĩcoka arĩ na hinya wa Muoyo, agĩthiĩ Galilea: nayo ngumo yake ĩgĩtambũka ng’ongo ciothe cia kũu. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akarutanaga thinagoga-inĩ mũthenya wa thabatũ andũ othe.  Nake agĩkinya Nazareth, o kũrĩa aarereirũo: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>agĩtonya thinagoga mũthenya wa thabatũ, o ta ũrĩa aamenyerete gwĩkaga, akĩrũgama athome.  Nake akĩheo ibuku rĩa Isaia ũrĩa mũrathi. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Akĩrĩkũnjũra, agĩcaria harĩa ũhoro wandĩkĩtwo ũũ: Muoyo wa Mwathani arĩ igũrũ rĩakwa,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ nĩ aanjitĩrĩirie maguta hunjagĩrie arĩa athĩni Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega: Nĩ andũmĩte menyithanie atĩ arĩa mohetwo nĩ mohorũo,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> o na atĩ arĩa atumumu nĩ megũcoka kuona; Na njohorithie arĩa mahinyĩrĩirio, ningĩ hunjanagĩrie ũhoro wa mwaka wa Mwathani,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> o ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩrĩtwo.  Agĩcoka agĩkũnja ibuku, akĩrĩcokeria ndungata, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>agĩikara thĩ; nao andũ othe arĩa maarĩ thinagoga makĩmũkũũrĩra maitho.  Nake akĩrika kũmera atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ũhoro ũcio wandĩkĩtwo nĩ wahingio o ũmũthĩ mweiguĩra na matũ manyu.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"d+wB/pDdZk+I5iVcdz4EAw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                 John 6:41-51</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Ayahudi magĩteta nĩ ũndũ wake, nĩ tondũ oigire: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ niĩ mũgate ũrĩa woimire Igũrũ.  Makiuga atĩrĩ: ũyũ anga towe Yesu, mũrũ wa Joseph, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na Ithe na nyina nĩ tũmoĩ? Nĩ atĩa tondũ rĩu ekuuga: Nĩ nyumĩte Igũrũ? Nake Yesu agĩcokia ũhoro, akĩmera:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Tigai gũtetania.  Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota gũũka kũrĩ niĩ atagucĩrĩirio nĩ Ithe witũ ũrĩa wandekirie;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na niĩ nĩ ngamũriũkia mũthenya wa kũrigĩrĩria.  Nĩ haandĩke atĩrĩrĩ maandĩko-inĩ marĩa ma irori:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nao othe makarutwo ũhoro nĩ Ngai.  Mũndũ o wothe  ũiguĩrĩire uhoro gwĩ Ithe witũ, agakĩĩruta-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ũcio nĩ okaga kurĩ niĩ.na tiatĩ kwi mundu wanona ithe witu tiga uria umite kwi Ngai:ucio nĩoete ithe witu.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Ndamwĩra atĩrĩ o ma, ma: Mũndũ ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩtie e na muoyo wa tene na tene. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ niĩ mũgate wa muoyo.  Maithe manyu ma tene maarĩaga irio icio cietagwo maana, me werũ-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nao nĩ maakuire.  Ũyũ-rĩ, nĩguo mũgate ũrĩa wa gũikũrũka  uumĩte Igũrũ, nĩguo mũndũ aũrĩe, aage gũkanakua.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ niĩ mũgate ũrĩa waikũrũkire uumĩte Igũrũ, wĩ muoyo; mũndũ aarĩa mũgate ũyũ, agatũũra tene na tene; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na mũgate ũrĩa ngakĩruta nĩ mwĩrĩ wakwa, ndĩũrute nĩ ũndũ wa muoyo wa kĩrĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"jy0s+GymTkGd3eUiSoPKbg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Mathayo 2:1-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa  Yesu aciarĩirũo Bethlehemu, itũũra rĩa Judea, matukũ ma mũthamaki wetagwo Herode,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> gũgĩũka andũ ogĩ a njata Jerusalem, moimire kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ, makĩũria atĩrĩ, “Ũrĩa ũciarĩtwo e mũthamaki wa ayahudi,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> arĩ ha”? Tondũ nĩ twonire njata yake kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ, na nĩ tũũkĩte tũmuturirĩe ndu tũmũgooce.  Na rĩrĩa Herode, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio ,mũthamaki, aaiguire ũhoro ũcio akĩĩgua ũũru, we mwene o na Jerusalem guothe hamwe nake. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Agĩkĩũngania athĩnjĩri Ngai arĩa anene othe na aandĩki-marũa a kĩrĩndĩ, akĩmoria harĩa Kristũ agaciarĩrũo. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nao makĩmwĩra, Nĩ Bethlehem, itũũra rĩa Judea, tondũ nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo nĩ mũrathi ũũ: Nawe Bethlehem,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o kũu bũrũri wa Judea, tiwe ũrĩa mũnyinyi  mũno wa aathani a Juda: tondũ rĩ, nĩ kũrĩ wee gũkoima ũrĩa ũgaathanaga, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o ũrĩa ũkarĩithagia andũ akwa  a Israeli”.
Hĩndĩ ĩo Herode agĩĩta andũ acio ogĩ a njata na hitho, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>agĩtuĩria wega kũrĩ o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njata yonekire.  Akĩmatũma Bethlehem, akĩmera, Thiĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mũgatuĩrie wega ũhoro wa gakenge kau, na mwakona, cokai mũhe ũhoro, nĩ getha na niĩ thiĩ ngagaturĩrie ndu ndĩkagooce. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nao maaigua ũrĩa mũthamaki ũcio aamerire, magĩĩthiĩra; na rĩrĩ, njata ĩrĩa monire o kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ ĩkamathiĩ mbere,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> o nginya ĩkĩrũgama igũrũ rĩa harĩa gakenge kau kaarĩ.  Nao mona njata ĩo, magĩkena gĩkeno kĩnene mũno. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Magĩtonya nyũmba, makĩona gakenge karĩ na nyina Maria, Makĩĩgũithia thĩ, magĩkagooca. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Makĩohora indo ciao cia goro na cio ciarĩ thahabu, ũbani na manemane.  Na tondũ wa gũkanio nĩ Ngai na kĩroto,</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ matigacokere kũrĩ Herode, magĩcoka bũrũri wao na njĩra ingĩ.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"63S+oalnY0KXZ0CU0+Z/5g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Luka 3:15-16,21-22</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, tondũ ĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ gĩatanyaga, gĩgĩthanganagia, nao andũ othe mageciragia ngoro-inĩ ciao ũhoro wa John,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kana hihi nĩwe Kristũ-rĩ, John agĩcokia akĩmera othe atĩrĩ: Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩmũbatithagia na maaĩ; no rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũgoka ũngĩ wĩna hinya kũrĩ niĩ, nayo mĩkwa ya iratũ ciake, niĩ-rĩ, ndiigaine wa kũmĩohora; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio nĩwe ũkamũbatithagia na Muoyo Mũtheru o na mwaki.  
Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, andũ othe maarĩkia kũbatithio, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o nake Yesu aarĩkia kũbatithio-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aahoyaga Ngai, Igũrũ rĩkĩhingũka, nake Muoyo Mũtheru agĩikũrũka, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>akĩũmba igũrũ rĩake arĩ na mwĩrĩ ũhaana ta wa ndutura, naguo mũgambo ũkiuma Igũrũ ũkiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Wee nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno; nĩ ngenaga nĩ ũndũ waku.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"RnpJZMmvJky/JTLEul32dw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    Marko 4:35-41</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na mũthenya o ũcio, hwaĩ-inĩ wakinya, Yesu akĩĩra Arekio ake: Nĩ tũringe mũrĩmo ũrĩa.  Magĩtigana na kĩrĩndĩ kĩu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmũtwara hamwe nao marikabu-inĩ, o ũguo aatariĩ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Na kwarĩ marikabu ingĩ ciatwaranire hamwe nake.  Na gũkĩgĩa kĩhuhũkanio kĩnene kĩa rũhuho, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>namo makũmbĩ ma maaĩ magĩĩtonyia o marikabu thĩinĩ, marikabu igĩkĩenda kũiyũra maaĩ</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>We nake aarĩ mũthia-inĩ wa thutha wa marikabu akomeire muuto e toro: makĩmũũkĩria, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>makĩmwĩra: Mũrutani, githĩ ndũkũũria tũkĩũra? Nake agĩũkĩra, agĩkaania rũhuho, na akĩĩra iria atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Kira, ũhorere.  Naruo rũhuho rũgĩtuĩka, gũkĩhorera o kũhorera.  Agĩcoka akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Mũmakĩtee nĩkĩ?</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Mũtirĩ mũretĩkia o na rĩu? Nao magĩĩtigĩra o mũno, makĩũrania atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Kaĩ mũndũ ũyũ akĩrĩ ũ, kuona atĩ o na rũhuho na iria nĩ imũiguaga?</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"4uehgBeLSE+zUJEyy5xKWw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 12:28-34</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo mwandĩki marũa ũmwe nĩokire kũrĩ Yesu, akĩigua magĩcira, na aamenya atĩ nĩ amacokeire ũhoro wega,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Nĩ rĩathani rĩrĩkũ rĩĩ mbere ya marĩa mangĩ mothe? Nake Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩrĩa rĩa mbere nĩ rĩrĩ: Igua Israeli; Mwathani Ngai witũ-rĩ, Mwathani nĩ ũmwe:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nawe enda Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku yothe, na muoyo waku wothe,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na gwĩcirĩra gwaku guothe, o na hinya waku wothe.  Narĩo rĩa kerĩ nĩ rĩrĩ: Enda mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩendete wee mwene.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Gũtirĩ rĩathani rĩngĩ inene kwĩ macio.  Nake mwandĩki marũa ũcio akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ti-itherũ Mwonania,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ woiga wega atĩ Ngai nĩ ũmwe, na gũtirĩ ũngĩ tiga we: ningĩ kũmwenda na ngoro yothe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o na ũũgĩ wothe, o na hinya wothe, o na mũndũ ende mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩendete we mwene, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ũguo nĩ ũkĩrĩte mũno mahaki mothe ma gũcinwo me magima, o na magongona mothe.  </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu o na atĩ nĩ aacokia ũhoro ta mũndũ mũũgĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, ndũrĩ haraya na ũthamaki wa Ngai. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Na thutha ũcio gũtirĩ mũndũ wacokire kwenda kũmũũria ũndũ.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"bUBe+MZscEi40qctAO9HSw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Luka 1:26-38</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Mũraika Gabriel agĩtũmwo nĩ Ngai itũũra-inĩ rĩa Nazareth, bũrũri wa Galilea,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kwĩ mũirĩtu wetagwo Maria wahikĩtio nĩ mũndũ wa nyũmba ya Davide wetagwo Joseph. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Na Mũraika atonya kwa mũirĩtu akĩmwĩra: Nĩ ngũkũgeithia, we mũiyũre nĩ wega; Mwathani arĩ nawe, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>we ũrĩ mũrathime thĩinĩ wa aka othe.  Maria aigua ndeto icio no kĩmako, na agĩikara agĩthugunda ngeithi icio ũrĩa ithiĩte;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nake mũraika agĩcokia; ndũgetigĩre, Maria, amu nĩ wonire wega kwa Ngai, nĩ ũndũ hau nĩ ũkagĩa nda na ũgaciara Mwana, na ũkamũtua Yesu. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũcio nĩ agatuĩka Mũnene, na nĩ agetwo Mwana wa mũnene-ma. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Ngai nĩ Akamũnengera ũnene wa Davide ithe wake na nĩ agathana mũciĩ-inĩ wa Jakubu hĩndĩ ciothe, na ũnene wake ndũgathira.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Maria agĩcokeria Mũraika: Ũhoro ũcio ũgathiĩ atĩa niĩ itoĩ mũndũ mũrũme. Mũraika agĩcokia: </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Muoyo Mũtheru nĩ ũgaikũrũka igũrũ rĩaku, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na hinya wa Ngai nĩ ũgakũhumbĩra; nĩ ũndũ hau ũrĩa ũgaciarũo nĩ we nĩ Mũthure, na agatuo Mwana wa Ngai. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> One, mũgendiguo Elisabeth nake nĩ agĩire nda, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>o na arĩ mũkũrũ ũguo, na mweri ũyũ tũrĩ nĩguo wa ĩtandatũ arĩ na nda, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>ũndũ areragũo nĩ thata; nĩ gũkorwo gũtirĩ ũndũ ũngĩrema Ngai.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Maria nake akiuga: One ndungata ya Mwathani, nĩ njĩkũo o ta ũrĩa woiga. Na Mũraika akĩmweherera agĩthiĩ.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"X5IU2cCd5kq3KggBuf5o1Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Luka 4:21-30</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩtonya thinagoga ya Nazareth na akĩrika kũmera atĩrĩ: Ũhoro ũcio wandĩkĩtwo nĩ wahingio o ũmũthĩ mweiguĩra na matũ manyu.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao othe makĩmũgatha, na makĩgega nĩ ũndũ wa ciugo iria horo cioimaga kanua gake: magĩkiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Githĩ ũyũ tiwe mũrũ wa Joseph? Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: No gũkorũo mwanjĩra thimo ĩno atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Mũthondekani ũyũ, wĩhonie wee mwene: o ũndũ o wothe twanaigua atĩ wanekwo nĩwe o kũrĩa Kafarnao,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> wĩke o na gũkũ bũrũri waku kĩũmbe.  Agĩcoka akĩmera: Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: Gũtirĩ mũnabii ũngĩĩtĩkĩrũo bũrũri wake kĩũmbe.  Ĩndĩ ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ kwarĩ atumia aingĩ a ndigwa bũrũri wa Israel, matukũ ma Elia, rĩrĩa matu maahingirũo mĩaka ĩtatũ na mĩeri itandatũ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa kwagĩire ng’aragu nene bũrũri ũcio wothe: no rĩrĩ, Elia ndatũmirũo kũrĩ ũrĩkũ wao,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> tiga o kũrĩ mũtumia ũmwe wa ndigwa ũrĩa watũire itũũra rĩetagwo Zarepta, o bũrũri wa Sidone.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Ningĩ nĩ kwarĩ andũ aingĩ maarũarĩte mangũ bũrũri wa Aisraeli hĩndĩ ya Eliseo ũrĩa mũnabii; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na gũtirĩ mũndũ wao wahonirio, tiga o Naaman, ũrĩa Mũsiria.  Nao arĩa othe maarĩ thinagoga thĩinĩ,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> maaigua mohoro macio, makĩrakara mũno; magĩgĩũkĩra, makĩmũthinĩkania oime itũũra rĩao,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmũtwara hururu-inĩ ya kĩrĩma kĩrĩa itũũra rĩao rĩaakĩtwo, nĩ getha mamũkurumanie agũe thĩ ho.  Nowe akĩhungurĩra gatagatĩ kao agĩĩthiĩra.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"GSwKwQDBg0eSBavNIT/8Vg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 10:17-30</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu oimagaraga erekeire njĩra, mũndũ akĩmũteng’erera, akĩmũturĩria ndu, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Mwonania mwega,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ atĩa ingĩĩka nĩ getha ngagae muoyo wa tene na tene? Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: Ũkũnjĩta mwega nĩkĩ?</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Gũtirĩ mwega tiga o ũmwe, nĩwe Ngai.  Ndũũĩ maathani atĩ: Ndũkanoragane, ndũkanatharanie, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ndũkanaiye, ndũkanaigĩrĩre mũndũ kĩgenyo, ndũkanahenanie, tĩa thoguo na nyũkwa? Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mũrutani, maũndũ macio ndũire ndĩmarũmĩtie nginya ndĩ o mũnyinyi.  Nake Yesu,  aamũrora, akĩmwenda, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ kũrĩ ũndũ ũmwe ũtigairie: nĩ rĩrĩ, thiĩ, ũkendie indo ciothe iria wĩ nacio, ũhe arĩa athĩni, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ũkagĩa na ũtonga Igũrũ: na ũũke, ũnũmĩrĩre.  Nowe agĩtuka gĩthithi aaigua ũhoro ũcio, agĩthiĩ e na kĩeha:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũndũ warĩ na indo nyingĩ. Nake Yesu akĩroranga, akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ: Andũ arĩa me na indo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> kaĩ nĩ makona hinya magĩgatonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai-ĩ! Nao arutwo makĩgega nĩ ciugo icio ciake. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu agĩcokia ũhoro rĩngĩ, akĩmera: Ciana ici, andũ arĩa mehokete indo-rĩ, kaĩ nĩ hinya magĩgatonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai!</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũhũthũ ngamĩra ĩhungure kahoro ga cindano, kũrĩ mũndũ mũtongu atonye ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Nao makĩgega mũno mũno, makĩmũũria: Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, nũ ũngĩkĩhota kũhonoka? Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ, amacũthĩrĩirie:</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Gũtingĩhoteka nĩ andũ, no ti ũguo Ngai: amu-rĩ, maũndũ mothe mahotekaga nĩ Ngai.  Nake Petro akĩrika kũmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> rĩu-rĩ, ithuĩ tũtitigĩte indo ciothe na tũgakũrũmĩrĩra? Nake Yesu akiuga: Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũtigĩte nyũmba, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>kana agatiga ariũ a nyina, kana aarĩ a nyina, kana nyina, kana ithe, kana ciana, kana ithaka,</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ wakwa na tondũ wa Injiri, ũtakaheo rĩu matukũ maya  tũrĩ, na akĩrĩrĩrio maita igana, nyũmba, na ariũ a nyina,</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384> na aarĩ a nyina, na manyina, na ciana, na ithaka, hamwe na mĩnyamaro; na hingo ĩrĩa ĩgoka thutha, aheo muoyo ũtathiraga.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"O1zXihEkik6FLr6ZXVohFw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                 John 6:24-35</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, tondũ ũcio kĩrĩndĩ gĩakĩona atĩ Yesu ndarĩ kuo, o na arutwo ake, gĩgĩtonya macua icio arĩ kĩo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> gĩgĩthiĩ Kafarnao  gũcaria Yesu.  Na maamũkora mũrĩmo ũrĩa, makĩmũũria: Mwonania, ũũkire rĩ gũkũ?</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩmacokeria akiuga: ndamwĩra atĩrĩ o ma, ma: Mũtikũnjaragia nĩ ũndũ mũronire ciama; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>mũkũnjaragia nĩ ũndũ mũrarĩire mĩgate, mũrahũna.
Tigaga gũtungatĩra irio iria ithiraga;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> tungatagĩrai irio iria ciikaraga nginya muoyo wa tene na tene, iria Mũrũ wa mũndũ akũmũhe;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> amu nĩwe mwĩkĩre mũhũri nĩ Ithe, Ngai.  Nao magĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Twĩkage atĩa, nĩguo tũtuĩke nĩ mawĩra ma Ngai tũraruta?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu agĩcokia akĩmera: Wĩra wa Ngai nĩ rĩrĩ, nĩ mwĩhoke ũrĩa areketie.  Magĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Wee-rĩ, kĩmenyithia gĩkĩrĩ kĩrĩkũ ũrutaga, nĩguo tuone tũgwĩtĩkie? Nĩ ũndũ ũrĩkũ wĩkaga? </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Maithe maitũ ma tene marĩaga irio iria cietagwo maana, me werũ-inĩ, o ta ũrĩa haandĩkirwo, atĩ:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Aamaheire mũgate uumĩte Igũrũ marĩe.  Nake Yesu agĩkĩmera: Ndamwĩra atĩrĩ o ma, ma: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ti Musa wamũheire mũgate uumĩte Igũrũ; no nĩ Awa mũmũhei mũgate uumĩte Igũrũ ũrĩa wa ma. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Amu-rĩ, mũgate wa Ngai no ũrĩa ũikũrũkaga uumĩte igũrũ, ũgekagĩra kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ muoyo. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Nao magĩkĩmwĩra: Mũthuri ũyũ, tũheage mũgate ũcio o hingo ciothe.  Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ niĩ mũgate wa muoyo; mũndũ ũũkĩte kũrĩ niĩ ndakahũta, na mũndũ wĩĩ’hokete, niĩ, ndarĩ hingo akanyota.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"J0uqEHsJCkCa/1IjgshKRQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI							John 20: 19-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthenya o ũcio wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia, gũkinyĩte hwai-inĩ, na mĩrango ĩkahingwo kũu arutwo maarĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi, Yesu agĩũka akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Gĩai na thayũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, akĩmonia hĩ ciake  o na mbaru.  Nao arutwo mona Mwathani magĩkena. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Yesu agĩkĩmera rĩngĩ atĩrĩ: Gĩai na thayũ; o ta ũrĩa Ithe witũ aandekirie niĩ, noguo ndamũrekia inyuĩ. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo akĩmaheeherera, akĩmera: Iyũkiai Muoyo Mũtheru; andũ arĩa othe mwarekera mehia mao,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ maarekerũo; arĩa othe mwarega kũrekera mehia mao, megũikara matarekeirũo.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"c14SlsoO50ePLNiwQQg7zQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                 Marko 6:30-34</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo arekio magĩcoka kũũngana kwĩ Yesu; na makĩmwĩra maũndũ mothe, o marĩa mekĩte,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na marĩa maarutĩte andũ.  Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ũkai inyuĩ inyuiki kũrĩa gũtarĩ andũ, mũkahurũke hanini.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ andũ nĩ aingĩ mokaga magĩthiaga, nao makaaga hingo o na ya kũrĩa irio. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Magĩthiĩ na marikabu kũndũ gũtaarĩ andũ, o oiki. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nao andũ makĩona magĩthiĩ, na aingĩ makĩmamenya, magĩtwarana kuo na magũrũ mahanyũkĩte moimĩte  matũũra mothe makĩmahĩta. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akiuma marikabu akĩona kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ, agĩkĩiguĩra tha, tondũ maatariĩ ta mbũri ciagĩte mũrĩithi: agĩitĩka kũmaruta mohoro maingĩ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"mRlp7ZKhqUKCbHkafwTraA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Marko 1:21-28</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu aikarĩte Kafarnao, nake o mũthenya wa thabatũ wakinya agĩtonya thinagoga akĩgwata kũruta andũ ũhoro. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nao makĩgega nĩ ũhoro ũrĩa aarutanaga: tondũ aamarutaga ta mũndũ wathanaga, na tĩ ta aandĩki-marũa.  Na ihinda, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o rĩu kũu thinagoga yao gũgĩkorũo kwĩ na mũndũ wĩ na ngoma thũku; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nake akĩgũũthũka, akiuga: Ũhoro witũ nawe ũkĩrĩ ũrĩkũ, wee Yesu wa Nazareth?</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũũkĩte gũtũnina? Nĩ ngũũĩ, nĩwe ũrĩa mũtheru wa Ngai.  Nake Yesu akĩmĩkaania, akiuga: Kira, na uume thĩinĩ wake. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nayo ngoma ĩo thũku a mũthiora na ya kaya na mũgambo mũnene, ĩkiuma thĩinĩ  wake.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Andũ othe magĩkĩgega, magĩitĩka kũũrania atĩrĩ: Ũguo nĩ atĩa-ĩ? Nĩ ũhoro mwerũ-nĩ ũyũ!</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ngoma thũku o nacio aciathaga na hinya, na ikamũigua.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nayo ngumo yake  o hingo ĩo ĩkĩhunja guothe, ĩkĩiyũra bũrũri wothe wa Galilea mwena ũcio.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"6IgZ1p1MekGhl3bXlWFREg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                        John 18:33b-37</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Pilato akĩũria Yesu: Wee nĩwe Mũthamaki wa Ayahudi? Nake Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkũũria ũguo wĩrĩtwo nĩ ngoro yaku mwene, kana nĩ andũ angĩ makwĩrire ũhoro wakwa?</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Pilato agĩcokia atĩrĩ: Kaĩ ndĩ mũyahudi niĩ? Anga ti rũrĩrĩ rũanyu na athacerdoti arĩa anene maakũneana kũrĩ niĩ; nĩ atĩa wĩkĩte?</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: Ũthamaki wakwa ti wana gũkũ thĩ; ũthamaki wakwa ũngĩrĩ wa gũkũ thĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>andũ akwa mangĩrĩ kũruta mbaara, ndikaneo Ayahudi; no rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ, ũthamaki wakwa ti wana gũkũ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ ũcio Pilato  akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Anga ũkĩrĩ o mũthamaki, wee? Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: wee nĩ woiga, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>amu ndĩ mũthamaki.  Nĩkĩo ndaciarirũo, na nĩkĩo njũkĩte gũkũ thĩ, atĩ nduĩke  mũira wa ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe waguo nĩ aiguaga mũgambo wakwa.</s>"},{ID:11,Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFFFFFFF"},Stroke:{Color:"FF789ECB"},StrokeThickness:30,ShadowColor:"FF83A9D8",ShadowRadius:36,ShadowDirection:-90,ShadowDepth:20}}},
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"M5fyy8gZlk6uscrW5NjDOQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                       John 6:60-69</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, arutwo ake aingĩ maaigua ndeto icio, magĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Ũhoro ũcĩo wĩ hinya; nũ ũngĩhota kũũigua? </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Yesu, tondũ nĩ oĩ na ngoro atĩ arutwo ake nĩ marateta nĩ ũndũ waguo akĩmera: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Githĩ ũhoro ũcio ũgũtũma mũhĩngwo? Ĩ, mũngĩkĩona Mũrũ  wa mũndũ akĩambata kũrĩa aarĩ mbere? </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Muoyo-rĩ, nĩguo wĩkanagĩra muoyo; mwĩrĩ ndũrĩ ũguni; ndeto icio ndamũhe nĩcio muoyo na nĩcio ũtũũro. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, inyuĩ kũrĩ amwe mategwĩtĩkia.  Amu gwata kĩambĩrĩria, Yesu nĩ aamenyaga arĩa matetĩkĩtie, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na ũrĩa ũkamũkunyanĩra anyitwo.  Agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩrĩ; nĩkĩo ndĩmwĩrire, atĩ;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota gũũka kũrĩ niĩ atarĩ mwendithie nĩ Ithe witũ. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Maaigua ũhoro ũcio, arutwo ake aingĩ makĩhũndũka, magĩtiga gũcoka gũthiĩ nake.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ ũcio Yesu akĩũria arĩa ikũmi na erĩ atĩrĩrĩ; Mũkwenda gũthiĩ, o na inyuĩ? Nake Simone Petro akĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani, tũgĩthiĩ kũrĩ ũ? Wee wĩna ndeto cia muoyo wa tene na tene.  Na ithuĩ nĩ twĩtĩkĩtie, tũkamenya nĩwe Mũtheru wa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"Pdz5R+qQ/0OidxG+U5qtfA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 6:39-45</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu erire arũmĩrĩri ake ngerekano ĩno:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Kaĩ mũndũ mũtumumu angĩkĩhota kuonereria  mũndũ ũngĩ mũtumumu njĩra? Githĩ o erĩ matingĩgũa irima-inĩ?</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Mũrutwo ti mũnene kũrĩ mũmũruti: no rĩrĩ, mũndũ o wothe rĩrĩa akaigania, nĩ agatuĩka o ta mũmũruti.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩ, nĩ kĩ gĩtũmaga ũrore kĩhuti kĩrĩa kĩĩ riitho rĩa mũrũ wa thoguo, na ndũkũũria  mũgogo ũrĩa wĩ riitho rĩaku mwene?</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Kana wakĩhota atĩa kwĩra mũrũ wa thoguo atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa awa, tareke ngũrute kĩhuti kĩu kĩĩ riitho rĩaku, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ũtakĩonete wee mwene mũgogo ũrĩa wĩ riitho rĩaku mwene? Wee, hinga ĩno, amba ũrute mũgogo ũrĩa wĩ riitho rĩaku mwene,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ ũkuona wega ũrute kĩhuti kĩu kĩĩ ritho rĩa mũrũ wa thoguo.
Nĩ gũkorũo gũtirĩ mũtĩ mwega ũciaraga maciaro mathũku;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ gũtirĩ mũtĩ mũthũku ũciaraga maciaro mega.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ o mũtĩ o mũtĩ ũmenyekaga nĩ ũndũ wa maciaro maguo mwene.  Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, andũ matituaga ngũyũ ciigua-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana magatua thabibũ mĩtare-inĩ.  Mũndũ ũrĩa mwega arutaga kĩrĩa kĩega mũthithũ-inĩ ũrĩa mwega wa ngoro yake;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> nake ũrĩa mũũru arutaga kĩrĩa kĩũru mũthithũ-inĩ ũrĩa mũũru: nĩ gũkorũo kanua gake kaaragia o maũndũ marĩa maiyũire ngoro. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"+yD/ZPWJ4UOncR0d2BrtMA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 7:1-8,14-15,21-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Afarisai na aandĩki-marũa amwe nĩ marũrũnganire kũrĩ Yesu, moimĩte Jerusalem,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na makona atĩ arutwo ake amwe maarĩaga irio ciao na moko mathũku, nĩguo matarĩ mathambie.  Amu Afarisai, o na Ayahudi othe,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> matingĩrĩa irio mataambĩte gwĩthamba moko o wega, nĩ kũigua kĩrĩra gĩa athuri: na moima kĩng’ang’a-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> matingĩrĩa mataambĩte gwĩthamba: o na kwĩ maũndũ mangĩ maingĩ marutĩte tene-inĩ mekage,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> mathambia ma ikombe na tũnyũngũ o na nyũngũ cia mũthemba wa gĩcango.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nao Afarisai acio na aandĩki-marũa makĩmũria atĩrĩ: Arutwo aku matiganĩte na kĩrĩra gĩa athuri nĩkĩ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> makarĩaga irio ciao na moko mathũku? Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Isaia nĩ aarathire ũhoro wanyu wega ma, hinga ici, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ta harĩa haandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: Andũ aya mandĩaga na mĩromo, no ngoro ciao ii kũraya na niĩ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> No kaĩ maturagia  ndu mahoyage tũhũ-ĩ maũndũ marĩa matũire marutanaga makĩrĩ o maathani ma andũ. Mũtiganaga na rĩathani rĩa Ngai,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mũkagwatagĩrĩra kĩrĩra kĩa andũ.  Agĩcoka agĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ gĩthengerere harĩ we, agĩkĩĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Thikĩrĩriai inyuothe,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> na mũigue: gũtirĩ kĩndũ gĩtarĩ thĩinĩ wa mũndũ, kĩngĩhota kũmũgwatia thahu gĩgĩtonya thĩinĩ wake:</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> maũndũ marĩa moimaga thĩinĩ wa mũndũ nĩmo magwatagia mũndũ thahu.  Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ thĩinĩ, nĩ ngoro-inĩ cia andũ,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> kuumaga meeciria moru, ũmaraya, na ũici, ũũragani, na ũtharia, na ũcumĩkĩri, na waganu, na ũhenania, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>na ũũra-thoni, na rũitho, na ũrumani, na mwĩtĩo, na ũrimũ:  maũũru macio mothe moimaga na thĩinĩ, makagwatia mũndũ thahu.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"s3+SAZJIvke0XzaROfANPg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                 John 6:1-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩthiĩ mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ wa iria rĩa Galilea, na norĩo iria rĩa Tiberiade.  Akĩrũmĩrĩrũo nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ ma,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ nĩ kĩonaga ciama  iria ekaga andũ arĩa arũaru akĩmahonia.  Nake Yesu akĩhaica kĩrĩma-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> agĩikara thĩ ho na arutwo ake. Na rĩrĩ, Paska yarĩ hakuhĩ gũkinya, nĩyo gĩathĩ kĩrĩa kĩa Ayahudi.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Yesu aagĩtiira maitho, ona atĩ gwĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ gĩgũũka kũrĩ we, akĩũria Filipo atĩrĩ: Tũkũgũra mĩgate kũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> andũ aya makĩrĩe? Akĩmũria ũguo atĩ amũgerie amu we mwene nĩ oĩ ũrĩa egwĩka. 
Filipo akĩmucokeria atĩrĩ :</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> mĩgate ya ciringi magana merĩ ndĩngĩmaigana atĩ nĩguo o mũndũ one kanini.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Na mũrutwo wake ũmwe, wetagwo Andrea, mũrũ wa nyina na Simone Petro, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Haha he kahĩĩ kena mĩgate itano  ya ngano ya cairĩ, na ciũngũyũ  igĩrĩ; ĩndĩ tũirio tũu-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>tũkĩrĩ kĩ, andũ maigana ũũ? Nake Yesu akiuga: Ĩrai andũ maikare thĩ. Na rĩrĩ, handũ hau haarĩ na nyeki nyingĩ. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Arũme magĩgĩikara thĩ, mangĩhinga ta ngiri ithano, nake Yesu agĩkĩiyũkia mĩgate ĩo, na aarĩkia gũcokeria Ngai ngatho, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>akĩgaĩra andũ acio maaikaire thĩ; o na ciũngũyũ nacio o ũndũ ũmwe, akĩmahe ciigana o ũrĩa mekwenda. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Na maahũna, akĩĩra arutwo ake: Oyai cienyu iria itigarĩte, gũtikore kĩndũ.  Magĩkĩoya,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> makĩiyũria  ciondo ikũmi na igĩrĩ cienyũ  cia mĩgate ĩo ĩtano ya cairĩ, iria ciatigirio nĩ  andũ acio maarĩire. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Nao andũ maakĩona kĩama kĩu aaringire, makiuga atĩrĩ: Ti-itherũ, ũyũ nĩwe mũrathi ũrĩa wa gũũka gũkũ thĩ.  </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Yesu aakĩona atĩ nĩ makiriĩ gũũka kũmũtwara na hinya makamũtue  mũthamaki wao, agĩcoka  kĩrĩma-inĩ wiki.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"F+0UXYIsukaXU43e+Wde0Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 12:20-33</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, hamwe na andũ arĩa maambatire makahoe Ngai gĩathĩ-inĩ kĩu haarĩ na Ayunani; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nao magĩgĩkora Filipo, ũrĩa wa kũrĩa gwĩtagwo Betsaida ya Galilea, makĩmũhoya makiuga: Mũthuri ũyũ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> tũkwenda tuone Yesu.  Filipo agĩthiĩ akĩĩra Andrea; nake Andrea, o na Filipo, magĩthiĩ makĩĩra Yesu. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩmacokeria ũhoro, akiuga atĩrĩ: Hingo nĩ nginyu Mũrũ wa mũndũ agoocithio.  Ndamwĩra atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o ma, ma, Hĩndĩ ya ngano yaaga kũgũa tĩri-inĩ ĩkue, ĩgũtũũra o ĩiki; no yakua, ĩgaciara maciaro maingĩ.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mũndũ ũrĩa wendaga muoyo wake nĩ kũũrũo oragwo nĩguo; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na ũrĩa ũthũũraga muoyo wake e gũkũ thĩ nĩ akaũtũũria nginya muoyo wa tene na tene. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ, mũndũ aatuĩka wa kũndungatagĩra, nianumagirire na kuu ndi nikuo ndungata yakwa nayo irigikoragwo iri</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> :Niĩ, mũndũ aatuĩka wa kũndungatagĩra,,Ithe witũ nĩ arĩmũtĩaga.  Rĩu nĩgũtangĩka ndĩratangĩka ngoro;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ngũkiuga atĩa? Njuge, Awa, honokia kũrĩ hingo ĩno? No ningĩ ũhoro ũyũ noguo watũmire nginyie hingo ĩno. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Awa, kĩgoocithie rĩĩtwa rĩaku Oiga ũguo, Igũrũ gũkiuma mũgambo, ũkiuga atĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ndĩrĩgoocithĩtie, o na nĩ ngarĩgocithia rĩngĩ. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ ũcio kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa kĩarũngiĩ ho na gĩkĩogua, gĩkiuga nĩ kũruruma kwaruruma; angĩ makiuga atĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ mũraika wamwarĩria.  Nake Yesu, agĩcokia akiuga atĩrĩrĩ, Mũgambo ũcio ndũnoka nĩ ũndũ wakwa; </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>woka nĩ ũndũ  wanyu.  Rĩu nĩ hingo thĩ ĩno ĩgũcirithio ĩtuĩrũo; rĩu mũnene wa gũkũ thĩ nĩ ekũingatwo. </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ niĩ, ndahaicio igũrũ kuuma thĩ, nĩ ngagucĩrĩria andũ othe moke kũrĩ niĩ.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>  Na nĩ oigire ũguo akĩorota gũkua kũrĩa agakua.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"i1gfSbTqCUyn25Grles2bA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 23:1-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩarĩria kĩrĩndĩ o na arutwo ake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Andĩki-marũa o na Afarisai nĩ maikaragĩra gĩtĩ kĩa Musa: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ ũcio maũndũ  marĩa mothe mamwĩraga mwĩke, mekagei na mũmarũmagie; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>no tigagai gwĩka ta ũrĩa mekaga o ene; nĩ ũndũ o moigaga, na matiĩkaga.  Na nĩ mohaka mĩrigo mĩritũ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ĩrĩa ĩtitikagwo na hinya, makamĩigĩrĩrithia ciande cia andũ; no-o ene-rĩ, o na kĩara matingĩmĩhutia nakĩo. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, ciĩko ciothe, maciĩkaga nĩguo  monagwo nĩ andũ: nĩ ũndũ nĩ maaramagia ithitũ ciao, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ maraihagia ciohe cia ndigi cia nguo ciao, na nĩ mendaga gũikara handũ harĩa ha gũtĩo maruga-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na gũikarĩra itĩ cia mbere thinagoga-inĩ, na kũgeithio nĩ andũ ing’ang’a-inĩ, o na gwĩtagwo nĩ andũ, Rabii. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> No inyuĩ mũtikanetwo Rabii: nĩ gũkorũo ũmwe nĩwe Mũrutani wanyu, o na inyuĩ inyuothe mũrĩ a Ithe ũmwe. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ mũtikanete mũndũ o na ũmwe ithe wanyu gũkũ thĩ: nĩ gũkorũo ũmwe nĩwe ithe wanyu, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>o ũrĩa wĩ Igũrũ, Ningĩ mũtikanetwo atongoria: nĩ gũkorũo ũmwe nĩwe Mũtongoria wanyu, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>nĩwe Kristũ.  No rĩrĩ, harĩ inyuĩ ũrĩa mũnene nĩ atuĩke ndungata yanyu.  Na mũndũ o wothe wĩtũũgagĩria,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ akanyihio: na mũndũ o wothe wĩnyihagia, ũcio nĩ agatũũgĩrio.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"1ociVI1oy0qm/o14fiVcfQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Marko 1:40-45</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, mũndũ wamũkorire warũarĩte mangũ:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> agĩũka akĩmũthaithaga, agĩturĩria Yesu ndu na akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ũngĩenda-rĩ, wahota kũ’honia ‘there. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩkĩringwo nĩ tha, agĩtambũrũkia guoko, akĩmũhutia, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Nĩngwenda; gũtherio</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Na o kahinda o kau agĩthirũo nĩ mangũ, agĩthera.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake akĩmũkaania na hinya, agĩcoka o hĩndĩ ĩo akĩmwĩra oime, ningĩ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Menya ũkera mũndũ:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> no wĩthiĩre, ũkeyonanie kwĩ mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, na ũrute indo cia ũguo watherio, o iria Musa aathanire, ituĩke kĩmenyithia kũrĩ andũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  No we agĩĩthiĩra akĩrika kuumbũra mũno na kũmemerekia ũhoro ũcio, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu agĩkĩremwo nĩ gũcoka gũtonya itũũra thĩinĩ akĩonagwo nĩ andũ, agaikaraga o kũrĩa gũtaarĩ mĩciĩ, kũrĩa gũtaathiagwo: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nao andũ makamũkora kuo moimĩte o kũndũ guothe. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"iqrrJzo56kCbhDCAEeDEDw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 9:28-36</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩtwarana na Petro, na John, na Jacob, akĩambata kĩrĩma nao, ahoere Ngai kuo. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na akĩhoyaga-rĩ, ũthiũ wake ũkĩgarũrũka ũrĩa wahaanaga, nacio nguo ciake ikĩerũha, igĩkenga mũno.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, hagĩkorũo athuri erĩ makĩaria nake, nĩo Musa na Elia; makĩmoimĩrĩra me na riri,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> makĩaria ũhoro wa ikua rĩake rĩrĩa akiriĩ gũkuĩra Jerusalem. Nake Petro, na arĩa maarĩ hamwe nake, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>magĩkorũo mahĩtĩtwo nĩ toro; no rĩrĩa maarahũkire, makĩigua, makĩona riri wake, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o na makĩona athuri acio erĩ marũgamĩte hamwe nake.  Na gũgĩkinya  atĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ acio maatiganaga nake, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>mathiĩ, Petro akĩĩra Yesu atĩrĩ: Mũnene witũ, nĩ twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũikara gũkũ: reka twake ithũnũ ithatũ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>kĩmwe gĩaku, na kĩmwe kĩa Musa, na kĩmwe kĩa Elia: nake ndoĩ ũrĩa oigaga.  Na akĩaragia maũndũ macio-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>gũgĩũka itu rĩkĩmahumbĩra; nao magĩĩtigĩra nĩ ũndũ wa kũhumbĩrũo nĩrĩo.  Na mũgambo uumĩte itu-inĩ rĩu ũkiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa, o ũrĩa ndĩĩthurĩire: mũiguagei.  Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũgambo ũcio waiguirũo, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu agĩcoka kũonwo arĩ wiki.  Nao magĩkĩra, na matierire mũndũ o na ũmwe matukũ macio ũndũ o wothe wa maũndũ macio monire.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"t1EDaQoYck6dDPXF2OQVGA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 10:35-45</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Jacob na Johana, ariũ arĩa a Zebedo, makĩmũkuhĩrĩria makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwonania, tũkwenda ũtwĩke o ũrĩa tũgũkũhoya. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akĩmoria: Mũkwenda ndĩmwĩke atĩa? Nao makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ũtwĩtĩkĩrie tũgaikara ũmwe guoko-inĩ gwaku kwa ũrĩo na ũmwe guoko-inĩ gwaku kwa ũmotho, wagĩa na riri waku.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Yesu akĩmera: Mũtiũĩ ũrĩa mũkũhoya. Mwahota kũnyuĩra gĩkombe kĩrĩa niĩ ngũnyuĩra,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> kana mũbatithio kũbatithio kũrĩa niĩ ngũbatithio nakuo? Makĩmwĩra: Twahota.  Yesu agĩkĩmera:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Gĩkombe kĩrĩa ngũnyuĩra no mũkanyuĩra, o na kũbatithio kũrĩa ngũbatithio no mũkabatithio nakuo: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ĩndĩ gũikara guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũrĩo, kana guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũmotho, ti ũndũ ũngĩheanwo nĩ niĩ;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũkaheo o arĩa mathondekeirũo.  Arĩa angĩ ikũmi nao maaigua, magĩitĩka kũrakara nĩ ũndũ wa Jakubu na Johana. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩmeta, akĩmera atĩrĩrĩ: Nĩ mũũĩ atĩ arĩa meragwo nĩ athamaki kwa andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ nĩ metũũgagĩria igũrũ rĩao, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na anene ao nĩ mamathaga.  No ti ũguo gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu; no rĩrĩ, ũrĩa ũngĩenda gũtuĩka mũnene thĩinĩ wanyu,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ atuĩke o ngombo yanyu inyuothe.  Tondũ ti-itheru Mũrũ wa mũndũ ndokire gũtungatĩrũo, no atungatanĩre, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>na arute muoyo wake ũtuĩke wa gũkũũra andũ aingĩ.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"es/TiEgQ/kevvowQX0cfUQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Marko 1: 7-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, John nĩ aaheanaga ũhoro, akoiga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ kũrĩ ũgũũka thutha wakwa ũrĩa wĩ na hinya kũrĩ niĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> itaigaine niĩ nyinamĩrĩre njohore mĩkwa ya iratũ ciake.  Niĩ ndĩmũbatithĩtie na maaĩ; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio akamũbatithia na Muoyo Mũtheru.
Na nĩ gwekirũo  atĩrĩ, matukũ macio, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu agĩũka oimĩte Nazareth, itũũra rĩa Galilea, akĩbatithio nĩ John thĩinĩ wa rũũĩ rũa Jordano. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Na kahinda o kau oimĩra maaĩ-inĩ, akĩona Igũrũ rĩemũkĩte,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na  akĩona Muoyo akĩmũikũrũkĩrĩra atariĩ ta ndutura: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ mũgambo ũkiuma Igũrũ ũkiuga atĩrĩ, Wee nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ngenaga nĩ ũndũ waku.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"d96r11R7oEKTh48OLqb4gw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Marko 6:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩthiĩ bũrũri wao; nao arutwo ake makĩmũrũmĩrĩra. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na mũthenya wa thabatũ wakinya akĩgwata kũruta andũ ũhoro thinagoga-inĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na andũ aingĩ maamũigua makĩgega, makĩũria atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũyũ akĩrutĩte maũndũ maya kũ?</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na ningĩ makĩũria: Nĩ atĩa ũũgĩ ũyũ mũndũ ũyũ aheetwo; o na ciĩko icio cia hinya mũnene ũũ ciĩkĩtwo na moko make?</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ũyũ anga towe mũtharamara, o we mũrũ wa Maria, na mũrũ wa nyina na Jakobu na Joseph na Juda na Simone?</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nao airĩtu a nyina anga matitũire o gũkũ gwitũ? Magĩkĩhingwo nĩ ũndũ wake.  Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mũnabii kũndũ aagaga gũkumio no bũrũri wake, na kwa andũ ao,na  gwake nyũmba.  Agĩkĩremwo nĩ gwĩka wĩko wa hinya kũu,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> tiga nĩ andũ amwe arũaru matarĩ aingĩ aaigĩrĩire moko make, akĩmahonia. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Na nĩ aagegire nĩ ũrĩa maaregete gwĩtĩkia.  Yesu agĩcoka gũceeranga mĩciĩ-inĩ akĩrutaga andũ ũhoro. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"43YcWFhMDkaQLLnv4/zQ2Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Mk. 13:33-37</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Yesu nĩ erire arũmĩrĩri ake: Wĩmenyagĩrĩrei, mwĩhũgage na mũhoyage, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>amu mũtiũĩ ihinda rĩrĩa rĩgakinya.  Nĩ ta mũndũ ũtũire ũgeni-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>atigĩte nyũmba yake, na agatigĩra ngombo ciake ũramati,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o ngombo wĩra wayo, na agĩtiga aatha mũikaria wa mũrango o nake aikarage ehũgĩte. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ ũcio ikaragai mwĩhũgĩte, amu mũtiũĩ rĩrĩa mwene nyũmba arĩũka, kana nĩ hwaĩ-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>kana ũtukũ gatagatĩ kana ngũkũ ĩkĩgamba, kana rũcinĩ; ndakae gũũka na kĩguũ amũkore mũkomete.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Na ũguo ndamwĩra inyuĩ, noguo ndera andũ othe, atĩrĩ, ikaragai mwĩhũgĩte.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"y1ucYfhOK06WzM57cqZyHg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI							Marko 16:15-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ  ĩyo Yesu akĩĩonithia arĩa ikũmi na ũmwe na akĩmera atĩrĩ: Thiĩi thĩ yothe mũkahunjĩrie andũ othe Injiri.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũrĩa wa gwĩtĩkia na abatithio nĩ akahonoka; nake ũrĩa wa kũrega gwĩtĩkia nĩ akahootwo ni ciira.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nacio ciama ici nĩcio irĩtwaranaga na arĩa metĩkĩtie:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa nĩ marĩtũmaga ndaimono ciume andũ; na nĩ marĩaragia thiomi njerũ; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ nĩ marĩoyaga nyamũ-cia-thĩ, o na mangĩkanyua kĩndũ kĩngĩrĩa mũndũ gĩtingĩmehia o na atĩa;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩ marĩigagĩrĩra andũ arĩa arũaru moko, nao mahone.  Hĩndĩ ĩo, arĩkia kũmahe ũhoro,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Mwathani Yesu agĩgĩtwarũo Igũrũ, agĩikara thĩ guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nao magĩthiĩ, 
makĩhunjia Ũhoro kũndũ guothe, Mwathani akĩrutaga wĩra hamwe nao,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na agĩĩkagĩra Ũhoro hinya na ciama iria ciatwaranaga naguo.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"YvXSjn/z9ESH59+u3AsKDw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 15:9-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩĩra arũmĩrĩri ake: O ta ũrĩa Ithe witũ anyendete, noguo ndĩmwendete inyuĩ; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ikaragai o na wendo wakwa.  Mwatũũra mũmenyereire maathani makwa, mũgũikara o na wendo wakwa,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa niĩ ndũire menyagĩrĩra maathani ma Awa, ngaikara o na wendo wake.  Ndamwĩra maũndũ macio, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mũgĩe na gĩkeno kĩrĩa ndĩ nakĩo, nakĩo gĩkeno kĩanyu gĩkinyanĩre.  Rĩrĩ nĩrĩo rĩathani rĩakwa,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ mwendane inyuĩ ene, o ta ũrĩa niĩ ndĩmwendete.  Gũtirĩ mũndũ wĩna wendani mũnene kũrĩ ũyũ atĩ mũndũ</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> arute muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wa arata ake.  Inyuĩ mũrĩ arata akwa, mweka maũndũ marĩa ndĩmwathaga.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ndigũcoka kũmwĩta ndungata, tondũ ndungata ndĩmenyaga ũrĩa mũmĩathi egwĩka;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> inyuĩ-rĩ ndĩmũtuĩte arata, nĩ gũkorũo inyuĩ nĩ ndĩmũmenyithĩtie maũndũ  mothe marĩa njiguĩte harĩ Awa. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Ti  inyuĩ mwathurire niĩ, nĩ niĩ ndamũthurire inyuĩ, ngĩmwamũra, nĩ getha mũthiĩ mũciare maciaro,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> namo maciaro manyu matũũre; nĩguo ũndũ o wothe mũkahoya Ithe witũ na rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>akamũhe. Ndĩramwatha ũguo, nĩ getha mwendanage.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"Oi8Rzxng1U+zqvWrvt4n+g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                 Marko 5:21-24, 35-43</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu aarĩkia kũringa rĩngĩ na marikabu, aakinya mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ, kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ gũkĩũngana harĩ we: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nake aarĩ hau hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria.  Na gũgĩũka mũnene ũmwe wa thinagogi, wetagwo Jairũ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na aamuona, akĩmũgũĩra thĩ magũrũ-inĩ, akĩmũthaitha mũno akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Kairĩtu gakwa nĩ gakiriĩ gũkua:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ndagũthaitha ũũke ũgakaigĩrĩre moko maku, nĩguo  kahonio gatũũre muoyo.  Magĩgĩthiĩ nake;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na kĩrĩndĩ  kĩingĩ gĩkĩmuuma thutha, na gĩkamũhatĩkaga.  Na mũtumia watũire oiraga thakame mĩaka ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> akanyamario na maũndũ maingĩ nĩ athondekani aingĩ, na akanina indo ciake ciothe, na ndahone, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>no kwĩhĩrũo akehĩrũo makĩria, ũcio-rĩ, tondũ nĩ aaiguĩte ũhoro wa Yesu, agĩũka na thutha wake thĩ-inĩ wa kĩrĩndĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> akĩmũhutia nguo.  Tondũ nĩ oigire atĩrĩ: ingĩhutia o nguo ciake ciiki ndahona.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Na kahinda o kau rĩurĩro rĩa thakame yake  rĩgĩtuma, akĩigua mwĩrĩ ta aahonio mũrimũ wake. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu, tondũ nĩ aamenyire na ngoro yake atĩ hinya ũrĩa woimaga kũrĩ we ũrĩ kuuma, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>akĩĩhũgũra o rĩmwe e thĩinĩ wa kĩrĩndĩ, akĩũria: Nũ wa’hutia nguo? Nao arutwo ake makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Woria, Nũ wa’hutia, ũkĩonaga kĩrĩndĩ gĩgĩkũhatĩka? Nake akĩroranga one ũrĩa wĩkĩte ũguo.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake mũtumia agĩũka o agĩĩtigagĩra na akĩinainaga, nĩ kũmenya ũrĩa ekĩtwo, akĩmũgũĩra thĩ, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>akĩmũhe ũhoro wothe na ma.  Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Mwarĩ ũyũ, gwĩtĩkia gwaku nĩkuo  gwatũma ũhone;</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> thiĩ na ũhoro, ũikare wĩ mũhonu mũrimũ waku.
Andũ magĩũka moimĩte kwa mũnene ũrĩa wa thunagogi, makiuga: Mwarĩguo nĩ aakua: </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>ũgũcoka gũtanga Mũrutani nĩkĩ? Nake Yesu, atekũũria ũrĩa kweranwo, akĩĩra mũnene wa thunagogi atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Ndũkamake, no gwĩtĩkia wĩtĩkie.  Na ndarĩ mũndũ etĩkĩririe matwarane nake, tiga Petro na Jakubu, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>na John ũrĩa mũrũ wa nyina na Jakubu.  Magĩkinya nyũmba ya mũnene ũcio wa thunagoga; </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>nakuo akĩona ironjo, na andũ aingĩ mekũrĩra na magakaya mũno.  Na aarĩkia gũtonya akĩmoria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>Mũraronja nĩkĩ, na mũkarĩra? Mwana ti mũkuũ, no toro arĩ.  Nao makĩmũthekerera.</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake aarĩkia kũmoimia nja othe, agĩtwara Ithe wa mwana na nyina na arĩa mokĩte nake, agĩtonya kũu mwana aarĩ. </s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384> Akĩnyita mwana gwoko, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: “Talitha kumi”! naguo wataũrũo, nĩ ta kuuga: Kairĩtu gaka, ndakwĩra atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkĩra! Nako kairĩtu gagĩũkĩra  o rĩmwe, gagĩĩtwara; nĩ gũkorũo nĩ kaahingĩtie miaka ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ.</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>  Magĩkĩgega kĩgeganio kĩnene mũno.  Nake akĩmakaania mũno matikamenyithie mũndũ ũhoro ũcio:</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384> agĩcoka akĩmaatha atĩ kairĩtu kaheo gĩa kũrĩa.</s>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"snKlS1MXUkKhERffI4KOVA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Luka 3:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, rĩrĩa Tiberio Cesare aathamakĩte mĩaka ikũmi na ĩtano, o hĩndĩ ĩo, nĩ Pontio Pilato warĩ barũthi wa gwathaga Judea,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nake Herode aarĩ mũthamaki wa mabũrũri ma Iturea na Tarakonitide, nake Lisania aarĩ mũthamaki wa Abilene.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Hĩndĩ ĩo-rĩ, rĩrĩa Anna na Kaifa maarĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene, Ũhoro wa Ngai ũgĩkinya kwĩ John mũrũ wa Zakaria,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> e werũ-inĩ.  Nake agĩkinya ng’ongo  ciothe iria ciarĩ hakuhĩ na Jordano, akĩhunjagia atĩ  andũ mabatithio,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o arĩa merirĩte, nĩguo moherũo mehia mao; o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo Ibuku-inĩ rĩa mohoro ma Isaia mũrathi, atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>He mũgambo wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra  werũ-inĩ, akoiga: Thondekai kĩng’aratua kĩa Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>rũngariani njĩra ciake.  Ihuhi ciothe nĩ igathikwo, ciambatĩre, nacio irĩma ciothe o na ithũngũri ciothe inyihio ciaraganio;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nakuo kũrĩa kuogomu kũrũngario, na kũrĩa gũtarĩ kwaraganu kwaraganio wega; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o na andũ othe nĩ makona kũhonokania kũrĩa kwa Ngai.  </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"Pp0QU27HxUORUUaPzhUTlA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 8:27-35</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu akiuma kũu, o na arutwo ake magĩthiĩ mĩciĩ ya Cesarea ya Filipo: na me njĩra, akĩũria arutwo ake atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ manduaga-ũ?  Makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Kũrĩ moigaga nĩwe John Mũbatithania, na kũrĩ moigaga nĩwe Elia,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ kũrĩ moigaga nĩwe ũmwe wa arathi.  Agĩcoka akĩmoria: Ĩ inyuĩ mũnduaga-ũ?</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Petro agĩcokia ũhoro akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee nĩwe Kristũ.  Nake akĩmakaania matikere mũndũ ũhoro ũcio wake.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Agĩitĩka  kũmaruta atĩ: Mũrũ wa mũndũ ndarĩ hingo atakona mathĩna maingĩ, na aregwo nĩ athuri, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na asacerdoti arĩa anene, na aandĩki-marũa, na ningĩ oragwo, na thutha wa mĩthenya ĩtatũ acoke ariũke.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Naguo ũhoro ũcio akĩwaria atekũhitha.  Nake Petro akĩmũtwara ndundu agĩitĩka kũmũkaania.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nake akĩĩhũgũra, na ona arutwo ake, agĩkaania Petro, akiuga atĩrĩ: Coka na thutha wakwa, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>shaitani: tondũ ndwĩciragia maũndũ ma Ngai, tiga o marĩa ma andũ.  Agĩcoka agĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa kĩarĩ ho,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o na arutwo ake, akĩmera atĩrĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũkwenda kũnũmĩrĩra, nĩ erege, na oe mũtĩ wake wa kwambĩrũo, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>anyume thutha.  Amu-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe wendaga gũtũũria muoyo wake, ũcio nĩ kũũrũo akorũo nĩguo;</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> na mũndũ o wothe ũkorũo nĩ muoyo wake nĩ ũndũ wakwa na wa Injiri, ũcio nĩ kũũtũria akaũtũũria.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"6e+aYeTB4UeY0VuLv/6w4A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 10:2-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Afarisei mokire kũrĩ Yesu, makĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Watho nĩ wĩtĩkĩrĩtie mũndũ ate mũtumia wake? Na nĩ kũmũgeria maamũgeragia. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩcokia ũhoro akĩmoria: Musa aamwathire atĩa? Makiuga:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Musa nĩ etĩkĩragia mũndũ aandĩke marũa ma gũtigana nake amũte.  Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Aamwandĩkĩire rĩathana rĩu nĩ ũndũ wa kũũma kwa ngoro cianyu.  No kuuma o kĩambĩrĩria rĩrĩa indo ciothe ciombirũo, gũtũire kwĩragwo ũũ:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Aamombire marĩ mũndũ mũrũme na mũndũ mũka.  Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũndũ mũrũme nĩ agatigana na ithe na nyina,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> magwatane na mũtumia wake, nao erĩ matuĩke mwĩrĩ ũmwe; ũguo-rĩ, matingĩcoka gũtuĩka erĩ, no mwĩrĩ ũmwe. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, arĩa Ngai agwatanĩtie, mũndũ ndakanamatigithanie. Na me nyũmba thĩinĩ, arutwo makĩmũũria rĩngĩ ũhoro ũcio.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũndũ o wothe wa gũte mũtumia wake, ahikie ũngĩ-rĩ, ha ũhoro wake nĩ atharĩtie: </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nake mũtumia we mwene angĩte mũthuriwe, ahikio nĩ ũngĩ,  nĩ atharĩtie.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ andũ makĩmũtwarĩra twana, atĩ atũhutie: nao arutwo makĩmakaania.  Nake Yesu ona ũguo akĩrakara, akĩmera atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Rekei twana tũũke kũrĩ niĩ, mũtige gũtũgiria: amu ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩ wa arĩa matariĩ tatuo.  Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ na ma: </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Mũndũ o wothe ũtakaamũkĩra ũthamaki wa Ngai ta kaana,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> ndagatonya guo o na atĩa.  Agĩcoka agĩtũiyũkia moko-inĩ make, agĩtũrathima agĩtũigagĩrĩra moko.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"jug6vXxEuEKc6o7DjNKCng",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 4:1-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akiuma kũu Jordano aiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo Mũtheru, agĩtwarũo nĩ Muoyo werũ-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>aikare kũu matukũ mĩrongo ĩna, akĩgeragio nĩ shaitani.  Na matukũ macio ndaarĩaga kĩndũ o na kĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>namo maathira, akĩhũta.  Nake shaitani akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ongorũo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai, ĩra ihiga rĩrĩ rĩtuĩke mũgate. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ũhoro nĩ wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: Ti mũgate wiki ũtũũragia mũndũ muoyo. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ agĩcoka akĩmũtwara kĩrĩma igũrũ, akĩmuonia mothamaki mothe ma thĩ o kahinda kanini ma.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake shaitani agĩcoka akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wathani wa gwathaga kũu guothe nĩ ngũkũhe, o na mwago wakuo:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ kũheo nĩ heetwo niĩ: na mũndũ o ũrĩa ingĩenda kũhe, ndamũhe.   Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, ũngĩĩtĩkĩra kũndurĩria ndu o haha ndĩ, ũhoe,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> ũcio wothe nĩ ũgũtuĩka waku.  Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ũhoro nĩ wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Turagĩria Mwathani Ngai waku ndu ũmũhoyage, na ũmũtungatagĩre o we wiki.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Agĩcoka akĩmũtwara Jerusalemu, akĩmũrũgamia o igũrũ gathũrũmũndũ-inĩ ka hekarũ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ongorũo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai, wĩtungumanie thĩ uumĩte haha: nĩ gũkorũo ũhoro nĩ wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ agaatha araika ake nĩ ũndũ waku, nĩ getha magũikaragie: na ningĩ atĩrĩ: Nĩ magakwanĩrĩria na moko mao, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>ndũkae kũgũthwo kũgũrũ nĩ ihiga.  Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: Ningĩ nĩ kwĩranĩtwo atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:" Ndũkanagerie Mwathani Ngai waku.  Nake shaitani aarĩkia kũmũgeria magerio macio mothe, agĩtigana nake ihinda."},{ID:17,
Text:"Injiri theru ya Mwathani "}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"gamK9RRu0UiuZev5HDjRqg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         John 1:6-8;19-28</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gwokire mũndũ wareketio nĩ Ngai, wetagwo John, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũndũ ũcio okire nĩ ũndũ wa ũira, oimbũre ũhoro wa ũtheri ũcio, nĩ getha andũ othe metĩkie nĩ ũndũ  wake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Na tiwe ũtheri ũcio; okire no getha oimbũre ũhoro waguo, ũtheri ũcio.
Ũira wa John naguo nĩ ũyũ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> rĩrĩa Ayahudi mamũrekeirie  athĩnjĩri Ngai na Alawii, me Jerusalemu, makamũrie, Wee nĩwe ũ? Akiumbũra na ndahithe; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>agĩkiumbũra akiuga, Niĩ ti niĩ Kristũ.  Nao  makĩmũũria, Ningĩ nĩ atĩa? Nĩwe Elia? Nake akiuga, Ti niĩ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũkĩrĩ mũnabii ũrĩa? Nake agĩcokia, Aca.  Tondũ ũcio makĩmũũria atĩrĩ, Ningĩ nĩwe ũ? nĩguo tũhũndũrĩre arĩa maatũrekirie ũhoro,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkuuga atĩa ũhoro waku? Nake akiuga atĩrĩ, Nĩ niĩ mũgambo wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra werũ-inĩ akoiga,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Rũngariani njĩra ya Mwathani, o ta ũrĩa Isaia  ũrĩa mũnabii oigire.  Na andũ acio maareketio nĩ Afarisai,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> magĩcoka ningĩ kũmũũria,  makĩmwĩra  atĩrĩ, Rĩu-rĩ, ongorũo tiwe Kristũ, na tiwe Elia, na tiwe mũnabii  ũrĩa-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ũkĩbatithagia andũ nĩ ũndũ kĩ? Nake John akĩmacokeria akiuga, Niĩ mbatithanagia na maaĩ: o gũkũ kwanyu nĩ kũrũngiĩ mũndũ ũngĩ mũtoĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa ũgũũka thutha wakwa, itaigaine niĩ njohore mũkwa wa kĩratũ gĩake.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>  Maũndũ macio mekĩirũo Bethania mũrĩmo ũrĩa wa Jordano, o kũu John aarĩ Kũbatithania.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"VsMRy1kMKEyufBTIABYqHA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    Mathayo 13:54-58</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu aakinya bũrũri wao, akĩruta andũ ũhoro thunagogi-inĩ yao, o nginya makĩgega, makiuga, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mũndũ ũyũ akĩrutĩte kũ ũũgĩ ũyũ, o na ciĩko ici cia hinya? Githĩ ũyũ tiwe mũrũ wa mũndũ ũrĩa mũtharamara? Nake nyina ndetagwo Mariamu? </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nao ariũ a nyina ti aa Jakubu, na Jusufu, na Simoni, na Juda? Nao airĩtu a nyina, anga matitũire gwitũ othe? </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Kaĩ mũndũ ũyũ akĩrutĩte kũ maũndũ macio mothe? Nao makĩhĩngithio nĩ ũndũ wake.  Nake Jesũ akĩmera,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Mũnabii-rĩ, kũndũ aagaga gũkumio no bũrũri wao, na kwao mũciĩ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake ndaigana gwĩka ciĩko nyingĩ cia hinya kũu nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa maagĩte kũmwĩtĩkia.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"T50sGAe0f06Nh8Urgxet6Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI						John 15:26-27;16:12-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, Mũteithia aarĩkia gũũka, ũrĩa ngarekia oke kũrĩ inyuĩ oimĩte gwĩ Ithe  witũ, o we Roho ũrĩa wa ma, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa uumanaga na Ithe witũ, we nĩagatuĩka mũira wakwa; o na inyuĩ mũrĩ o aira,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ mũtũire na niĩ gwata kĩambĩrĩria.
Nĩndigairie maũndũ maingĩ ma kũmwĩra, no mũtingĩhota kũmetiiria rĩu. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, ũcio Roho wa ma oka, we nĩakamũtongoria amuumĩrĩrie ũhoro-inĩ ũrĩa wa ma wothe;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ ndakaaragia na kwĩĩra gwake mwene, ĩndĩ maũndũ o mothe marĩa akaigua, nomo akoiga;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩakamuumbũrĩra maũndũ marĩa magoka thutha.  We nĩ niĩ akagocithia;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ maũndũ makwa akanyitaga, amuumbũragĩre.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Maũndũ o mothe marĩa ithe witũ  e namo nĩ makwa; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nĩkĩo ndoiga atĩ nĩ maũndũ makwa akanyitaga, amuumbũragĩre inyui</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri therũ ya Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"XXuHPGbJTEaMfcT0wgszIQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 25:14-30</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:
Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩmahe ũhoro rĩngĩ na ngerekano:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846> mũndũ wathiaga ũgeni, agĩĩta ndungata ciake agĩcine indo ciake. Akĩne ĩmwe yacio taranda ithano, na ĩngĩ taranda igĩrĩ, na ĩngĩ taranda ĩmwe:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846> o ndungata kũringana na ũhoti wayo: agĩgĩthiĩ ũgeni.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846>Na kahinda o kau ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda ithano ĩgĩthiĩ, ĩkĩonjorithia nacio, ĩkĩona ĩngĩ ithano.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846>  Nayo ĩrĩa yaneirũo igĩrĩ ĩgĩĩka o taguo, ĩkĩona ingĩ igĩrĩ.  No ĩrĩa yaneirũo ĩmwe ĩgĩthiĩ ĩkĩenja thĩ, ĩkĩhitha mbia cia mwathani wayo.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846>Na rĩrĩ, matukũ maingĩ maathira, mwathani wa ndungata icio akĩinũka gwake mũciĩ, agĩciĩta iheane ũhoro wa mbia ciake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846>  Na ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda ithano ĩgĩũka ĩkiuga: mwathani, nĩ waneire taranda ithano:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1846> atĩrĩ, nĩ nyumithĩtie taranda ingĩ ithano.  Nake Mwathani wayo akĩmĩĩra: Nĩ wĩkĩte wega, ndungata ĩno njega na ya kwĩhokeka:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1846> nĩ wĩhokekete na indo itarĩ nyingĩ, nĩ ngũgũtua mwathi wa indo nyingĩ: tonya gĩkeno-inĩ kĩa mwathani waku.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1846>Nayo ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda igĩrĩ o nayo ĩgĩũka ĩkĩmwĩra: Mwathani, nĩ waneire taranda igĩrĩ, atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1846> nĩ nyumithĩtie taranda ingĩ igĩrĩ.  Nake mwathani wayo akĩmĩĩra: Nĩ wĩkĩte wega, ndungata ĩno njega na ya kwĩhokeka; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1846>nĩ wĩhokekete na indo itarĩ nyingĩ, nĩ ngũgũtua mwathi wa indo nyingĩ:</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1846> tonya gĩkeno-inĩ kĩa mwathani waku.  Nayo ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda ĩmwe ĩgĩũka kũrĩ we ĩkĩmwĩra:</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1846> Mwathani, nĩ ndakũũĩ atĩ wĩ mũndũ mwĩĩ, ũgethaga kũrĩa ũtahandire, na ũcokagĩrĩria kũrĩa ũtaahurire; </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1846>ngĩgĩĩtigĩra, ngĩthiĩ ngĩhitha taranda yaku thĩ: atĩrĩrĩ, ĩno nĩyo ĩrĩa yaku ndagũcokeria. </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1846> Nowe mwathani wayo agĩcokia, akĩmĩĩra atĩrĩ: Ndungata ĩno njũru na ngũtaru,</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1846> nĩ woĩ atĩ nĩ ngethaga kũrĩa itaahandire, na ngacokereria kũrĩa itaahurire;</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1846> nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩ waagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũiga mbia ciakwa kũrĩ andũ arĩa monjorithagia mbia, na ndacoka-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1846>nĩ ingĩacokerio mbia ciakwa o na uumithio wacio. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũtunyei taranda ĩo, na mũhe ũrĩa wĩna taranda iria ikũmi.</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1846>  Nĩ gũkorũo mũndũ o wothe wĩ na indo, nĩwe ũkaheo, na akĩrĩrĩrio; no ũrĩa ũtarĩ na indo,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1846> nĩ agatunyũo o na kĩrĩa arĩ nakĩo. Nayo ndungata ĩo ĩtarĩ bata mũmĩikie na kũu nja kwĩ na nduma:</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1846> kũu nĩkuo gũkagĩa kĩrĩro na kũharagania magego.</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"U0Nen5Qln0u78mz9fWZ34w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 20:1-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthenya wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia Maria wa Magdala akĩroka mbĩrĩra-inĩ rũcinĩ tene, kũrĩ o nduma, akĩona ihiga rĩĩ ithengie muungu-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Agĩgĩteng’era agĩthiĩ gwĩ Simone Petro, na kwĩ mũrutwo ũrĩa ũngĩ, ũrĩa Yesu endete, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Nĩ marutĩte mwathani muungu-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> tũtiũĩ harĩa mamũigĩte.  Petro agĩkiumagara o na mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ, magĩthiĩ marorete mbĩrĩra-inĩ mbere: Makĩgwata gũteng’era o erĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nake mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ agĩkĩria Petro ihenya agĩkinya muungu-inĩ mbere; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>aainamĩrĩra aarora thĩinĩ akĩona matama marĩa ma gatani me maige thĩ na ndatonye. Simone Petro nake agĩgĩũka, amũrũmĩrĩire,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> agĩtonya mungu thĩinĩ;  nake akĩona matama macio ma gatani me maige thĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o na gĩtambaya nakĩo kĩrĩa kĩarĩ mũtwe wake, gĩtaigĩtwo hamwe na matama macio ma gatani, nĩ gũkũnjwo  gĩakũnjĩtwo gĩkaigwo handũ mwanya. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Hĩndĩ ĩo mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ nake agĩtonya, ũcio waambire gũkinya muungu-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nake akĩona, agĩĩtĩkia.  Amu nginya hĩndĩ ĩo matiamenyete wega ũhoro ũrĩa wandĩkĩtwo, atĩ no mũhaka acoke ariũke  oime kwĩ arĩa akuũ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"0Tmkv50oE0Ss6Y5cvzOPBQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 13:1-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ haarĩ andũ amwe ho maamwĩrire ũhoro wa Agalilea arĩa Pilato aatukanirie thakame yao na ĩrĩa ya nyamũ ciao cia magongona. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akĩmacokeria akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Githĩ mũgwĩciria atĩ Agalilea acio maarĩ ehia gũkĩra Agalilea  othe, kuona atĩ nĩ maanyaririrũo ũguo? </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Tiguo: no rĩrĩ, mũngĩaga kwĩrira, inyuothe mũkaninwo o tao.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Kana andũ acio ikũmi na anana-rĩ, o arĩa maagũĩrĩirũo nĩ nyũmba ĩrĩa ndaya na igũrũ kũu Siloe, ĩkĩmoraga,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> githĩ mũkĩũĩ atĩ nĩ maahĩtĩtie gũkĩra andũ othe arĩa maatũire Jerusalemu? Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Tiguo: no rĩrĩ, mũngĩaga kwĩrira, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>inyuothe mũkaninwo o tao.  Nake akĩaria na ngerekano ĩno, akiuga atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũmwe aarĩ na mũkũyũ wahandĩtwo mũgũnda wake wa mĩthabibũ; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nake agĩũka gũcaria maciaro mũtĩ-inĩ ũcio, akĩmaaga.  Agĩcoka akĩĩra mũcehi wa mĩthabibũ, atĩrĩrĩ: rĩu nĩ mĩaka ĩtatũ njũkaga gũcaria  maciaro mũkũyũ-inĩ ũyũ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o ngĩmaagaga: ũũteme, wĩkagĩra mũgũnda kiura nĩkĩ? Nake mũcehi agĩcokia akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwathani, reka ũikare mwaka ũyũ o naguo, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o kinya ndĩũrĩmĩre, na ndĩũitĩrĩrie thumu: na thutha wa ũguo, ũgĩciara, nĩ wega; na ũngĩaga gũciara, no ũtemwo.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"/8HQ8eByW0yWvcCnVF+7rA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                John 8:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩthiĩ kĩrĩma kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ.  Ningĩ rũcinĩ tene agĩcoka o hekarũ-inĩ, na andũ othe magĩthiĩ kũrĩ we; nake agĩikara thĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>akĩgwata kũmaruta ũhoro.  Nao aandĩki-marũa ma Afarisei makĩrehe mũtumia wanyitirũo agĩtharia,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na maarĩkia kũmũrũgamia gatatĩ-ini, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Mũrutani, mũndũ mũka ũyũ aanyitwo o agĩtharia. Rĩu-rĩ, watho-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Musa aatwĩrire tũhũre aka ta acio na mahiga nyuguto tũmorage; wee ũgũkiuga atĩa ũhoro wake?  Na moigire ũguo mamũgerie, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mone ũndũ wa kũmũthitakĩra.  Nake Yesu akĩinamĩrĩra, akĩgwata kwandĩka thĩ na kĩara.  Ningĩ maakĩrũmanĩria kũmũũria, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>agĩĩtiira, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Inyuĩ ũrĩa ũtarĩ ehia-rĩ, nĩ akĩambe amũikĩrie ihiga.  Agĩcoka o kũĩnamĩrĩra, akĩandĩka thĩ na kĩara. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nao, maaigua ũguo, makĩgwata kuuma ũmwe ũmwe, marutĩtie harĩ arĩa akũrũ, o nginya ũrĩa wa kũrigĩrĩria; Yesu agĩtigwo wiki,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na mũtumia arũngiĩ o hau gatagatĩ.  Nake Yesu agĩĩtiira, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ:  Me ha, mũtumia ũyũ? Anga gũtirĩ mũndũ wagũtuĩra? </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nake akiuga: Gũtirĩ, Mwathani.  Nake Yesu akiuga atĩrĩ: Na niĩ ndigũgũtuĩra; thiĩ, thutha ũyũ ndũkanacoke kwĩhia.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"U2VPa9gdiESazbzoVitYnQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                John 13:31-33, 34-35</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:
 </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Juda oima nyũmba-inĩ ya irĩĩro, Yesu agĩkiuga atĩrĩrĩ: Rĩu nĩ hĩndĩ Mũrũ wa mũndũ agoocithĩtio nake Ngai akagoocithio e thĩinĩ wake.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩ, Ngai aakorũo agoocithĩtio e thĩinĩ wake, Ngai o nake nĩ ekũmũgoocithia  e thĩinĩ wake mwene, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ekũmũgoocithia o narua.  Twana tũtũ, no kahinda kanini ndigairie ga gũikarania na inyuĩ.  Rĩu ngũmũhe rĩathani  rĩerũ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ atĩ mwendane; o ta ũguo niĩ ndĩmwendete, inyuĩ mwendane o ro ũguo inyuene.  Nĩ ũguo  andu othe marĩmenyaga mũrĩ  arutwo akwa, mwatũũra mwendaine.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI"},{Guid:"NyLbKSdkpkShsfRctC+Qug",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    Luka 24:35-48</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Arutwo makĩheana ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa moneire njĩra-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na ũrĩa emenyithirie kũrĩ o na ũndũ wa kwenyũra mũgate.  Ningĩ o makĩaragia maũndũ macio-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>We mwene akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ kao, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũrogia na thayũ. Nao magĩtuĩka nda magĩĩtigĩra mũno,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> makĩĩgereria atĩ nĩ ngoma mekuona.  Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgũtangĩka nĩkĩ? Na nĩ kĩ gĩgũtũma mũgĩe na mathangania ngoro-inĩ cianyu? Rorai moko makwa, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o na magũrũ makwa, atĩ nĩ niĩ mwene; ‘hambatani, mwĩonere;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo ngoma ndĩrĩ mwĩrĩ na mahĩndĩ ta ũũ mũkũona ndĩ nacio.  Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, akĩmonia moko make,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o na magũrũ.  Nao maakorũo matarĩ maretĩkia nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa makenete na makagega-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Mũrĩ na irio haha? Nao makĩmũhe gĩcunjĩ gĩa kĩũngũyũ kĩhĩhie.  Nake agĩkĩoya, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>akĩrĩa o makĩĩonagĩra.
Agĩcoka akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ici nĩcio ciugo ciakwa iria ndamwĩrire rĩrĩa ndatũire na inyuĩ, ngĩmwĩra atĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Gũtirĩ hingo maũndũ mothe matakahingio, o marĩa maandĩkĩtwo ũhoro wakwa watho-inĩ wa Musa, o na mabuku-inĩ ma anabii, o na thaburi-inĩ. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Hĩndĩ ĩo agĩcoka akĩmahe ũũgĩ, mamenye wega Maandĩko: agĩkĩmera atĩrĩ, Ũũ nĩguo wandĩkĩtwo Maandĩko-inĩ atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ no mũhaka Kristũ anyarirĩke, na acoke kũriũka oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ mũthenya wa gatatũ; </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>no ningĩ atĩ ũhoro wa kwĩrira na kuohanĩrũo mehia ũkahunjĩrio ndũrĩrĩ ciothe na rĩĩtwa rĩake,</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> na kwambĩrĩrio o kũu Jerusalem.
Na inyuĩ nĩ inyuĩ aira a maũndũ macio.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"jtbVsrWEh0+gwk3LYBL+yA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 22:15-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Afarisai maigua ta ũrĩa Yesu akirĩtie Asadukai magĩthiĩ ndundu nĩguo mamenye ũrĩa mangĩhota kũmũtega akĩaria. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Magĩtũma arutwo ao me na Aherodia kũrĩ we, makiuga atĩrĩ; Mũrutani ũyũ, nĩ tũũĩ atĩ ũrĩ wa ma,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o na atĩ nĩ ũrutanaga ũhoro wa njĩra ya Ngai na ma, o na ndũũragia irũngo rĩa mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ ndũroraga ũrĩa andũ matariĩ gĩthiithi.  Nĩ ũndũ ũcio rĩ, ta twĩre ũrĩa ũgwĩciria. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ wega Cesare arutagĩrũo mbia cia igoti, kana ti wega? Nowe Yesu akĩmenya ũũru wao akĩmacokeria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>mũkũngeria nĩkĩ, hinga ici? Nyoniai kĩrĩa mũrutaga kĩa igoti.  Nao makĩmũtwarĩra ciringi.  Nake akĩmoria atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Mũhianano ũyũ na rĩĩtwa rĩrĩ nĩ cia ũ? Makĩmwĩra: Nĩ cia Cesare. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nake akĩmera: Tondũ ũcio nengagĩrai Cesare indo iria cia Cesare, o nake Ngai, mũmũnengagĩre indo cia Ngai.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"gTHER0DwtEyRZojv4Wdbmg",Verses:[{
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 7:31-37"},{ID:2,
Text:"GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:"},{ID:3,
Text:"Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu, agĩcoka akiuma kũu bũrũri wa Tiro, agĩtũrĩkĩria Sidone, agĩkinya iria rĩa Galilea, atuĩkanĩtie bũrũri wa Dekapoli gatagatĩ."},{ID:4,
Text:"  Makĩmũrehere mũndũ gĩtaigua, na warogoyaga; makĩmũthaitha amũigĩrĩre guoko.  "},{ID:5,
Text:"Nake akĩmwamũrania na kĩrĩndĩ akĩmũtwara keheri-inĩ, agĩtonyia ciara matũ ma mũndũ ũcio, "},{ID:5,
Text:"agĩtua mata, akĩmũhutia rũrĩmĩ; akĩrora igũrũ, akĩhũmũka, akĩmwĩra:  Effata, ũguo nĩ’rĩ: Hingũka.  Matũ make magĩkĩhingũka, naguo ,"},{ID:6,
Text:"mũkiha wa rũrĩmĩ rwake ũkĩregera, akĩaria o wega.  Nake akĩmakaania matikere mũndũ; "},{ID:7,
Text:"nao o aakĩria kũmakaania, noguo maakĩragia kũmemerekia ũhoro ũcio o mũno.  "},{ID:8,
Text:"Na nĩ maagegete mũno mũno, makoiga atĩrĩ: Nĩ ekĩte maũndũ mothe wega: arĩa mataiguaga nĩ atũmaga maigue, nao arĩa matahotaga kwaria atũma maarie."},{ID:9,
Text:"Injiri theru ya Mwathani "}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI Marko 7:31-37		"},{Guid:"ZOM6fTC2P0+NHnc6FgMoiw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			            Luka 21: 25-28, 34-36</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu nĩ erire arũmĩrĩri ake: nĩ gũkagĩa imenyithia riũa-inĩ, na njata-inĩ;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nakuo gũkũ thĩ ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikanyarirĩka, ikĩrigagwo nĩ ũrĩa iria rĩrĩa inene rĩkarurumaga, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>rĩĩ na makũmbĩ manene.  Nao andũ nĩ makaringagwo nĩ iringi nĩ ũndũ wa gũtubunyĩka,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o magĩetagĩrĩra maũndũ marĩa magakinya gũkũ thĩ; nĩ gũkorũo mahinya ma kũrĩa igũrũ nĩ makenyenyio.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Na hĩndĩ ĩo nĩguo makona Mũrũ wa mũndũ agĩũka na itu, arĩ na hinya na riri mũingĩ.  No rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maũndũ macio makarĩka gũkinya-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>rorai na igũrũ, na mũtiire mĩtwe yanyu; nĩ gũkorũo hingo yanyu ya gũkũũrũo nĩ ĩkuhĩhĩirie.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩndĩ wimenyagĩrĩrei arĩ inyuĩ, nĩ getha ngoro cianyu itikanakorũo ititikithĩtio ũrĩi, na ũrĩu, na mĩhang’o ya muoyo  ũyũ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> naguo mũthenya ũcio ũmũhobanĩrie narua ta arĩ mũtego: nĩ gũkorũo nĩ ũkahobanĩria andũ arĩa othe magakorũo matũire gũkũ thĩ guothe. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, ikaragai mwĩiguĩte mahinda mothe, mũkĩhoyaga  Ngai nĩ getha mũkahota kũhonoka maũndũ-inĩ macio mothe magoka, na mũhote kũrũgama mbere ya Mũrũ wa mũndũ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"A5h9SjQi/E2doDpvADy4AA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Luka 3:39-48</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ macio Maria agĩũkĩra matukũ macio, agĩthiĩ ahiũhĩte bũrũri ũrĩa wa Zakaria, akĩgeithia Elisabeth.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Na gũgĩtuĩka atĩrĩ, rĩrĩa Elisabeth aaiguire ngeithi icio cia Maria, kaana gake gakĩambarara  karĩ nda thĩinĩ;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nake Elisabeth akĩiyũrũo nĩ Muoyo Mũtheru, akĩanĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene, akiuga atĩrĩ</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>: Kũrathimwo nĩwe kũrĩ andũ-a-nja othe; o nako karĩa ũgaciara no karathime.  Na niĩ-rĩ, ũndũ ũyũ ũnyumĩte kũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ nyina wa Mwathani wakwa oke anjeerere? Nĩ ũndũ atĩrĩ, mũgambo wa ngeithi ciaku wakinya matũ-inĩ makwa,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> kaana nĩ kaambarara nda yakwa thĩinĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa gũkena.  Na gũkena-rĩ, nĩ  ũcio wetĩkirie;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo maũndũ marĩa erirũo nĩ Mwathani nĩ makahingio.  Nake Maria akiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ngoro yakwa nĩ ĩrakumia Mwathani, naguo muoyo wakwa nĩ ũkeneire Ngai Mũhonokia wakwa. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ nĩ arorete ũrĩa ndungata yake ĩĩnyihĩtie: tondũ rĩrĩ, kuuma rĩu njiaro ciothe nĩ irĩnduaga mũkenu.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"uHzP6NoEVEiKIyE1Nrm5Sg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 6:27-38</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu erire arũmĩrĩri ake: ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ inyuĩ mũrathikĩrĩria: endagai thũ cianyu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na mwĩkage wega arĩa mamũnenaga, na ningĩ mũrathimage arĩa mamũrumaga, na mũhoyagĩre arĩa mamũcambagia. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, mũndũ wa gũkũringa rũthĩa rũmwe, mũhũgũkĩrie rũrĩa rũngĩ naruo: na ũrĩa wa gũgũtunya nguo yaku ya igũrũ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ndũkamũgirie athiĩ na nguo ĩrĩa ya thĩinĩ o nayo.  O mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũgũkũhoya kĩndũ, mũhe; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na ũrĩa ũngĩgũtunya indo ciaku, ndũkamũrandũre.  Na rĩrĩ, o ũrĩa mwendaga gwĩkwo nĩ andũ, mekagei o ũguo.  Rĩu-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> mũngĩkorũo mwendaga  o arĩa mamwendaga inyuĩ, mũkĩrĩ na ngatho ĩrĩkũ? Nĩ gũkorũo ehia nao nĩ mendaga andũ arĩa mamendaga.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Na ningĩ, mũngĩkorũo mwĩkaga wega inyuĩ, mũkĩrĩ na ngatho ĩrĩkũ? Nĩ gũkorũo ehia nao nĩ mekaga o ũguo. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ mũngĩkorũo muohoragĩra o arĩa mwĩhokete atĩ nĩ makamũrĩha, mũkĩrĩ na ngatho ĩrĩkũ?</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo o na andũ ehia nĩ mohoragĩra ehia angĩ, nĩ getha
Magacokagĩrio indo ciiganaine na iria maarutire. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, endagai thũ cianyu, na mũciĩkage wega, o na mũohoranagĩre, mũtegwĩkũũĩra mũndũ,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> na igai rĩanyu rĩgatuĩka rĩnene, na nĩ mũgatuĩka ariũ a Ũrĩa-wĩ-Igũrũ-mũno: nĩ gũkorũo we nĩ atugaga arĩa matacokagia ngatho, o na arĩa oru.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>  Iguanagĩrai tha o ta ũrĩa Ithe wanyu nake aiguanagĩra tha.  Ningĩ mũtikanekũũanĩre,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> na inyuĩ ene mũtikanekũũĩrũo: mũtikanatuanĩre, na mũtikanatuĩrũo: ohanagĩrai na nĩ mũkoherũo:</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> heanagai, na nĩ mũkaheo; mũgererũo na kĩgeri kĩrĩa kĩega, o kĩrĩa gĩkindĩrĩtwo na gĩthukathukĩtwo, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>na kĩrĩa kĩhũmbĩrĩirũo o kinya irio igaitĩka thĩ, nokĩo mũkaheo nakĩo na kiunĩrũo nguo-inĩ cianyu. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo o kĩgeri kĩrĩa mũgeranagĩra nakĩo, nĩkĩo mũgacoka kũgeragĩrũo nakĩo.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"CNdwVgV8g0yPCtWP3f+viw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 15:1-3, 11-32</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo etia mbia cia igoti o na ehia nĩ maathengereire othe Yesu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha mamũigue.  Nao Afarisei na aandĩki-marũa makĩng’ong’ora makĩĩranaga atĩrĩ:  Mũndũ ũyũ nĩ aamũkagĩra ehia akarĩanĩra nao. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake akĩmera ngerekano ĩno, akiuga atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũmwe aarĩ  na ariũ eerĩ: nake ũrĩa mũnyinyi  akĩĩra ithe atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Awa, ngaĩra indo o iria ingĩgatuĩka  ciakwa.  Nake ithe akĩmagayania indo ciake ciothe.  Na matukũ manyinyi maathira, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mũriũ ũcio mũnyinyi akĩũngania indo ciake ciothe, akĩgwata njĩra, agĩthiĩ bũrũri warĩ kũraya;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> agĩitanga indo ciake ciothe kũu na mĩtũũrĩre ya ũmaramari.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nake aanina indo ciake ciothe, gũkĩgĩa ng’aragu nene mũno bũrũri ũcio; nake agĩitĩka kũhũta na gũthĩna.  Agĩthiĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> akĩĩiguithania na mũndũ wa bũrũri  ũcio; nake mũndũ ũcio akĩmũrekia akariithie ngũrũe gĩthaka-inĩ gĩake.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nake nĩ endaga mũno kwĩhũnia  na makoro ma maciaro  ma mũtĩ wa mũkarabi, marĩa maarĩagwo nĩ ngũrũe; na gũtirĩ mũndũ wamũheire kĩndũ.  </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩa ecokerire, akiuga atĩrĩ: Hĩ! Nĩ ndungata ciigana atĩa cia awa irĩ na irio cia gũciigana, na igatigara, na niĩ nĩ ngũkuĩra gũkũ nĩ ng’aragu! Nĩ ngũũkĩra ‘thiĩ kũrĩ awa,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> ngamwĩra atĩrĩ: Awa, nĩ njĩhĩtie Igũrũ, o na ngakwĩhia wee: ndiagĩrĩirwo nĩ gũcoka gwĩtagwo mũrũguo: ndua ta ndungata ĩmwe yaku.  </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩũkĩra agĩthiĩ kũrĩ ithe.  No rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aarĩ o haraya, ithe akĩmuona, akĩringwo nĩ tha, akĩhanyũka akĩmũhĩmbĩria ngingo, akĩmũmumunya mũno. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Nake mũriũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Awa, nĩ njĩhĩtie Igũrũ, o na ngakwĩhia wee, na ndiagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũcoka gwĩtagwo mũrũguo.  No ithe akĩĩra ndungata ciake atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Thiĩi narua, mũgĩre nguo ĩrĩa njega mũmũhumbe; na mũmwĩkĩre gĩcũhĩ kĩara na iratũ magũrũ; ningĩ mũcoke mũrehe njaũ ya gĩcegũ ĩrĩa noru mũmĩthĩnje,</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> tũrĩe na tũcanjamũke, nĩ gũkorũo mũriũ ũyũ wakwa ararĩ mũkuũ, na nĩ mũriũku; ningĩ nĩ arorĩte, na nĩ acokete kuoneka.  Nao magĩitĩka gũcanjamũka. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, mũriũ  ũrĩa mũkũrũ aatindĩte mũgũnda: na rĩrĩa aainũkaga, aakuhĩhĩria nyũmba-rĩ, akĩigua mĩtũrirũ ĩkĩhuhwo, gũkĩinagwo rũĩmbo.  </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Agĩgĩĩta ndungata ĩmwe ya mũciĩ, akĩmĩũria gĩtũmi kĩa maũndũ macio.  Nayo ĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa nyũkwa nĩ okĩte; nake thoguo nĩ athĩnjĩte  njaũ ya gĩcegũ ĩrĩa noru, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ nĩ aamũcokerera arĩ mũgima.  Nake akĩrakara, akĩrega gũtonya nyũmba, ĩndĩ ithe akiuma nja akĩmũthaitha atonye.  Nowe agĩcokia akĩĩra ithe atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384> Ndanakũrutĩra wĩra mĩaka mĩingĩ, na ndirĩ ndagarara rĩathani rĩaku o rĩothe; no ndũrĩ wa’he o na kori tũthĩnje, tũcanjamũke na arata akwa: no rĩrĩ, mũrũguo oka,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384> ũcio waninire indo ciaku ciothe na aka a maraya, nĩ wamũthĩnjĩra njaũ ya gĩcegũ ĩrĩa noru.  Nake ithe akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee nĩ ũtũũraga na niĩ hĩndĩ ciothe,</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384> nacio indo iria ciothe ndĩ nacio nĩ ciaku.  No rĩrĩ, nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũcanjamũke na tũkene; nĩ gũkorũo ũcio mũrũ wa nyũkwa ararĩ mũkuũ, na nĩ mũriũku; ningĩ nĩ arorĩte, na nĩ acokete kuoneka.</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"/lH3x9EO30y6JtrJqFzNxQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 7:1-8,14-15,21-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Afarisai na aandĩki-marũa amwe nĩ marũrũnganire kũrĩ Yesu, moimĩte Jerusalem,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na makona atĩ arutwo ake amwe maarĩaga irio ciao na moko mathũku, nĩguo matarĩ mathambie.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Amu Afarisai, o na Ayahudi othe, matingĩrĩa irio mataambĩte gwĩthamba moko o wega,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ kũigua kĩrĩra gĩa athuri: na moima kĩng’ang’a-inĩ, matingĩrĩa mataambĩte gwĩthamba: </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o na kwĩ maũndũ mangĩ maingĩ marutĩte tene-inĩ mekage, mathambia ma ikombe na tũnyũngũ o na nyũngũ cia mũthemba wa gĩcango. 
 
Nao Afarisai acio na aandĩki-marũa makĩmũria atĩrĩ: Arutwo aku matiganĩte na kĩrĩra gĩa athuri nĩkĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> makarĩaga irio ciao na moko mathũku? Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Isaia nĩ aarathire ũhoro wanyu wega ma, hinga ici, ta harĩa haandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ aya mandĩaga na mĩromo, no ngoro ciao ii kũraya na niĩ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  No kaĩ maturagia  ndu mahoyage tũhũ-ĩ maũndũ marĩa matũire marutanaga makĩrĩ o maathani ma andũ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mũtiganaga na rĩathani rĩa Ngai, mũkagwatagĩrĩra kĩrĩra kĩa andũ.  Agĩcoka agĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ gĩthengerere harĩ we,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> agĩkĩĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Thikĩrĩriai inyuothe, na mũigue: gũtirĩ kĩndũ gĩtarĩ thĩinĩ wa mũndũ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>kĩngĩhota kũmũgwatia thahu gĩgĩtonya thĩinĩ wake: maũndũ marĩa moimaga thĩinĩ wa mũndũ nĩmo magwatagia mũndũ thahu. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ thĩinĩ, nĩ ngoro-inĩ cia andũ, kuumaga meeciria moru, ũmaraya, na ũici, ũũragani,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> na ũtharia, na ũcumĩkĩri, na waganu, na ũhenania, na ũũra-thoni, na rũitho, na ũrumani, na mwĩtĩo, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>na ũrimũ:  maũũru macio mothe moimaga na thĩinĩ, makagwatia mũndũ thahu.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"d41ziFLmEkG0dmsgdcQuMw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 25:14-30</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩmahe ũhoro rĩngĩ na ngerekano: mũndũ wathiaga ũgeni, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>agĩĩta ndungata ciake agĩcine indo ciake. Akĩne ĩmwe yacio taranda ithano, na ĩngĩ taranda igĩrĩ, na ĩngĩ taranda ĩmwe: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o ndungata kũringana na ũhoti wayo: agĩgĩthiĩ ũgeni.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Na kahinda o kau ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda ithano ĩgĩthiĩ, ĩkĩonjorithia nacio, ĩkĩona ĩngĩ ithano.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Nayo ĩrĩa yaneirũo igĩrĩ ĩgĩĩka o taguo, ĩkĩona ingĩ igĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> No ĩrĩa yaneirũo ĩmwe ĩgĩthiĩ ĩkĩenja thĩ, ĩkĩhitha mbia cia mwathani wayo.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩrĩ, matukũ maingĩ maathira, mwathani wa ndungata icio akĩinũka gwake mũciĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> agĩciĩta iheane ũhoro wa mbia ciake.  Na ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda ithano ĩgĩũka ĩkiuga:</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> mwathani, nĩ waneire taranda ithano: atĩrĩ, nĩ nyumithĩtie taranda ingĩ ithano.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Mwathani wayo akĩmĩĩra: Nĩ wĩkĩte wega, ndungata ĩno njega na ya kwĩhokeka:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ wĩhokekete na indo itarĩ nyingĩ, nĩ ngũgũtua mwathi wa indo nyingĩ: tonya gĩkeno-inĩ kĩa mwathani waku.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Nayo ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda igĩrĩ o nayo ĩgĩũka ĩkĩmwĩra: Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ waneire taranda igĩrĩ, atĩrĩ, nĩ nyumithĩtie taranda ingĩ igĩrĩ.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake mwathani wayo akĩmĩĩra: Nĩ wĩkĩte wega, ndungata ĩno njega na ya kwĩhokeka;</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ wĩhokekete na indo itarĩ nyingĩ, nĩ ngũgũtua mwathi wa indo nyingĩ: tonya gĩkeno-inĩ kĩa mwathani waku. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> Nayo ĩrĩa yaneirũo taranda ĩmwe ĩgĩũka kũrĩ we ĩkĩmwĩra: Mwathani, nĩ ndakũũĩ atĩ wĩ mũndũ mwĩĩ,</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384> ũgethaga kũrĩa ũtahandire, na ũcokagĩrĩria kũrĩa ũtaahurire; ngĩgĩĩtigĩra, ngĩthiĩ ngĩhitha taranda yaku thĩ:</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384> atĩrĩrĩ, ĩno nĩyo ĩrĩa yaku ndagũcokeria.  Nowe mwathani wayo agĩcokia, akĩmĩĩra atĩrĩ: Ndungata ĩno njũru na ngũtaru,</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ woĩ atĩ nĩ ngethaga kũrĩa itaahandire, na ngacokereria kũrĩa itaahurire; </s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ ũcio nĩ waagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũiga mbia ciakwa kũrĩ andũ arĩa monjorithagia mbia, na ndacoka-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ingĩacokerio mbia ciakwa o na uumithio wacio. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũtunyei taranda ĩo, </s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>na mũhe ũrĩa wĩna taranda iria ikũmi.  Nĩ gũkorũo mũndũ o wothe wĩ na indo, nĩwe ũkaheo, na akĩrĩrĩrio; </s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>no ũrĩa ũtarĩ na indo, nĩ agatunyũo o na kĩrĩa arĩ nakĩo. </s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>Nayo ndungata ĩo ĩtarĩ bata mũmĩikie na kũu nja kwĩ na nduma:</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384> kũu nĩkuo gũkagĩa kĩrĩro na kũharagania magego.</s>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"I1lbGx0cxk+y40eeDY7wWw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Jon 2:1-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Gũkĩgĩa kĩhikanio kũndũ gwĩtagwo Kana ya Galilea, nake nyina wa Yesu aarĩ ho.  O na Yesu nake nĩ etirũo, na arutwo ake, mathiĩ kĩhikanio kĩu. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nayo njohi yaaga kũmaigana, nyina wa Yesu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Matirĩ na njohi.  Nake Yesu akĩmwĩra: Mũtumia ũyũ, ũhoro nĩ ũrĩkũ witũ na we? </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ihinda rĩakwa rĩtirĩ rĩrakinya.  Nyina agĩkĩĩra ndungata atĩrĩrĩ: O ũrĩa ekũmwĩra, ĩkai guo. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, kwarĩ ndigithũ cia mahiga ciagĩtwo kuo nĩ ũndũ wa mĩtugo ya Ayahudi ya gwĩtheria, ĩmwe no gũthirĩra maaĩ ma mũtũngi ũrĩa mũnene maita merĩ kana matatũ. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ: Iyũriai ndigithũ icio maaĩ.  Magĩgĩciiyũria  o riita.  Agĩcoka akĩmera atĩrĩ: Rĩu tahiai, mũtwarĩre mũtabania  wa iruga.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nao makĩmũtwarĩra.  Mũtabania wa iruga nake aacama maaĩ macio matuikĩte njohi, na ndamenye harĩa yumĩte (ĩndĩ ndungata iria ciatahĩte maaĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>cio nĩ ciamenyaga) ũcio mũtabania wa iruga agĩĩta mũhikania, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mũndũ aambaga kũruta njohi ĩrĩa njega;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na andũ maarĩkia kũnyua mũno, akaruta ĩrĩa ĩtarĩ njega mũno; wee-rĩ, ũkũigĩte njohi ĩrĩa njega ũkamĩruta rĩu.  Yesu nĩ ekire ũguo kũu Kana ya Galilea, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>akĩambĩrĩria ciama ciake, agĩkĩonania ũnene wake; nao arutwo ake makĩ ya kũmwĩhoka.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"5zUw8cvqL0mhdJK6llnTQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    John 3:14-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩyo Yesu akĩĩra Nikodemo: Na ta ũrĩa Musa aahaicirie nyamũ-ya-thĩ igũrũ werũ-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> noguo Mũrũ wa mũndũ e na bata ahaicio igũrũ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha mũndũ o wothe wĩtĩkĩtie agĩe muoyo wa tene na tene thĩinĩ wake we.  Amu, Ngai, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ wa ũrĩa endete kĩrĩndĩ gĩa gũkũ thĩ, nĩ aarutire Mũrũ wake wa mũmwe, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩhokete ndakore, no agĩe muoyo wa tene na tene. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Amu Ngai ndatũmire Mũriũ thĩ acirithie kĩrĩndĩ, tiga kĩrĩndĩ kĩhonoke nĩ ũndũ wake. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ũrĩa ũmwĩhokete ti wa gũcirithio,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa nake ũtamwĩhokete nĩ arĩkĩtie gũcirithio tene agagĩtuwo mwĩhia, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ ndehokete rĩĩtwa rĩa Mũriũ wa Ngai wa mũmwe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Na gĩtũmi gĩa gũtuwo ũguo nĩ atĩrĩ, atĩ ũtheri nĩ ũũkĩte thĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nao andũ nĩ mendire nduma mbere ya ũtheri;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ mawĩko mao maarĩ moru.  Amu-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe wĩkaga ũũru nĩ athũire ũtheri,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ndokaga ũtheri-inĩ ciĩko ciake itikae kuumbũka.  Nake ũrĩa wĩkaga maũndũ marĩa ma ma nĩ okaga ũtheri-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nĩguo ciĩko ciake cionekane, imenyeke atĩ ciĩkĩtwo me na Ngai.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"GWeexVOhU0CTLQzr0HUBMg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			          Mathayo 25:31-46</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu nĩ erire Arũmĩrĩri ake: Rĩrĩa Mũrũ wa mũndũ agoka e na riri wake, na araika othe hamwe nake, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ agaikarĩra gĩtĩ gĩake gĩa ũthamaki kĩrĩa kĩĩ na riri: na ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ ikonganio mbere yake: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nake nĩ agaciamũrania, o ta ũrĩa mũrĩithi aamũranagia ng’ondu na mbũri: aige ng’ondu mwena wake wa ũrĩo,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> no mbũri aciige mwena wake wa ũmotho.  Hĩndĩ ĩo Mũthamaki nĩ akera arĩa marĩ mwena wake wa ũrĩo atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkani, inyuĩ mũrathimĩtwo nĩ Awa, gwatai igai rĩa ũthamaki ũrĩa mwathondekeirũo gwata rĩrĩa thĩ yombirũo:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo ndarĩ mũhũtu, na mũkĩhe irio; ndarĩ mũnyotu, na mũkĩhe gĩa kũnyua; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ndarĩ mũgendi, na mũkĩndaarĩrĩria kwanyu; ndarĩ njaga, na mũkĩhe gĩa kwĩhumba;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> ndarĩ mũrũaru, na mũgĩũka kũndora; ndarĩ korokoro-inĩ, na mũgĩũka kũrĩ niĩ.  Hĩndĩ ĩo arĩa athingu nĩ makamũcokeria mamũũrie atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Mwathani nĩ rĩ twakuonire wĩ mũhũtu, tũgĩkũhe irio? Kana wĩ mũnyotu, tũgĩkũhe gĩa kũnyua? </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ nĩ rĩ twakuonire wĩ mũgendi, tũgĩkũraarĩrĩria gwitũ? Kana wĩ njaga, tũgĩkũhe gĩa kwĩhumba?</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Na nĩ rĩ twakuonire wĩ mũrũaru, kana wĩ korokoro-inĩ, na tũgĩũka kũrĩ wee? Nake Mũthamaki nĩ agacokia amere:</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: o ta ũrĩa mwekire ũmwe wa ariũ a Awa, o na arĩ arĩa anyinyi mũno, maũndũ macio, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>o ũguo nĩ niĩ mwekire.  Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ akera arĩa marĩ mwena wake wa ũmotho atĩrĩ: Umai kũrĩ niĩ, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>inyuĩ mũgwatĩtwo nĩ kĩrumi, mũthiĩ mwaki-inĩ ũtahorekaga ũrĩa ũthondekeirũo thaitani na araika ake:</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo ndarĩ mũhũtu, na mũtihe irio; ndarĩ mũnyotu, na mũtihe gĩa kũnyua; ndarĩ mũgendi, </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>na mũtindaarĩrĩrie kwanyu; ndarĩ njaga, na mũtihe gĩa kwĩhumba; ndarĩ mũrũaru, na ndarĩ korokoro-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384> na mũtiũke kũndora.  Hĩndĩ ĩo o nao nĩ magacokia mamũũrie atĩrĩ: Mwathani, nĩ rĩ twakuonire wĩ mũhũtu, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>kana wĩ mũnyotu, kana wĩ mũgendi, kana wĩ njaga, kana wĩ mũrũaru, kana wĩ korokoro-inĩ, na tũtigũtungatĩre? </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ agacokia amere: Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: O ta ũrĩa mũtekire ũmwe wa acio anyinyi mũno maũndũ macio,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384> o ũguo nĩ niĩ mũtekire.  Nao andũ acio nĩmagathiĩ kũrĩa kũherithanagĩrio tene na tene: no rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384> arĩa athingu nĩ magatonya muoyo-inĩ wa tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI	"},{Guid:"YFB+h2WXm0qn5T3dWdPwFg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 13:24-32</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu akĩĩra arũmĩrĩri ake: no rĩrĩ matukũ macio, thutha wa thĩna ũcio-rĩ, riũa nĩ rĩgekĩrũo nduma, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>naguo mweri ũtige kwara, nacio njata irĩke kũgũa ciume igũrũ, namo mahinya marĩa me igũrũ nĩ makenyenyio. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Na hĩndĩ ĩo andũ nĩ makona Mũrũ wa mũndũ agĩũka na matu e na hinya mũnene o na riri. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ agatũma araika, no onganie andũ arĩa ake aamũre moime mĩena ĩrĩa ĩna yumaga rũhuho, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>kwaruma o gĩturi gĩa thĩ nginya o gĩturi kĩa Igũrũ.  Na rĩu mũkũyũ-rĩ, mwĩrute ngerekano yaguo:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> honge ciaguo ciarĩkia kũgĩa thundo na ciaruta mathangũ, mũmenyaga  atĩ hingo ya riũa ĩĩ hakuhĩ; noguo na inyuĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>mwona maũndũ macio magĩkinya, mũmenye atĩ arĩ hakuhĩ, o ta mũromo-inĩ.  Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Rũciaro rũrũ rũtigathira maũndũ macio mothe matahingĩtio.  Igũrũ na thĩ nĩ gũgathira: </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>no ũhoro wakwa ndũgathira.  No ũhoro wa mũthenya ũcio kana wa ihinda rĩu, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>gũtirĩ mũndũ ũũĩ, o na araika arĩa me Igũrũ, o na kana Mũriũ, tiga o Ithe witũ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI		"},{Guid:"6iaJPY5OTU694r/J8jrpeQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			            	 Luka 2: 22-40</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA INJIRI  YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Na matukũ mao na gũtherio thutha wa gũciara maahinga, o ta ũrĩa gwaathanirũo nĩ Musa-rĩ (Maria na Joseph) </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>makĩambata Jerusalem magakanengere Mwathani,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo Maandĩko-inĩ  ma irĩra cia Mwathani atĩrĩ, O kahĩĩ karĩa gakarigithathwo gagatuwo kaana gatheru ka Mwathani,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ marute ihaki o ta ũrĩa gũtuĩtwo Maandĩko-inĩ ma irĩra cia Mwathani atĩrĩ, Nĩ ndirahũgĩ igĩrĩ, kana ndutura igĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, nĩ kwarĩ  mũndũ watũire Jerusalem wetagwo Simeoni; nake aarĩ mũthingu na mũigua- Ngai,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩ aatanyĩte hindĩ ĩrĩa Israeli makanyamarũrũo: na Muoyo Mũtheru aarĩ hamwe nake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Na mũndũ ũcio nĩ aaguũrĩirio ni Muoyo Mũtheru atĩ ndagakua atonete Kristũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩtonya hekarũ ya Ngai  arĩ na Muoyo Mũtheru: na rĩrĩa aciari a kaana kau, Yesu, maagatwarire hekarũ ya Ngai thĩinĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha magageke kũringana na mũtugo  wa watho-rĩ, hindĩ ĩo Simeoni agĩkaiyũkia moko-inĩ make,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> akĩgatha Ngai akiuga atĩrĩ: “ Rĩu Mwathani nĩ hindĩ ũkũnjugĩra ũhoro, niĩ ngombo yaku, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>‘ thiĩ na thayũ o ta ũrĩa wanjĩrire; nĩ gũkorũo maitho makwa nĩ monete ũhonokio waku, ũrĩa wathondekire mbere ya irĩndĩ ciothe;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo ũtheri wa kũguũrĩrio andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ, o na riri wa andũ aku Israeli”.  </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Nao ithe na nyina nĩ maagegaga nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ marĩa maaririo nĩ ũndũ wake;</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> nake Simeoni akĩmarathima, akĩĩra Maria, nyina, Atĩrĩrĩ, kaana gaka nĩ gatuĩtwo ga kũgũithia o na gũũkĩria andũ aingĩ a Israeli;</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ gatuĩke kĩmenyithia kĩrĩa kĩrĩtendagwo; o na rĩrĩ, rũhiũ rũa mbaara nĩ rũgagũtũrĩkia ngoro wee mwene , </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>nĩguo meciria ma ngoro nyingĩ maguũke.  
Na nĩ kwarĩ mũtumia mũnabii wetago Anna, mwarĩ wa Fanueli, </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>wa mũhĩrĩga wa Asher, nake aarĩ mũkũrũ mũno; aaikarire na mũthuriwe mĩaka mũgwanja kuuma ahika, </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ aatũire arĩ wa  ndigwa mĩaka ĩngĩ mĩrongo ĩnana na ĩna; mũtumia ũcio-rĩ, ndoimaga hekarũ, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>no aatũire aturagiria NGai ndu akamũhoyaga ũtukũ na mũthenya akĩĩhingaga kũrĩa irio, na akĩmũthaithaga.  </s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Nake agĩkinya  oro hindĩ ĩo, akĩgatha Ngai, akĩheana ũhoro wa kaana kau kũrĩ arĩa othe maatũire matanyaga hindĩ ĩrĩa Jerusalem gũgakũũrũo.</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao maahingia maũndũ marĩa mothe maathanĩtwo irĩra-inĩ cia Mwathani, magĩcoka Galilea, </s>"},{ID:23,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"},Luminosity:0}},
Text:"<s1384>makĩinũka itũũra rĩao rĩa Nazareth.  Nako kaana kau gagĩkũra, gakĩgĩa na hinya , gakĩiyũrũo nĩ ũũgĩ; naguo Wega wa Ngai watũire nako.  </s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			            	 Luka 2: 22-40
"},{Guid:"/T6ro7X/GU+NKJibn5Sj8w",Verses:[],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"Githomo kia keri"},{Guid:"mI1CcFqLDkOE0lQ0REvd8g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Githomo kia keri	</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Inyui athuri-ri, endagai atumia anyu o ta uria Kristo nake endire kanitha, akiya kwineana niundu wa guo;</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> nigetha awamure autherie, nikuuthambia guthambia kuria kwa mai hamwe na Uhoro,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nigeth aahote kwirehere kanitha wiriri, uteri na kimeni, kana handu hagutharu, kana undu o na umwe ta ucio;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> no utuike mutheru, na ukaaga kauugu. O uguo noguo athuri nao maagiriiruo no kwendaga atumia ao ene,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ari o miiri ya oene. Mundu uria wendaga mutumia wake, niwe wiendaga: niundu gutiri kwonwo mundu uthuire mwiri  wake mwene;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> no niku uhea uheaga irio na akau ikaragia wega, o ta uria Kristo nake ekaga kanitha: niundu turi ciiga cia mwiri wake. Tondu ucio-ri</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>mundu niatigane naithe na nyina, agwatanio na mutumia; nao eri matuike mwiri umwe.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Ucio ni uhoro wahitho, wibata o ma; no ngiuga uguo-ri, ni uhoro waKristo na kanitha ndiragweta.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ningi gukira maundu macio mothe-ri, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>giagai na wendani, na niguo wohanagia maundu mothe hamwe niguo maagirire  kuna.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"Githomo kia keri	
"},{Guid:"G8n9izrRVUeBC/PJrrNI1A",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                              Atũmwo 4:32-35</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nao arĩa othe a thiritũ ya arĩa metĩkĩtie maarĩ rũmwe ngoro o na muoyo; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na gũtirĩ mũndũ wao woigaga atĩ kĩndũ o na kĩmwe kĩa indo ciake nĩ gĩake wiki; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>no indo ciao ciothe ciarĩ cia ngũatanĩro.  Nao atũmwo nĩ maaheanaga ũira wao wa kũriũka kwa Mwathani Yesu me na hinya mũnene. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nao othe magĩitĩrĩrio Wega wa Ngai mũingĩ.  Amu thiritũ-inĩ yao-rĩ, gũtiarĩ mũndũ wagĩte kĩndũ; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo arĩa othe maarĩ na ithaka kana nyũmba nĩ maaciendirie, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>magĩtwara mbia iria cioimĩte, magĩciiga thĩ kũrĩa atũmwo maikaire: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na mũndũ o mũndũ akagayagĩrũo o ta ũrĩa mabata make maatariĩ.
 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"sU4BZcWFykCYwNUupkogpQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                  Isaia 42:1-4,6-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Mwathani  ekuuga ũũ: ĩno nĩyo ndungata yakwa ĩrĩa ndiirĩrĩire; nĩyo ĩrĩa ndĩĩthurĩire, na nĩyo ĩkenagia ngoro yakwa: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ndĩmĩikũrũkĩirie muoyo wakwa ũkamĩhuba, na nĩyo ĩkarehithĩrie ndũrĩrĩ cira wa kĩhooto.  Ndĩkaanĩrĩra, o na kana ĩhaicie kayũ kayo na igũrũ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana ĩtũme mũgambo wayo ũigwo njĩra-inĩ.  Kamũrangi kagondoku ndĩgakoina, o na kana rũtambĩ rũa ũguta rũgĩtoga ĩrũhorie.
  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũtua ĩgatuanagĩra cira wa ma. Ndĩkahwererekera, o na kana yume tha, o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ĩgakorũo ĩtũmĩte gũkũ thĩ kũgĩe cira wa kĩhooto; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>andũ arĩa matũũraga ithama-inĩ magaikaraga metereire watho wayo.  Niĩ Mwathani-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ niĩ ngwĩtĩte o ta ũrĩa nyonaga kwerekeire, na nĩ ngakũnyita guoko na ngũmenyagĩrĩre,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na ngũheane nĩ getha ũtuĩke wa kũrĩkanĩra kĩrĩkanĩro na andũ, o na ũtuĩke ũtheri wa gũtherera andũ a ndũrĩrĩ;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> o na ningĩ nĩ getha ũhingũrage maitho marĩa matumumu, nao andũ arĩa mohetwo ũmarutage kĩoho-inĩ,  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o nao arĩa maikarĩte nduma-inĩ-rĩ, ũmarutage korokoro-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"F4fZzVb0qUmfpcAIz23SrQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Isa. 40:1-5;9-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:
	
Atĩrĩrĩ, ta horanĩriai, mũhorerie andũ akwa; ũguo nĩguo Ngai wanyu ekuuga. </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> Arĩriai itũra rĩa Jerusalemu maũndũ ma kũrĩhoreria ngoro; anĩrĩrai mũrĩĩre atĩrĩ, atĩ mbaara iria rĩrarĩ nayo nĩyathira, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o na atĩ waganu warĩo nĩ wohanĩrũo; o na ningĩ atĩ nĩ rĩhũrĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani rĩgacokerithio maita</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> merĩ nĩ ũndũ wa mehia  marĩo mothe.  He mũgambo wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra akoiga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Thondekai njĩra ya Mwathani o kũu werũ-inĩ, araganĩriai Ngai witũ njĩra ya gĩtwari o kũu rung’ũri-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Mĩkuru nĩ ĩgathĩnjwo yambatĩre, o nacio irĩma ciothe, o na ithũngũri ciothe, inyihio ciaraganio; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o nakuo kũrĩa kuogomu kũrũngario, nakuo kũrĩa gũtarĩ kwaraganu kwaraganio wega.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Naguo riri wa Mwathani nĩ ũkaguũranĩrio, nao andũ othe a gũkũ thĩ mawonanĩre me hamwe,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ kanua ka Mwathani kaarĩtie ndeto icio.
Atĩrĩrĩ, wee ũheaga Sion ũhoro ũrĩa mwega-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ta haica kĩrĩma kĩrĩa kĩraya igũrũ; wee ũheaga Jerusalemu ũhoro mwega rĩ, ta haicia kayũ gaku na igũrũ na hinya mũno;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> ta gĩkahaicie o na igũrũ na ũtige gwĩtigĩra, ĩra matũũra ma Juda atĩrĩ: Ũyũ nĩwe Ngai wanyu! Atĩrĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Ngai agoka o ta njamba irĩ hinya mũno, na guoko gwake nĩkuo gũkamwathanagĩra;</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> atĩrĩrĩ, ũtungati wake e naguo, o na irĩhanĩria rĩake rĩrĩ o mbere yake. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Mbũri cia rũũru rũake agacirĩithagia o ta mũrĩithi, natuo tũgondu atuoyage na moko make,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> atũkuuage tũrĩ gĩthũri-inĩ gĩake; nacio ng’ondu iria ikuongithia acitwarage o kahora.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"8SG4Imj0WEC1fvNN1amydA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                         Atũmwo 5:27-32.40-41</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ macio, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene akĩmoria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Githĩ tũtiramũkaanirie  o kũmũkaania mũtikae kũrutana na rĩĩtwa rĩu? Na rĩu-rĩ, nĩ mũiyũrĩte Jerusalem </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>guothe ũrutani wanyu, mũkenda gũtũma thakame ya mũndũ ũcio itũcokerere arĩ ithuĩ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nowe Petro me na atũmwo arĩa angĩ makĩmacokeria makiuga atĩrĩ: Nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũigue Ngai kũrĩ kũigua andũ. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Ngai wa maithe maitũ nĩ ariũkirie Yesu, o ũcio inyuĩ mworagithirie na kũmũcuurithia mũtĩ igũrũ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũcio nĩwe Ngai aatũũgĩririe aikare guoko-inĩ gwake kwa ũrĩo atuĩke Mũnene na Mũhonokia,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha atũme Aisraeli merire na moherũo mehia mao.  Na ithuĩ-rĩ, nĩ ithuĩ aira a mohoro macio; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nake Muoyo Mũtheru no mũira, o we Ngai aheete arĩa mamũiguaga. Nao magĩĩtĩkania nake, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>na maarĩkia gwĩta atũmwo macoke harĩ o, makĩmahũrithia, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>makĩmakaania matikae gũcoka kwaria ũhoro o na ũrĩkũ na rĩĩtwa rĩa Yesu, makĩmarekia mathiĩ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>magĩkiuma kĩama-inĩ makenete nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa maatuĩtwo aagĩrĩru a kũmenererio  nĩ ũndũ wa Rĩĩtwa rĩa Yesu.
 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"80ndAzpZdE+UKG4SbtoA5w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                          Ũũgi 1:13-15.2:23-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨŨGĨ:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Gĩkuũ gĩtiarĩ wĩko wa Ngai, ndakenagio nĩ ũndũ wa kũharaganio kwa arĩa marĩ muoyo. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ nĩ ombire indo ciothe itũũre muoyo; indo ciothe iria ciombirũo nĩ ikoragwo na ũgima thĩinĩ wacio gũtingĩkorũo kũrĩ ũrogi, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na gĩkuũ gĩtikoragwo na hinya thĩinĩ wa thĩ; tondũ mũtugo mwega ndũkuaga.  Na ningĩ Ngai ombire mũndũ atarĩ wa kũharagana;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> amũmbire thĩinĩ wa mũhiano wa mũgĩre wake Wee mwene;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ũiru wa Shaitani nĩguo warehire gĩkuũ thĩinĩ wa thĩ, o ta ũrĩa arĩa maikaranagia na Ngai makamenya.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"YqSXZwZQi0ChWKB6OgdEag",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				           Atũmwo 10:25,27;34, 35; 44-48</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nake petro aakorũo agĩtonya harĩa aarĩ, Kornerio akĩmũtunga, akĩigũithia thĩ magũrũ-inĩ make, akĩmũgooca. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nowe Petro akĩmũkĩria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: ta rũgama; niĩ ndĩ o mũndũ tawe. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Na makĩaranagĩria, agĩtonya nyũmba, agĩkora andũ aingĩ monganĩte.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Petro agĩitĩka kwaria akiuga atĩrĩ: Ti itherũ ndĩ kuona atĩ Ngai ndatĩagĩra andũ maũthĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>no thĩinĩ wa ndũrĩrĩ ciothe mũndũ ũrĩa ũmwĩtigagĩra na ageka maũndũ ma ũthingu nĩ etĩkagĩrũo nĩwe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, Petro akĩaragia ciugo icio, Muoyo Mũtheru agĩikũrũkĩrĩra andũ othe arĩa maaiguaga ũhoro. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nao andũ arĩa etĩkia a thiritũ ya arĩa maruaga, o acio mokĩte na Petro,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> makĩgega mũno tondũ atĩ Muoyo Mũtheru nĩ aheanagwo agaitĩrĩrio andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ o nao. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ maamaiguire magĩthioma thiomi na magĩkumagia Ngai.  Hĩndĩ ĩo Petro agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Kaĩ gũkĩrĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kũgiria maaĩ, nĩguo atĩ andũ aya maheetwo Muoyo Mũtheru </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>o ta ithuĩ matikabatithio? Agĩgĩathana atĩ mabatithio thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Yesu Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao magĩcoka makĩmũringĩrĩria atĩ aikarage nao matukũ mamwe.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"fnVWwOsGYEqeWSFt8TVcGg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				            Maũndũ ma Alawi 13:1-2,44-46</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MAŨNDŨ MA ALAWI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani agĩkĩarĩria Musa na Harũni, akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũndũ akagĩa na handũ haimbu gĩkonde-inĩ kĩa mwĩrĩ wake, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>kana thundo, o na kana handũ haregethũku thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ wake, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>naho handũ hau honwo ta arĩ mangũ me mwĩrĩ-inĩ  wake, hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ agatwarũo kwĩ Harũni,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, kana harĩ ũmwe wa ariũ ake arĩa athĩnjĩri-Ngai.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nake mũndũ ũrĩa ũrũarĩte mangũakehumbaga nguo ndembũkangu,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> njuĩrĩ ya mũtwe wake ĩikarage ĩrĩ  nguũrie, na ehumbage kĩromo kĩa mwena wa igũrũ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>akaanagĩrĩra ũũ: Ndĩ na ng’ũki! Ndĩ na ng’ũki! Namo  matukũ mothe marĩa mũndũ ũcio</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> agaikara arĩ o na mũrimũ ũcio nĩ akonagwo arĩ na ng’ũki, na akeikaragia wiki; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ũtũũro wake ũkagĩa na kũu gĩthaka-inĩ mbarĩ  ĩrĩa ĩngĩ ya hau kĩraaro-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"jvA7IvemTEewEpvbJwT+3Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				            2 Chronicles 36:14-16,19-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MAŨNDŨ MA MATUKŨ MA TENE:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, anene othe a athĩnjĩri-Ngai, o na andũ arĩa angĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ maagararire watho wa Mwathani mũno nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩka maũndũ me thahu ma ndũrĩrĩ iria itoĩ Ngai; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nao magĩkĩgwatia nyũmba ya Mwathani iria aamũrĩte kũu Jerusalem thahu.  Nake Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai wa maithe mao, akĩmatwarithĩria ũhoro na andũ ake arĩa aarekagia na kĩyo, o marũmanĩria;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ nĩ aaiguagĩra andũ ake tha, o na handu ha utuuro wake; no rĩrĩ, nĩ maathekereire andũ acio maarekagio nĩ Ngai, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o na makĩmena ndeto iria aamatwarithagĩria nao, o na makĩnyarara anabii ake, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>magĩgĩtũma matũkũya ma Mwathani maarahũke makore andũ ake, o nginya hakĩaga kĩhonia. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nao magĩgĩcina nyũmba ya Ngai, o naruo rũthingo rũa Jerusalem makĩrũtharia, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o nacio nyũmba ciakuo ciothe cia ũnene magĩcicina na mwaki, o na magĩkĩananga indo iria ciothe njega ciakuo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> No andũ arĩa maahonokire kũragwo na hiũ cia njora, akĩmatwarithia Babiloni,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> magĩtuĩka ndungata ciake we mwene, o na cia ariũ ake,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa gwacokire gũthamakwo nĩ ũthamaki wa Persia;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha ũhoro wa Mwathani ũrĩa waaririo na kanua ka Jeremia ũhingio , na guo ũguo nĩtakuuga o nginya rĩrĩa </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>bũrũri ũcio wahingirie thabatũ ciaguo, nĩgũkorũo hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yothe wakorirũo wagĩĩte andũ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo watũire ũhurũkĩte ta kwĩ thabatũ, o nginya mĩaka mĩrongo mũgwanja ĩkahinga.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩ, mwaka wa mbere ũrĩa Cirus mũthamaki wa Persia aakorirũo athamakĩte-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani akĩarahũra muoyo wa Cirus, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio mũthamaki wa Persia, nĩgetha ũhoro wa Mwathani ũrĩa waaririo nĩ Jeremia ũhingio,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> agĩgĩtũmwo ahunjanĩrie ũhoro mabũrũri mothe marĩa aathamakaga, o na awandĩke, oige ũũ: Atĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Cirus, mũthamaki wa Persia, oiga ũũ: Mwathani, Ngai wa igũrũ, nĩ aheete mabũrũri mothe ma gũkũ thĩ, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ndĩmaathage; na nĩ anjathĩte ngamwakĩre nyũmba Jerusalem, itũũra rĩa Juda.  Tondũ ũcio, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>mũndũ o wothe wa andũ ake ũrĩa wĩ thĩinĩ wanyu-rĩ, Mwathani Ngai wake aroikara hamwe nake, nake nĩ aambate athiĩ kuo.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> 
   Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"H4gZo+JaoEuFrGgl++T6JA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Thama 22:21-27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani akuuga ũũ: ndũkaneke mũndũ wa kũngĩ ũũru, kana ũmũhinyĩrĩrie, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ o na inyuĩ nĩ mwatũire bũrũri wa Misri mũrĩ andũ a kũndũ kũngĩ. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Ndũkananyarire mũka wa ndigwa o na ũrĩkũ, kana mwana wa ngoriai. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, ũngĩmanyarira na ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ, nao mangaĩre-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ndirĩ hingo itakaigua gũkaya  kwao, njinwo nĩ marakara,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ndĩmũũragithie na hiũ  cia mbaara, o nao atumia anyu matuĩke ndigwa, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o na ciana cianyu ituĩke cia ngoriai.  Na rĩrĩ, ũngĩohorera mũndũ  o na ũrĩkũ mbia wa andũ akwa arĩa mwĩ nao, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>tigaga gũtinda ũkĩmũrandũra, kana ũmwĩtagie uumithio wa mbia icio. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Ũngĩthiĩ na nguo ya mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ, atĩ nĩguo akamĩkũũra kũrĩ wee-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũkamũcokeria nguo ĩo mũthenya o ro ũcio riũa rĩtanathũa; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo nguo ĩo iiki noyo arĩ nayo ya kwĩhumba, na nĩyo ahumbagĩra mwĩrĩ wake nayo; rĩu-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> kaĩ agagĩkomera kĩ? Na nĩ gũgakinya atĩrĩ, atĩ rĩrĩa akangaĩra,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> no kũigua ngamũigua; nĩ ũndũ niĩ ndĩ wa tha. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"WJQQVLvTY02KB/xqLyrpfw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                     Joshua 24:1-2, 15-17. 18b</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA JOSHUA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Joshua agĩcokanĩrĩria mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya Israeli kuũ Shikem, agĩgĩĩta athuri a  Isiraeli,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o anene ao, o na aciiri ao, o na anyabara ao; nao magĩgĩthiĩ  makĩrũgama hau mbere ya Ngai.  Nake Joshua agĩkĩĩra andũ acio  atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩu mũngĩkorũo  nĩ mũkuona arĩ ũũru gũtungatĩra Mwathani, thurai ũmũthĩ ũrĩa mũrĩtungatagĩra; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>mũmenye kana nĩ ngai iria maithe manyu maatungatagĩra mũrĩmo ũcio wa rũũĩ rũa Farati,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> kana nĩ ngai cia Aamori, arĩa mũtũũranĩtie nao bũrũri wao; no rĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wakwa niĩ mwene, na nyũmba yakwa-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>tũrĩtungatagĩra Mwathani
Nao andũ acio magĩcokia makiuga atĩrĩ: Tũroaga gũkanatigana na Mwathani atĩ nĩguo tũtungatĩre ngai ingĩ; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani Ngai witũ nĩwe watũrutire bũrũri wa Misri ithuĩ ene, ona maithe maitũ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> tuume nyũmba ya ũkombo, na akĩringa ciama icio nene tũgĩciyonagĩra  na maitho maitũ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na agĩtũmenyerera njĩra-inĩ ĩrĩa yothe twagerire, o na agĩtũmenyerera twĩ thĩinĩ wa andũ othe arĩa twatuĩkanĩirie kwao;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ ũcio o na ithuĩ tũrĩtungatagĩra Mwathani, nĩ ũndũ nĩwe Ngai witũ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"fwnUv0dcqUKqhixfFZNDEA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                    Jeremiah 33:14-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI JEREMIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ, atĩ matukũ nĩ magoka marĩa ngahingia ũhoro ũcio mwega njarĩtie ũkoniĩ nyũmba ya Israeli,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na nyũmba ya Juda.  Matukũ-inĩ macio, o na ihinda-inĩ rĩu-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ngaarahũrĩra Davide mũndũ mũthingu ũgerekanĩtio na Thuuna a mũtĩ, nake nĩ agatuanĩra cira na kĩhooto,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o na ekanage maũndũ ma ũthingu gũkũ bũrũri ũyũ. Matukũ-inĩ macio-rĩ, Juda nĩ gũkahonokanio,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o narĩo Jerusalemu rĩtũũre rĩĩgangarĩtwo; narĩo rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa rĩgetagwo nĩrĩo rĩrĩ, Mwathani-Ũthingu-Witũ.</s>"},{ID:8,Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1}},
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"0nCVJOGPT0W2jazyiyHQzA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Isa. 61:1-2;10-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Atĩrĩrĩ, Muoyo wa Mwathani Ngai arĩ igũrũ rĩakwa; </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ Mwathani nĩ anjitĩrĩirie maguta hunjagĩrie arĩa athĩni ũhoro ũrĩa mwega. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ andũmĩte ngohohanie arĩa athuthĩku ngoro, na ngahunjanagĩrie atĩ andũ arĩa mohetwo nĩ mohorũo,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o nao arĩa mohetwo korokoro-inĩ ndĩmere atĩ nĩ mahingũrĩirũo; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o na hunjanagĩrie ũhoro wa mwaka ũrĩa Mwathani Ngai akonania ũtugi wake,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o na wa mũthenya ũrĩa wĩ hakuhĩ ũrĩa Ngai witũ akagerana ngero cia kwĩrĩhĩria;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ horagĩrie arĩa othe me na kĩeha.  Gũkena-rĩ, ndĩrĩkenagĩra Mwathani mũno,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o nayo ngoro yakwa ĩkenũkĩre Ngai wakwa mũno; nĩ ũndũ ahumbĩte ũhonokio ta arĩ nguo,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o na akahumba ũthingu o ta ũrĩ kĩremba kĩrĩa mũhikania eĩkagĩra egemie nakĩo, o na ta mathaga marĩa mũhiki egemagia namo.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa thĩ ĩmeragia thuuna, o na ta ũrĩa mũgũnda ũkunũraga indo iria ihandĩtwo kuo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> ũguo noguo Mwathani Ngai agatũma ũthingu o na kũgoocwo ciumĩre, cioneke nĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"uEMmj36O7kqFYWaDJWTWyQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                    Kĩambĩrĩria 1:26-2:3</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨAMBĨRĨRIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai akiuga atĩrĩ: 
Nĩtũũmbeni andũ matariĩ ta mũhianĩre witũ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>mahaanane na ithuĩ, nao maathage ciũngũyũ cia iria-inĩ, na nyamũ iria irĩ na njoya cia rĩera-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na nyamũ cia magũrũ mana, na nyamũ ciothe cia gũkũ thĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o gwata kanyamũ o gothe gatambi  karĩa gatambaga thĩ.  We Ngai agĩgĩtũma kũgĩe andũ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>matariĩ ta mũhianĩre wake we mwene, agĩgĩtũma magĩe na mũhianĩre o ta wa Ngai;
 </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>agĩtũma magĩe kuo marĩ mũndũ mũrũme na mũndũ mũka.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Ngai agĩkĩmarathima, akĩmera atĩrĩ, Ciarai mũno, mũthegee, mũiyũre thĩ, na mũmĩtorie; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ mwathage ciũngũyũ cia iria, na nyamũ iria irĩ njoya cia rĩera-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o na nyamũ o yothe ĩrĩa ĩthiangaga thĩ.  Ningĩ Ngai akiuga atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ta onei, nĩndĩmũheete kahuti o gothe karĩa kagĩaga handũ o na ha thĩ yothe, o harĩa yakinya,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o karĩa koimagia mbeũ, o na ningĩ mũtĩ o wothe ũrĩa wĩ na maciaro  marĩa me mbeũ thĩinĩ wamo;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> mĩthemba ĩo yothe-rĩ, ĩgũtuĩka  ya irio cianyu;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nayo nyamũ o yothe ya werũ, o na nyamũ o yothe ĩrĩ njoya  ya rĩera-inĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na kanyamũ o gothe karĩa gatambaga thĩ, o icio ciothe ii muoyo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nĩndĩciheete kahuti o gothe karĩa karũraga, gatuĩke irio ciacio; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>gũgĩtuĩka o ũguo.  Ngai agĩkĩona atĩ kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩrĩa ombĩte nĩ kĩega mũno. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nakuo gũkĩgĩa hwaĩ-inĩ, na gũkĩgĩa rũcinĩ; ũcio ũgĩtuĩka mũthenya ũngĩ, wa gatandatũ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Igũrũ na thĩ gũgĩkĩrĩka o kũrĩka, o na mwaranĩrie wa ũingĩ wothe wakuo; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>naguo mũthenya wa mũgwanja Ngai agĩkorũo arĩkĩtie wĩra ũcio wake aarutaga wa ũũmbi; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ningĩ mũthenya o  ũcio wa mũgwanja akĩhurũka atiganĩte na wĩra wake wothe ũcio aarutĩte wa ũũmbi. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya ũcio wa mũg
wanja-rĩ, Ngai akĩũrathima, akĩwamũra,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ mũthenya ũcio nĩguo aahurũkire agĩtiga wĩra wake, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>wothe ũrĩa we Ngai aarutĩte wa gũtũma indo igĩe, o na wa gũciũmba.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"TLTM9MESF0O5UyFQzu4i1g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                              Atũmwo 4:8-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Petro aiyũrĩtwo  nĩ Muoyo Mũtheru, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Inyuĩ anene a kĩrĩndĩ o na athuri,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kũngĩkorũo ũmũthĩ nĩ kũũrio ũhoro wa wĩko ũcio mwega ũrekirũo mũndũ ũcio ũratũire e kĩonje,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na ũrĩa arahonirio-rĩ, menyai inyuothe, o na andũ othe a Israel, atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ ũndũ ũrĩa ũtũmĩte mũndũ ũcio arũgame haha mbere yanyu, arĩ mũgima, nĩ rĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ rĩĩtwa rĩa Yesu Kristũ wa Nazareth, ũrĩa inyuĩ mwambithirie mũtĩ igũrũ, nake Ngai akĩmũriũkia oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩwe Ihiga rĩrĩa rĩaregirũo nĩ inyuĩ aaki, na nĩrĩo rĩtuĩkĩte rĩrĩa inene rĩa koine.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Naguo ũhoro wa kũhonokio ndũngĩoneka harĩ ũngĩ o na ũrĩkũ: nĩ ũndũ atĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>gũtirĩ rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ rĩanaheanwo gũkũ thĩ kũrĩ andũ rĩngĩagĩrĩra rĩa gũtũhonokia.
 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"efppQ/tN2EqFnOTXz4cHRQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                  
Ezekieli 34:11-12,15-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI EZEKIELI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Ngai akuuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, niĩ, o niĩ mwene-rĩ, nĩ gũcaria ngecarĩria mbũri icio ciakwa, o na ndĩcituĩrie kũrĩa irĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na ndĩcione.  O ta ũrĩa mũrĩithi athũrimaga mbũri cia rũũru rũake  agacicaria mũthenya ũrĩa ikoragwo ihurunjũkĩte-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ũguo noguo ngathũrima mbũri ciakwa; na nĩ ngaciruta kũndũ guothe kũrĩa ciahurunjĩirũo  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>mũthenya ũrĩa kwarĩ matu mathimbu o na nduma ndumanu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ mwene nĩ niĩ ngerĩithagĩria mbũri icio ciakwa, na nĩ ngaciarathagia; ũguo nĩguo Mwathani Ngai oigĩte.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Iria ciũrĩte nĩ ngacicaria, o nacio iria hahũre ndĩcicokithie, ningĩ iria nyunĩku ndĩciohe,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> o nacio iria ndũaru ndĩciĩkĩre hinya; no iria noru na ikagĩa hinya-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩcio nganina, na ndĩcirĩithie ngĩciherithagia.  O naho ha ũhoro wanyu, inyuĩ mbũri cia rũũru rũakwa-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Ngai oigĩte ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩ gũteithũrana ngateithũrana ũhiũ, o na ndeithũrane ndũrũme na thenge.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"vml8zFj0Mk+ptERAAxwB+w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Malaki 1:14-2:2.8-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI MALAKI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita akuuga: Niĩ ndĩ mũthamaki mũnene, na rĩĩtwa rĩakwa nĩ rĩĩtigagĩrũo mũno nĩ andũ arĩa matarĩ Ayahudi.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Na rĩu inyuĩ asacerdoti aya, rĩathani rĩrĩ nĩ inyuĩ mwathĩrĩirio.  Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita ekũmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Mũngĩrega kũnjigua, na mwage gwĩcũrania rĩathani rĩrĩ na ngoro cianyu, nĩguo mũgoocithagie rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ngamũrehithĩrie kĩrumi mũgwatwo nĩkĩo, o nacio irathimo cianyu iria mũrathimanaga nacio ndĩcigeke. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> 
No inyuĩ nĩ mũtigĩte njĩra, mũgakerũra na mwena ũngĩ, mũgatũma andũ aingĩ maikare ta mahingithĩtio kĩrĩra-inĩ kĩa Ngai. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ mwĩhĩtie kĩrĩkanĩro giitũ na Lewii; ũguo nĩguo Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita ekuuga.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩkĩo ndũmĩte mũnyararũo nĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩothe, na mũmenererio nĩkĩo, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ nĩ mũregete gũthiaga na mĩthiĩre yakwa, na mũgathurania ũrĩa andũ matariĩ mũgitua cira. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Githĩ tũtirĩ a ithe ũmwe ithuothe? Ningĩ githĩ tũtiombirũo nĩ Ngai o ũmwe?</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ kĩ gĩgĩtũmaga tũrĩanĩre ng’ũũrũ mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ, tũgagĩthahia kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩa maithe maitũ?</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"PNhXYGtqw0yJWIpjCb4KpQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                      Isaiah 53:10-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>(Ndungata ya Mwathani) yatũire ĩkũraga ĩrĩ mbere yake o ta mũtĩ mwĩthĩ, o na ta mũri ũmerete rũng’ũrĩ-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩa yamenirũo o na ĩkĩregwo nĩ andũ; nĩ mũndũ wĩ kĩeha, ũrĩĩte thĩna.  No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩ onire arĩ mwega amũhehenje,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> agĩkĩmũiguithia ũũru ngoro; na  rĩrĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa akeruta mouyo wake utuĩke igongona ria mehia 
nĩakona ruciaro rwake ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ akaingĩhia matukũ make, o namo maũndũ marĩa mwathani endaga mekwo nĩ makagaacĩra nĩ ũndũ wake.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ akona kĩguni kĩa ũrĩa ngoro yake yanaigua ruo mũno, na tondũ ũcio nĩ akaigua wega.  O na ningĩ tondũ wa ũmenyi wayo, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ndungata ĩo yakwa thingu ĩgatũma andũ aingĩ matuwo athingu; namo maũũru mao nĩ ĩkamakuua ĩmeherie.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"MIm0pUQjkUqoEB7jTY+y6Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				            Thama   20:1-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Ngai akĩaria mohoro maya mothe, akiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani Ngai waku ũrĩa wakũrutire bũrũri wa Misiri, o nyũmba-inĩ ya ũkombo. (Ndũkanagĩe na ngai ĩngĩ tiga niĩ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Ndũkanethondekere mũhianano mwacũhie, kana mũhianĩre wa  kĩndũ o gĩothe  gĩĩ kũrĩa Igũrũ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>kana wa kĩndũ gĩĩ gũkũ thĩ,   maaĩ-inĩ marĩa mee mũhuro wa thĩ; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ndũkanaciinamĩrĩre ka ũcitũngatĩre; nĩ gũkorũo niĩ Mwathani Ngai waku ndĩ Ngai wĩ ũiru, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ngagĩkinyĩria ciana waganu wa maithe, nginya rũciaro rwa gatatũ na rũa kana rũa andũ arĩa mathũire;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> na ngaiguĩra andũ ngiri na ngiri tha, o arĩa manyendete na makaigua maathani makwa.)</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ndũkanagwete rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani Ngai waku na itheru, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani ndakoiga atĩ mũndũ ndehĩtie ũrĩa ũgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩake na itherũ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Ririkanaga mũthenya wa thabatũ ũwamũrage.  (Rutaga wĩra mĩthenya ĩtandatũ, ũgeka maũndũ maku mothe;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> no mũthenya wamũgwanja nĩ thabatũ ya Mwathani Ngai waku; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>mũthenya ũcio ndũkanarute wĩra o na ũrĩkũ, wee mwene, kana mũrũguo,. Kana mwarĩguo, kana ndungata yaku ya mũndũ mũrũme,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> kana ya mũndũ-wa-nja, kana ũhiũ  waku, kana mũgeni ũrĩa ũrĩ gwaku mũciĩ; </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani ombire igũrũ na thĩ, na iria rĩrĩa rĩnene, o na indo ciothe iria irĩ kuo mĩthenya ĩtandatũ; </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>akĩhurũka mũthenya wa mũgwanja; nĩ ũndũ ũcio Mwathani akĩrathima mũthenya ũcio wathabatũ, akĩwamũra.)</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Tĩa thoguo na nyũkwa, nĩguo matukũ maku maingĩhe ma gũtũũra bũrũri ũrĩa ũheetwo nĩ Mwathani Ngai waku.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>  Ndũkanoragane, Ndũkanatharanie, Ndũkanaiye, Ndũkanaigĩrĩre mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ kĩgenyo, </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Ndũkanacumĩkĩre nyũmba ya mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ, ndũkanacumĩkĩre mũka wa mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ,</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384> kana ũcumĩkĩre ndungata yake ya mũndũ mũrũme kana ya mũndũ-wa-nja,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384> kana ndegwa yake, kana ndigiri yake, o na kana kĩndũ gĩake gĩothe.</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"pyivivJCfUS4FEcpUVTu1w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					     Gũcokerithia Maathani 6:2-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Musa agĩgĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ na akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ũgetigagĩra Mwathani Ngai waku, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ũmenyagĩrĩre irĩra ciothe cia watho wake wa kũrũmĩrĩrũo, na maathani make marĩa ngũgwatha  wĩkage, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>we mwene, na mũrũguo, o na mwana wa mũrũguo, matukũ mothe ma muoyo waku; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩguo matukũ maku makĩingĩhio. Tondũ ũcio, wee Israeli, igua, o na ũmenyagĩrĩre ũhoro wa gwĩkaga maũndũ macio; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ũtũũre wonaga wega, na ningĩ nĩ getha mũthaathare mũingĩhe mũno, mũrĩ bũrũri wĩ bũthi wa iria o na ũũki, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o ta ũrĩa Mwathani, Ngai wa mathoguo, aakwĩrire.  Atĩrĩrĩ! Wee Israeli, thikĩrĩria; Mwathani Ngai witũ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> we wiki nowe Mwathani, nawe enda Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku yothe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na muoyo waku wothe, o na hinya waku wothe.  Namo mohoro maya ndĩrakũhe ũmũthĩ ngĩgũtaara-rĩ, reka matũre ngoro-inĩ yaku.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"U6IpRFv+kEm2VwAqGKJxQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                          Job 38:1,8-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA JOB:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ  ĩo Mwathani agĩcokeria Job ũhoro e kĩhuhũkanio-inĩ , akiuga atĩrĩrĩ :</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nũ wahingĩire iria rĩrĩa inene na mĩrango rĩrĩa rĩatothokire rĩkiuma ihu-inĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndatuire matu nguo yarĩo,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ngĩgĩtũma nduma ndumanu ĩtuĩke tama warĩo, ta ũrĩa ũrigicagĩrio mwana? Na ngĩrĩĩkĩrĩra mũhaka  mũtue nĩ niĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ngĩkĩrĩhingĩra na mĩgĩĩko o na mĩrango.  Ngiuga: Ũrĩkinyaga o hau, na ndũkanaagarare;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> hau nĩ ho makũmbĩ maku megugumi marĩtĩmagĩrĩra.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"OD8jVz/SGU2bdK/vYUc7aA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                       Jeremia 31:31-34</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MURATHI JEREMIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, matukũ nĩ magoka marĩa ngarĩkanĩra kĩrĩkanĩro kĩerũ na nyũmba ya Israeli,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na nyũmba ya Juda.  Nakĩo kĩrĩkanĩro kĩu gĩtigatuĩka ta kĩrĩa ndarĩkanĩire</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na maithe mao hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndamanyitire na guoko ngĩmaruta bũrũri wa Misri;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ matiigana kũrũmia kĩrĩkanĩro kĩu twarĩkanĩire nao, o na harĩa ndatuĩkĩte ta ndĩ mũthuri wao; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga. No rĩrĩ, Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ, atĩ gĩkĩ nĩkĩo </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa ngarĩkanĩra na nyũmba ya Israeli matukũ macio mathira; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gwĩkĩra ngekĩra watho wakwa ngoro-inĩ ciao thĩinĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o na ndĩwandĩke meciria-inĩ mao; na nduĩke Ngai wao, nao matuĩke andũ akwa. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nao matigacoka kũrutana mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ, o na kana mũndũ arute mũrũ wa ithe akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Umĩrania ngoro na Mwathani, nĩ gũkorũo andũ othe nĩ magakorũo mamenyete, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>kuuma o ũrĩa mũnyinyi mũno wao gwata ũrĩa mũnene makĩria; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga; nĩ ũndũ nĩ ngamohera waganu wao, o namo mehia mao ndigacoka kũmaririkana o rĩ, o rĩ.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"7Mr4i4z12UGJnoNKenX+PA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					     1Athamaki 17:10-16 </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MBERE RĨA ATHAMAKI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Elia agĩgĩũkĩra agĩthiĩ Zarepta.  Na aakinya  mũrango-inĩ wa kĩhingo gĩa itũũra, akĩona mũtumia wa ndigwa akĩũngania tũkũ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>akĩmwĩta, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ndagũthaitha ndehere tũ ĩ na kahuri nyue ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na rĩrĩa athiaga gũtũgira akĩmuĩta akĩmuĩra atiri  Ndagũthaitha  ũndehanĩrie na kenyũ ka mũgate.  Nake agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: O ta ũrĩa Mwathani Ngai waku atũũraga muoyo-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ndirĩ na kamũgate tiga o kamũtu ka rũhĩ rũmwe ke ndigithũ-inĩ, o na tũguta tũnini twĩ cuba-inĩ; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na atĩrĩrĩ, rĩu ndĩrongania tũkũ nĩguo ‘thiĩ ngathondeke ndĩkaruge nĩ ũndũ wakwa niĩ mwene, o na mũrũ wakwa, nĩguo tũkarĩe tũcoke tũkue. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Elia agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Tiga gwĩtigĩra, thiĩ wĩke o ta ũguo woiga; no rĩrĩ, amba ũthondekere kamũgate kanini kaguo, ũndehere,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na thutha wa ũguo wĩthondekere wee mwene mwĩ na mũrũguo.  Nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani, Ngai wa Israeli, oigĩte ũũ: Ndigithũ ĩo ya mũtu ndĩninũka, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o na kana cuba ũcio wa maguta ũninũke, tiga o mũthenya ũrĩa Mwathani akoiria mbura gũkũ thĩ. Nake agĩgĩthiĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> agĩĩka o ta ũguo  Elia oigĩte gwĩkwo; nake mũtumia ũcio, o na Elia, o na andũ othe a nyũmba yake, makĩria  kandũ kau matukũ maingĩ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nayo ndigithũ ĩo ndĩigana gũthira mũtu, o na kana cuba ũgĩthira maguta, o ta ũrĩa uuge wa Mwathani watariĩ  ũrĩa aaririe na kanua ka Elia.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"IowbGGUiD02sjIXfLRhdZw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			     Thama 24:3-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Musa agĩthiĩ akĩhe andũ mohoro macio mothe aaheetwo nĩ Mwathani,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> o na matuĩro marĩa marĩrũmagĩrĩrũo nĩo cira-inĩ; nao andũ magĩĩtĩkanĩria othe hamwe o ta mũndũ ũmwe, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>makiuga atĩrĩ: Maũndũ macio mothe Mwathani oigĩte-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> nomo tũrĩĩkaga.  Nake Musa akĩandĩka mohoro macio  mothe ma Mwathani, na akĩroka-gũũkĩra rũcinĩ tene, agĩaka kĩgongona  kĩanda-inĩ gĩa kĩrĩma kĩu,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> na akĩhanda itugi ikũmi na igĩrĩ, o ta ũrĩa mĩhĩrĩga ĩo ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ ya ciana cia Israeli yatariĩ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Ningĩ akĩrekia aanake amwe a ciana cia Israeli, nao magĩthiĩ makĩruta mahaki ma njino, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>na magĩthĩnja ndegwa, ituĩke magongona ma ũiguano ma kũrutĩrũo Mwathani.  Nake Musa akĩgayania thakame yacio kerĩ; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>ĩmwe akĩmĩĩkĩra mbakũri-inĩ, nayo ĩrĩa ĩngĩ akĩmĩminjaminja kĩgongona igũrũ.
Agĩcoka akĩoya ibuku rĩa kĩrĩkanĩro,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> akĩrĩthomera andũ othe monganĩte, makĩĩiguĩra, nao makiuga atĩrĩ: Maũndũ macio mothe Mwathani oigĩte-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> nomo tũrĩĩkaga, na nĩ tũgwathĩka.  Ningĩ Musa akĩoya thakame, akĩmĩminjaminjĩria andũ acio, akiugaga ũũ:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, ĩno nĩyo thakame ya kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa Mwathani aarĩkanĩra na inyuĩ  gĩkoniĩ ciugo icio ciothe.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"OAdKi9ooCUq6jWJ/uuGKsQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                          Mika 5:1-4 </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MIKA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: no rĩrĩ, wee Betlehem Efrata-rĩ o na  Orĩa wĩ mũnyinyi mũno thĩinĩ wa mĩhĩrĩga ya Juda, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>gwaku nĩkuo gũkoima mũndũ igũrũ rĩakwa, na nĩwe ũgatũĩka mwathani o kũu Israeli; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nake kĩhumo gĩake aarĩ o ho o tene na tene, o na mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.
Tondũ ũcio kũrekereria akamarekereria,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa nyina akaamba kũrũmwo na acoke ohoke; hĩndĩ ĩo nĩguo matigari ma ariũ  a ithe magacokerera ciana cia Israeli.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nake nĩ kũrũgama akarũgama, arĩithie andũ ake na ũndũ wa hinya ũrĩa aheetwo nĩ Mwathani ta marĩ rũũru rũa mbũri, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>amarĩithie na ũndũ wa mwago wa ũnene wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwthani Ngai wake; ũguo nĩguo magatũũra megangarĩte, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ hĩndĩ ĩo agakorũo atuĩtwo mũnene o nginya ituri ciothe cia thĩ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"MxW3jqremU+dIbyg0234MA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				             Ũgĩ(Wisdom) 2:12. 17-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨGĨ: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ arĩa matoĩ Ngai moigaga atĩrĩ: Rekei tweterere mũndũ ũrĩa mũthingu, tondũ nĩ atũrakaragia, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na akamenereria ũtũũro witũ, agatũruma tondũ nĩ tũthũkagia rĩathana na  agatũcuka nĩ ũndũ wa mĩtugo iitũ mĩũru.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Ta kĩrekei twone kana ũrĩa oigaga nĩ ũhoro wa ma.  Ta rekei twone ũrĩa ithirĩro rĩake rĩgakorũo rĩtariĩ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Angĩkorũo mũndũ ũyũ mũthingu nĩ Mwana wa Ngai-rĩ, Ngai nĩ akamũgitĩra na amũkũre kuuma moko-inĩ ma thũ ciake.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Rekei tũmũgerie nĩ getha aigue ruo, nĩ getha tũmenye ũhoreri ũyũ wake, na twone ũrĩa ũkirĩrĩria wake ũigana.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Rekei tũmũrage gĩkuũ gĩa thoni tondũ Ngai nĩ ekũmũmenyerera, kũringana na ũrĩa oigire.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"wD8lLUTU70WgEDa7t8ZS9w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                           Kĩambĩrĩria 2:18-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨAMBĨRĨRIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Ngai akiuga atĩrĩ: Ti wega mũndũ ũyũ aikare wiki; nĩ ngũmũũmbĩra mũmũteithia o ũrĩa maaganĩrĩirũo nake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩ, Mwathani Ngai ombire nyamũ o yothe ya gĩthaka na tĩri, o na nyamũ o yothe ĩrĩa ĩrĩ njoya ya rĩera-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>agĩcoka agĩcitwara ciothe kwĩ mũndũ ũcio, nĩguo emenyerere ũrĩa egũciĩta; na rĩrĩ, kĩũmbe o gĩothe gĩa icio irĩ muoyo-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa mũndũ ũcio aagĩtuire, rĩu rĩgĩtuĩka rĩtwa rĩakĩo.  Nake mũndũ ũcio agĩtua mahiũ mothe marĩĩtwa, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o na nyamũ iria ii njoya cia rĩera-inĩ, o na nyamũ ciothe cia gĩthaka; no rĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa mũndũ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>gũtiakorirũo kwĩ na mũmũteithia maaganĩrĩirũo nake.  Nake Mwathani Ngai agĩtũma mũndũ ũcio agwatwo nĩ toro mũnene mũno, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>agĩgĩkoma; ningĩ akĩmũruta rũbaru ũmwe, agĩcoka agĩcokania nyama hau ruuma,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> naruo rũbaru rũu Mwathani Ngai aarutire mũndũ ũcio, akĩrũkũmbania  rũgĩtuĩka mũndũ mũka, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>agĩcoka akĩmũtwara kwĩ mũndũ ũcio.  Nake mũndũ ũcio akiuga atĩrĩ: Rĩu  kaĩ ũyũ nĩwe ihĩndĩ rĩmwe riumĩte mahĩndĩ-inĩ makwa,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o na nyama yumĩte nyama-inĩ ya mwĩrĩ wakwa-ĩ! Nĩ wega etawo mũndũ-mũka, tondũ arutirũo thĩinĩ wa mũndũ-mũrũme.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ wa ũguo-rĩ, mũndũ mũrũme nĩ atigane na ithe na nyina, magwatane na mũka, nao erĩ matuĩkire mwĩrĩ ũmwe.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"WMrAmwVpvkOPmKQNI75vaw",Verses:[{},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                      
 
GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩkĩ, nĩkuo Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita akarugithĩria ndũrĩrĩ ciothe iruga rĩa nyamũ noru, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>narĩa ndibei njega ĩĩkĩrĩtwo mũrĩo nĩ kĩnyita itanakeerũo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> acirugithĩrie iruga rĩa nyamũ noru ĩĩ na maguta maingĩ mĩthimo-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na rĩa ndibei ĩrĩa njega makĩria ĩĩkĩrĩtwo mũrĩo nĩ kĩnyita ĩtanakeerũo.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ akeheria kĩndũ kĩrĩa kĩhumbĩte andũ a mĩhĩrĩga yothe akĩninĩre kĩrĩma-inĩ  gĩkĩ, hamwe na tama wa kwĩhumba mũtwe ũrĩa ũthiikĩrĩirie andũ a ndũrĩrĩ  ciothe. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Gĩkuũ  nĩ kũng’aria akĩng’arĩtie agakĩnina biũ tene na tene; ningĩ Mwathani Ngai nĩ akagiria maithori mathiũ mothe, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>na rũmena rũrĩa andũ ake mamenetwo arũnine rũthire thĩ; tondũ Mwathani nĩwe warĩtie ũhoro ũcio.  Mũthenya ũcio nĩ gũkeranwo ũũ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, ũyũ nĩwe Ngai witũ, na nĩwe twetereire atũhonokie.  Ũyũ nĩwe Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩwe twetereire, nĩ getha  tũkene na tũcanjamũke nĩ ũndũ wa kũhonokania gwake.  Amu-rĩ, kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩkĩ nĩkĩo guoko kwa Mwathani kũrĩikaraga.
	</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"69HqCtUVNU67suMbFWAibQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Ũũgi 6:12-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨŨGĨ:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>Ũũgĩ nĩ mũkengu na ndũhorahoraga, na arĩa mawendaga nĩ mawonaga narua, na ũkonwo nĩ arĩa maũmathaga. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846> Nĩ wĩyonithagia arĩa marĩ na wendi wa kũũwona, na ũkamenyeka nĩo. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846> Ũkĩra tene nĩ ũndũ wa kũũcaria na ndũkanoga; ũkaũkora ũikaire ihingo-inĩ ciaku. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846> O na gwĩciria gwiki igũrũ rĩaguo nĩ ũmenyi mũkinyanĩru; ikara ũũcũthĩrĩirie na wĩnyagunyĩki nĩ ũrĩgũtiga na ihenya.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846>  
Guo mwene nĩ ũcangacangaga ũgĩetha arĩa magĩrĩirũo nĩguo na nĩ wĩmenyithagia kũrĩ o na ũhoreri ũkĩmakora  magĩthiĩ, ũthiĩte kũmathagana nĩ ũndũ wa meciria mao.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"CijoFylh0keC3JcS65Umeg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             	         Thama 3: 1-8,13-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> 
Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Musa nĩ gũkorũo aakorirũo akĩrĩithia ndĩithia ya mũthoniwe jethero mũthĩnjĩri </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ngai wa Madian, nake akĩmĩtwara mbarĩ ĩrĩa ĩngĩ ya werũ wakuo, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>agĩkinya  kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Ngai na kũu Horeb.  Nake mũraika wa Mwathani akĩmuumĩrĩra arĩ rũrĩrĩmbĩ-inĩ rũa mwaki ruoimaga kĩhinga-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>agĩcũthĩrĩria, na atĩrĩ, kĩhinga kĩu nĩ mwaki gĩakanaga, na gĩtingĩhĩa.  Nake Musa akiuga atĩrĩ: Rĩu nĩ ngũkerũra naho, nĩ getha nyone kĩũndũ gĩkĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>‘menye kĩrĩa gĩkũgiria kĩhinga kĩhĩe.  Nake Mwathani ona atĩ egũkerũra naho nĩguo one wega-rĩ, we Ngai agĩkĩmwĩta e kĩhinga-inĩ kĩu thĩ-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>akiuga atĩrĩ: Musa, Musa.  Nake agĩcokia atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ.  Agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Menya ũkuhĩhĩrie haha; amba ũrute iratũ ciaku magũrũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo hau ũrũngiĩ nĩ handũ hatheru.  O na ningĩ agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩ: Nĩ niĩ Ngai wa thoguo, Ngai wa Abraham, Ngai wa Isaka,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ngai wa Jakobu.  Nake Musa akĩhitha ũthiũ tondũ nĩ etigagĩra gũcũthĩrĩria Ngai.  Nake Mwathani akiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Ti-itherũ nĩ nyonete mĩnyarirĩko ya andũ akwa arĩa marĩ Misri, na ngaigua kĩrĩro kĩao nĩ ũndũ wa akaburũ akuo, tondũ nĩ njũĩ maruo marĩa marĩ namo; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na niĩ ngĩikũrukĩte nĩguo ndĩmateithũre moko-inĩ ma andũ a Misri, ndĩmarute bũrũri ũcio, ndĩmahire bũrũri mwega mwariĩ, wa bũthi wa iria na ũũkĩ.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Musa akĩũria Ngai atĩrĩ: Rĩrĩa ngakinya kũrĩ ciana cia Israeli, ndĩciĩre ũũ: Ngai wa maithe manyu nĩwe ũndeketie kũrĩ inyuĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nacio injũrie atĩrĩ: Agĩĩtagwo atĩa? Ngagĩciĩra atĩa hihi? Nake Ngai akĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ: Niĩ ndũire o ta ũrĩa ndũire; agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩra ciana cia Israeli ũũ, atĩ ũrĩa wĩtagwo Niĩ ndũire, nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ.  O na ningĩ Ngai akĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ: Ĩra ciana cia Israeli ũũ, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>atĩ Mwathani, o we Ngai wa maithe manyu, o we Ngai wa Abraham, Ngai wa Isaka, Ngai wa Jakobu, nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ,; </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>rĩu nĩrĩo rĩĩtwa rĩakwa tene na tene, na norĩo kĩririkania gĩakwa o nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"7v3sB+Sfc0O6pPsOFlwhkg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                  Isaia 60:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Atĩrĩrĩ,  ũkĩra ũikare ũcangararĩte, nĩ ũndũ ũtheri wa gũgũtherera nĩ mũũku, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>naguo riri wa Mwathani ũkũratha ta riũa ũkwarĩre.  Tondũ rĩrĩ, nduma nĩ ikaiyũra thĩ, nayo nduma ndumanu ĩhumbĩre ndũrĩrĩ; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>no wee-rĩ Mwathani nĩ kwara agakwarĩra, o naguo riri wake wonagwo ũkwarĩire.
Nacio ndũrĩrĩ igokokaga harĩ ũtheri waku,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o nao athamaki mokokage makinye kũrĩa ũcangararĩte ta riũa rĩkĩratha. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, inamũra maitho maku wĩhũgũre na mĩena yothe wĩonere ũrĩa andũ mecokanĩrĩirie, magoka harĩ wee;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> arĩũ aku makoima kũndũ kũraya mũno, o nao airĩtu aku moke makuuĩtwo na ngoi.  Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ ũkona wega,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> warĩrio ũtheri, o nayo ngoro yaku nĩ ĩgacamjamũka  o na ĩigue wega nĩ ũrĩa ĩmakũkĩte, tondũ indo ciothe iria ikuuagwo ikagerio igũrũ rĩa iria rĩrĩa inene,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa ciingĩhĩte, nĩ ikerekerio harĩ wee, o naguo ũtonga wa ndũrĩrĩ ũrehwo harĩ wee. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ngamĩra nyingĩ cia rũgendo nĩ ikaiyũra gwaku, o nacio njaũ cia ngamĩra cia Madiana, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o na Efa, nacio ciothe ikorũo ciumĩte Saba.  Nacio thahabu na ũbani nĩcio ikarehe, o na iheanage ũhoro wa ũrĩa Mwathani akumagio.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"RaPrVmsc0kCoDEn2gIHQgw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				             Isaia 35:4-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩa marĩ na guoya ngoro merei atĩrĩ: Wĩũmĩrĩriei, mũtige gwĩtigĩra; atĩrĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ngai wanyu agoka na ũhoro wa kũrĩhanĩria, we Ngai agerane ngero iringaine na ũrĩa gwĩkĩtwo. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩwe ũgoka amũhonokie.  Hĩndĩ ĩo maitho ma atumumu nĩ makahingũrũo o namo matũ ma arĩa mataiguaga  nĩ magakunũrũo. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo  mũndũ ũrĩa ũthuaga agacimbicaga o ta thwariga , o naruo rũrĩmĩ rũa ũrĩa ũtahotaga kwaria nĩ kũina rũkaina; nĩ gũkorũo werũ-inĩ nĩ gũgatathũka maaĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o na kũu rũng’ũri-inĩ gũthererage tũrũũĩ.
O naguo  mũthanga ũrĩa ũhenahenagia nĩ ũkagarũrũo ũtuĩke karia ka maaĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nakuo kũndũ kũrĩa gwĩ tĩri mũnyotu kũgĩe ithima cia maaĩ megũtherũka.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE Isaia 35:4-7"},{Guid:"itUW+6i+9ECnwBtIeOv96g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                              Atumwo 10:34,37-43</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATUMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Petro agĩitĩka kwaria akiuga, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>“inyuĩ nĩmũĩ, naguo nĩguo wahunjanĩirio Judea guothe wambĩrĩirio o Galilea thutha wa rĩrĩa John aheanire ũhoro </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>wa atĩ andũ mabatithio.  Naguo nĩ wa Yesu wa Nazareth, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa Ngai aamũitĩrĩirie Muoyo mũtheru o na hinya nake agĩcanga agĩĩkaga maũndũ mega na akĩhonagia andũ arĩa othe</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> matũire manyariragwo nĩ mũcukani: nĩ gũkorũo Ngai aarĩ hamwe nake.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Naithuĩ-rĩ tũrĩ aira a maũndũ macio mothe ekire kũu bũrũri wa Ayahudi, o na Jerusalemu. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake oragirũo nĩ andũ na kũmũcuria mũtĩ igũrũ. Nĩwe Ngai aariũkirie mũthenya gatatũ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> agĩĩtĩkĩra atĩ acoke kuoneka no ti kuonwo nĩ andũ othe o tiga o aira arĩa mathurirũo o mbere nĩ Ngai nao nĩ ithuĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o ithuĩ arĩa twarĩaga na tũkanyuaga hamwe nake,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> arĩĩkia kũriũka akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ.  Na gũtwatha nĩ aatwathire atĩ tũhunjagĩrie andũ na tuumbũrage atĩ we nĩw</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> watuirũo nĩ Ngai mũtui-ciira wa andũ arĩa marĩ muoyo na wa arĩa makuĩte.  Nao irori ciothe nĩwe maheanagĩra ũira, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>makoimbũra atĩ nĩũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa gakorũo amwĩhokete nĩ akoherũo mehia make.
 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"n+KFDYWDB0ivGH+BqFuSog",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                       Amosi 7:12-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA KĨRORI AMOSI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Amasia agĩcoka akĩĩra Amosi atĩrĩ: Wee muoni ũyũ wa maũndũ, wĩthiĩre ũũrĩre bũrũri wa Juda, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ũkarĩage irio kuo, na ũrathagĩre ũhoro kuo: no gũkũ Bethel-rĩ, ndũkanarathe ũndũ rĩngĩ:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> amu nĩ handũ haamũre haikairio nĩ mũthamaki, nĩ nyũmba nyamũre ya rũrĩrĩ rũrũ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Amosi agĩcokeria Amasia ũhoro, akiuga atĩrĩ: Niĩ-rĩ, ndirĩ mũnabii, o na ndirĩ wa thiritũ ĩo ya anabii;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> niĩ ndĩ mũndũ wa ũhiũ-inĩ na mwĩthondekeri mĩkũyũ: nake Mwathani agĩkĩnduta rũũru-inĩ rũrĩa ndarũmagĩrĩra,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> We Mwathani agĩkĩnjĩra atĩrĩ: Thiĩ, ũkarathĩre kĩrĩndĩ gĩakwa gĩa Israeli ũhoro.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"7aBMfRzuS0+LtmaCK4lQxA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                      Jeremia 31:7-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI JEREMIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Kũngũĩra Jakobu, mũmũinĩre mũkenete, o na mũkũngũĩre mũnene wa ndũrĩrĩ; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>hunjanĩriai ũhoro mũgĩkũngũyagia, mũkiugaga atĩrĩrĩ; Ĩ Mwathani, honokia andũ aku,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o arĩa matigarĩte a Israeli.  Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩkũrehe ngamarehithie ndĩmarute bũrũri wa gathigathini, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ndĩmacokererie ndĩmarutĩte ituri-inĩ cia thĩ iria irĩ kũraya mũno, nao magakorwo marehanĩte na atumumu ao,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na ithua, o na atumia arĩa me mahu, ona arĩa mekũrũmwo moke me kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ mũno, gĩcoke gũkũ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nao magoka makĩrĩraga, na niĩ ndĩmatongorie o magĩ’thaithaga, ndũme magere njũĩ-inĩ cia maaĩ,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o na magere njĩra iria nũngaru itarĩ kĩndũ kĩngĩmahĩnga;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩgũkorwo niĩ nĩniĩ Ithe wa Israeli, nake Efraim nĩwe irigithathi rĩakwa.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"j1xZzOU4SES4PH/+jSJR0g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					     	Danieli 7:13-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI DANIELI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngĩcoka ngĩkĩona maũndũ mangĩ na cioneki cia ũtukũ, na atĩrĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>He mũndũ wahaanaga  ta mũrũ wa mũndũ wokire na matũ ma igũrũ, nake agĩkinya harĩ Ũrĩa-ũtũire-ho-kuuma-o-tene,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na agĩtwaratwarũo hakuhĩ nake.  Nake agĩkĩheo wathani, na riri, o na ũthamaki, nĩgetha andũ a nduka ciothe,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>na a ndũrĩrĩ  ciothe, na a mĩario yothe, mamũtungatagĩre. Naguo wathani ũcio wake nĩ wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na ndũgathira o rĩ, o rĩ.  Naguo ũthamaki ũcio wake ndũkonũhĩka o  na atĩa.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"P8bqgU6NOEOdzRnCuKAi5g",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					     	Danieli 7:13-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI DANIELI: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngĩcoka ngĩkĩona maũndũ mangĩ na </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cioneki cia ũtukũ, na atĩrĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>He mũndũ wahaanaga  ta mũrũ wa mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wokire na matũ ma igũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nake agĩkinya harĩ Ũrĩa-ũtũire-ho-kuuma-o-tene,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na agĩtwaratwarũo hakuhĩ nake.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake agĩkĩheo wathani, na riri, o na ũthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩgetha andũ a nduka ciothe,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na a ndũrĩrĩ  ciothe, na a mĩario yothe, mamũtungatagĩre. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo wathani ũcio wake nĩ wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndũgathira o rĩ, o rĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo ũthamaki ũcio wake ndũkonũhĩka o  na atĩa.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 93:1ab;1c-2;5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; nĩ ũnene ehumbĩte; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwĩhumba, Mwathani nĩ ehumbĩte hinya, akawĩoha ta ndoho.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩĩ-ni, thĩ nĩ kũrũmio ĩrũmĩtio, ũndũ ĩtangĩenyenyeka.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gĩtĩ gĩaku kĩa ũnene gĩtũire gĩĩ kĩrũmu kuuma o tene na tene, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee-rĩ, ũtũire o ho gwata mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maũira maku, Mwathani, nĩ mehokeku o mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtheru ũgũtũũra wagĩrĩtie nyũmba yaku, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matukũ matarĩ mũthia.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũroka ũnene waku wa ũtheri</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                        Kũguũrĩrio 1:5-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu Kristũ, mũira ũrĩa mwĩhokeku, o we irigithathi rĩa arĩa akuũ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nowe mwathi wa athamaki a thĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>we ũcio ũtwenda, na watuohorire na thakame </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake tuume mehia-inĩ maitũ, na agĩtũtua kĩrĩndĩ kĩa mũthamaki,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> tũtuĩke athĩnjĩri Ngai wake, o we Ithe-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũgoocwo na Mwathani arogĩaga kũrĩ we nginya tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.  Atĩrĩrĩi, nĩ gũũka egũũka na matu, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na gũtirĩ riitho rĩtakamuona, o na arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maamũthecire o nao mamuone; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndũrĩrĩ ciothe cia thĩ nĩ gũcakaya nĩ ũndũ wake.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Noguo gũgatuĩka, Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ niĩ Alfa o na Omega, nĩguo Mwathani Ngai ekuuga, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa ũrĩ ho, na nowe warĩ ho, na nowe ũgũũka, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o we Mwene-Hinya-Wothe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mark 11,10</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ ũrĩa ũgũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani! </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ ũthamakĩ ũrĩa ũgũũka.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                        John 18:33b-37</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Pilato akĩũria Yesu: Wee nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũthamaki wa Ayahudi? Nake Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũkũũria ũguo wĩrĩtwo nĩ ngoro yaku mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana nĩ andũ angĩ makwĩrire ũhoro wakwa? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Pilato agĩcokia atĩrĩ: Kaĩ ndĩ mũyahudi 
niĩ? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Anga ti rũrĩrĩ rũanyu na athacerdoti arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anene maakũneana kũrĩ niĩ; nĩ atĩa wĩkĩte? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: Ũthamaki wakwa ti </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wana gũkũ thĩ; ũthamaki wakwa ũngĩrĩ wa gũkũ thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ akwa mangĩrĩ kũruta mbaara, ndikaneo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ayahudi; no rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ, ũthamaki wakwa ti wana gũkũ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ ũcio Pilato  akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Anga ũkĩrĩ o mũthamaki, wee? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu agĩcokia atĩrĩrĩ: wee nĩ woiga, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amu ndĩ mũthamaki.  Nĩkĩo ndaciarirũo, na </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩkĩo njũkĩte gũkũ thĩ, atĩ nduĩke  mũira wa ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe waguo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ aiguaga mũgambo wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"THIGUKUU YA MWATHANI WITU YESU KRISTU MUTHAMAKI"},{Guid:"VbJxsL7U5UeZRdptyiyc4g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 			Kũguĩrĩrio 7: 2-4, 9-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ, John, ngĩcoka ngĩona mũraika ũngĩ aambatĩra irathĩro-inĩ rĩa riũa, e na kĩrĩmi kĩa Ngai ũrĩa wĩ mũoyo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> kĩrĩa gĩa gwĩkanĩra rũũri; nake akĩanĩrĩra araika acio ana na mũgambo mũnene,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> acio maahetwo hinya mehie thĩ na iria, akiuga atĩrĩ: mũtikehie thĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> kana iria, kana mĩtĩ, kinya tũkorũo tũrĩkĩtie gwĩkĩra ndungata cia Ngai witũ rũũri mathiithi mao.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Na nĩ ndaiguire mũigana wa acio mekĩrirũo rũũri, na nĩ  ngiri igana rĩa ngiri mĩrongo ĩna na inya, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>arĩa mekĩrirũo rũũri a mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya ciana cia Israeli.
Thutha wa maũndũ macio ngĩrora, ngĩona atĩrĩ, gwĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ mũno,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> gĩtangĩgereka nĩ mũndũ, kĩa andũ moimĩte ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ ciothe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na marĩ a mĩhĩrĩga yothe na nduka ciothe o na mĩario yothe, marũgamĩte mbere-inĩ ya gĩtĩ kĩrĩa gĩa ũthamaki na mbere ya Gatũrũme 
mehumbĩte  nguo njerũ ndaya na me na makĩndũ moko;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩ kwanĩrĩra maanagĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene, makoiga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Kũhonokania nĩ kwa Ngai witũ ũrĩa ũikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki, na gwa Gatũrũme.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>  Nao  araika othe nĩ marũngiĩ mathũrũrũkĩire gĩtĩ kĩu gĩa ũthamaki, na magathiũrũrũkĩria athuri arĩa o na  ciũmbe iria inya ii muoyo; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>nao makĩĩgũithia thĩ na mothiũ mao kũu mbere-inĩ ya gĩtĩ  kĩu gĩa ũthamaki, magĩthathaiya Ngai, makiuga:</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũtuĩke guo! Kĩrathimo, na riri, na ũũgĩ, o na ngatho, o na gĩtĩo,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> o na ũhoti, o na hinya, irotũũra na Ngai witũ nginya tene na tene . Nĩ gũtuĩke guo.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Nao athuri, ũmwe agĩcokia ũhoro, akĩnjũria atĩrĩ: Acio mehumbĩte nguo icio njerũ nĩ a? </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Na moimĩte kũ? Na niĩ ngĩmwĩra : Mũthuri  ũyũ, nĩwe ũũĩ.  Nake akĩnjĩra atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> Acio nĩo arĩa moimĩte mĩnyamaroinĩ ĩrĩa mĩnene, na nĩ maathambirie nguo ciao, </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>magĩgĩcierũhia na thakame ya Gatũrũme. </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384> 
Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"qoHDsUtJV0KDmt5y0TxQTg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                          Atũmwo 3:13-15,17-19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Petro onire ũhoro ũcio, agĩcokeria kĩrĩndĩ atĩrĩ: Ngai wa Abraham, na wa Isaaka, na wa Yakobu, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o we Ngai wa maithe maitũ-rĩ, nĩwe wagoocithia ndungata yake Yesu,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o ũcio inyuĩ mwaneanire na mũkĩmũkaana mbere ya Pilato, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aatuĩte atĩ amũohore. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ũcio Mũtheru na Mũthingu-rĩ, nĩwe inyuĩ mwakaanire, mũkĩhoya atĩ muohorerũo mũũragani, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mũgĩkĩũragithia Mũthamaki ũrĩa mũheani muoyo. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake nĩwe Ngai aariũkirie  oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ: na nĩ ithuĩ aira a ũhoro ũcio.
Na rĩu-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ariũ a Ithe witũ, nĩ njũĩ atĩ mwekire ũguo nĩ ũndũ wa kũrigwo, o ta ũrĩa anene anyu nao mekire.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, mohoro marĩa Ngai aamenyithanirie o mbere na tũnua twa anabii othe,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ma atĩ Kristũ wake nĩ akanyarirĩka, nĩmo ahingĩtie ũguo.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ ũndũ rĩ, wĩrirei na mũgarũrũke, nĩ getha mehia manyu marihũrũo.
 </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"j08AyDDLxk2mEnxCvJT7jg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                       Job 7:1-4,6-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA JOB:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Job agĩcokia, akĩũria atĩrĩ: Anga mũndũ to ta kũgererũo agereirũo ihinda rĩake rĩa gũtũũrio ita-inĩ gũkũ thĩ?</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Namo matukũ make anga to ta matukũ ma ũrĩa mwandĩke wĩra? Niĩ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ndariĩ ta ngombo ĩĩrirĩirie mũno kĩĩgunyi, ningĩ ta mũthũkũmi ũrĩa ũthethũkĩire mũcara wake</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>.  Niĩ nĩguo nduĩrĩirũo atĩ ngĩe na mĩeri ya tũhũ, na ngaathĩrĩrũo ndaarage maraara ma mĩnoga.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩrĩa ndakoma , njũragia atĩrĩ: Ndĩrĩũkĩra rĩ? Ũtukũ ũgagĩtuĩka no mũraya na ndaaraga ngĩanganga o nginya gũkĩe. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Matukũ makwa nĩ marathira na ihenya rĩkĩrĩte rĩa kanyamũ karĩa gakonjanithangia uthi tama ũgĩtumwo,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũthira marathira itarĩ na ũndũ ũrĩa ndĩĩrĩgĩrĩire. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> No kĩririkane atĩ muoyo wakwa no rũhuho; riitho rĩakwa rĩtigacoka kuona ũndũ mwega.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"F7/dbfe9Rk+4dz5I10eILA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                       Jeremia 23:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI JEREMIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩ!, kaĩ arĩithi arĩa maninaga mbũri cia rũũru rũakwa o na magacihurunja marĩ na haaro-ĩ!</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.  Tondũ ũcio, Mwathani Ngai wa Israeli ekuuga ũũ ha ũhoro wa arĩithi acio marĩithagia andũ akwa-rĩ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ kũhurunja mũhurunjĩte mbũri cia rũũru rũakwa, na mũgacihahũra, na mũkaaga gũthiĩ gũcirora;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> atĩrĩ, nĩ ngamũherithĩria ũũru o ro ũcio wa ciĩko cianyu; ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ na niĩ nĩ ngacokereria mbũri iria itigarĩte cia rũũru rũakwa, ciume mabũrũri mothe marĩa ndacitwarithirie, ndĩcicokie ciugũ ciacio; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nacio nĩ igaciara ciongerereke mũno.  Na niĩ nĩ ngaciigĩra arĩithi a gũcirĩithia; na itigacoka gwĩtigĩra o na rĩ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o na kana imakio, na hatirĩ o na ĩmwe yacio ĩkaagwo; ũguo nĩ guo Mwathani ekuuga.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, matukũ nĩ magoka marĩa ngaarahũrĩra Davide mũndũ mũthingu ũgerekanĩtio na Thuuna ya mũtĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩwe ũgathamaka, na thĩinĩ wa ũthamaki wake agaacĩre o kũgaacĩra; nĩ agatuanagĩra cira wega, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na ekage maũndũ ma kĩhooto bũrũri ũcio.  Matukũ-inĩ make-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Juda nĩ akahonokio, nake Israeli atũũre egangarĩte; narĩo rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa agetagwo nĩrĩo rĩrĩ, Mwathani ũthingu witũ.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"lRe6hBTqsU+ibsyAOVCr3g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                         1 Samuel 3:3, 10.19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MBERE RĨA SAMUEL: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Samuel agĩkorũo akomete kũu hekarũ-inĩ ya Mwathani thĩinĩ,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> ĩo yaigĩtwo ithandũkũ rĩa Mwathani-rĩ, Mwathani agĩgĩĩta Samuel,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nake agĩcokia atĩrĩ, Niĩ ũyũ haha.  Agĩgĩteng’era kwĩ Eli, akiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ ũyũ haha tondũ nĩ wanjĩta.  nake akiuga  atĩrĩ: Ndiĩtanĩte  ; coka ũgakome.  Agĩgĩthiĩ,  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>agĩkoma.  Ningĩ Mwathani agĩĩtana o rĩngĩ atĩrĩ: Samuel.nake Samuel agĩkĩarahũka, agĩthiĩ kwĩ Eli,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> akiuga atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ haha, tondũ nĩ wanjĩta.  Agĩgĩcokia atĩrĩ: Ndiĩtanĩte, mũrũ wakwa; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>coka ũgakome.  Na rĩrĩ, Samuel ndakorirũo amenyete Mwathani hĩndĩ ĩo,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> kana akaguũrĩrio ũhoro wa Mwathani.  Ningĩ Mwathani agĩgĩĩta Samuel rĩngĩ hĩndĩ ya gatatũ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nake agĩkĩarahũka, agĩthiĩ kwĩ Eli, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ haha, tondũ nĩ wanjĩta.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Eli agĩkĩmenya atĩ nĩ Mwathani wetaga mwana ũcio.  Tondũ ũcio Eli agĩkĩĩra Samuel atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> thiĩ ũgakome, na gũgakinya atĩrĩ, atĩ aagwĩta, ũge atĩrĩ: Aria, Mwathani; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ ndungata yaku nĩ iraigua.  Samuel agĩgĩcoka agĩthiĩ, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>agĩkoma handũ hake hau aakomaga.  Nake Mwathani agĩthiĩ, akĩrũgama, </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>agĩĩtana o ta mahinda marĩa mangĩ, ũũ: Samuel! Samuel! Nake Samuel agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>aria, nĩ ũndũ ndungata yaku nĩ ĩraigua.  Samuel agĩgĩkũra, nake Mwathani aarĩ hamwe nake, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>akĩaga kũreka kiugo o na kĩmwe gĩake kĩage kũhingio</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"Y9AtMoCuOUmF0Elb0CDwaA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                          Sofonia 3,14-18 </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA SOFONIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, wee mwarĩ wa Sion, ina rũĩmbo, o nawe Israeli-rĩ, anĩrĩra mũno; o nawe mwarĩ wa Jerusalem canjamũka,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na ũkene na ngoro yaku yothe, Mwathani nĩ akuoheire agatiga gũkũhingĩria matuĩro ma cira waku, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>nacio thũ ciaku nĩ acithinĩkanĩtie; mũthamaki wa Israeli arĩ thĩinĩ waku, nake nĩwe Mwathani;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> wee ndũgacoka kũonerũo kĩrĩi  o na rĩ.  Mũthenya ũcio Jerusalem rĩkerũo atĩrĩ: Menya ũkanetigĩra; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o narĩo Sion rĩĩrũo atĩrĩ: Menya ũkanaregeria moko maku. Mwathani Ngai waku arĩ thĩinĩ waku,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> o we ũrĩa hoti ya kũhonokania; nĩ arĩgũkenagĩra agũthererie ngoro, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na agũkĩrĩre nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa akwendete mũno; agagũkũngũĩra na ndũrũhĩ cia nyĩmbo.</s>"},{ID:9,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FFFF00FF"}}},
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"mo9u35PuHkOs8xhNSK/FaQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                  Isaia 42:1-4,6-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Mwathani  ekuuga ũũ: ĩno nĩyo ndungata yakwa ĩrĩa ndiirĩrĩire; nĩyo ĩrĩa ndĩĩthurĩire,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩyo ĩkenagia ngoro yakwa: nĩ ndĩmĩikũrũkĩirie muoyo wakwa ũkamĩhuba, na nĩyo ĩkarehithĩrie ndũrĩrĩ cira wa kĩhooto.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Ndĩkaanĩrĩra, o na kana ĩhaicie kayũ kayo na igũrũ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana ĩtũme mũgambo wayo ũiguwo njĩra-inĩ.  Kamũrangi kagondoku ndĩgakoina,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana rũtambĩ rũa ũguta rũgĩtoga ĩrũhorie.  
Nĩ gũtua ĩgatuanagĩra cira na ma. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ndĩkahwererekera, o na kana yume tha, o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ĩgakorũo ĩtũmĩte gũkũ thĩ kũgĩe cira wa kĩhooto;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> andũ arĩa matũũraga ithama-inĩ magaikaraga metereire watho wayo.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Niĩ Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ niĩ ngwĩtĩte o ta ũrĩa nyonaga kwerekereire, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ngakũnyita guoko na ngũmenyagĩrĩre, na ngũheane nĩ getha ũtuĩke wa kũrĩkanĩra kĩrĩkanĩro na andũ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o na ũtuĩke ũtheri wa gũtherera andũ a ndũrĩrĩ; o na ningĩ nĩ getha ũhingũrage maitho marĩa matumumu,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nao andũ arĩa mohetwo ũmarutage kĩoho-inĩ,  o nao arĩa maikarĩte nduma-inĩ-rĩ, ũmarutage korokoro-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"B49UVpx5WUGkd/6X2hAQaw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                2 Athamaki 4:42-44</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATHAMAKI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, na rĩrĩ, hagĩgĩũka mũndũ oimĩte Baali-Shalisha, akĩrehere mũndũ ũcio wa Ngai irio cia mũro wa mbere,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nacio nĩ mĩgate mĩrongo ĩĩrĩ ya cairĩ, o na igira njigũ cia ngano aciĩkĩrĩte Kĩondo-inĩ.  Nake akiuga atĩrĩ;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Cinengere andũ marĩe. Nayo ndungata yake ĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Hĩ! Atĩ atĩa? Njigĩre andũ igana mĩgate o ro ĩno?</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No Elisha akiuga atĩrĩ; Mĩhe andũ marĩe; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani oigĩte ũũ: Nĩmekũrĩa, na nĩ mekũmĩtigaria.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ ũcio ndungata yake ĩgĩkĩmĩiga   mbere ya andũ acio, nao makĩrĩa na makĩmĩtigaria, o ta ũrĩa uuge wa Mwathani watariĩ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"neRBeguFBkiEOUyU4cLvcw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Jonah 3:1-5.10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA KĨRORI JONAH:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	
Nayo ndũmĩrĩri ya Mwathani ĩgĩcoka ĩgĩkinyĩra Jonah rĩa kerĩ, akĩĩrũo atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ũkĩra ũthiĩ Nineve, itũũra rĩrĩa inene, ũrĩgũtũkĩre ũrĩhunjĩrie ũhoro o ũrĩa ngũkwĩra.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Jonah agĩgĩũkĩra agĩthiĩ Nineve, kũringana na ũhoro ũcio wa Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩ, itũũra rĩu rĩa Nineve rĩarĩ inene mũno, rĩa kũnina matukũ matatũ rĩgĩgatuĩkanĩka.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Jonah akĩambĩrĩria gũtonya itũũra rĩu, agĩthiĩ itĩĩna rĩa mũthenya ũmwe,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> agĩkĩanĩrĩra akiuga atĩrĩ: No matukũ mĩrongo ĩna matigaire gũkũ Nineve kũhang’ũranio! Nao andũ acio a Nineve magĩgĩĩtĩkia Ngai; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>makĩanĩrĩrithia atĩ kũgĩe hĩndĩ ya kwĩima irio, na makĩĩhumba nguo cia makũnia,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> kuuma o ũrĩa mũnene wao othe o kinya ũrĩa mũnyinyi wao othe.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Ngai akĩona ciĩko icio ciao atĩ nĩ maathengeire mĩthiĩre yao mĩũru;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ Ngai agĩkĩĩricũkwo agĩtiga ũũru ũrĩa oigĩte ekũmeka; na ndaigana kũwĩka.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"RlBWhABFIEC7E8MFAlY4Zg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             	         Deuter. 26:4-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Musa agĩgĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ na akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũthĩnjĩri Ngai aiyũkie kĩondo kĩu, akĩruta guoko gwaku,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> akĩige thĩ o hau mbere ya kĩgongona kĩa Mwathani Ngai waku.  Nawe hĩndĩ ĩo ũgagĩcokia uugĩre  o hau mbere ya Mwathani Ngai waku atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Baba aarĩ Mũsuriata worũraga; nake agĩgĩikũrũka agĩthiĩ Misri, agĩtũũra kuo e mũgeni, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>andũ ake marĩ anyinyi mũno magĩtarũo; nao magĩkĩingĩhĩra kuo magĩtuĩka rũrĩrĩ rũnene, na rũĩ  hinya, na rũa andũ aingĩ mũno; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nao andũ a Misri magĩtũhinyĩrĩria, na magĩtũnyarira, magĩtũigĩrĩra mawĩra ma hinya mũno matũtuĩte ngombo ciao:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na ithuĩ tũgĩgĩkaĩra Mwathani Ngai wa maithe maitũ; nake Mwathani akĩigua gũkaya kũu gwitũ, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nake akĩona ũrĩa tũranyarirũo, o na wĩra ũrĩa tũrarutithio wa hinya, o na kũhinyĩrĩrio kũrĩa tũrahinyĩrĩrio;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:" nake Mwathani agĩtũruta Misri,  na njara irĩ hinya, o na guoko gũtambũrũkĩtio, hamwe na maũndũ ma kũguoyohania mũno, na kũringa ciama,"},{ID:11,
Text:" o na maũndũ ma kũgegania; nake nĩ atũrehete kũndũ gũkũ, agatũhe bũrũri ũyũ,"},{ID:12,
Text:" o bũrũri wĩ bũthi wa iria, o na ũũkĩ.  Na atĩrĩrĩ, wee Mwathani, rĩu nĩ ndakũrehere maciaro ma mbere ma thĩ ĩno ũheete. "},{ID:13,
Text:" Nawe ũkĩmaige thĩ mbere ya Mwathani Ngai waku, ũcoke ũinamĩrĩre mbere ya Mwathani Ngai waku, ũmũhoe."},{ID:14,
Text:"Ciugo cia Mwathani"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"8u8VV58gekWYprzsZ3wTFQ",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					           Jeremia 1:4-5,17-19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI JEREMIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ ma Josia, mũthamaki wa Juda, ndũmĩrĩri ya Mwathani  yanginyĩrĩire ngĩĩrũo ũũ: O na mbere ya itaanakũũmba nda ya nyũmba-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> no ndakũũĩ, ningĩ o na mbere ya ũtaanoima kũu nda-rĩ, noguo ndakwamũrire ngĩgũtheria;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũtua ngũtuĩte mũrathi wa kũrathĩra ndũrĩrĩ maũndũ.  Tondũ ũcio wee nawe-rĩ, wĩhotore, ũũkĩre mwaranĩrie nao, ũmere maũndũ mothe marĩa ngũgwatha.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Menya ũmakio nĩo, nĩ getha hihi ndigagũconorithie harĩ o.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ  ũndũ ũmũthĩ nĩ kũgitĩra ngũgitĩire ũgatuĩka ta itũũra rĩirige, o na  ũgatuĩka ta gĩtugĩ gĩa kĩgera,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> o na thingo cia gĩcango, nĩ getha wĩũmie harĩ andũ a bũrũri ũyũ wothe, o na wĩũmie harĩ athamaki a Juda, o na anene akuo, o na athĩnjĩri-Ngai akuo,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o na andũ a bũrũri wothe.  Nao nĩ magacoka kũrũa mbaara nawe, no matigagũtoria, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũndũ ndĩ hamwe nawe ngũhonokie; ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"nWad6n15FUyTWUFb/6oCFA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				         Gũcokerithia Maathani 4:1-2,6-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Musa agĩgĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ na akĩmera atĩrĩ: rĩu inyuĩ Aisraeli aya, ta thikĩrĩriai mũigue irĩra cia watho wa kũrũmĩrĩrũo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na matuĩro macira marĩa ngũmũruta mũrũmagĩrĩre, nĩ getha mũtũũre muoyo, na mũkahota gũthiĩ mũtonye bũrũri ũrĩa mũheagwo nĩ Mwathani,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Ngai wa maithe manyu, mũwĩgwatĩre ũtuĩke wanyu.  Ũhoro ũrĩa ndĩmwathĩte-rĩ, mũtikanawongerere, kana mũũnyihanyihie,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ getha mũtũũre mũmenyereire maathani ma Mwathani Ngai wanyu, marĩa ngũmwatha.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Tondũ ũcio mamenyagĩrĩrei o na mũmekage; nĩ gũkorũo macio nĩmo marĩonanagia ũũgĩ wanyu, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o na ũhoro wanyu wa ũrĩa mũmenyete maũndũ, makĩonwo nĩ ndũrĩrĩ iria irĩiguaga ũhoro wothe wa irĩra icio cia watho wa kũrũmĩrĩrũo, nacio ciugage atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Kaĩ ti-itherũ rũrĩrĩ rũrũ rũnene nĩ rũũgĩ-ĩ, o na kaĩ nĩ andũ mamenyete wega maũndũ-ĩ! Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ rũrĩrĩ rũrĩkũ rũnene rũĩ na Ngai yaruo ĩrũkuhĩhĩirie, o ta ũrĩa Mwathani Ngai witũ atũkuhagĩrĩria mahinda marĩa mothe twamũkaĩra? </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ-rĩ, nĩ rũrĩrĩ rũrĩkũ rũnene rũĩ na irĩra cia watho wa kũrũmĩrĩrũo cia kĩhooto, o na matuĩro ma cira ma kĩhooto, ta watho ũyũ wothe ndĩramwatha naguo ũmũthĩ?</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"LvfUkhKcSkGtkp+I/MlE7Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				             Ndari 11:25-29</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA NDARI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Mwathani agĩgĩikũrũka arĩ thĩinĩ wa itu, akĩaria nake,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> akĩgaya hinya ũmwe wa muoyo ũrĩa aarĩ naguo akĩũhe athuri acio mĩrongo mũgwanja;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ hinya ũcio wa muoyo wake wagĩa hamwe nao, makĩratha mohoro, no matiacokire gwĩka ũguo hĩndĩ ĩngĩ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, nĩ haatigarire andũ erĩ maaikarĩte kĩraaro-inĩ, nao ũmwe etagwo Eldad, na ũrĩa ũngĩ Medad, naguo hinya ũcio wa muoyo wa Musa ũkĩgĩa nao;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nao maarĩ a gĩkundi-inĩ gĩa acio maandĩkĩtwo, no rĩrĩ, matiathiĩte Hema-inĩ ĩo; nao andũ acio makĩratha mohoro maikarĩte o ro kũu kĩraaro-inĩ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Hagĩgĩteng’era mwanamke ũmwe, akĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ: Eldad na Medad nĩ mararatha mohoro marĩ o kũu kĩraaro-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake Joshua wa Nun, ũrĩa watungatagĩra Musa gwata o rĩrĩa aarĩ mũnyinyi, agĩcokia ũhoro akiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani wakwa Musa, makaanie.  Nake Musa agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Kaĩ ũkũmaiguĩra ũiru nĩ ũndũ wakwa? Niĩ-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ndenda makĩria korũo andũ othe a Mwathani nĩ arathi na amahe hinya wa muoyo wake!</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"iYFwZ/dBGk+5itBFJ8efmg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384> </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                       Ezekiel 2:2-5</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI EZEKIELI:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Muoyo wa Ngai agĩtonya thĩ-inĩ wakwa, akĩndũgamia na magũrũ makwa, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na niĩ ngĩkĩigua ũcio ũraaria na niĩ.  Nake agĩkĩnjĩra atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa Mũndũ, nĩkũrekia ngũkũrekia harĩ ciana cia Israeli, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ũthiĩ kũrĩ ndũrĩrĩ icio nemu, nacio nĩcio ciagararĩte watho wakwa na ikanema, cio nyene o na maithe ma cio, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o nginya mũthenya ũyũ tũrĩ; nacio ciana icio nĩ ciĩndĩĩire na ikoma ngoro; nacio nĩcio ndakũrekia harĩ cio, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nawe ũciĩre atĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai oigĩte ũna na ũna.  Nacio nĩ ikamenya atĩ hoima mũrathi thĩ-inĩ wacio, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o na ingĩkũigua kana irege gũkũigua, nĩ ũndũ kĩruka kĩu nĩ kĩremu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"UCa9AitzOkCGsJfJGbEg2Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                                  Isaia 60:1-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Atĩrĩrĩ, wee Jerusalem ũkĩra ũikare ũcangararĩte, nĩ ũndũ ũtheri wa gũgũtherera nĩ mũũku,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> naguo riri wa Mwathani ũkũratha ta riũa ũkwarĩre.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Tondũ rĩrĩ, nduma nĩ ikaiyũra thĩ, nayo nduma ndumanu ĩhumbĩre ndũrĩrĩ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>no wee-rĩ, Mwathani nĩ kwara agakwarĩra, o naguo riri wake wonagwo ũkwarĩire.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nacio ndũrĩrĩ igokokaga harĩ ũtheri waku, o nao athamaki mokokage makinye kũrĩa ũcangararĩte ta riũa rĩkĩratha. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, inamũra maitho maku wĩhũgũre na mĩena yothe wĩonere ũrĩa andũ mecokanĩrĩirie, magoka harĩ wee;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> arĩũ aku makoima kũndũ kũraya mũno, o nao airĩtu aku moke makuuĩtwo na ngoi. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ ũkona wega, warĩrio ũtheri, o nayo ngoro yaku nĩ ĩgacanjamũka  o na ĩigue wega nĩ ũrĩa ĩmakũkĩte,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ indo ciothe iria ikuuagwo ikagerio igũrũ rĩa iria rĩrĩa inene,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa ciingĩhĩte, nĩ ikerekerio harĩ wee, o naguo ũtonga wa ndũrĩrĩ ũrehwo harĩ wee.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Ngamĩra nyingĩ cia rũgendo nĩ ikaiyũra gwaku, o nacio njaũ cia ngamĩra cia Madian,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> o na Efa, nacio ciothe ikorũo ciumĩte Saba.  Nacio thahabu na ũbani nĩcio ikarehe,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> o na iheanage ũhoro wa ũrĩa Mwathani akumagio.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"ZQRzDnesKEadXdXUL60j9g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             			  Sirach 27: 4-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨŨGĨ WA SIRACH BIN SIRAH:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> 
Rĩrĩa gĩcungi kĩa mũtu kĩainainio, nĩ gĩtigagia macungo thĩinĩ wakĩo, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ũguo mahĩtia ma mũndũ nĩ monekanaga thĩinĩ wa mĩario yake. </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> Mwaki nĩ ũgeragia mawĩra ma mũmbi nyũngũ, kĩgeranio kĩa mũndũ gĩkoragwo ndereti-inĩ ciake. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Matunda nĩ monanagia ta ũrĩa mĩtĩ ĩkũragio, ũguo na taguo atĩ mĩgambo ya mũndũ nĩyo ĩmũcukaga ũrĩa eiguaga. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Ndũkae gũkagathĩrĩria mũndũ ũtarĩ waigua ũrĩa aragia, tondũ njĩra nĩyo yonanagia ũrĩa andũ matariĩ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"tXTVVpYvoEi0BWMhN8bP9Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				             Isaia 50:5-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani Ngai angunũrĩte gũtũ, na niĩ ndirĩ ndamũrema, o na kana ngacoka na thutha.  Andũ arĩa ahũrani-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ kũhutata ndamahutatĩire ma’hũre, o namo makai makwa ngĩmahũgũkĩria andũ arĩa maa’munyaga nderu.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Ndiigana kũhitha ũthiũ wakwa atĩ nĩguo ndigaconorithio kana ndige gũtuĩrũo mata.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani Ngai nĩwe ũkandeithia, na tondũ ũcio ndiconorithĩtio;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ nĩ tondũ ũcio ndũmĩte ũthiũ wakwa ũikarage uumĩte o ta ihiga rĩa nyaigĩ, ngakĩmenya atĩ ndigaconorithio.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>  Ningĩ We ũrĩa ũnduaga mũthingu  e hakuhĩ; nũ ũgagĩtetania na niĩ? Nĩ tũrũgamei ithuerĩ hamwe.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Ningĩ ũrĩa ũkũnjirithia nĩwe ũrĩkũ? Ta nĩ agĩokoke anguhĩrĩrie.  Atĩrĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai nĩwe ũkandeithia; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nũ ũgakĩndua mwĩhia cira-inĩ? Othe nĩ gũkũra magakũra ta nguo; mathire biũ ta nguo irĩĩkĩte nĩ memenyi.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"LnG2KdmgK0W+bJ0oCKUZdw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                          Isa. 62:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa kũrũĩrĩra Sion, ndigatumia kanua, o na kana ndigithĩrie gũtetera Jerusalem, o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro wakuo wa ũthingu ũkoimbũka ware o ta ũtheri,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o naguo ũhoro wakuo wa kũhonokania woneke o ta tawa ũrĩa wakanaga mũno.  Nacio ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikona ũthingu waku, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o nao athamaki othe mone riri waku; wee nawe ũcoke gwĩtwo rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ rĩkagwetwo na kanua ka Mwathani.  Ningĩ ũgatuĩka ta tanji ya ũthaka ũnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> na ũhaane ta thũmbĩ ya ũthamaki ĩnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Ngai waku.  Wee nawe-rĩ, ndũgacoka gwĩtwo Mũtirike, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>o na kana bũrũri waku wĩtwo Mũkiru Ihooru; na rĩrĩ, ũrĩĩtagwo Hefiziba, o naguo bũrũri waku wĩtagwo Beula; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ akenagio nĩwe, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o naguo bũrũri waku ũgatuĩka o ta mũhiki ũrĩa ũhikĩtio.  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa mwanake ahikagia mũirĩtu, ũguo noguo aanake aku magakũhikia,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> ningĩ o ta ũrĩa mũhikania ekenagĩra nĩ mũhiki wake-rĩ, o ũguo noguo Ngai waku arĩĩkenagĩra nĩwe.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"oboQB/1JqkmzLPV6d28gaw",Verses:[{
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 
Isaya. 62:1-5"},{ID:2,
Text:"GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: "},{ID:3,
Text:"Atĩrĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa kũrũĩrĩra Sion, ndigatumia kanua, o na kana ndigithĩrie gũtetera Jerusalem, o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro wakuo wa ũthingu ũkoimbũka ware o ta ũtheri,"},{ID:4,
Text:" o naguo ũhoro wakuo wa kũhonokania woneke o ta tawa ũrĩa wakanaga mũno.  Nacio ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikona ũthingu waku, "},{ID:5,
Text:"o nao athamaki othe mone riri waku; wee nawe ũcoke gwĩtwo rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ rĩkagwetwo na kanua ka Mwathani.  Ningĩ ũgatuĩka ta tanji ya ũthaka ũnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani,"},{ID:6,
Text:" na ũhaane ta thũmbĩ ya ũthamaki ĩnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Ngai waku.  Wee nawe-rĩ, ndũgacoka gwĩtwo Mũtirike, "},{ID:7,
Text:"o na kana bũrũri waku wĩtwo Mũkiru Ihooru; na rĩrĩ, ũrĩĩtagwo Hefiziba, o naguo bũrũri waku wĩtagwo Beula; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ akenagio nĩwe, "},{ID:8,
Text:"o naguo bũrũri waku ũgatuĩka o ta mũhiki ũrĩa ũhikĩtio.  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa mwanake ahikagia mũirĩtu, ũguo noguo aanake aku magakũhikia,"},{ID:9,
Text:" ningĩ o ta ũrĩa mũhikania ekenagĩra nĩ mũhiki wake-rĩ, o ũguo noguo Ngai waku arĩĩkenagĩra nĩwe."},{ID:10,
Text:"Ciugo cia Mwathani"},{
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 96:1 na 3;4-5;7-8;9-10"},{ID:2,
Text:"ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya"},{ID:3,
Text:"Ĩ itĩkai kũinĩra Mwathani rũĩmbo rũerũ! Mũinĩre Mwathani, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. "},{ID:4,
Text:"Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ, mawĩko make ma magegania mũkĩmaganĩre iruka ciothe cia andũ."},{ID:5,
Text:"ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya"},{ID:6,
Text:"Nĩ ũndũ Mwathani nĩ mũnene, na nĩ wa kũgoocwo mũno: we nĩ wa gwĩtigĩrũo gũkĩra ngai ciothe."},{ID:7,
Text:"Thima-rĩ, ngai icio ciothe cia irĩndĩ no indo itarĩ kĩene, ĩndĩ Mwathani nĩwe wombire igũrũ."},{ID:8,
Text:"ICOKIA 
Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya"},{ID:9,
Text:"Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya irĩndĩ, rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e na hinya."},{ID:10,
Text:"Rahai Mwathani nĩ kũgwetaga riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake: ũkai na ihaki, mũgĩtonye nja-inĩ ciake."},{ID:11,
Text:"ICOKIA 
Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya"},{ID:12,
Text:"Tetemekai mwĩ mbere yake, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. Ugai ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ atĩrĩ: "},{ID:13,
Text:"Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; ĩĩ-ni, thĩ nĩ kũrũmio ĩrũmĩtio, ũndũ"},{ID:14,
Text:" ĩtangĩenyenyeka; arĩciragĩra irĩndĩ ciakuo o ũrĩa kwerekereire."},{ID:15,
Text:"ICOKIA 
Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya"},{
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 12:4-11"},{ID:2,
Text:"GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:"},{ID:3,
Text:"Ariũ a Ithe witũ, iheo iria iheanagwo ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, no rĩrĩ, Muoyo mwene cio no ũmwe."},{ID:4,
Text:"  Mĩtungatĩre o nayo nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, na Mwathani mwene yo no ũmwe.  O nayo mĩĩkĩre ya maũndũ nĩ ĩtiganĩte mĩthemba,"},{ID:5,
Text:" ĩndĩ Ngai no ũmwe, ũcio wĩkithagia maũndũ macio mothe thĩinĩ wa andũ  othe. "},{ID:6,
Text:" No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ aheagwo ũndũ wake ũrĩa wonanagia atĩ arĩ na Muoyo nĩ getha "},{ID:7,
Text:"ũndũ ũcio ũgune andũ othe.  Tondũ wa kũheo nĩ Muoyo-rĩ, mũndũ ũmwe agĩaga na ũhoro wa kwaria ũrĩ ũũgĩ; "},{ID:7,
Text:"ũngĩ akagĩa na ũhoro ũrĩ ũmenyi mũkinyanĩru werekanĩrĩire na wa Muoyo  o ro ũcio; nake ũngĩ akaheo wĩtĩkio , "},{ID:8,
Text:"nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o oro ũcio; ũngĩ akaheo ũhoti wa kũhonania mĩrimũ, no ũndũ wa Muoyo o ũcio  ũmwe; ũngĩ nake akaheo ũhoti wa kũringa ciama,"},{ID:9,
Text:" ũngĩ ũrathi, ũngĩ ũhoti wa gũkũũrana mioyo; ũngĩ gũthioma thiomi, na ũngĩ ũtaũri ahote gũtaũra thiomi icio.  No rĩrĩ, "},{ID:10,
Text:"maũndũ macio mothe no wĩra wa Muoyo o ro ũcio ũmwe, akĩgayagĩra andũ o ta ũrĩa ekwenda, o mũndũ mwanya, o mũndũ mwanya."},{ID:11,
Text:"Ciugo cia Mwathani"},{ID:12,
Text:"RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 2:11"},{ID:13,
Text:"	
Alleluya. Alleluya."},{ID:13,
Text:"Yesu nĩ ekire ũguo kũu Kana ya Galilea, akĩambĩrĩria ciama ciake, agĩkĩonania ũnene wake; nao arutwo ake makĩya kũmwĩhoka."},{ID:14,
Text:"Alleluia"},{
Text:"Injiri
JOHANA 2;1  11"},{ID:2,
Text:"Ningi muthenya wagatatu gukigia na kihikanio kundu gwitagwo Kana ya Galili, nake nyina wa Jesu aari ho;"},{ID:3,
Text:" o naJesunakenietiruo, naarutwoake, mathiikihikaniokiu. Nayondibeiyaagakumaigana, nyina wa Jesu akimwira atiri, Matiri na ndibei."},{ID:4,
Text:" Nake Jesu akimwira, Mutu mia uyu, uhoro niu riku witu nawe? Ihinda riakwa ritiri rirakinya. Nyina agikiir andu ngata atiriri, O uria ekumwira, ikaiguo."},{ID:5,
Text:" Na riri kwari ndigithu ithathatu cia mahiga ciaigitwo kuo niundu wamitugo ya Ayahudi yagwitheria,"},{ID:6,
Text:" imwe no guthirira mai ma mutungi uria munene maita meri kana matatu. Nake Jesu akimera atiri, "},{ID:7,
Text:"Iyuria indigithu icio mai. Magigiciiyuria o riita. Agicoka akimera atiri, Riu tahiai, mutwarire mutabania wa iruga."},{ID:8,
Text:" Nao makimutwarira. Mutabania wairuga nake aacama mai macio matuikite ndibei, nandamenye haia yumite [indindungata iria ciatahite mai, "},{ID:9,
Text:"cio nicia menyaga ucio mutabania wairuga agiita muhikania, akimwira atiri, Mundu aambaga kuruta ndibei iria njega;"},{ID:10,
Text:" na andu maarikia kunyua muno, akaruta iria itari njega muno; wee-ri, ukuigite ndibei iria njega ukamiruta riu."},{ID:11,
Text:" Jesu niekire uguo kuu Kana ya Galili, akiambiriria ciama ciake, agikionania unene wake; nao arutwo akemaki yakumwihoka."}],
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 
Isaya. 62:1-5
"},{Guid:"cCDDnWUPQ0W6tx+dIuApEg",Verses:[{
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>HWAINI MBERE YA THIGUKUU YA ICIARIRO</s></f></b>"},{
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Isaia. 62:1-5</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa kũrũĩrĩra Sion, ndigatumia kanua, o na kana ndigithĩrie gũtetera Jerusalem,</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro wakuo wa ũthingu ũkoimbũka ware o ta ũtheri</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o naguo ũhoro wakuo wa kũhonokania woneke o ta tawa ũrĩa wakanaga mũno.  Nacio ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikona ũthingu waku, </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o nao athamaki othe mone riri waku; wee nawe ũcoke gwĩtwo rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ rĩkagwetwo na kanua ka Mwathani.  </s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ ũgatuĩka ta tanji ya ũthaka ũnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani,</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846> na ũhaane ta thũmbĩ ya ũthamaki ĩnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Ngai waku.  Wee nawe-rĩ, ndũgacoka gwĩtwo Mũtirike, </s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o na kana bũrũri waku wĩtwo Mũkiru Ihooru; na rĩrĩ, ũrĩĩtagwo Hefiziba, </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o naguo bũrũri waku wĩtagwo Beula; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ akenagio nĩwe, </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o naguo bũrũri waku ũgatuĩka o ta mũhiki ũrĩa ũhikĩtio.  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa mwanake ahikagia mũirĩtu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ũguo noguo aanake aku magakũhikia,</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846> ningĩ o ta ũrĩa mũhikania ekenagĩra nĩ mũhiki wake-rĩ, o ũguo noguo Ngai waku arĩĩkenagĩra nĩwe.</s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>THABURI 89;3-4,15-16,26,28</s></f></b>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1846>Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Nīī-rī, nindikānīīre na muthurūo wākwa, ndūgatā yākwa Dāudi nī kwīhīta ndīīhītīte </s></f></b>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ngamīrīkīrīa atīrī mbeū yākū ngumītūūrīa īī numū </s></f></b>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o ngīnyā tene na tene, ngīākē gītī gīākū kīa ūnēnē gīkīnyagīrīre njīārwā na njīārwā.</s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>wē arītānāgā na kūrī nīī ta ūū; wēw nīwē awa, nōwē mūrungū wākwa, </s></f></b>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o na ndūmbā yā īhīgā īrīa nyēnē ūhōnōkīō wākwa utūgī wākwa ngūtūrā </s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ndīmūrūmīīrīe kīnyā o tene na tene, 
nakīō kīrīkānīrō gīākū gītūrē kīrī o gīa kwīhōkekā nīwē.</s></f></b>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>gūkēnārī nī kīrīndī kīrīa kīmenyēte rīūgīrīrīo rīrīa rīa gīkēnō;</s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>kīū nīgīthīāgā o na ūtherī wā gīthīīthī gīākū, </s></f></b>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>wēē Jehōvā gītīndāgā gīcānjamūkīte mūthēnyā wōthē nī undū wā rītwā rīū rīākū,</s></f></b>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>na tōndū wā ūthīngu wākū gīgāgītūūgīrīrā.</s></f></b>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Icokia:Nġanīrīa hĩndī cīothe, Mwathani mawega makũ.</s></f></b>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846>Gĩthomo gĩa Keri</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1846>: </s></f></b>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>(Atumwo 13;16-17;22-25)</s></f></b>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Paulo na andũ a thirĩtũ yake magĩkīnya Antiokia nake Paulo agikirugama, na aarikia kumakiria na guoko, akiũgũa atĩrĩ,</s></f></b>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>andu āya a Isiraeli, na inuyui mwītīgagira Ngai tathikirīriai. Ngai wa rurīrī ruru rua Isiraeli </s></f></b>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nīaathurīre maīthe maītu agītūgīrīa andũ a rurīrī ruru </s></f></b>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>hīndī īrīa maātūīre buburī wa Misiri agicoka akīmoīmīa kuo na guoko gwake kwīna uhoti.</s></f></b>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>na aarikia kumwēheria, agīūkīrīa Daudi atūīke muthamaki wāo; </s></f></b>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nīwē Ngai oimburīre uhōrō wake akiūgā atĩrĩ, Ninyonete Daudi, </s></f></b>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>mūrū wa Jesīī, arī mundu urīa ngōrō yākwā yendīre o ngōga, </s></f></b>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>urīa urīkāga maundū mārīa mothe ndīrīendāga mekwo. </s></f></b>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, Ngai nīaarehīthīrīe Āīsirāelī muhonōkīa oīmīte rucīārō-īnī rūa mundu ūcīo, </s></f></b>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>o tā urīa erānīīre, nake nīwē Jesū.</s></f></b>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Ūcīo atānokarī, Johānā nīāmbīrīe kuhunjīrīa andũ ōthe a Isiraeli uhōrō wa atī andũ mērīre gūkū thīrī, </s></f></b>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>akiūgā atĩrĩ, mugūkīgererīa atī nīī ndī ū?</s></f></b>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Nīī tī nīī urīa ugūkā. Nō atīrī, nīharī ugūkā thūta wākwa, urīa nīī itāīgaīne wa kuohorā mikwā yā iratū cīāke.</s></f></b>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcīo ciūgō cīa Mwathānī.</s></f></b>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846>Rwĩmbō rwa injĩlĩ</s></f></u></b>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Āllelūia, āllelūia</s></f></b>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Rūcīu urū wa thĩ ūgāthīra, na ūthāmākī wa thĩ agāthānā īgūrū rīītu.</s></f></b>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Āllelūia</s></f></b>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>INJILI: </s></f></b>"},{ID:30},{ID:31,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846>LONG FORM
</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1846>(Mathayo 1: 1-25)</s></f></b>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Ibuku riri nirio riandikitwo Ühoro wa rūciaro rūria Jesu Kristo,</s></f></b>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>mūrŭ wa Daudi, mūrũ wa Iburahımu, oimire.
Iburahimu niwe waciarire Isaaka,</s></f></b>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Isaaka agiciara Jakubu; nake
Jakubu agiciara Juda o na ariūũ a ithe; </s></f></b>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Juda agiciara Perezu na Zera,
na nyina wao aari Tamaru; </s></f></b>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Perezu agiciara Hezironi; nake Hezi-roni agīciara Ramu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Ramu agīciara Aminadabu; nake Aminadabu
agiciara Nahashonı ; nake Nahashoni agiciara Salimoni; </s></f></b>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Salimoni agiciara Boazu, na nyina aari Rahabu; nake Boazu agiciara Obedi, na nyina aari Ruthu; </s></f></b>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>näke Obedi agiciara Jesii; nake Jesii agīciara Daudi,
üria wari mūthamaki.</s></f></b>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Nake Daudi agiciara Solomoni, na nyina aari mūtumia üria wari o mbere wa Uria; ' </s></f></b>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Solomoni agiciara Rehoboamu; nake Rehoboamu agi-ciara Abija; </s></f></b>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Abija agiciara Asa; nake Asa agiciara Jehoshafatu;
nake Jehoshafatu agiciara Joramu;</s></f></b>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Joramu agīciara Uzia; nake Uzia agiciara Jothamu; nake Jothamu agiciara Ahazu; </s></f></b>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Ahazu agiciara Hezekia; nake Hezekia agiciara Manase; </s></f></b>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Manase agīciara Amoni; nake Amoni agiciara Josia; </s></f></b>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Josia agiciara Jekonia na ariû a ithe,
hindi iria andū maatahirūo magitwarūo Babuloni.</s></f></b>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>O na andū maąrīkia gūtahwo magītwarūo kūu Babuloni, Jekonia</s></f></b>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ūcio agiciara Shealitieli; nake Shealitieli agiciara Zerubabeli; </s></f></b>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Zerubabeli agiciara Abihudu; nake Abihudu agiciara Eliakimi; </s></f></b>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Eliakimi agīciara Azoro; nake Azoro agiciara Zadoku, </s></f></b>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Zadoku agiciara Akimi, nake Akimi agiciara Eliudu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Eliudu agiciara Eleazaru; nake Eleazaru agiciara Mathani;</s></f></b>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>nake Mathani agiciara Jakubu; nake Jakubu agiciara Jusufu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>uria wari muthuri wa mariamu, uria waciarire Jesu, uria witagwo Kristo</s></f></b>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Noguo njiaro ciothe gwata Iburahimu kinya Daudi, ni ikūmi na  inya;</s></f></b>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846> 
ningi gwata Daudi kinya andũ maatahwo magītwarūo Babiloni,</s></f></b>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ni njiaro ikūmi na inya; ria ningi gwata andû maatahwo magitwarüo kūu</s></f></b>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Babiloni, kinya Kristo, ni njiaro ikümi na inya.</s></f></b>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Ningi gwata Daudi kinya andu maatahwo magitwaro Babiloni, ni njiaro ikumi na inya;</s></f></b>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>na ningi gwata andu maatahwo magitwaro
kuu Babiloni, kinya Kristo, ni njiaro ikumi na inya</s></f></b>"},{ID:59},{ID:60,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846>SHORT FORM</s></f></u></b>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Riu-ri, gūcıarūo kwa Jesu Krısto gwatarii ūu' nyina Mariamu orio ni Jusufu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>matanonana, akionwo ar</s></f></b><b><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f></b><b><fArial Black><s1846> na ihu rĩa Roho Mãtheru. </s></f></b>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Nake mūthuriwe Jusufu, tondū aari mũndū mūthingu, na ndendaga gūcono-rithia</s></f></b>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846> 
müiritu ücio küri andű, akienda atigane nake na hitho.Na hindi Iria eciragia maündū macio, </s></f></b>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>atiriri, müraika wa Mwathanı akimuumirira kiroto-ini, akimwira atiri, Jusufu, mũrũ wa Daudi, </s></f></b>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ndūgetigire kühikia Mariamu atuike mūtumia waku, tondū-ri, </s></f></b>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ihu riu ari narīo ni ria Roho Mütheru. Nake niagaciara kahii, nako niügagatua JESU, </s></f></b>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>ni ündũ niwe ükahonokia andū ake mehia-ini mao. </s></f></b>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Na riri, maūndū macio mekirūo ni getha ciugo iria cioigirüo ni Mwathari na kanua ka műnabii ikinye, riria oigire atiri:</s></f></b>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Onei, müiritu niakagīa ihu, na aciare kalhil, Nako gatuwo Imanueli;</s></f></b>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>üguo naguo ügitaürűo, nĩ kuuga, Ngai hamwe na ithui. </s></f></b>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>Nake Jusufu agiükira toro, agīika o ta üria müraika wa Mwathani aamwathire, akihikia </s></f></b>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>mütumia wake, kinya na ndaigana kümūmenya aaciara kahii; agigatua Yesu </s></f></b>"}],
Text:"HWAINI MBERE YA THIGUKUU YA ICIARIRO MWAKA A,B"},{Guid:"MrdPXs/HO0av9S1CzJ6k9w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                         Atũmwo 13:14, 43-52</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ macio, Paul  na Barnaba, maarĩkia gũtuĩkanĩria bũrũri ũcio moimĩte Perje, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>magĩkinya Antiokia itũũra rĩa bũrũri wa Pisidia.  Na magĩtonya thinagoga mũthenya wa thabatũ, magĩikara thĩ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>  Na rĩrĩa kũu thinagoga-inĩ gwaitĩkire kũharaganio-rĩ, andũ aingĩ, Ayahudi o na andũ meamũrĩire Ngai a thiritũ ya arĩa megarũrĩte magatuĩka Ayahudi,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> makĩrũmĩrĩra Paul na Barnaba: nao atũmwo acio makĩmaarĩria, makĩmahatĩrĩria atĩ matũre marũmĩte Wega-inĩ wa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Naguo mũthenya  ũyũ ũngĩ wa thabatũ gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ ta andũ othe a itũũra makĩũngana maigue Ũhoro wa Ngai. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩa Ayahudi monire kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa kĩingĩ kĩonganĩte, makĩigua ũiru mũno, magĩkararia  maũndũ marĩa maaragio nĩ Paul,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmũruma.  Nao Paul na Barnaba magĩitĩka kwaria na ũcamba, makĩmera atĩrĩ: Nĩ kwarĩ bata atĩ Ũhoro wa Ngai wambe wario kũrĩ inyuĩ.  No rĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>kuona atĩ nĩ mwaũrega kũna, mwaũte, mwatua atĩ mũtiagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũheo muoyo wa tene na tene, rĩu-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> tũkũgarũrũkĩra andũ arĩa a Ndũrĩrĩ.  Nĩ gũkorũo ũguo nĩguo Mwathani atwathĩte twĩke, akoiga atĩrĩ: Nĩ ngũigĩte Wee ũtuĩke ũtheri wa gũtheria andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ũtuĩke wa gũkinyia ũhoro wa kũhonokania o ituri-inĩ ciothe cia thĩ.  Nao andũ arĩa mataarĩ Ayahudi maaigua ũhoro ũcio,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> magĩkena, magĩgĩkumia ũhoro wa Ngai: nao arĩa othe maathĩrĩirio kuona muoyo wa tene na tene magĩitĩkia.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Naguo Ũhoro wa Mwathani ũgĩkĩhunja bũrũri ũcio wothe.  No rĩrĩ, Ayahundi makĩhatĩrĩria atumia arĩa meamũrĩire Ngai,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> o arĩa maarĩ igweta, o na anene a itũũra, makĩrutithia ngũĩ nĩguo Paul na Barnaba manyarirũo,</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmaingata na hinya moime ndere-inĩ ciao.  No-o magĩthukia magũrũ mao rũkũngũ rũitĩke, kũmenyũo atĩ nĩ maatigana nao, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>magĩthiĩ Ikonio.  Nao arutwo magĩkena o gũkena, na makĩiyũrũo nĩ Muoyo Mũtheru</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"b21BQWEMyEeN4Ee6M9UXVg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                           Ũũgĩ 7:7-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨŨGĨ: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ndahoire na ngĩheo ũmenyi; nĩ ndaririe na hinya, na ngĩheo muoyo wa Ũũgĩ.  Ndamũtuire wa goro kũrĩ mũthĩgi na itĩ cia ũthamaki; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ũtonga ũgerekanĩtio nake nĩ wa tũhũ.  Gũtirĩ ihiga o na rĩrĩkũ rĩa goro ndamũgerekanirie narĩo nĩ amu thahabu</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> yothe ĩgerekanĩtio nake no ta kĩhumbu kĩa mũthanga, na ningĩ mbere yake mbeca ihuana ta ndoro.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ndamwendete kũrũga ũgima wa mwĩrĩ kama ũthaka, ngĩmũhuanania na ũtheri, tondũ mũrũri wake ndũkomaga. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndatwaranire nake nĩ ndonire indo ciothe njega, na ũtonga ũrĩa woimaga njara-inĩ ciake ndũngĩtarĩka.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"AH1UfoyVjkKVqH9AANgEuw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                              Atumwo 10:34,37-43</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATUMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Petro agĩitĩka kwaria akiuga atĩrĩ: Inyuĩ nĩmũĩ, naguo nĩguo wahunjanĩirio Judea guothe wambĩrĩirio</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o Galilea thutha wa rĩrĩa John aaheanire ũhoro wa atĩ andũ mabatithio.  Naguo nĩ wa Yesu wa Nazareth, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ũrĩa Ngai aamũitĩrĩirie Muoyo mũtheru o na hinya; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nake agĩĩcanga agĩĩkaga maũndũ mega na akĩhonagia andũ arĩa othe matũire manyariragwo nĩ mũcukani:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo Ngai aarĩ hamwe nake.  Na ithuĩ-rĩ, tũrĩ aira a maũndũ macio mothe ekire kũu bũrũri wa Ayahudi, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o na Jerusalemu.  Nake oragirũo nĩ andũ na kũmũcuuria mũtĩ igũrũ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩwe Ngai aariũkirie mũthenya wa gatatũ, agĩĩtĩkĩra atĩ acoke kuoneka, no ti kuonwo nĩ andũ othe, tiga o aira arĩa maathurirũo o mbere nĩ Ngai,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nao nĩo ithuĩ, o ithuĩ arĩa twarĩaga na tũkanyuaga hamwe nake, arĩĩkia kũriũka akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Na gũtwatha nĩ aatwathire atĩ tũhunjagĩrie andũ, na tuumbũrage atĩ we nĩwe watuirũo nĩ Ngai Mũtui-cira wa andũ arĩa marĩ muoyo na wa arĩa makuĩte. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nao irori ciothe nĩwe maheanagĩra ũira, makoimbũra atĩ nĩũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũgakorũo amwĩhokete nĩ akoherũo mehia make.
 </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"xsZ0Fg+UdUujN6V4KWNZoA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Isa. 63:16-17;64:1,4-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:
	
Wee Mwathani, nĩwe Ithe witũ; nario rĩĩtwa rĩaku nĩrĩrĩ, nĩ mũkũũri witũ kuuma tene na tene.  </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, wee Mwathani, nĩkĩ gĩtũmaga ũtũhĩtithie njĩra ciaku, na ũkomia ngoro ciitũ itige gũgwĩtigĩra?</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Garũrũka nĩ ũndũ wa ndungata ciaku, o mĩhĩrĩga ĩno ĩtuĩtwo ũgai waku.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, na arĩ korũo waikara harĩ cio watarũranga matu, nĩguo ũikũrũke gũkũ thĩ, nĩgetha ithuuri ithingithe waikara harĩ cio.  </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa wekire maũndũ ma kũmakania tũtamatanyĩte-rĩ, nĩguo waikũrũkire gũkũ thĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> nacio ithuri igĩthingitha nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa wĩ harĩ cio. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo kuuma tene o tene, andũ matirĩ maaigua maũndũ ta macio, na gũtirĩ gũtũ kũrĩ kwaigua ũguo, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o na kana riitho rĩkĩĩonera Ngai ũhaana tawe, wee ũgunaga andũ arĩa maikaraga magũcũthĩrĩirie. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Wee ũkoragia ũtugi waku mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa wĩkaga maũndũ ma ũthingu akenete, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>o arĩa maririkanaga kũhingia maathani maku.  Atĩrĩrĩ, wee nĩ warakarĩte, na ithuĩ tũgĩkirĩrĩria kwĩhia,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> tũgĩgĩikara mehia-inĩ maitũ ihinda iraya; na githĩ nĩ tũgakĩhonokio?</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũkorũo ithuothe nĩ tũtuĩkĩte o ta mũndũ wĩ thahu, o naguo ũthingu witũ wothe ũtariĩ o ta nguo thũku mũno;</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> na ithuĩ ithuothe tũrahoha o ta ithangũ, namo mahĩtia maitũ magatũhuruta o ta ũrĩa rũhuho rũhurutaga maragara.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>  Na gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe ũkayagĩra rĩĩtwa rĩaku, o na kana ũkwĩhĩka anyitane nawe;</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo wee nĩ ũtũhithĩte ũthiũ waku, na ũgatũng’ũria nĩ ũndũ wa mahĩtia maitũ.  </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, wee Mwathani, nĩwe Ithe witũ; ithuĩ twĩ rĩũmba, nawe nĩwe mũtũũmbi, na ithuothe tũrĩ wĩra wa moko maku.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"IZrnSI8ETkC/5Zpqwwgxgg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                         Atũmwo 14:21-27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Paul na Barnaba magĩcoka Listria, Ikonio na Antiokia, makĩũmagĩrĩria arutwo ngoro,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmataaraga atĩ marũmagie  wega morutani marĩa ma Wĩtĩkio,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> makĩmaririkania atĩ ũthamaki wa Ngai ndũngĩtonyeka nĩ ithuĩ tiga o twambire kuona mathĩna maingĩ. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Na maarĩkia kũmathurĩra andũ a gũtuĩka athuri makanitha-inĩ mothe, na kũhoya Ngai makĩĩgiragia kũrĩa irio, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>makĩmatigĩra Mwathani o we mehokete.  Magĩcoka magĩtuĩkanĩria bũrũri wa Pisidia, magĩkinya Panfilia. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Na maarĩkia kũheana Ũhoro wa Ngai kũu Perje, magĩtherera magĩkinya Atalia; makiuma kuo, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>magĩcoka Antiokia mahaicĩte marikabu.  Kũu nĩkuo moimĩte, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>maarĩkia kũhoerũo Ngai atĩ maheo Wega wake wa kũmahotithia kũruta wĩra o ro ũcio rĩu maarĩkĩtie.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Na maakinya kuo, makĩũngania andũ a kanitha, makĩmahe  ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa mothe Ngai  ekĩte hamwe nao,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o na ũrĩa aahingũrĩire andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ mũrango nĩguo maũtonyere, na matuĩke a gwĩtĩkia.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"EE3zAGLErkKAWe/LJJWi1Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             	         Joshua  5: 9,10-12</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA JOSHUA:
 
Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Mwathani akĩĩra Joshua atĩrĩ: Ũmũthĩ nĩguo ndeheria rũmena rũa Misri ruume kũrĩ inyuĩ. </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> Nacio ciana cia Israeli igĩkĩamba hema ciacio  hau Galgala; nacio ikĩrĩa gĩathĩ kĩa Paska Mũthenya wa ikũmi na ĩna wa mweri ũcio, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o hwai-inĩ, irĩ kũu werũ-inĩ ũcio wa Jeriko.  Naguo mũthenya o ro ũcio wa kerĩ thutha wa Paska ikĩrĩa irio iria ciarĩ </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>o kũu mĩgũnda-inĩ ya bũrũri  ũcio, ithondeketwo igatuwo mũgate ũtarĩ  mũimbie, o na ngano hĩhie.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Naguo mũthenya ũyũ ũngĩ wa kerĩ thutha  wa mũthĩ ũcio ciarĩire irio ciarĩ kũu, mana makĩroka kwaga, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nacio ciana cia Israeli itiigana gũcoka  kuona mana rĩngĩ; na rĩrĩ, ciarĩire maciaro ma bũrũri ũcio wa Kanaan mwaka ũcio.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"gYtiHJtdHUWdDyCVL92VGQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				         Kũguũrĩrio 11:19; 12: 1-6a. 10ab</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nayo hekarũ ya Ngai ĩkĩhingũrũo, ĩrĩa ĩrĩ Igũrũ; na kũu hekarũ yake thĩinĩ gũkĩoneka  ithandũkũ rĩrĩa rĩa kĩrĩkanĩro gĩake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ gũkĩĩoneka ũrirũ mũnene Igũrũ; na nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja wĩhumbĩte riũa, na akinyĩte mweri na magũrũ make, na akagĩa na thũmbĩ mũtwe ya njata ikũmi na igĩrĩ; </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na aarĩ na ihu, na nĩ gũkaya aakayaga akĩrũmagwo akĩrĩwo nĩ ruo rũa kwenda gũciara.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Na gũgĩcoka gũkĩoneka ũrirũ ũngĩ igũrũ, na nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ ndamathia nene, ndune mũno, ĩĩ na mĩtwe mũgwanja na hĩa ikũmi, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na mĩtwe  yayo igũrũ ĩkagĩa na managĩ mũgwanja ma ũnene.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nakĩo gĩthita kĩayo gĩakururĩtie njata cia igũrũ gĩcunjĩ gĩa ithatũ, gĩgĩcirekania thĩ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Nayo ndamathia ĩo ĩkĩrũgama mbere ya mũndũ-wa-nja ũcio wakiriĩ gũciara, nĩguo aaciara, ĩrĩe mwana wake.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Nake agĩciara mwana wa kahĩĩ, ũrĩa ũkariyĩraga ndũrĩrĩ ciothe na rũthanju  rũa kĩgera;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na mwana ũcio wake akĩhurio na igũrũ agĩkinyio kwĩ Ngai, o gĩtĩ-inĩ gĩake gĩa ũthamaki. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nake mũndũ-wa-nja akĩũra werũ-inĩ, kũndũ athondekeirũo nĩ Ngai. Na nĩ ndaiguire mũgambo mũnene Igũrũ, akiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩu nĩ gũkinyu kĩhonokanio, na ũhoti, na ũthamaki wa Ngai witũ, o naguo wathani wa Kristũ wake. </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE"},{Guid:"xUTRDcjJsUK33SAgEuNfZQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Gīthomo kīa mbere							Isaiah 52: 7-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Gūthoma kuma ibuku rīa Mūrathi Isaiah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Küu irīīma-inī igūrü-rī, kaï magürū ma mündü ürīa ūrarehe ühoro mwega  nīmaagīrīire-ī,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o ücio ürahunjīria ūhoro wa thayū, na akarehe ühoro mwega wa maündū maagīrīru,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o na akahunjanīria ühoro wa kūhonokanio, o we ūrīa ūreera Zayuni atīrī, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai waku nīwe ürathamaka! Ta igua Mūgambo wa arangīri aku!Nīmaühaicītie na igūrü na mekūina me hamwe;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nī ündū nīmekuonana nake üthiü kwa üthiü hīndī îrīa Jehova egūcka Zayuni.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Atīrīrī inyuī kūndū kwanangīku kwa Jerusalem, ītīkaniai na gükena mūine hamwe, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nī gükorwo Jehova nīahoreretie andū ake na agaküüra Jerusalem. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Jehova  Nīaguürīirie ndürīrī ciothe guoko gwake gütheru, ikuone na maitho macio;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nacio ituri ciothe cia thī nī irīona ühonokanio wa Ngai witü.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Gīthomo kīa mbere	"},{Guid:"rSN3g5aYQkGt11isTOamug",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Gīthomo kīa mbere							Isaiah 52: 7-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Gūthoma kuma ibuku rīa Mūrathi Isaiah </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Küu irīīma-inī igūrü-rī, kaï magürū ma mündü ürīa ūrarehe ühoro mwega  nīmaagīrīire-ī, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o ücio ürahunjīria ūhoro wa thayū, na akarehe ühoro mwega wa maündū maagīrīru,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o na akahunjanīria ühoro wa kūhonokanio, o we ūrīa ūreera Zayuni atīrī, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai waku nīwe ürathamaka! Ta igua Mūgambo wa arangīri aku!Nīmaühaicītie na igūrü na mekūina me hamwe;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nī ündū nīmekuonana nake üthiü kwa üthiü hīndī îrīa Jehova egūcka Zayuni.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Atīrīrī inyuī kūndū kwanangīku kwa Jerusalem, ītīkaniai na gükena mūine hamwe,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nī gükorwo Jehova nīahoreretie andū ake na agaküüra Jerusalem. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Jehova  Nīaguürīirie ndürīrī ciothe guoko gwake gütheru, ikuone na maitho macio;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> nacio ituri ciothe cia thī nī irīona ühonokanio wa Ngai witü.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Gīthomo kīa mbere	"},{Guid:"qdE0figB/ESraNRNU4NGaQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					           Nehemia 8:2-4a, 5-6,8-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA NEHEMIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ macio, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, aatwarire ibuku rĩu rĩa watho harĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩu kĩa andũ acio monganĩte, arũme o na andũ-a-nja,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> o na andũ othe arĩa maahotaga kũigua gĩtũmi kĩa watho ũcio. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩthoma mohoro marĩa maarĩ thĩinĩ warĩo arĩ o handũ hau haariĩ haarĩ mbere ya Kĩhingo kĩu kĩa Maĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> kuuma o rũcinĩ gwakĩa nginya a mĩaraho, andũ acio othe, arũme na andũ-a-nja, o na andũ arĩa othe maahotaga kũigua gĩtũmi kĩamo, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>marĩ ho.  Nao andũ acio othe magĩtega matũ mao maigue ũhoro wa ibuku  rĩu rĩa watho.  Nake Esra, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio mwandĩki-marũa, akĩrũgama handũ hokĩrĩirie haakĩtwo na mĩtĩ nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro ũcio kĩũmbe.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Esra agĩkũnjũra ibuku rĩu andũ othe makĩonaga; nĩ ũndũ aarũgamĩte handũ igũrũ agatũũgĩra gũkĩra andũ arĩa angĩ othe; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aarĩkũnjũrire, andũ othe makĩrũgama; nake Esra akĩgooca Mwathani, Ngai ũrĩa Mũnene. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Nao andũ othe magĩcokia atĩrĩ: Amen, Amen, moete moko mao na igũrũ; nao makĩinamia mĩtwe yao, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>makĩhoya Mwathani maturumithĩtie mothiũ  mao thĩ.  Nao magĩthoma  ciugo iria cia watho ũcio wa Ngai ciarĩ ibuku-inĩ rĩu,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> magĩcitaũranĩra na mũgambo mũnene, nĩguo andũ mamenye wega gĩtũmi  gĩacio.  Nake Nehemia, barũthi,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> na Esra, mũthĩnjĩri Ngai ũrĩa mwandĩki-marũa, o na Alawii arĩa maarutaga andũ maũndũ, makĩĩra andũ othe atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Mũthenya wa ũmũthĩ nĩ mwamũrĩre Mwathani Ngai  wanyu; menyai mũgĩe na kĩeha, o na kana mũrĩre. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo andũ othe nĩ maarĩrire rĩrĩa maaiguire ciugo icio cia watho wa Ngai.  Nake agĩkĩmera atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> Wĩthiĩrei mukarĩe nyama noru, na mũkanyue indo irĩ mũrĩo, o nake mũndũ ũrĩa ũtarĩ kĩndũ aigĩirũo mũmũgaĩre rũgai rũake;</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo mũthenya wa ũmũthĩ nĩ mwamũrĩre Mwathani  witũ; o na ningĩ tigai kũigua ũũru, nĩ gũkenera Mwathani nĩkuo hinya wanyu.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"DNaTp0s/KUKHYMDOfiktXg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Isaia  45:1, 4-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani erire mũndũ wake, nĩwe Cyrus: Atĩrĩrĩ, niĩ nyitĩtie guoko gwake nĩguo ndoorie ndũrĩrĩ  iria irĩ mbere yake.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Niĩ nĩ kũohora ngohora ndoho njohero-inĩ cia athamaki nĩ getha mamũhingũragĩre mĩrango mbere yake, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>na ndagakora ihingo cia matũũra mao ihingĩtwo. Nĩ gũkorũo ngwĩtĩte  ngĩkũgwetaga  rĩĩtwa nĩ ũndũ wa Jacobu ndungata yakwa, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>o na Israeli mũndũ wakwa ũrĩa mũthure, o na ngagũtua rĩĩtwa rĩĩ igweta, o na harĩa ũtanjũĩ.  Niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na gũtirĩ ũngĩ o na ũrĩkũ; thengia o niĩ-rĩ, hatirĩ Ngai ũngĩ.  Nĩ niĩ ngakuoha ndoho o na harĩa ũtanjũĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ũhoro ũmenyũo kuuma irathĩro-inĩ rĩa riũa, o na kuuma ithũĩro-inĩ rĩarĩo, atĩ gũtirĩ ũngĩ thengia o niĩ nyiki; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani, na gũtirĩ ũngĩ o na ũrĩkũ.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"Q2w5S/6YG0aOtT9twRpfrg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird1.JPG"}},
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                          Baruk 5:1-9 </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI BARUK: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Jerusalem, ruta nguo yaku ya runo na thĩĩna, ĩkĩra ũthaka wa ũkumio wa Ngai  hĩndĩ ciothe,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> wĩhumbe gĩthii gĩa kwĩhoka Ngai, ĩkĩra kĩraũni kĩa ũkumio wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ mũtwe-inĩ waku: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ Ngai nĩ ekwonania ũnene waku kũrĩ ndũrĩrĩ  ciothe iria irĩ ruungu rũa matu,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa Ngai egũkũhe hĩndĩ ciothe nĩ “Thayũ na njĩra ya wĩhokeku, na gĩtĩo na njĩra ya ũhoreri”</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ũkĩra Jerusalem, rũgama na ũrũrie maitho maku mwena wa irathĩro:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> cũthĩrĩria ciana ciaku icokanĩrĩire ciumĩte mwena wa irathĩro na ithũĩro na njĩra ya watho wa “ũrĩa Mũthure” ikenete atĩ Ngai nĩ aciririkana.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ona gũtuĩka ciagũtigire na magũrũ, itongoretio nĩ thũ, rĩu Ngai nĩ egũcicokia kũrĩ we ihana ta ihĩĩ cia anene igĩcokio</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> kwao na ũkumio.  Tondũ Ngai nĩ athanĩte irĩma ciothe ndaihu ciaraganio, o na tũrĩma twothe tũrĩa tũtũraga hĩndĩ ciothe,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na mĩkuri yothe ĩiyũrio nĩ guo thĩ yothe ĩiganane nĩguo Israeli ahote gũthiĩ wega arĩ ruungu rũa ũkumio wa Ngai.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Na mĩtitũ oro hamwe na mũtĩ oro wothe mũnungi wega nĩ ũkaheane  kĩruru nĩ ũndũ wa Israeli wa watho wa Ngai; </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>tondũ Ngai nĩ agatongoria Israeli na ũkeni na ũtheri wa ũkumio wake hamwe na tha ciake na wĩhokeku.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"UxWrE3kJOkSOOVfI5zEK/w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             	         Isaia 43:16-21</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MURATHI ISAIA: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: O we ũrĩa ũtemaga njĩra irĩa-inĩ, o na agatema gacĩra kũndũ kũrĩa kũrĩ maaĩ me hinya,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na akoimagarithia ngari cia ita, o na mbarathi, o na mbũtũ cia ita hamwe  na anene a cio, ekuuga ũũ: </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩ! Magakoma othe hamwe, na maticoke kwarahoka; nĩ macingimanĩtio makahora ta rũtambĩ rũa ũguta.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> No rĩrĩ, tigai kũririkana maũndũ marĩa mahĩtũkĩte, o na kana mwĩcũranie maũndũ ma tene.  Atĩrĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ngwĩka ũndũ ũngĩ mwerũ, naguo ũgũkunũka o ro rĩu; githĩ mũtirĩkĩũmenya? Ũrĩa ngwĩka nĩguo ũũ, atĩ nĩ ngatema njĩra werũ-inĩ, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>o naguo rũng’ũrĩ-inĩ ndũme kũgĩe na njũĩ. Nyamũ cia gĩthaka ta mbwe, na nyaga, nĩ ikanjĩkĩrĩra,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ gũkorũo kũu werũ-inĩ nĩ ngatũma kũgĩe na maaĩ, o na ndũme o kũu rũng’ũrĩ-inĩ kũgĩe na njũĩ, nĩ getha andũ akwa manyuage maaĩ kuo, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o andũ arĩa akwa  athure; nao nĩo andũ arĩa ndeyũmbĩire, nĩ getha maheanage ũhoro wa ũrĩa njagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũkumagio. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"RTVojwU30kC1543AcmhtfA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                      1 Athamaki 19:4-8</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATHAMAKI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Elia agĩthiĩ rũgendo rũa mũthenya mũgima arorete werũ-inĩ, agĩikara thĩ gĩtina-inĩ kĩa mwethia;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nake akĩĩhoera atĩ akue, agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Rĩu nĩ njiganĩtie; wee Mwathani, nduta  muoyo,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ  ũndũ ti niĩ mwega gũkĩra aa baba.  Agĩgĩkoma thĩ toro hau mwethia-inĩ. Gũgĩtuĩka atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> atĩ akĩhutio nĩ mũraika, akĩĩrũo ũũ: Arahũka ũrĩe irio.  Nake agĩgĩcũthĩrĩria, na atĩrĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mũtwe wake hagĩkorũo he mũgate ũhĩhĩirio makara igũrũ, o na mbũthũ ya maaĩ. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nake agĩkĩrĩa o na akĩnyua; agĩcoka agĩkoma o rĩngĩ.  Ningĩ mũraika wa Mwathani agĩthiĩ harĩ we rĩngĩ, hĩndĩ ya kerĩ; akĩmũhutia, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>akiuga atĩrĩ: Arahũka ũrĩe irio; nĩ gũkorũo rũgendo rũrĩa ũgũthiĩ nĩ rũgũkũnenehera mũno.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Agĩkĩarahũka, akĩrĩa, o na akĩnyua: nake agĩgĩthiĩ na hinya wa irio icio aarĩire matukũ mĩrongo ĩna, mũthenya  na ũtukũ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>agĩgĩkinya kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Ngai kĩrĩa gĩĩtagwo Horeb.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"7DPJ+aBVikO08gwfOL4n7g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				          Gũcokerithia Maathani 18:15-20</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Musa agĩgĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ na akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai waku nĩ egũgũũkĩrĩria mũnabii o ta niĩ, oime thĩinĩ waku, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>wa ariũ a thoguo; ũcio nĩwe mũrĩiguaga; nĩ getha gũkoneka maũndũ maringaine na marĩa mwetirie Mwathani Ngai waku, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>mũthenya ũrĩa mwacemanĩtie o kũrĩa Horeb, mũkiuga atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Reke ndige gũcoka kũigua mũgambo wa mwathani Ngai wakwa, kana njoke kuona mwaki ũyũ mũnene ũũ rĩngĩ o na rĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ getha ndigakue.  Nake Mwathani agĩkĩnjĩra atĩrĩ: Ndeto icio maaria, nĩ  moiga wega. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ngamokĩrĩria mũnabii oime  thĩinĩ wa ariũ a ithe wao, o tawe, na nĩ ngekĩra ciugo ciakwa kanua gake, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nake aarie nao maũndũ mothe marĩa ngamwatha.  Na nĩ gũgakinya atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>atĩ mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũtakaigua ũhoro wakwa ũrĩa akaaria rĩĩtwa-inĩ rĩakwa-rĩ, ũcio nĩwe ngoria ũhoro ũcio.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  No rĩrĩ, mũnabii ũrĩa  ũkaaria kiugo na mwĩgerero akĩgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, kĩrĩa itamwathĩte aarie ũhoro wakĩo,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> kana ũrĩa ũkaaria ũhoro akĩgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩa Ngai ĩngĩ-rĩ, no mũhaka mũnabii ũcio akue.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"45x/iDDsdkqq4fIT8eHoHA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                      Thama  16:2-4,12-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, nakĩo kĩrĩndĩ kĩu gĩothe gĩa ciana cia Israeli gĩgĩteteria  Musa na Haron kũu werũ-inĩ;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nacio ciana cia Israeli ikĩmera atĩrĩ: Na arĩ korũo nĩ kũũragwo tworagĩirũo na guoko kwa Mwathani oro kũu bũrũri wa Misri, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twaikaraga tũkuhĩhĩirio nĩ nyũngũ cia nyama, o na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twarĩaga mũgate o nginya tũkahũna! Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, mwatũrutire kũu,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> mũgĩtũrehe werũ-inĩ ũyũ, mũũrage kĩrĩndĩ gĩkĩ gĩothe na ng’aragu.  Hĩndĩ ĩo Mwathani agĩkĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ngũmuurĩria irio ciume igũrũ o ta mbura; nao andũ nĩ makoimagara mũthenya o mũthenya makonganie cia kũmaigania,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo ndĩmagerie kana nĩ marĩthiaga marũmĩrĩire watho wakwa, kana aca.
Nĩ njiguĩte ũrĩa ciana cia Israeli itetete. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Aria nacio ũciĩre atĩrĩ: Hwaĩ-inĩ mũrĩrĩaga nyama, na rũcinĩ mũrĩhũnagio nĩ mũgate; na nĩ mũkũmenya atĩ niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani Ngai wanyu. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ hwaĩ-inĩ wakinya, hagoka tũmakia-arũme; natuo tũkaiyũra handũ hau maambĩte hema ciao;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na rũcinĩ-rĩ, ime rĩkaroka kũgĩa handũ hau mambĩte hema ciao, rĩkaharigicĩria.  Na rĩrĩ, ime rĩu rĩaitĩka, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>kũndũ jũu werũ-inĩ guothe gũkaiyũra tũnyamũ tũthiũrũrĩ, tũnyihĩte o ta ũrĩa ime rĩikaraga rĩĩ thĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa rĩamatio nĩ mbaa. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Na rĩrĩa ciana cia Israeli cionire tũnyamũ tũu, ikĩũrania o mũndũ na mũndũ atĩrĩ: Ĩ nĩ kĩ gĩkĩ? </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ itiamenyaga kĩrĩa kĩo.  Nake Musa agĩciĩra atĩrĩ:Nĩ irio iria Mwathani amũheete cia kũrĩa.  </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"IMKQS1D6N0OUyYP93WmdZg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			               1 Samueli 26:2,7-9,12-13,22-23</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MBERE RIA SAMUELI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ-inĩ macio, Saulo agĩgĩũkĩra, agĩikũrũka kũu werũ-inĩ wa Zifu arĩ na Aisraeli ngiri ithatũ athure,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> magacarie Davide kuo.  Tondũ ũcio Davide na Abisai magĩgĩkinya harĩ andũ a Saulo ũtukũ; na atĩrĩrĩ:  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Saulo agĩkorũo akomete handũ hau harigicĩrie na ngari, narĩo itimũ rĩake rĩkahandwo  mũtwe-inĩ wake; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nake Abner, na andũ arĩa angĩ, magakoma mamũrigicĩirie na mĩena yothe.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Abisai agĩkĩĩra Davide atĩrĩ: Ngai nĩ arekereirie thũ yaku akamĩneana guoko-inĩ gwaku ũmũthĩ;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> tondũ ũcio, ta reka ndĩmĩthece na itimũ rĩrĩ, ndĩmĩthecethanie na thĩ o itheca rĩmwe, nandimĩtheca rĩa kerĩ.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Davide agĩkĩĩra Abisai atĩrĩ: Menya ũmũũrage; no ũndũ-rĩ, nũ ũngĩkĩhota gũtambũrũkia guoko okĩrĩre mũitĩrĩrio maguta wa Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>na onwo ta atehĩtie? 
Davide agĩgĩcokia akiuga ũũ: Itimũ nĩ wa rĩrĩ, mũthamaki ũyũ; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>mũndũ ũmwe wa aanake acio nĩ aringe arĩiyĩre.  Mwathani nĩwe ũrĩĩkaga mũndũ maũndũ o ta ũrĩa ũthingu wake, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>na wĩhokeki wake, itariĩ; nĩ ũndũ Mwathani nĩ egũkũneanĩte guoko-inĩ gwakwa ũmũthĩ,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> na ndinetĩkĩra gũtambũrũkia guoko gwakwa njũkĩrĩre mũitĩrĩrio maguta wa Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"o0HA1lHWxEqpMY2oz8ITew",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				         Kĩambĩrĩria 22:1-2.9.10-13.15-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨAMBĨRĨRIA:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo Ngai akĩgeria Abrahamu, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Abrahamu-Ĩ, Abrahamu-Ĩ.  Nake agĩĩtĩka akiuga: Niĩ ũyũ. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Rĩu ũkĩra woe mũrũguo o ũcio wa mũmwe ũcio wendete  mũno.  O we Isaaka, ũthiĩ bũrũri wa Moria,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ũkamũrutĩre kuo kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩmwe kĩa iria ii kuo, o kĩrĩa ngakwĩra, atuĩke ihaki rĩa njino.  Makinya o handũ harĩa erĩtwo nĩ Ngai;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> nake Abrahamu agĩaka kĩgongona ho, agĩcoka akĩara nguo wega. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Nake Abrahamu agĩtambũrũkia guoko akĩoya rũhio orage mũriũ. Na rĩrĩ, mũraika wa Mwathani arĩ o igũrũ akĩmwĩta  akiuga atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Abrahamu, Abrahamu.  Nake abrahamu agĩĩtĩka akiuga: Niĩ ũyũ.  Agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Menya ũhutie kĩhĩĩ kĩu na guoko  gwaku,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> o na kana ũgĩĩke ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ, nĩ gũkorũo rĩu nĩ ndamenya atĩ nĩ wĩtigĩrĩte Ngai, kuona atĩ ndũnangiria mũrũguo,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o mũrũguo ũcio wa mũmwe.  Nake Abrahamu agĩgĩtiira maitho, akĩbaraga; </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>na atĩrĩ, thutha wake gũgĩkorũo kwĩ ndũrũme  inyitĩtwo hĩa nĩ mĩrita gĩthaka-inĩ. Nake Abrahamu agĩthiĩ, akĩnyita  ndũrũme ĩo,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> akĩmĩĩta ĩtuĩke ihaki rĩa njino ithenya rĩa mũriũ.  Nake mũraika ũcio wa Mwathani arĩ o igũrũ agĩcoka agĩĩta Abrahamu ihinda rĩa kerĩ,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> akiuga ũũ: Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Nĩ ndĩĩhĩtĩte ngegweta niĩ mwene, ngoiga atĩrĩ, atĩ tondũ nĩ weka ũguo,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> waaga kũngiria mũrũguo, o mũrũguo ũcio wa mũmwe-rĩ kũrathima no mũhaka ngũrathime, o na gũthegeiya no mũhaka ngũthegeerie mbeũ,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> ĩingĩhe o ta njata cia igũrũ, o na ta mũthanga ũrĩa ũrĩ hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria rĩrĩa inene;</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> nayo mbeũ yaku nĩ ĩkerigagĩria na kĩhingo gĩa thũ ciayo.  Na ningĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe cia thĩ ikarathimwo nĩ ũndũ wa mbeũ ĩo yaku;</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ tondũ-rĩ, nĩ wĩtĩkĩrĩte kũigua mũgambo wakwa.
 </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"IkrD+vSrikybI4nHQ01RQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                   2 Samuel 7:1-5;8-12;14;16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA SAMWELI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>	 
Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũthamaki Davide aatũũrire nyũmba yake, </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>o nake Mwathani agĩkorũo atũmĩte ahurũke agatiga gũũkĩrĩrũo nĩ thũ ciake iria ciamũrigicĩirie na mĩena yothe-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> agĩkĩĩra Nathani, ũrĩa mũnabii, atĩrĩ, Ta rora wone atĩ rĩu niĩ ndũũraga nyũmba yakĩtwo na mĩtarakwa,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> no rĩrĩ, ithandũkũ rĩa Ngai rĩtũũraga o matama-inĩ marĩa ma kũrĩhumbĩra. Nake Nathani agĩkĩra mũthamaki atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Thiĩ ũgeke ũndũ o wothe ũrĩa wĩ ngoro-inĩ yaku;  nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani arĩ hamwe  nawe. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ ũtukũ o ro ũcio, ndũmĩrĩri ya Mwathani ĩgĩkinyĩrĩra Nathani, akĩĩrũo atĩrĩ,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Thiĩ ũkere ndungata yakwa Davide atĩrĩ, Mwathani oiga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, anga nĩ wega ũnjakĩre nyũmba nĩguo ndĩmĩtũũre?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, ndakũrutire ciugũ-inĩ cia mbũri ũtige gũcirũmĩrĩra, nĩ getha  ũtuĩke mũnene wa gwathaga andũ akwa Israeli;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩ njikarĩte hamwe nawe kũndũ kũrĩa guothe wanathiĩ, na nĩ ninĩte thũ ciaku ciothe, ikehera mbere yaku;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩ ngatũma ũgĩe igweta mũno o ta andũ a gũkũ thĩ arĩa marĩ igweta mũno. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nao andũ akwa Israeli nĩ ngũmathurĩra handũ ndĩmahande ho nĩ getha matũũrage handũ hao kĩũmbe, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>na matigacoke gũthamio rĩngĩ o na rĩ; o na kana ciana iria njaganu icoke kũmanyarira o na atĩa,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> o ta ũrĩa ciekaga tene, o na ta ũrĩa gwatariĩ kuuma mũthenya ũrĩa ndaathanire</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> ngiuga atĩ atiirĩrĩri bũrũri matuĩke a gũtirĩrĩra andũ akwa Israeli. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384> Na nĩ ngũkũhurũkia, ũtige kũnyarirũo nĩ thũ ciaku ciothe. O na ningĩ Mwathani egũkwĩra atĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>atĩ Mwathani nĩ akahanda nyũmba yaku.  Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa matukũ maku makahingio nawe ũkome hamwe na mathoguo, </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ngahada mũndũ wa mbeũ yaku ĩrĩa ĩgoka thutha waku, yumĩte mũthirimo waku;</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384> o naguo ũthamaki wake nĩ ngatũma ũikare ũrũmĩte mũno. Na nĩ niĩ ngatuĩka ithe,</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384> nake atuĩke mũrũ wakwa.  Naruo rũciaro rũaku, o na ũthamaki waku, nĩ ũkona ihandĩtwo igatũũra irũmĩte mũno,</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>tene na tene; o naguo ũhoro waku wa gũikarĩra gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki nĩ ũkahandwo ũtũũre ũrũmĩte wega tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"Ht1UUg4IbkCqUNwIcNg++w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					     Daniel 12:1-3 </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI DANIELI: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩguo Mikaeli agokĩra, o we mũtongoria mũnene ũrĩa ũrũgamagĩrĩra ciana cia andũ anyu, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ gũkagĩa ihinda rĩa mĩnyamaro mĩingĩ ĩtarĩ yonwo tayo mbere ĩo, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>kuuma o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ anyu maambĩrĩirie gũtuĩka rũrĩrĩ rũgima o nginya  hĩndĩ ĩo.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  No matukũ-inĩ macio andũ anyu nĩ makahonokio, o ũrĩa wothe ũgakorũo aandĩkĩtwo </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ibuku-inĩ nao andũ aingĩ a kũu arĩa magakorũo makomete rũkũngũ-inĩ rũa thĩ nĩ makariũkio, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>amwe mariũkire muoyo-inĩ ũrĩa ũtagathira, nao arĩa angĩ mariũke nĩ getha maconorithio, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na matũre mamenekete  mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.  Nao arĩa marĩ ogĩ nĩ magacangarara ta ũtheri wa mũtambũrũko wa matu-mairũ,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> nao andũ arĩa macokagia andũ arĩa angĩ njĩra-inĩ ya ũthingu matũre makengete ta njata tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"t36pl1sAGkW7m4lig0cnEQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>MŨCIĨ MŨTHERU WA YESU, MARIA NA JOSEPH</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE					                 1 Sam. 1:20-22, 24-28</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA SAMŨELI WA MBERE: </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Agĩkĩgĩa nda agĩciara kaana ga kahĩĩ, agĩgatua Samũeli, agĩkiuga atĩrĩ, “Nĩ gũkorwo  nĩkũhooya ndakahoire kũrĩ Mwathani.”</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Mahinda nĩmaagĩkinyire o rĩngĩ ma Elikana na mũciĩ wake gũthiĩ Shilo akarutĩre Mwathani igongoona rĩa mwaka o mwaka,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> o na akahingie igongoona rĩa mwanya rĩrĩa eeranĩire.  Hingo ĩyo Hana ndaigana gũthiĩ.  Eerire mũthuuriwe atĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“Mwana atiga kuonga-rĩ, nĩguo ngaamũtwara nyũmbainĩ ya Mwathani kũrĩa agatũũra matukũ ma muoyo wake wothe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩĩkia kũmũtigithia kuonga, akĩmũtwara Shilo, na agĩthiĩ na ndeegwa ya mĩaka ĩtatũ, na kiro ikũmi cia mũtu, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na mondo ĩmwe ya rũũa ĩiyũrĩĩte ndibei.  Agĩgĩtwara Samũeli, arĩ o mũnyiinyi, nyũmbainĩ ya Mwathani o kũu Shilo.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Maarĩkia gũthĩnja ndeegwa ĩyo, magĩtwarĩra Eli mwana ũcio.  Hana akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthũũri ũyũ, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>tanjĩtĩkĩria.  No ũndirikane? Nĩ niĩ mũtumia ũrĩa warũũgamĩĩte haaha akĩhooya Mwathani.  Ndamũhooire mwana ũyũ, naake akĩĩhe. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, nĩndamwamũrĩra Mwathani.  Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yothe  egũtũũra muoyo-rĩ, egũtũũra e wa Mwathani.”Magĩgĩthaathaĩria Mwathani kũu.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	"},{Guid:"naLdk+f4Lk+QfBtvWjcDpg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Githomo kiambere</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Jehova Ngai agitwara mundu ucio ombite akimuiga mugunda ucio wari kuu Edeni, aurutage wira,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> na auikaragie.Nake Jehova Ngai agiatha mundu ucio, akimwira atiri, Muti o wothe uria wimugunda uyu-ri,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> niurekereirio uuriage; no riri, muti uria wakumenyithania wega o na uuru,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ndukanaurie, nigukoruo muthenya uria ukauria, no muhaka ugakua.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ningi Jehova Ngai akiuga atiri, Ti wega mundu uyu aikare wiki; ningumuumbira mumuteithia o uria maaganiriiruo nake.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Na riri, Jehova Ngai ombire nyamu o yothe ya githaka na tiri, o na nyamu o yothe iria iri njoya ya riera-ini,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> agicoka agicitwara ciothe kwi mundu ucio, niguo emenyere uria eguciita; na riri, kiumbe o giothe gia icio iri muoyo-ri</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>o riitwa riria mundu ucio aagituire, riu rigituika riitwa riakio. Nake mundu ucio gitua mahiu mothe mariitwa, o na nyamu iria ii njoya cia riera-ini,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o na nyamu ciothe cia githaka; no riri, ha uhoro wa mundu-iri. Gutiakoriruo kwina mumuteithia maaganiriiruo nake.</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Nake Jehova Ngai agȋtὺma mὺndὺ ὺcio agwatwo ni toro mὺnene mὺno,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> agȋcokania nyama hau ruuma, naruo rὺbaru rὺu Jehova  Ngai aarutire mὺndὺ ὺcio,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> akȋrὺkὺmbania rὺgȋtuȋka mὺndὺ mὺka, agȋcoka akȋmὺtwara kwȋ mὺndὺ ὺcio. Nake mὺndὺ ὺcio akiuga atȋrȋ, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Rȋu kaȋὺyὺ nȋwe ihȋndi rimwe riumite mahindi-ini makwa, o na nyama yumite nyama-ini ya mwiri wakwa-i!</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ni we gaetagwo Mundu-muka, tondu arutiruo thiin iwa Mundu-murume.Tondu wauguo-ri, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>mundu murume niatigane na ithe na nyina, magwatane na muka, nao erimatuike mwiri umwe</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
