Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Igongona ni riarika guthii rekei tuthii, tutware ngumo ya Kristu kuri nduriri ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni tuinuke na thayu thayu ucio twaheo.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tutwarire andu othe thayu ucio wa Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Igongona ni riarika guthii rekei tuthii, tutware ngumo ya kristu kuri nduriri ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai ni atwariria na mugambo wake,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Waguna mioyo itu tuikare twina  thayu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Igongona ni riarika guthii rekei tuthii, tutware ngumo ya kristu kuri nduriri ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee ni aturathima na ndathimi nyingi,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni tutuikei kirathimo kuri aria angi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Igongona ni riarika guthii rekei tuthii, tutware ngumo ya Kristu kuri nduriri ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiria giothe twagaya muthenya wa umuthi,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rekei gitugune tuturanie na rwendo.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Igongona ni riarika guthii rekei tuthii, tutware ngumo ya kristu kuri nduriri ciothe.</s></f>"}],
