Text:"Itega riri riitu nitugugutegera"},{Guid:"QwB8XMAQzUajic6P0nRCig",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384> Jesus my Lord my God My All
  How can I love thee as I ought</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>  And how revere this wondrous gift
  So far surpassing hope or thought</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Sweet sacrament we thee adore 
O make us love thee more and more
O make us love thee more and more</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Had I but Mary sinless heart
To love thee with my dearest kiny</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>with what bursts of fervent praise
Thy goodness Jesus would I sing </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> O see with in a creature hand 
 The vast creator degns to be
  Reposing infant like as though
  On Joseph’s arm on Mary’s knee.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Thy body soul and God head all
O mystery of love divine
I cannot compass all
I have for all thou 
hast and art are mine</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Sound, sound his praises higher still
And  come ye Angels to our aid</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Tis God tis God the very God
Whose power both
 man and angels made.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Jesus my Lord "},{Guid:"IuMTscnNQEGhpK4tz1pXKg",Verses:[{
