Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>TWARANA NA ITHUII</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twarana na ithui we Ngai witu, twarana na ithui mahinda me mothe x2</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Igongona riu ni riakirika,
tukuinuka na thayu waku we Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitwaigua ciugo 
(ciaku we Ngai), ni ciugo (njega ciagutuhe hinya)</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.(We Ngai)  witu ii, twarana na ithui, (ii) utuhe thayu uturoini witu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Utuhe hinya, wa guthii kuhunjiria, aria,othe tutigire micii</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.(Twa) (twarana na ithui,twarana na ithui, (ii) cua cua na ithui we Ngai witu x2</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twacokia ngatho 
kuri we Ngai ,
nigutumenyerera mahinda mothe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>5.Ngai witu twarana na ithui hindi ciothe, twarana na ithui, (na ithui) hindi ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ririra tuguthii kuruta wira waku Ngai, twarana na (ii), twarana na itui Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Micii-ini itu Ngai, utwaranage na ithui, ona maturaini maitu twarana na ithui.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Tugithii kuhunjia), kiugo (kiugo) giaku, twarana na ithui (ii), cua cua na ithui x2</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>6.Niwega niwega Ngai, nitwacokia ngatho, niundu wa gutwarana na ithui hindi ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Koguo Ngai witu, turania na ithui, cua cua na ithui, twarana na ithui .</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twarana na ithui we Ngai witu, twarana na ithui mahinda me mothe x2</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_8cbd5bc4.jpg"}},
Text:"TWARANA NA ITHUII
"},{Guid:"nPr+ubz6lkiehtu3s4IArg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MAHOYA MA KIROKO</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na riitwa ria Ithe na mwana na Muoyo Mutheru. Ni gutuike uguo</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu, Maria na Josebu ningumunengera ngoro na muoya wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoro njega ya Yesu wakwa hotithia ngwende nginya ngakua</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoro njega ya Maria ndeithia kuhonoka</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arokumio Ithe na Mwana na Muoyo Mutheru </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ta kiambiriria riu na hingo ciothe . Ni gutuike uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NI NGUGUTIA</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngugutia Ngai wakwa na ni ngukwenda na ngoro yakwa yothe. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngukugatha niundu ni wanyumbire, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wanduire mukristu na undaritie utuku uyu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngugutegera ikiro cia umuthi: hotithia ciagire </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciothe ta uria wendaga na irogu kumia.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uthengerie wihia na mauru mothe, Wega waku urotura hingo </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciothe na nii, o na andu akwa end othe. Ni gutuike uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BABA WITU</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Baba witu uri iguru, riitwa riaku riroiguo, unene waku uroka,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uria ukwenda uroekwo guku thi ta uria wikagwo iguru </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utuhe umuthi irio citu cia gutuigana: 
na utuohere mehia</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maitu, ta uria ithui tuohagira aria matwihitie na ndugatutware </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uhitithiaini na utuhonokie uuruini. 
Ni gutuike uguo</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NI NGUKUGEITHIA MARIA</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngukugeithia Maria, muiyure ni wega. Mwathani ari na We. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee uri murathime kuri aka othe na Yesu Mwana wa ndaa yaku </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nimurathime. Maria Mutheru nyina wa Ngai tuhoere ithui </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>riu na ihinda ria gukua gwitu . Ni gutuike uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>AROKUMIO ITHE</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arokumio Ithe na Mwana Na Muoyo Mutheru. Ta kiambiriria , </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na riu na hingo 
ciothe na magaini ma miaka . Ni gutuike guo</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NI NGUITIKIA</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni nguitikia Ngai Ithe Kihoti-othe Muumbi wa iguru na thii, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na Yesu Kristu, Mwana wake wa Muumwe, Mwathani witu, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uria wetuire mundu na wiki wa Muoyo Mutheru. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni aciarirwo ni Maria thingi hingo ciothe; </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni atandiurirwa Ponsyo Pilato agiathana; ni ambirwo, ni akuire, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni athikiruo, ni aikurukire gwa akuo. ni ariukire muthi wa ithatu </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni ambatire iguru kuria aikare mwena wa urio 
wa Ithe wa Ngai Ithe Kihoti-othe;</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni agacoka guku thi athuranie aria mari muoyo na aria akuo, Ni nguitikia Muoyo Mutheru, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kanitha theru Gatoriki, uteithania wa Atheru, riohora ria mawihia, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iriuka ria miiri, utuuro wa mindi na mindi. Ni uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>YUKIA NGEITHI MARIA</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yukia ngeithi, Maria, nyina wa tha, muoyo murio na wetereri </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>witu, yukia ngeithi. 
Nitugukuririra ithui agendi ciana cia Ewa </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>acai na ariri kiandaini giki kia maithori, na ni twagukaira. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uguo muciririri witu, ikia kuri ithui maitho maku mari tha. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na thutha wa wuikari uyu utuonie Yesu Mwana murathime</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa nda yaku. Wee Maria Thingi mwendi uri tha na murio</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MURAIKA WA NGAI</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muraika wa Ngai, urei mureri wakwa, thereria njikaria,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndugamirira na njatha, ni undu ni ndakunengeriruo </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni Ngai Mwene tha. Nigutuike guo</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MUGIRE WA WITIKIA</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wakwa ni ni ngwitikia na hinya uria Wee Uge utangihitia, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>woimburiririe, na Kanitha theru igatunengera wa guitikia. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na ni ndoiga ni ni ngwitikia wee Ngai uria wike murungaru, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thi-inii wa ciumbe ithatu ciiganaine na iri mwanya, Ithe, Mwana na Muoyo Mutheru; </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na Mwana uria wetuire mundu na wakuire ni undu witu, ni we Yesu Kristu </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uria ukanengera o mundu muigana uria ekire, niguo utugi kana thinjo itagathira, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ni ngwenda gutura hingo ciothe uigana witikia uyu. Mwathani matia witikia wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MUGIRE WA WETERERI </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wakwa ninjetereire utuuro utathira na hinya </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa kuhota uguo 
niundu wa utana na mawiriri maku, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na ikiro ciikitwo ni Yesu Kristu Muhonokia witu,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngiika ikiro njega iria njiriiruo na ngwenda gwika, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ni ndaguthaitha ndikanakoruo </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nyimitwo kinya tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MUGIRE WA RUENDO</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wakwa ni ngukwenda na ngoro yakwa yothe na </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iguru ria indo ciothe, Wee Mwene utari muhaka, ukeni witu utathiraga, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na niundu wa ruendo ni ngwenda andu othe o ta nii mwene </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ni nguohera aria manjikite uuru. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani hotithia matamatie ruendo ruaku hingo ciothe. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MURAIKA WA MWATHANI</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muraika wa Mwathani ni akinyiirie Maria uhoro</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akigia nda na wiki wa Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngukugeithia Maria, muiyure ni wega. Mwathani ari na Wee. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee uri murathime kuri aka othe na Yesu Mwana wa ndaa yaku </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nimurathime. Maria Mutheru nyina wa Ngai tuhoere ithui </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>riu na ihinda ria gukua gwitu . Ni gutuike uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akigia nda na wiki wa Muoyo Mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngukugeithia Maria.............</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>One ndungata ya Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni njikuo ta uria wauga</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngukugeithia Maria ................</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na Uge niwetuire mundu</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na ugituura thi-ini witu</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ngukugeithia Maria............</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utuhoere Nyina Mutheru wa Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niguo twagiriruo ni mawiriri ma Kristu</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NI TUHOE</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni tuguguthaitha Mwathan uturirie wega waku mioyo-ini itu; </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha ithui tumenyete witu mundu wa Mwana </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waku Kristu, tumenyithitio ni Muraika, tukinyire </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ukumio wa iriuka  na njira ya mutharaba na itandiuruo riake. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni undu wa Kristu  mwene Mwathani witu. Nigutike guo</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arokumio Ithe na Mwana Na Muoyo Mutheru........ X 3</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Kuuma iriukiro kinya Pentecoste nikwiragwo)</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>canjamuka Ngatha ya iguru: Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amu uria wagiriiruo ni gukua: Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ariukite ta o uria oigire: Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hoya Ngai niundu witu; Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kena na canjamuka Thingu Maria: Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amu Mwathani ni ariukire: Allelya</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NI TUHOE</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai uria wetekirire thii thi-inii wa iriuka ria Mwana waku, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani witu Yesu Kristu: tuhotithie ni tuguthaitha tugwate  </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mokeni ma utuuro utathiraga na njira ya Nyina wake Thingi Maria. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niundu wa Kristu Mwene Mwathani witu. Ni gutuike guo</s></f>"}],
Text:"MAHOYA MA KIROKO"},{Guid:"2PwMMaqsvEyQhjcrFnLsYg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MAHOYA MBERE YA WAMUKIRI</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>UHERI</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu mwega Muumbi na Muhonokia wakwa </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni ndahera na ndaigua ruo, amu ni ndakumenire </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ni njuui no Wee mwega utangithuka. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ningwihita na hinya waku ndikanacoke gugukararia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ninguthengera maundu mothe makuhiriirie wihia</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>WITIKIA</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni njitikitie na ngoro, Yesu, uri ho Ekarisita-ini </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Mwiri na Thakame, na Muoyo na Ungai waku wothe;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni nguona ta ari mugate tiguo ni njuui. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Riu ndibataire gukuona na maitho, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni nguitikia mugambo waku; </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ti mugate ni Mwiri; niwe mwene uri ho ta uria utuire </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iguru: na ni nguitikia kinya gukua kana kuragwo.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITIO</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni ndatiia uhoti waku muno, Ngai amu Araika othe </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na andu othe, no We umathaga We mwene. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ingiiganania nawe ndi kii nii? Ndi mwihia </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na no ngwenda gugutia na ngoro yothe, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ithenya-ini ria aria matagukumenya. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ndagutia umuthi na hingo ciothe, ndi na Araika na Atheru </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>othe mari ikenero, ni undu uri Baba, Mumbi Muhonokia, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muthamaki na Ngai wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RUENDO</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu ni kii kingi utigitie kunyonia ruendo ruaku? </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni wanyendire amu ni woimire iguru na ugikuua </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mutharaba-ini ni undu wakwa na riu ninge ni ukwenda guuka </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee mwene na Mwiri na Muoyo waku ngoro-ini yakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utuike undu umwe na nii, ung'une unyumiririe </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ungwatie urugari waku. Yesu ningwenda o na nii </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ngoro o na muoyo wothe. Ndagire gukwenda hingo ciothe ni kii? </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Anga tiwe mwega kuri indo na kuruga andu? </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tiwe uheaga mawega maingi? Ndeithia riu ndute maundu </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngoro-ini yakwa maundu maria magiragia ruendo ruaku,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>niguo ngwende o gukwenda. Reke nguonie ruendo rwaku umuthi </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na gukuoya thii-ini wakwa na ngoro njega na ngiiyohanie na we </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na munyororo munyitu, 
ngukenie na ikiro ciakwa, ngwendithie </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andu othe, nguigue na ndigakuiguithagie uuru na mikire yakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maitu Maria, undu wendire Muru-guo Yesu kuruga andu othe,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na wamukuaga moko-ini maku ukimukenagia na ruendo na ikiro</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciaku, nyonia wee uria nguamba kwenda Yesu, uria </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ungimugwata ngoro-ini yakwa, uria ingimukunguira. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Unjikarie muri na Muthure Joseph na Araika na Athure othe, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hote kumukenerera ta uria mumukenagira iguru</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THUTHA WA KWAMUKIRA</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>IHOYA KURI NGORO YA YESU</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>One uria rwendo rwaku runenehete. Yesu wakwa mwende ma! </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee ti-itheru ni wendire guthondekera ikaari </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Mwiri waku o na Thakame yaku theru. Ukiinengere nii we wothe. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nuu watumire wike ciama icio nene uguo cia ruendo? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ti ungi, ni njui no ngoro yaku nyendi-ma. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoro ya Yesu wakwa nyene gitio, ikira ngoro yakwa thii-ini </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa ngoro yaku thakama. Ni getha ngiona thi-ini wayo monio maku </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mothe mathaka ma ruendo, menye o na nii kwenda Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uria unyonetie ikiro icio nene uguo cia ruendo. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni gutuike guo. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NI NDAGUKAIRA YESU</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ndagukaira, Yesu Kristu Mwathani mwene ukeni, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha itandiuruo riaku rituike hinya wa kiindeithia, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kunyumiriria na kunjikaria wega.
Ngurara ciaku ituike irio </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kinyuo giakwa gia kuria na kunyua na kugwa wega; </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>riitika ria Thakame yaku rituike ithambia ria mawihia makwa mothe. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ikuiro riaku rituike utuuro wakwa wa hingo giothe.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Riambiro riakwa rituike ikenero riakwa ritathiraga.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maundu macio ni matuike uhoni, ukeni, hinya na yakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:26,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee utuire na wathanaga Magana-ini mothe ma miaka.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nigutuike guo</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MUOYO WA YESU</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muoyo wa Yesu, undathime
Mwiri wa Yesu, uhonie.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thakame ya Yesu inyumiririe. Maai ma mbaru cia Yesu mathambie.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Itandiuruo ria Yesu ring’une.
Yesu mwega unjigue.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uhithe ngurara-ini ciaku. Ndukanandekie o na ri.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Undeithie mbaara-ini ya caitani.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ikuiro-ini riakwa unjite gwaku.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hotithia ngagukinyira.
Ngugaathage na athure aku,</s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Magana-ini mothe ma miaka.
Ni gutuike guo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arokumio Ithe na mwana na Muoyo Mutheru........ X 3</s></f>"}],
