Text:"Nani kati ya watala "},{Guid:"73U1Fu31XEKeI/pdaameFw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NANI NI NANI
(AGJ 98/339)(NAGJ 74/266)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ameniumba jinsi nilivyo, nipendezavyo ni nani kama Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niseme nini, niimbe nini, nilie vipi ninani kama Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384></s></f><fArial Black><s2769>Nani ni nani, nani ni nani, nani ni nani nani kama Mungu;</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwenye uweza (na) mwenye  ukuu, nani nina ni nanikama Mungu; x2</s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384></s></f><fArial Black><s2769>Nani ni nani, nani ni nani, nani ni nani nani kama Mungu;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwenye uweza (na) mwenye  ukuu, nani ni nani nanikama Mungu x 2</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384></s></f><fArial Black><s2769>Tazama jua, mwezi na nyota, mbingu na nchi  ni nani kama Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Loo usiku, jua li wapi, ni maajabu ni nani kama Mungu</s></f><fArial Black><s1384>.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384></s></f><fArial Black><s2769>Nani ni nani, nani ni nani, nani ni nani nani kama Mungu;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwenye uweza (na) mwenye  ukuu, nani ni nani nani kama Mungu x 2</s></f>"}],
Text:"NANI NI NANI (AGJ 98/339)(NAGJ 74/266)
"},{Guid:"cAvUbj+d2UanERI/I54WEg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Mungu mmoja, 
Baba Mwenyezi, Mwumba mbingu na nchi, na vitu vyote vinavyoonekana, na visivyoonekana.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Bwana mmoja Yesu Kristu, Mwana wa pekee wa Mungu.  Aliyezaliwa kwa Baba tangu milele yote. 
 
Mungu aliyetoka kwa Mungu, mwanga kwa mwanga, Mungu kweli kwa Mungu kweli.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aliyezaliwa  bila kuumbwa, mwenye umungu mmoja na Baba; ambaye vitu vyote vimeumbwa naye. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ameshuka toka mbinguni kwa ajili yetu sisi wanadamu na kwa ajili ya wokovu wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akapata mwili kwa uwezo wa Roho Mtakatifu kwake yeye Bikira Maria; Akawa mwanadamu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akasulibiwa pia kwa ajili yetu sisi; akateswa kwa mamlaka ya Ponsio Pilato, akafa, akazikwa. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akafufuka siku ya tatu, ilivyoandikwa. 
Akapaa mbinguni; amekaa kuume kwa Baba Atakuja tena kwa utukufu kuwahukumu wazima na wafu; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao ufalme wake hautakuwa na mwisho.
Nasadiki kwa Roho Mtakatifu, Bwana mleta uzima; atokaye kwa Baba na Mwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Anayeabudiwa na kutukuzwa pamoja na Baba na Mwana: aliyenena kwa vinywa vya Manabii.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Kanisa moja, takatifu, katoliki, la Mitume.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naungama ubatizo mmoja kwa maondoleo ya dhambi.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nangojea na ufufuko wa wafu. Na uzima wa milele ijayo. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amina.</s></f>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
