Kwa ajili yetu kateswa-		
Alikufa na akazikwa-			</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Kafufuka katika wafu-
Akapaa juu mbinguni		
Ameketi kuume kwake		
Mungu Baba yetu Mwenyezi-		</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Ndipo atakapotokea			
Ili awahukumu wote			
Kwake Roho Mtakatifu		
Kwa kanisa la katoliki		</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Ushirika wa watakatifu		
Ondoleo la dhambi zetu		
Nangojea‘fufuko wa miili		
Na uzima wa milele	</s></f>"}],
Text:"Nasadiki kwa Mungu Mmoja-(mimi nasadiki)
"},{Guid:"q6vZ4PtV1EW0ALmh+PBTTA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>1 Wakorintho 13: 4-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ndugu zangu: Upendo umejaa subira, hujionyesha katika hisani. Upendo hauoni kijicho, haujigambi,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> wala haujitutumui. Upendo haukosi adabu, hautafuti faida ya ubinafsi, haukubali
kupatwa na chuki, hauweki uchungu tumboni.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Haufurahii uovu, bali hufurahia ukweli. Upendo huvumilia yote, husadiki yote, hutumaini yote, hustahimili yote. Upendo hauna mwisho.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Unabii utatoweka, lugha pia zitakwisha, elimu nayo itapita. Maana utambuzi wetu ni haba, na unabii wetu ni haba. Lakini ukamilifu utakapokuja,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> uhaba utakoma. Nilipokuwa mtoto, nalisema kama mtoto, nalikuwa na ufahamu kama mtoto, nalifikiri kama mtoto.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Tangu nimepata utu uzima, nimeacha nyuma mambo ya kitoto. Sasa tunaona kwa kioo kwa jinsi ya fumbo, baadaye tutaona uso kwa uso. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Sasa nafahamu kwa sehemu, lakini baadaye nitajua sana. Sasa inadumu imani, tumaini na upendo. Lililo kuu katika hayo ni upendo. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"SHANGILIO LA INJILI 
						Tazama Luka 4:18"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya. 	Aleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana amenituma niwahubirie maskini habari njema, kuwatangazia wafungwa kufunguliwa.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA PILI"},{Guid:"sQtSRcoJ0UeqAN8+RtOx4Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1076></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Neno lake Bwana ni la uzima na linatuliza
Neno lake Bwana ni la uzima linatuongoza</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1076></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Neno lako linatuongoza shughulini za kila  siku
Majaribuni hutufariji na kutuongezea  nguvu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1076></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Ninasikia sauti yako inatuita tuke kwako
Nayo yasema tukiamini tutafika kwako mbinguni</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1076></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Tulisikiliza kwa makini tutafakari usemayo
Tukiifuata injili hii tutaepuka maovu yote.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1076></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Tayarisha nyoyo zetu Bwana, kulipokea neno hili
Ili lidumu mioyoni yetu lituongoze maishani</s></f>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Neno lake Bwana ni la uzima na linatuliza
"},{Guid:"XIlWWVARok2z/5GqqmQQTg",Verses:[{
Text:"GOSPEL"},{ID:2,
Text:"A reading from the Holy Gospel according to Mark   	      Mark 12:28b-34"},{ID:3,
Text:"At that time:
One of the scribes came up to Jesus and asked him, “Which commandment is the first of all?” Jesus answered, "},{ID:4,
Text:"“The first is, “Hear, O Israel: The Lord our God, the Lord is one; and you shall love the Lord your God with all your hearts,"},{ID:5,
Text:" and with all your soul, and with all your mind, and with all your strength.’  The second is this, "},{ID:6,
Text:"‘You shall love your neighbor as yo
urself.’ There is no other commandment greater than these.”
And the scribe said to him, “You are right, Teacher; you have truly said that he is one, and there is no other but he; and to love him with all the heart, and with all the  understanding, and with all the strength, and to love one’s neighbor as oneself, is much more than all whole burnt offerings and sacrifices.” And when Jesus saw that he answered wisely, he said to him, “You are not far from the kingdom of God.” And after that no one dared to ask him any question."},{ID:7,
Text:"The Gospel of the Lord."}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GOSPEL"},{Guid:"N4goaHd5g0eCeIgQY3vdjg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Namwungamia   Mungu Mwenyezi,  nanyi ndugu zangu, kwani nimekosa mno kwa mawazo,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> kwa maneno, kwa matendo, na kwa  kuto timiza wajibu;
Nimekosa mimi, nimekosa mimi, nimekosa sana.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ndiyo maana na mwomba Maria mwenye heri, Bikira daima, Malaika na Watakatifu wote, nanyi ndugu zangu, niombeeni kwa Bwana Mungu wetu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"NAMUUNGAMIA"},{Guid:"dYjtSQNnFkaZrsy9s47Vqg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1076>SECOND READING				                         Romans 4:13, 16-18,22</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076>A reading from the Letter of Saint Paul to the Romans		</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076>Brethren:
The promise to Abraham and his descendants, that they should inherit the world, did not come through the law but through the righteousness of faith.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076>That is why all depends on faith, in order that the promise may rest on grace  and be guaranteed to all his descendants –</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076> not only to the adherents of the law but also to those who share the faith of Abraham</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076>for he is the father of us all, as it is written, “I have made you the father of many nations” – in the presence of the God in whom he believed, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076>who gives life to the dead and calls into existence the things that do not exist.  In hope he believed against hope,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076> that he should become the father of many nations; as he had been told, “So shall your descendants be.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076>” That is why his faith was “reckoned to him as righteousness.”</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076> Word of the Lord</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076>ALLELUIA								          		          </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076>Psalm 68:20
Alleluia, Alleluia</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076>Day after day, may the Lord be blest.  He bears our burdens; God is our Saviour.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076>Alleluia</s>"}],
Text:"SECOND READING"},{Guid:"+6iH+7L1uEGEvlgT9wy4Rw",Verses:[{
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					                 Aroma 4:13.16-18;22"},{ID:2,
Text:"GŨTHOMA MARŨA KŨRI ANDŨ A ROMA"},{ID:3,
Text:"Aruna akwa, kĩĩrĩro gĩkĩ gĩa atĩ Iburahimu agatuĩka mũgai wa kũgaĩrũo thĩ yothe, nderĩirũo we mwene, o na kana arĩa a mbeũ yake, nĩ ũndũ wa gwathĩkĩra watho, no nĩ ũndũ wa ũthingu ũrĩa uumanaga na wĩtĩkio.  Ũguo, ũthingu ũcio uumanaga na wĩtĩkio, nĩ getha wonekage no ũndũ wa Wega wa Ngai; nĩguo ũndũ ũrĩa mwĩranĩre wonekage hatarĩ nganja nĩ andũ othe a mbeũ ya Iburahimu, to arĩa maaheirũo ũhoro wa watho oiki, no ningĩ arĩa o nao metĩkĩtie wĩtĩkio ta ũcio wake.  Amu iburahimu ũcio-rĩ, o ta ũrĩa ũhoro wake wandĩkĩtwo, atĩ, Nĩngũtũire ithe wa ndũrĩrĩ nyingĩ-rĩ, maitho-inĩ ma ũcio etĩkĩtie nĩwe ithe witũ ithuothe, o maitho-inĩ ma Ngai, we ũriũkagia arĩa makuĩte, na aaragia ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa matarĩ ho o ta marĩ ho.
Nake Iburahimu, o na kũngĩtuĩka ũndũ ũcio erĩirũo ndũngĩĩrigĩrĩrĩka-rĩ, nĩaawĩtĩkĩtie, agĩgĩtũũra erĩgĩrĩire atĩ nĩagatuĩka ithe wa ndũrĩrĩ nyingĩ, kũringana o na ũhoro ũrĩa aaheirũo akĩĩrũo ũũ, Ũguo noguo a mbeũ yaku makaigana.  Naguo ũhoro ũcio agĩgĩtuĩrũo ta arĩ ũthingu e naguo"},{ID:4,
Text:"Ciugo cia Mwathani."}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"GITHOMO KIA IGIRI Aroma 4:13.16-18;22"},{Guid:"+GnGHTh7TkaXsk3Hv6cTfg",Verses:[{
Text:"VR/ 	I will sing for ever of your mercies, O Lord"},{ID:6,
Text:"“With my chosen one I have made a covenant; 
I have sworn to David my servant:"},{ID:7,
Text:"I will establish your descendants for ever, 
and set up your throne through all ages.”  R/"},{ID:8,
Text:"R/ 	I will sing for ever of your mercies, O Lord"},{ID:9,
Text:"“He will call out to me, ‘You are my father, 
my God, the rock of my salvation.’"},{ID:10,
Text:"I will keep my faithful love for him always; 
with him my covenant shall last.” R/"},{ID:11,
Text:"R/ 	I will sing for ever of your mercies, O Lord"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"I will sing for ever of your mercies, O Lord
"},{Guid:"KiKY5/Hgqk26vd6DgJT3Xg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Somo la Kwanza
Mwanzo 2:18-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana Mungu akasema: \"Si vema mtu awe peke yake: nataka kumfanyizia msaada wenye kufanana naye.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>\" Bwana Mungu akawafinyanga kwa udongo wanyama wote wa porini na ndege wote wa angani,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> akawaleta mbele ya mtu, ili aone atawaita majina gani: nao wote walio na uzima waitwe jina lile atakalowaita.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Mtu akawaita majina yao wanyama wote wa kufugwa, ndege wa angani na wanyama wa porini;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> lakini hakuonekana msaada wa mtu wenye kufanana naye.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Hapo Bwana Mungu akamtia mtu usingizi mzito, naye akalala. Halafu akatwaa ubavu wake mmoja, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>akatia nyama mahali pake. Bwana Mungu akaufanya ubavu alioutwaa katika mtu, kuwa mwanamke,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> akamleta kwa mtu. Hapo mtu akasema: \"Sasa, huyu ni mfupa kutoka mifupa yangu na nyama kutoka nyama yangu. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Huyu ataitwa 'mwanamke,'  maana ametwaliwa katika mwanamume.\" Kwa sababu hiyo, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>mwanamume atamwacha baba yake na mama yake,  naye ataambatana na mke wake, nao watakuwa mwili mmoja.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Somo la Kwanza"},{Guid:"Foa8ZYHRc0qNEPjTHOV01Q",Verses:[{
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 90:2;2-4;12-13;14-16"},{ID:2,
Text:"ICOKIA	Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ"},{ID:3,
Text:"1.	O mbere irĩma itaanaciarũo, 
o ũtaanomba thĩ na mabũrũri, 
kuuma o tene na nginya tene, wee ũrĩ o Mũrungu."},{ID:4,
Text:"2.	Ũhũndũraga andũ magacoka gũtuĩka mũthegethege; 
ũkoiga, Cokai, ciana ici cia kĩrĩndĩ.
Amu harĩ wee, mĩaka ngiri 
no ta mũthenya wa ira, o ũguo ũrathirire ũrehera, 
ningĩ no ta ituanĩra rĩmwe rĩa camu wa ũtukũ."},{ID:5,
Text:"3.	Gĩtũmenyithie gũtara matukũ maitũ 
nĩ getha tũgĩe na ngoro cia kũũhĩga.  
Garũrũka, Jehova; nĩ nginya rĩ? 
gĩcoke kũiguĩra ndungata ciaku tha."},{ID:6,
Text:"4.	Rũcinĩ ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku; 
nĩguo tũtũũre tũkũngũyagia o tũgĩkenaga matukũ maitũ mothe.
Wĩko waku ũroonwo kũrĩ ndungata ciaku, 
na ũkaru waku woneke kũrĩ ciana ciacio."}],
