Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ni hindi njega ya güthikiriria, Mügambo wa Kristü tüüige ngoro-ini.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ni ciugo njega cia kugüna mioyo, Nitüthikiririe Mwathani atwaririe.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ni hindi (njega) ya güthikiriria Tüigue Mwathani agitwariria.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Mügambo (üyü) niütühotithagia Tüikare üria Ngai endete.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Mügambo üyü wariirie Saülü, agitiga künyarira akristiano.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Agituika mükristu mwikindiru. Agiteithiriria kühunjia ühoro üyü.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ni hindi (njega) ya güthikiriria Tüigue Mwathani agitwariria.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Mügambo (üyü) niütühotithagia Tüikare üria Ngai endete.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Mügambo üyü wariirie Zakayo. Nuthu ya indo ciake 'kigaira athiini.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Agicokia indo ciothe iria aiyite. Mügambo üyü niguo ciugo ciohonokio.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ni hindi (njega) ya güthikiriria Tüigue Mwathani agitwariria.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Mügambo (üyü) niütühotithagia Tüikare üria Ngai endete.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Noguo wariirie Maria Magdalina Agicenjia mithiire iria yari miüru </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Akioherwo mehia mothe maria ehitie 'gituika mürümiriri wa Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ni hindi (njega) ya güthikiriria tüigue Mwathani agitwariria.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Mügambo (üyü) niütühotithagia tüikare üria Ngai endete.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Na ithui akristü nitüthikiririe küria tüogomete tügerie kwirünga</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Küria tuumite wega-ini wa Ngai Tücoke rüüru-ini rwa ng'ondu cia Kristü</s></f>"},{ID:10,
