Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NITUINGIRE NA GIKENO (BARICHO PAGE 18)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Nituingire na gikeno na nduhiu ( na nduhiu) nyumbaini theru ya Ngai tugacokie ngatho)*2</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nyumba ya Ngai ni ya irathimo, tuthii ithuothe tukamathe irathimo</s></f>"},{ID:4,
