Text:"<s1384>RESPONSORIAL PSALM                              Psalm 103:1-2,3-4, 8 and 10,12-13(R. 8a)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>R/ 	The Lord is compassionate and gracious</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Bless the Lord, O my soul, 
and all within me, his holy name.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Bless the Lord, O my soul, 
and never forget all his benefits. R/</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>R/ 	The Lord is compassionate and gracious</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>It is the Lord who forgives all your sins, 
who heals  every one of your ills, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>who redeems your life from the grave, 
who crowns you with mercy and compassion. R/</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>R/ 	The Lord is compassionate and gracious</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>The Lord is compassionate and gracious, 
slow to anger and rich in mercy.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>He does not treat us according to our sins, nor repay us according to our faults. R/</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>R/ 	The Lord is compassionate and gracious</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>As far as the east is from the west, 
so far from us does he remove our transgressions.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>As a father has compassion on his children,the Lord’s compassion is on those who fear him. R/</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>R/ 	The Lord is compassionate and gracious</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
