Text:"<s1384>Au:</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Bwana, kilatunapo kula mkate hu una kukinywea kikombe hiki, tunatangaza kifo chako, mpaka utakapokuja.</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>Au: </s>"},{ID:26,
