"},{Guid:"apS9bqM47Uq5JfWb9c+GQg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SEKWENSIA</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Uje, Roho Mtakatifu,
Tuangaze toka mbingu,
Roho zetu kwa mwangao.</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Uje Baba wa maskini,
Uje mtoa wa vipaji vya Mungu,
Uje Mwanga wa mioyo,</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>Ee mfariji mwema sana,
Ee rafiki mwanana,
Ewe raha mustarehe,</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa kazi u pumziko,
kwenye joto burudisho,
U mfutaji wa machozi,</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Ewe mwanga wenye heri,
Uwajaze waamini,
Neema yako mioyoni,</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>Bila nguvu yako Wewe,
Mwanadamu hana kitu,
Kwake yote yana koma,</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>Osha machafuko yetu,
Panyeshee pakavu petu,
Na kuponya majeraha,</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384>Elegeze ukaidi,
Pasha moto ubaridi,
Nyosha upotovu wote,</s>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1384>Wape waamini wako,
Wenye tumaini kwako,
Paji zako zote saba,</s>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<s1384>Wape tuzo ya fadhila,
Wape mwisho bila ila,
Wape heri ya milele.</s>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<s1384>Amina. Aleluya.</s>"},{ID:31,
Text:"Aleluya.		 Aleluya."},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Njoo Roho Mtakatifu, jaza nyoyo za waumini wako; washa moto wa mapendo ndani yao.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"Aleluya."}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SEKWENSIA
"},{Guid:"pTdmpQKfSE+3dP+wHovWdg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SEKWENSIA
 
Ee Sayuni mtukuze
Uwezavyo umwimbie,</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Mkombozi na Mwalimu
apitaye kila sifa,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa nyimbo na shangwe kuu,
Itokayo kwa watu,</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Nia yetu ya kusifu,
Lishe hili walipewa,
Hasa mkate Mtakatifu,
Wale kumi na wawili,
uletao uzima,
Karamuni mwa mwisho.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Shangilio la rohoni,
Lipendeze liwe zuri,
Sifa tele livune,
Ipo leo siku kubwa,
Kwa kumbusho la kuwekwa,
Kwanza ile karamu.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Muda ule umekwisha,
Ipo meza ya mfalme,
Na sheria mpya,
Tumepata mapya yote.
Nuru, sio nusu giza,
Mwanga sio usiku.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Tendo lake karamuni,
Kristo ametuamuru,
Tutende tumkumbuke,
Twafuata amri yake,
Tukitoa hii sadaka,
Kwa mkate na divai</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mkate wageuka mwili,
Na divai ikawa damu,
Kanuni kwa Wakristo,
Huelewi huioni,
Kweli hio; hukubali,
Maana ni muujiza mkuu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Unaota tu maumbo,
Ni alama zifumbazo,
Utukufu wenyewe,
Ule mwili unywe damu,
Kila umbo linafumba,
Yesu mzima halisi.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ukipewa tu kimego,
Umempata Yesu mzima,
Si sehemu yake tu,
Moja hula, elfu hula,
Wote hupokea sawa,
Na mpokewa hakomi.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Hula wema na wabaya,
Kwa bahati mbali mbali,
Kifo au uzima,
Basi, mkate Mtakatifu,
Huwa sumu kwa wabaya,
Dawa bora kwa wema.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ikimegwa sakramenti,
Usisite, uamini,
Huwa ndani ya kipande,
Mwili wote wa Yesu,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwili wake haumegwi,
Ni alama ivunjwayo,
Hali yake pia kimo cha,
mwenyewe ni sawa.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> 
*Kumbe mkate wa malaika,
Huwalisha wasafiri,
Kweli mkate wa wana,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Usitupwe kwa mbwa,
Hii mifano ya zamani, 
Hutolewa mwana Isaka,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Na kondoo kuchinjwa pasaka,
Pia mana ya jangwani.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Mchungaji wetu mwema, 
Yesu utuhurumie,
Utuchunge utulinde,
Ee Mchungaji wetu mwema,
Tuonyeshe  mema yako,
Huko kwenye wazima.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Mchungaji wetu mwema,
Ee Mwenyezi na Mjuaji,
Mwenye kutuchunga hapa,
Tujalie pia huko, 
Tushiriki meza moja,
Na raia wa mbinguni.  </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Amina.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> 
SHANGILIO LA INJILI  							Yohane 6:51</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya. 		Aleluya.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Mimi ndimi mkate wa uzima ulioshuka toka mbinguni, asema Bwana; aulaye mkate huu ataishi milele.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SEKWENSIA
"},{Guid:"jXueFc9dw06XDZWVzquT3Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SEQUENCE “LAUDA SION, SALVATORE”</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384> 
Sion kumia mũhonokia
Mũthamaki na Mũrĩithi
Na Thaburi na nyĩmbo.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mũkumie ta ũrĩa wahota
Nĩ akĩrĩte ũkumio wothe
Ndũngĩmũkumia kũigana.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Ũmũthĩ nĩ tũinĩre mũno
Mũgate ũrĩ muoyo 
Na ũrĩ na ũgima.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ũrĩa kũna Yesu aheire
Atũme ikũmi na erĩ
Irio-inĩ cia mũthia.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ũkumio mũhingu ũiguo
Wa ũkeni na wĩ riri
Ũcanjamũre ngoro.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Amu ũmũthĩ gwĩ thigũkũũ nene
Ya kũririkana, Ekaristi ya mbere
Irio-inĩ cia mũthia.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Metha-inĩ ya Mũthamaki mwerũ Paska njerũ ya watho mwerũ
Yanina Paska ya tene.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ũndũ mwerũ weheria mũkũrũ
Kĩrĩa kĩa ma, kĩeheria mũhianano
Ũtheri weheria nduma.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ũrĩa Kristũ ekire tene
Agĩtwatha twĩkage guo
Tũkĩmũririkana.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Tũrutĩtwo nĩ Kanitha
Tũrutaga igongona
Mũgate na Dibai.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Wĩtĩkia wa Akristũ nĩ ũyũ
Mũgate ũtuĩkaga Mwĩrĩ
Na dibai Thakame.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Tũtekuona kana kũhutia
Nĩ twĩtĩkĩtie na hinya
Kĩama gĩkĩ kĩnene.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ tuonaga mũhuanĩre
Wa mũgate na dibei
No nĩ Yesu ũrĩ ho.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Mwĩrĩ nĩ irio, Thakame ya kũnyua
No Kristũ eho mũgima
O thĩinĩ wa o kĩmwe</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ndangĩnyiha nĩ kũrĩo
Ndegaĩka nĩ kwenyũrũo
Amũkĩrũo e mũgima.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩo nĩ ũmwe kana ngiri
Othe marĩe ũndũ ũmwe
Na Yesu ndangĩthira</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Marĩaga ega na oru
No maciaro ti ũndũ ũmwe
Gĩkuũ kana ũgima.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Gĩkuũ kũrĩ oru ũgima kũrĩ ega No wone marĩa ũndũ ũmwe
No matigana atĩa.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>O na Hostia yenyũrũo
Ndũkae kũgĩa na nganja
Ririkana Yesu eho
Kenyũ-inĩ e mũgima</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu ndagayũkanagio
No mũhuanĩre guo wiki
Na ũhingu na mũigana
Wa Yesu ndũnyihaga.</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>Oneni mũgate wa Araika
Ũtuĩkĩte irio cia agendi
Kũna mũgate wa ciana
Ndũkanaheo ngui.</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgate warathirũo tene
Rĩrĩa Isaaka arutagwo igongona
Na ndũrũme ya Paska ĩgĩthĩnjwo
Na manna ma werũ-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Mũrĩithi mwega, mũgate wa ma
Yesu ũtuiguire tha
Wee tũrĩithie  no tũgitĩre
Wee tũma tũkona wega
Bũrũri wa Ikenero.</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>Wee mwene ũũgĩ na ũhoti wothe
Ũtũrĩithagia ithuĩ andũ</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>Ũtwĩte kũu gwaku mũciĩ
Ũtũtue agai na aikari
A mũciĩ wa Atheru.</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384> 
Nĩ gũtuĩke guo. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							John 6:51
			
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ekuuga atĩ; Niĩ ndĩ mũgate ũrĩ muoyo ũrĩa woimire igũrũ;</s>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1384> mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩrĩa mũgate ũyũ nĩ agatũũra mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SEQUENCE"},{Guid:"pw017rm7bEOS+1L/GrtABQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Laud, O Zion, your salvation, 
Laud with hymns of exultation,
Christ, your king and shepherd true:</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Bring him all the praise you know,
He is more than you bestow,
Never can you reach his due.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Special theme for glad thanksgiving
Is the quick’ning and the living
Bread today before you set:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>From his hands of old partaken,
As we know, by faith unshaken,
Where the Twelve at supper met.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Full and clear ring out your chanting,
Joy nor sweetest grace be wanting,
From your heart let praises burst:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>For today the feast is holden,
When the institution olden
Of that supper was rehearsed.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Here the new law’s new oblation,
By the new king’s revelation,
Ends the form of ancient rite:</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Now the new the old effaces,
Truth away the shadow chases,
Light dispels the gloom of night.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>What he did at supper seated,
Christ ordained to be repeated, 
His memorial ne’er to cease:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>And his rule for guidance taking,
Bread and wine we hallow, making 
Thus our sacrifice of peace.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>This the truth each Christian learns,
Bread into his flesh he turns,
To his precious blood the wine:</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Sight has fail’d, nor thought conceives,
But a dauntless faith believes,
Resting on a pow’r divine.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Here beneath these signs are hidden 
Priceless things to sense forbidden;
Signs, not things are all we see:</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Blood is poured and flesh is broken,
Yet in either wondrous token
Christ entire we know to be.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Whoso of this food partakes,
Does not rend the Lord nor breaks;
Christ is whole to all that taste:</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Thousands are, as one, receivers,
One, as thousands of believers,
Eats of him  who cannot waste.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Bad and good the feast are sharing, 
Of what divers dooms preparing,
Endless death, or  endless life.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Life to these, to those damnation,
See how like participation
Is with unlike issues rife.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>When the sacrament is broken,
Doubt not, but believe ’tis spoken
Thant each sever’d outward token
Doth the very whole contain.</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>Nought the precious gift divides,
Breaking but the sign betides
Jesus still the same abides,
Still unbroken does remain.</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>*Lo! the angel’s food is given 
To the pilgrim who has striven;
See the children’s bread from heaven,
Which on dogs may not be spent.</s>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1384>Truth the ancient types fulfilling,
Isaac bound, a victim willing,
Paschal lamb, its life blood spilling,
Manna to the fathers sent.</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>Very bread, good shepherd, tend us,
Jesu, of your love befriend us,
You refresh us, you defend us,
Your eternal goodness send us
In the land of life to see.</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>You who all things can and know,
Who on earth such food bestow,</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>Grant us with your saints, though lowest,
Where the heav’nly feast you show,
Fellow heirs and guests to be 
Amen. Alleluia.</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>ALLELUIA								John 6:51
			
Alleluia.  Alleluia.</s>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1384>I am the living bread which came down from heaven, says the Lord; if any one eats this bread he will live for ever.</s>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SEQUENCE 
"},{Guid:"WaLDITENXkuwxhd+mhaqGw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SEQUENCE (Prose text)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>To the Paschal Victim let Christians offer a sacrifice of praise.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>The Lamb redeemed the sheep.
Christ, sinless, reconciled sinners to the Father.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Death and life were locked together in a unique struggle.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Life’s captain died; now he reigns, never more to die.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Tell us, Mary, “What did you see on the way?”</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>“I saw angels who gave witness; 
the cloths too which once had covered head and limbs.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>“Christ my hope has arisen. 
He will go before his own into Galilee.”</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>We know that Christ has indeed risen from the dead.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Do you, conqueror and king, have mercy on us.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Amen. Alleluia.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"Verse 22
<s1384>ALLELUIA	</s>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia, Alleluia</s>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1384>Christ, our Paschal Lamb, has been sacrificed; let us, therefore, celebrate the festival in the Lord.</s>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SEQUENCE (Prose text)
"},{Guid:"ZE3Z5o1kS06lMxDnmKb+1Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SEQUENCE</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu Kristũ atarĩ na wĩhia – Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ikua na ũtũũro igĩcemanio ikĩrũa
Mũnene wa ũtũũro arĩ mũkuũ agĩathana arĩ muoyo</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu Kristũ atarĩ na wĩhia – Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Twĩre Maria: wonire kĩ njĩra-inĩ?
Nĩ ndonire mbĩrĩra ya Kristũ arĩ muoyo – na ngĩona ũkumio wa mũriũku.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu Kristũ atarĩ na wĩhia – Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Araika marĩ aira, matama ma nguo
Kristũ mwĩhoko wakwa, nĩ ariũkĩte. Nĩ akamatongoria Galilea</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu Kristũ atarĩ na wĩhia – Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ithuĩ nĩ tũĩ Kristũ ti itherũ - Nĩ ariũkĩte kuuma kũrĩ akuũ: 
Wee mũnene mũcindani, ũtũigwĩre tha.  Nĩ gũtuĩke guo</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Akristũ makumie – Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu Kristũ atarĩ na wĩhia – Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI						       1 Akorintho 5:7-8</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya,         Alleluya			   </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu Paska iitũ nĩ athĩnjĩtwo.  Rekei tũgĩe na thigũkũ thĩinĩ wa Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SEQUENCE
"},{Guid:"8uETE0hi+k2feWGM6tNhLQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>SEQUENCE:</s></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>1.	Ũkĩra Muoyo Mũtheru
Rekia mĩrũri mĩerũ
Ĩtũtheragie ngoro
Tuonwo tũrĩ ahoro</s></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>2.	Ũka wee mwendi witũ
Aria na ngoro ciitũ
Ũka tũtikũrega
Ũrĩ mũthingu mwega.</s></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>3.	Ũka mũguni wa andũ
Tũtigathĩne handũ
Tũkenage ithuothe
Gũkinya hĩndĩ ciothe.</s></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>4.	Wahũnia mũndũ ahũtiĩ
Wanyotora ũnyotiĩ
Wanogora mĩnoga
Kĩĩ gĩothe ũkaruga</s></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>5.	Ũtheri ũkĩhenia
Nĩwe ũgĩtũkenia
Ũtherie ngoro ciitũ
Ĩtĩkia ũhoro witũ.</s></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>6.	Andũ marĩ gũkwaga 
matũũraga na njaga
njaga ya indo ciothe
Na ya moguni mothe</s></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>7.	Ũngwatie ũrugarĩ
Ndikwenda heho narĩ
Ũrihũre ũthitu
Njũhĩgia ndĩ mũritu</s></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>8.	Wanyona ndĩ mũregi
Ũngucie ndige ũregi 
Hehũra ndĩ mũhehu 
Ngarũra niĩ mwĩhu </s></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>9.	Mũgwanja wa mawega
Nĩ wa andũ makarega
Njiriri kana guoya
Hingo magĩkũhoya</s></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>10.	Ũtũhe kĩhurũko
Gĩa thutha wa mĩinũko
Amu Wee wike mwega
Ũgĩtũkenia wega.
Nĩ gũtuĩke guo
 </s></b>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI		</s></b>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>			    
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></b>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>Ũkĩra Muoyo Mũtheru, ũiyũrie ngoro cia etĩkĩa aku na ũmagwatie thĩinĩ wao mwaki wa rũendo rũaku.</s></b>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<b><s1384></s></b><b><s2769>Alleluia
		</s></b>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
