Text:"Shukrani zetu Baba"},{Guid:"soFxwJQflkWUuNh1s9Unog",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Silent night, holy night!
Sleeps the world; hid from sight,</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Mary and Joseph in stable bare
Watch o'er the Child beloved and fair,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Sleeping in heavenly rest,
Sleeping in heavenly rest.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Silent night, holy night!
Shepherds first saw the light,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Heard resounding clear and long,
Far and near, the angel-song:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>'Christ the Redeemer is here,
Christ the Redeemer is here.'</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Silent night, holy night!
Son of God, O how bright
Love is smiling from Thy face!</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Strikes for us now the hour of grace,
Saviour, since Thou art born,
Saviour, since Thou art born.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
Text:"Silent night"},{Guid:"01pvs/k/3kCQ/cjJYzbYPQ",Verses:[{
