Text:"<fArial Black></f><fArial Black><s1384>Siwezi  baki kubaki kitini, lazima ninyanyuke, 
nikamtolee Mungu
Kwani amenijalia mengi yasiyo idadi</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><fArial Black><s1384>Mahangaiko ya njaa sipati  Zawadi hii yatoka kwa Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><fArial Black><s1384>Kwa nini nisinyanyuke nikamshukuru Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><fArial Black><s1384>Siwezi  baki kubaki kitini, lazima ninyanyuke, 
nikamtolee Mungu
