Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA  						1 Samueli 3:3b-10. 19</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha kwanza cha Samueli</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zile: Samueli alikuwa amelala katika hekalu la Bwana,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> pale lilipokuwapo sanduku la Bwana.
Bwana akaita: \"Samueli, Samueli,\" naye akaitikia,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> \"Mimi hapa!\" Naye akamwendea Eli kwa haraka akasema, \"Mimi hapa, kwa kuwa uliniita.” </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Eli akasema, \"Sikukuita, nenda ukalale.\" Akaenda kulala. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Bwana akaita tena: Samueli, Samueli!\" Naye akamwendea tena Eli, na kusema, \"Mimi hapa, kwa maana uliniita!\"</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Naye akajibu, akasema, \"Sikukuita mwanangu, nenda ukalale.\"</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Wakati ule Samueli alikuwa bado hajamfahamu Bwana, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na neno la Bwana lilikuwa bado halijafunuliwa kwake. Bwana akamwita tena Samueli mara ya tatu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Hapo aliamka na kumwendea Eli akasema, \"Mimi hapa, kwa maana uliniita.\"</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Ndipo Eli akatambua ya kuwa Bwana ndiye aliyemwita kijana. Akamwambia Samueli, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>\"Nenda ukalale na utakapoitwa, utasema, 'Nena Bwana kwa kuwa mtumishi wako anasikia.’”</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Basi akaenda tena kulala mahali pake.
Bwana akaja, akasimama, na kuita kama awali:</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> \"Samueli, Samueli!\" Ndipo Samueli akaitikia, \"Nena Bwana kwa kuwa mtumishi wako anasikia.\" </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Samueli akakua, na Bwana alikuwa pamoja naye, wala hakuacha neno lolote lianguke chini.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"vkGUS4F6RkuLFbwfgBNAkw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA  						Yeremia 33 14 16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Yeremia,</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Tazama, Siku zitakuja asema Bwana - nitakapotimiza neno njema nililotangaza</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ya Juu ya nyumba ya Israeli na juu ya nyumba ya Yuda.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Katika siku zile na wakati ule, nitamwoteshea Daudi mzao mtakatifu naye atatenda hukumu na haki katika nchi.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zile Yuda ataokolewa na Yerusalemu utakaa salama.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Na mji utaitwa jina hili: \"Bwana - haki - yetu.\"</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"Kld5f3rqbUC+8iM7rkhqwQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA 							Hesabu 6:22-27</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Hesabu</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana alimwambia Musa: \"Mwambie Haruni na wanawe: 
Hivi ndivyo mtakavyowabariki wana wa Israeli. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mtawaambia:Bwana akubariki na kukulinda!
Bwana akuangazie uso wake, na kukufadhili!</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana akuelekezee uso wake na kukuletea amani!
Waliweke hivyo jina langu juu ya wana wa Israeli,
nami nitawabariki.\"</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"DYnda6MRR0SSSR9O67QFzw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA  							Ezekieli 2:2-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Ezekieli</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zile:
Roho ikaniingia, kama nilivyoambiwa, ikanisimamisha, nikamsikia mwenye kusema nami.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Akaniambia: \"Mwana wa mtu, nakutuma kwa wana wa lsraelı, kwa taifa la waasi walioniasi mimi.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Mpaka siku ya leo, wao na baba zao wamenikataa mimi, wana hawa wana nyuso kaidi na mioyo migumu,-</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ninakutuma kwao, nawe utawaambia: Bwana Mungu amesema hivi.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nao wakisikiliza, au wakikataa kusikiliza - maana wao ni taifa lenye kuasi- watatambua kuna nabii katikati yao.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"y05CS0kNkUe/lMTNDwnlkQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA  						Mwanzo 15:5-12, 17-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Wakati ule: Bwana alimleta Abramu nje, akasema: “Tazama mbinguni, hesabu nyota, kama waweza kuzihesabu.”</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Akamwambia: \"Ndivyo uzao wako utakavyokuwa.” Abramu akamwamini Bwana, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>naye Bwana akamhesabia jambo hilo kuwa haki. Akamwambia: \"Mimi ndimi Bwana niliyekutoa toka Uru wa Wakaldayo, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nikupe nchi hii iwe yako.\"
Abramu akamwambia, \"Ee Bwana, nitajuaje ya kuwa nitapewa  iwe yangu?\"</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Akamwambia: Unipatie ndama wa miaka mitatu, mbuzi jike wa miaka mitatu, kondoo dume wa miaka mitatu, hua na mwana njiwa. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Abramu akamletea wanyama hao wote, akawapasua katikati, akaweka kila kipande kuelekeana na kingine;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> lakini ndege hakuwapasua. Na tai wakaishukia ile mizoga, lakini Abramu akawafukuza. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Jua lilipokuwa likishuka, usingizi mzito ukamshika Abramu, na hofu na giza vikamwangukia.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Jua lilipokwisha kushuka, na giza kuenea, tanuri ya moshi na mwenge wa moto vikapita kati ya vipande vile vya nyama.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Siku ile Bwana akafanya agano na Abramu akisema:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>“Nimeupatia uzao wako nchi hii, kutoka mto wa Misri, mpaka mto mkubwa, Mto Eufrate.\"</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"Cc7i3Jv58ky8+TR6TE9/tQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA                       					Kutoka 20:1-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Kutoka</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zile: Mungu alisema maneno haya yote: \"Ndimi Bwana Mungu wako, niliyekutoa katika nchi ya Misri, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>katika nyumba ya watumwa. Usiwe na miungu mingine ila yangu.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Usijifanyizie sanamu ya kuchonga wala mfano wa kitu chochote kilicho juu mbinguni, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>wala kilicho chini duniani, wala kilicho majini chini ya dunia. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Usizisujudie sanamu hizo wala usizitumikie, kwa maana mimi, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana Mungu wako, mimi ni Mungu mwenye
wivu, ninayeyapatiliza maovu ya baba juu ya watoto,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> hata kizazi cha tatu na cha nne cha wanichukiao, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>lakini nawafanyia rehema vizazi maelfu vya wale wanipendao na kuzishika amri zangu. 
Usilitaje bure jina la Bwana Mungu wako, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>kwa maana Bwana hataacha kumwadhibu mwenye kulitaja jina lake bure.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ikumbuke siku ya Sabato, uitakase. Siku sita fanya kazi, ufanye kazi zako zote, lakini siku ya saba ni Sabato ya Bwana,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> Mungu wako. Siku hiyo usifanye kazi yoyote, wewe, wala mwana wako, wala binti yako, wala mtumishi wako, </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>wala mjakazi wako, wala Wanyama wako wa kazi, wala mgeni anayekaa kwako. Maana kwa siku sita Bwana alifanya mbingu,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> nchi, bahari na vyote vilivyomo, lakini alipumzika siku ya saba. </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Ndiyo maana Bwana ameibariki siku ya Sabato na kuifanya takatifu.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>Waheshimu baba yako na mama yako, upate kuwa na maisha marefu katika nchi upewayo na Bwana Mungu wako.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Usiue.Usizini.Usiibe.
Usimshuhudie jirani yako uongo.
Usiitamani nyumba ya jirani yako.</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>  Usimtamani mke wa jirani yako, wala mtumishi wake, wala mjakazi wake, wala ngómbe wake,</s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384> wala punda wake, wala kitu chochote kilicho mali ya jirani yako.”</s>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"ujDLYS0/skK7z+DfIFkmcQ",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana Yesu, u Mwana Baba, mpendwa milele. </s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uliridhisha upendo wako kwa watoto, kwa </s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuwakumbatia, kuwawekea mikono na kuwabariki. </s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunashukuru kwa ajili ya zawadi ya watoto, na </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tunakuomba uwashushie neema yako na baraka yako.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wawezeshe wakue wakiiga mfano wako, na wafahamu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwamba upo katika Ekaristi.
Twaomba wakupende wewe </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuliko yote, na wajitole kutumikia Ufalme wa Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa moyo wote.
Kwa msaada wako, wazazi </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na walezi na wawe mifano bora ya imani na maadili.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wape nguvu, hekima na ujasiri wa kustahimili </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kushinda changamoto za malezi.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Unayeishi na kutawala milele na milele. Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s2769>V/. Maria mtakatifu, Mama wa shauri njema;</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s2769>R/. Utuombee.</s></f></b>"}],
Text:"SALA KWA AJILI YA WATOTO"},{Guid:"XadZcpLzRU64kRWlPIpfvA",Verses:[{
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA 						           
Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya"},{ID:2,
Text:"Neno la Bwana alilomwambia mfalme Sairusi, ndiye mpakwa wake,"},{ID:3,
Text:" aliyemshika mkono wake, ili kuwatiisha mataifa chini ya amri yake, na kulegeza uwezo wa wafalme;"},{ID:4,
Text:" ili kufungua milango mbele yake, hata mlango mmoja usiwe umefungwa. "},{ID:5,
Text:"Nimekuita kwa jina lako kwa ajili ya mtumishi wangu Yakobo, na ya Israeli mteule wangu,"},{ID:6,
Text:" nikikukuza ijapokuwa hunijui. Ndimi Bwana, wala hakuna mwingine; hakuna Mungu ila mimi tu."},{ID:7,
Text:" ljapokuwa hunifahamu, nimekufungia silaha, wapate kufahamu toka mawio ya jua mpaka machweo yake, "},{ID:8,
Text:"ya kuwa hakuna mwingine zaidi ya mimi.  Ndimi Bwana, na hakuna mwingine."},{ID:9,
Text:"Neno la Bwana."}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"M5ST4ynmMEOl0BHwZ3rwbQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA 
				Kumbukumbu la Torati 6:2-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Kumbukumbu la Torati</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Musa aliwaambia wana wa Israeli, akisema, \"Umwogope Bwana
Mungu wako siku zote za maisha yako,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ukishika maagizo yake yote na
amri zake nilizokuagiza leo hivi, utakuwa na maisha marefu, wewe,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> mwanao na wana wa mwanao. Basi, ewe Israeli, ungeweza kusikiliza, kushika na kutenda yale,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> yatakayokuletea heri na kuongezeka, jinsi Bwana Mungu wa baba zako, alivyokuahidia,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>akikuwekea nchi ijaayo maziwa na asali.
Sikiliza, ee Israeli! Bwana Mungu wetu, ndiye Bwana peke yake!</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Umpende Bwana Mungu wako, kwa moyo wako wote, na kwa roho yako yote na kwa nguvu zako zote. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Maneno hayo ninayokuagiza leo yawe moyoni mwako.\"</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"wzIYYrkd0k+JkYkvg4BMvg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA 					   Isaya 40:1- 5, 9-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Watulizeni, wapeni tulizo watu wangu, asema Mungu wenu. Semeni na moyo wa Yerusalemu,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> utangazieni ya kwamba: huduma yake ngumu imekwisha, dhambi yake imeondolewa, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>maana kwa mkono wa Bwana amepokea adhabu maradufu kwa maovu yake yote. Mtu analia: </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>tengenezeni jangwani njia ya Bwana! Nyosheni nyikani barabara kwa Mungu wetu! Kila bonde lifukiwe,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> kila mlima na kilima kishushwe, Njia zenye kupotoka zinyoshwe, na njia zenye mashimo zisawazishwe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Hapo utukufu wa Bwana utafunuliwa, na watu wote watauona mara; maana kinywa cha Bwana kimenena haya.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Panda juu ya mlima mrefu, uutangaziye Sioni habari njema!  Paza sauti kwa nguvu, uutangaziye Yerusalemu habari njema! Paza sauti, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>usiogope!  Sema kwa miji ya Yuda: Tazama, Mungu wenu! Yupo hapa Bwana Mungu: anakuja kwa uwezo, na mkono wake utatawala;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> tuzo ya ushindi wake litamsindikiza, mateka yake yatamtangulia. Kama mchungaji, atachunga kundi lake; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>mkononi mwake atawakusanya wanakondoo, atawachukua kifuani mwake, atawaongoza kondoo wenye kunyonyesha.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA "},{Guid:"FGZjUGsL70mffH7iFjkzFw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"sky1.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>KIUMIA GIA THUTHA WA EPIPHANIA UBATITHU WA YESU KRISTU</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"lake1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"lake2.JPG"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Isaia 42:1-4,6-7</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>	 
Mwathani  ekuuga ũũ: ĩno nĩyo ndungata yakwa ĩrĩa ndiirĩrĩire; </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩyo ĩrĩa ndĩĩthurĩire, na nĩyo ĩkenagia ngoro yakwa: </s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ndĩmĩikũrũkĩirie muoyo wakwa ũkamĩhuba, </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩyo ĩkarehithĩrie ndũrĩrĩ cira wa kĩhooto.</s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndĩkaanĩrĩra, o na kana ĩhaicie kayũ kayo na igũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o na kana ĩtũme mũgambo wayo ũigwo njĩra-inĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kamũrangi kagondoku ndĩgakoina, </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana rũtambĩ rũa ũguta rũgĩtoga ĩrũhorie.
  </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gũtua ĩgatuanagĩra cira wa ma. Ndĩkahwererekera, </s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana yume tha, </s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ĩgakorũo ĩtũmĩte gũkũ thĩ kũgĩe cira wa kĩhooto; </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ arĩa matũũraga ithama-inĩ magaikaraga metereire watho wayo. </s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ niĩ ngwĩtĩte o ta ũrĩa nyonaga kwerekeire, </s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ ngakũnyita guoko na  ngũmenyagĩrĩre,</s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ngũheane nĩ getha ũtuĩke wa kũrĩkanĩra kĩrĩkanĩro na andũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ũtuĩke ũtheri wa gũtherera andũ a ndũrĩrĩ;</s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o na ningĩ nĩ getha ũhingũrage maitho marĩa matumumu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao andũ arĩa mohetwo ũmarutage kĩoho-inĩ,  </s></f>"},{ID:9,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nao arĩa maikarĩte nduma-inĩ-rĩ,
ũmarutage korokoro-inĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"sky1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Thaburi 29: 1-2;3-4;8-10</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ ariũ a Mũrungu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e hinya;</s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> rahai Mwathani mũkĩgane riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake; </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thathaiyai Mwathani mwĩgemetie na ũgemu ũrĩa wa ũtheru.</s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ kũgamba ũragamba na kũu iria-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũrungu, ũcio wĩ riri, nĩ hĩndĩ egũkĩruruma,</s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o we Mwathani akaruruma kũu igũrũ rĩa maaĩ maingĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũgambo wa Mwathani wĩna hinya; </s></f>"},{ID:9,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ mũkaru o gũkara.</s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:9,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ ũthingithagia werũ; </s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgatũma mĩtitũ ĩhũrũrũke o gũthera; Mwathani-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o hingo ĩrĩa ya Mũiyũro wa Maaĩ; ĩĩ-ni, </s></f>"},{ID:11,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani aikaraga  ho e mũthamaki wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:11,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Atumwo  10:34-38</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"sky1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"sky1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Peter agĩitĩka kwaria akiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti-itherũ ndĩ kuona atĩ Ngai ndatĩagĩra andũ maũthĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no thĩinĩ wa ndũrĩrĩ ciothe mũndũ ũrĩa ũmwĩtigagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ageka maũndũ ma ũthingu nĩ etĩkagĩrũo nĩwe. </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Atĩrĩrĩ: Ũhoro ũrĩa aarekeirie ciana cia Israeli, </s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũrĩa wa kũhunjanĩria ndeto njega cia thayũ ũrĩa wonekaga na Yesu Kristũ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nake nĩwe Mwathani wa guothe.  Ũhoro ũcio-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyuĩ nĩ mũũĩ, naguo nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"flybird2.jpg"}},
