Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana Mungu amenizibua sikio langu; nami sikukataa, sikurudi nyuma.
Niliwatolea mgongo wangu wale walionipiga, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>na mashavu yangu kwa wale walioning'oa ndevu; wala sikuuficha uso wangu ili usifedheheshwe na kutemewa mate.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana Mungu ndiye anayenisaidia, ndiyo maana sihangaiki na hayo; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ndiyo maana nimefanya uso wangu nmgumu kama jiwe, najua ya kwamba sitaona aibu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Anayenipatia haki yu karibu. Ni nani atakayeshindana nami? Twende tusimame barazani pamoja.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ni nani atakayenishtaki hukumuni? Na anikaribie basi. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Tazama, Bwana Mungu ndiye msaada wangu; ni nani atakayenihukumu kuwa mkosa haki?</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
