Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Danieli</s></f></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Niliangalia katika maono yangu ya usiku, na tazama, </s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Mmoja kama mwana wa mtu akaja katika </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>mawingu ya mbingu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>akaendelea mpaka akamfikie yule Mzee wa Kale, </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>akakaribishwa mbele yake.</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Akapewa utawala, utukufu na ufalme:</s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>watu wa makabila yote na mataifa yote </s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>na lugha zote wakamtumikia. </s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Utawala wake ulikuwa utawala wa milele usiopita,</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076> na ufalme wake hautaangamizwa.</s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Neno la Bwana.</s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 				Zaburi 93:1ab. 1c-2. 5(K 1a)</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>K. Bwana ametamalaki, amejivika adhama.</s></f></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Bwana ametamalaki, amejivika adhama</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Bwana amejivika utukufu,
amejifunga uweza. (K)</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>K. Bwana ametamalaki, amejivika adhama.</s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Ameukaza ulimwengu usitikisike.</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Kiti chako ni imara tangu mwanzo;</s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>tangu milele wewe upo, ee Mungu! (K)</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>K. Bwana ametamalaki, amejivika adhama.</s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Maagizo yako yaaminika kabisa;</s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>nyumba yako imepambwa utakatifu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>ee Bwana, kwa siku zisizo na mwisho. (K)</s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>K. Bwana ametamalaki, amejivika adhama.</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>SOMO LA PILI								Ufunuo 1:5-8</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Somo katika kitabu cha Ufunuo wa Mtakatifu Yohane</s></f></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Yesu Kristo ni shahidi mwaminifu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>mzaliwa wa kwanza wa wafu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>na mkuu wa wafalme wa dunia.</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Yeye  anatupenda, </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>na ametufutia dhambi zetu kwa damu yake. </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Ametufanya kuwa ufalme, tena makuhani </s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>kwa Mungu aliye Baba yake:</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>yeye astahili utukufu na mamlaka </s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>daima na milele. Amina.
Tazameni,</s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>anakuja kati ya mawingu. Kila jicho litamwona, </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>hata wale waliomtoboa. </s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Na makabila yote ya dunia yataomboleza </s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>kwa sababu yake.</s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Naam. Amina.</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>\"Mimi ndimi Alfa na Omega\" - </s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Mwanzo na Mwisho - </s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>asema Bwana Mungu \"aliyeko, </s></f></b>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>aliyekuwako na anayekuja, Mwenyezi.\"</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Neno la Bwana.</s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>SHANGILIO LA INJILI  						Marko 11:9, 10</s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Aleluya.  	Aleluya.</s></f></b>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Mbarikiwa anayekuja kwa jina la Bwana! </s></f></b>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Umebarikiwa ufalme ujao wa baba yetu Daudi!</s></f></b>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Aleluya.</s></f></b>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>INJILI  
Yohane 18:33b-37</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Wakati ule:</s></f></b>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Pilato alimwambia Yesu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>“Je, wewe u Mfalme wa Wayahudi?\"</s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Yesu akajibu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>\"Unasema hivi kwa nafsi yako, </s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>au ni watu wengine waliokupa habari yangu?\"</s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Pilato akajibu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>\"Ni Myahudi mimi? </s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Ni taifa lako na makuhani wakuu waliokutoa kwangu. </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Umefanya nini?\" </s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Yesu akajibu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>“Ufalme wangu si wa ulimwengu huu</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Kama ufalme wangu ungekuwa wa ulimwengu huu,</s></f></b>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>watumishi wangu wangenipigania, </s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>nisije nikatolewa kwa Wayahudi.</s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Lakini ufalme wangu si wa hapa.\" </s></f></b>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Basi Pilato akamwambia, </s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>\"Wewe u mfalme, basi?”
Yesu akajibu, </s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>“Wewe unasema ya kuwa mimi ni mfalme.</s></f></b>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Mimi nimezaliwa kwa ajili hiyo,</s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>na kwa ajili ya hiyo nimekuja ulimwenguni</s></f></b>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>ndiyo nishuhudie ukweli.</s></f></b>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s3076>Kila aliye wa ukweli husikia sauti yangu.\"</s></f></b>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black></f><b><fArial Black><s3076>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f></b>"}],
Text:"SHEREHE YA BWANA WETU YESU KRISTU MFALME WA ULIMWENGU"},{Guid:"FC5brciqEkuiuHaI8H+w1g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA					                        Isaya 62:1-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii  Isaya</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa ajili ya Sioni, sitanyamaza, kwa ajili ya Yerusalemu sitatulia, mpaka haki yake itokee kama mapambazuko, na wokovu wake uwake kama mwenge.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  
Hapo mataifa wataiona haki yako, nao wafalme wote utukufu wako; nawe utaitwa jina jipya, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>lenye kutajwa kwa kinywa cha Bwana. Utakuwa taji lenye kumetameta mkononi mwa Bwana, na kilemba cha kifalme mkononi mwa Mungu wako.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Hutaitwa tena, “Yule alieachwa,” wala nchi yako haitaitwa tena, “Jangwa.” 
Bali watakuita,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> “Furaha yangu imo ndani yake,” na nchi yako, “Bibi harusi wangu,” Maana Bwana amependezwa nawe,  na nchi yako itaolewa naye.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Kama kijana anavyomwoa bikira, hivyo aliyekujenga atakuoa wewe; na kama bwana harusi anavyomfurahia bibi harusi, hivyo Mungu wako atafurahishwa nawe.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Mungu</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA	"},{Guid:"+xYJq4AUtk+OKFWufZyq2g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA					Matendo ya Mitume 1:1-11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Mwanzo wa kitabu cha Matendo ya Mitume</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Katika kitabu changu cha kwanza, Theofilo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nilisimulia yote aliyofanya na kufundisha Yesu toka mwanzo mpaka siku alipowapa mitume aliowachagua </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>agizo kwa nguvu ya Roho Mtakatifu na kuchukuliwa mbinguni. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Kwao pia alijionyesha kwa uthibitisho mwingi ya kuwa yu hai baada ya mateso yake, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>kwa muda wa siku arobaini aliwatokea na kusema nao juu ya ufalme wa Mungu.
Alipokuwa mezani pamoja nao,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> aliwaamuru wasitoke Yerusalemu, bali waingoje \"ahadi ya Baba, mliyosikia kutoka kwangu; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>yaani Yohane alibatiza kwa maji, bali ninyi mtabatizwa kwa Roho Mtakatifu baada ya siku chache.\"</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Hapo wale waliokusanyika wakamwuliza, \"Bwana, je, wakati huu ndipo utakaporudisha upya ufalme wa Israeli?\"</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Akawajibu,
\"Si shauri lenu kujua nyakati kamili alizoweka Baba kwa uwezo wake.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Lakini mtapokea nguvu ya Roho Mtakatifu atakayewashukia, na mtakuwa mashahidi wangu Yerusalemu,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> na katika nchi yote ya Yudea, Samaria, na hata miisho ya dunia.\"</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Baada  ya maneno hayo, akainuliwa, mbele ya macho yao, na wingu likampokea wasimwone tena.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Walipokazia bado macho juu mbinguni alikoenda yeye, </s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>watu wawili wenye mavazi meupe walisimama
ghafula pembeni mwao. Wakasema, 
“Enyi watu wa Galilaya,</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384> mbona mmesimama na kutazama juu mbinguni? </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>Huyu Yesu aliyechukuliwa mbinguni kutoka kwenu atakuja tena jinsi hiyo hiyo mlivyomwona akipaa mbinguni.\"</s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA	"},{Guid:"GQ1GO6LlTEegsmcriLWGtg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA				Kumbu kumbu la Torati 26:4-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo  katika kitabu cha Kumbu kumbu la Torati</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Musa aliwaambia watu:
”Naye kuhani atakipokea kikapu mkononi mwako atakiweka chini mbele ya altare ya BWANA Mungu wako. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nawe utasema maneno haya mbele ya BWANA Mungu wako: ‘Baba yangu alikuwa Mwaramu aliye tangatanga huko na huko akashuka Misri,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> nakukaa huko, akiwa na watu wachache, lakini huko akageuka kuwa taifa kubwa lenye nguvu na watu wengi. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Halafu wamisri wakatutenda vibaya, wakatudhulumu na kututumikisha utumwa mgumu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Hapo tuka mlilia BWANA Mungu wa baba zetu. Naye BWANA akasikia sauti yetu, akaona taabu zetu, masumbuko yetu na msiba wetu. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>BWANA akatutoa kutoka Misri kwa mkono wenye nguvu na kwa mkono ulionyoshwa, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>akitenda mambo ya kutisha na miujiza, akatufikisha mahali hapa, akatupatia nchi hii,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> nchi yenye kujaa maziwa na asali. Ewe BWANA, sasa nimeleta malimbuko ya mazao ya udongo uliyo nipa. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Halafu utayaweka mbele ya BWANA Mungu wako nakumwangukia BWANA Mungu wako.\"</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA	"},{Guid:"kLJ9WHjkZk2vQsBUEvMg0g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>
Verse 2
Misa ya Kubariki Mafuta.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>ALHAMISI KATIKA JUMA KUU MWAKA</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>MISA YA KRISMA</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA				                               Isa 61:1-3a,6a,8b-9</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Roho wa Bwana Mungu yu juu yangu, kwa sababu Bwana amenipaka mafuta.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Amenituma niwahubirie maskini habari njema, kuwaponya waliovunjika moyo:</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>kuwatangazia mateka uhuru, na wafungwa kuwa huru, kutangaza mwaka wa rehema ya Bwana,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na siku ya kisasi cha Mungu wetu; kuwafariji wenye uchungu, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>na kuweka juu ya hao waliao Sioni taji badala ya majivu, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>kuwapa mafuta furaha badala ya maombolezo, vazi la sifa badala ya roho nzito.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nanyi mtaitwa, Makuhani wa Bwana;\"  mtapewa jina la, \"Watumishi wa Mungu wetu.\"</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Nitawapa kwa uaminifu tuzo yao, na nitaagana nao agano la milele.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Kizazi chao kitasifiwa kati ya mataifa, na wazao wao kati ya watu; </s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> wote watakaowaona watakubali kuwa, \"Ni kizazi kilichobarikiwa na Bwana.\"</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Mungu</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA	"},{Guid:"cq78a3nIyEiJbpbc+91ULQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA					Yoshua 24:1-2a, 15-17, 18b</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zile: Yoshua aliwakusanya na kuwakutanisha makabila yote ya Israeli huko Shekemu. Akawaita wazee wa Israeli, wakuu wao,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na waamuzi na wasimamizi na wakajipanga mbele ya Mungu.
Yoshua akawaambia watu wote, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>\"Kama hampendezwi na kumtumikia Bwana, basi, chagueni leo hivi mtamtumikia nani:</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> kama ni miungu ile waliyoitumikia mababu zenu huko ng'ambo ya mto: au kama ni miungu ya Waamori ambao nchi yao mnaikalia.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Lakini mimi na nyumba yangu tutamtumikia Bwana.\"
Watu wale wakamjibu, wakisema, \"La hasha, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>iwe mbali nasi kuwa tutamwacha Bwana na kuitumikia miungu mingine! Kwa maana Bwana Mungu wetu,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> yeye ndiye aliyetuokoa sisi na mababu zetu kutoka nchi ya Misri, na katika hiyo nyumba ya utumwa; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>naye ndiye aliyezifanya ishara zile kubwa mbele ya macho yetu na kutulinda katika njia ile yote tuliyosafiria,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na kati ya mataifa yote tuliyopita katikati yao. Kwa hiyo,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> nasi pia tunataka kumtumikia Bwana, kwa maana yeye ndiye Mungu wetu.\"</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA	"},{Guid:"dJ0ZBn878E+sGvFdgSTIXQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA					             1 Wafalme 17:10-16</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha kwanza cha Wafalme</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Siku zile:
Eliya nabii] aliondoka, akaenda zake Sarepta. Alipofika kwenye lango la mji, akamkuta mwanamke mjane akiokota kuni; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>akamwita na kumwambia, \"Nakuomba, uniletee maji kidogo, nipate kunywa.\" Alipokuwa akienda, akamwambia, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>\"Niletee pia kipande cha mkate mkononi mwako.\" Naye akasema, \"Kama aishivyo Bwana, Mungu wako, sina mkate ulio tayari; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>isipokuwa konzi ya unga katika pipa, na mafuta kidogo katika chupa. Nami ninaokota kuni chache, nikajipikie mimi na mwanangu;</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> tule, tukafe.” Eliya akamwambia, \"Usiogope, enenda ukafanye kama ulivyosema. Lakini unifanyizie kwanza, mkate mdogo uniletee.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Kisha ukajitengenezee wewe na mwanao. Kwa maana, Bwana Mungu wa Israeli asema hivi: Lile pipa la unga halitapungua, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>wala ile chupa ya mafuta haitaisha, hata Bwana atakapoinyeshea mvua nchi.\" Mwanamke yule akaondoka, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>akafanya kama Eliya alivyomwambia. Yeye mwenyewe, na mwanawe na Eliya wakala siku nyingi.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Lile pipa la unga halikupunguka, wala ile chupa ya mafuta haikuisha, sawa na neno Bwana alilolisema kwa kinywa cha Eliya.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"SOMO LA KWANZA	"},{Guid:"fHbxCBQaSEOr6D1D8BHf7w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA			         Hekima ya Sulemani 1:13-15; 2:23-24</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Somo katika kitabu cha Hekima ya Sulemani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mungu hakuifanya mauti, wala haufurahii upotevu wa walio hai. Maana aliviumba vitu vyote vipate kuwepo,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na vizazi vya ulimwengu ni vyenye kuleta wokovu; hamna ndani ya hivyo dawa ya kuangamiza,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>wala ufalme wa kuzimu haupo juu ya dunia, maana haki yaishi milele. 
Mungu alimwumba mtu apate kuishi milele; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>naye alimfanya mfano wa hali yake mwenyewe.
Lakini kwa wivu wa Shetani, kifo kiliungia ulimwengu,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na wale walioungana naye hushiriki mauti hayo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Neno la Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
