Text:"<s1384>Ngai watha nyingı̃,nı twagũcokeria ngaatho nıũ̃ndũ wa gwakia thı̃inı̃ wa ndungata yaku Mũkeni Irene Stefani “ Nyaatha”</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384> ũrugarı̃ wa gũtũũra hı̃ndı̃ ciothe thıĩ nı ̃wa Kristũ.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nı ̃ erutıĩ re biũ kwanır̃ ır̃ a injiri na gũtungata andũ arı ̃ na wıh̃ eani wa ũnyina ngı̃nyagia akı̃ruta ũtũũro wake wothe. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Tuhotithie na njır̃a ya ũthaithanı̃ri wake tũtuı̃ke amıc̃ onaria rwendo rwaku, aira a tha ciaku na ũiyũru wa ũtũũro waku.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Twahoya ũguo nıũ̃ndũ wa Kristũ Mwathani Witũ. Nıg̃ ũtuık̃e guo.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"Stefani “ Nyaatha”"},{Guid:"kiHWxUU2ek6TAPi/Q2NhHw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>1. Jesus my Lord my God My All 
    How can I love thee as I ought? 
    And how revere this wondrous gift 
   So far surpassing hope or thought </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Sweet sacrament we thee adore 
O make us love thee more and more
O make us love thee more and more</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>  Had I but May’s sinless heart
To love thee with my dearest king
Oh with what bursts of fervent praise 
Thy goodness Jesus would I sing </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Sweet sacrament we thee adore 
O make us love thee more and more
O make us love thee more and more</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>3. O see with in a creature hand 
The vast creator deigns to be 
Reposing infant like as though 
On Joseph’s arm on Mary’s knee. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>4. Thy body soul and God head all 
O mystery of love divine 
I cannot compass all I have
for all thou hast and art are mine</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Sweet sacrament we thee adore 
O make us love thee more and more
O make us love thee more and more</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>5. Sound, sound his praises higher still 
And come ye Angels to our aid 
Tis God tis God the very God 
Whose power both man and angels made?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Sweet sacrament we thee adore 
O make us love thee more and more
O make us love thee more and more</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
