Text:"<s1384>1.No ndetĩkĩtie ũhoro wake, o na rĩrĩa ndaririe ngiuga,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ thĩnĩkĩte mũno! Arĩa marĩ ũiguano nake-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> ikua rĩao nĩ ũndũ wĩ bata maitho-inĩ ma Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>        ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani o mabũrũri-inĩ ma arĩa me muoyo. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>2.ĩ Mwathani, ti itheru niĩ ndĩ ndungata yaku,</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> ndĩ o ndungata yaku, mwana wa ngombo yaku ya mũndũ wa-nja; wee-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũnjohorete mĩhĩndo.  No ngũrutĩre magongona  ma gũcokia ngatho, ngĩthathaiye rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>          ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani o mabũrũri-inĩ ma arĩa me muoyo. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>3.Ngũkĩhingĩria Mwathani njĩra ĩrĩa ndehĩtire, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>kũhingia ndĩmĩhingie andũ ake othe marĩ ho, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nja-inĩ cia nyũmba ya Mwathani, o thĩinĩ waku, Wee Jerusalemu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"           <s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani o mabũrũri-inĩ ma arĩa me muoyo. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨ"},{Guid:"3ewbm26qj06H4g/q+mq6/w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>chorus	Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova </s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>1.	Gocaai Jehova!
Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova, ũrĩa wĩkenagĩra o mũno nĩ ũndũ wa maathani make.
Mbeũ yake ĩrĩtuĩkaga o ing’ara  bũrũri-inĩ; andũ arĩa arũngĩrĩru, rũciaro rũao nĩ kũrathimwo rũrĩrathimagwo.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>chorus	Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Gwake gũikaraga kwĩ na ũrugarĩ o na ũtonga, naguo ũthingu wake ũtũũraga wĩ mũrũmu o kinya tene.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Acio arũngĩrĩru-rĩ, nĩmoimagĩrĩrũo  nĩ ũtheri me nduma-inĩ, o mũndũ muuma-andũ na wĩ na matha  maingĩ  na nĩ mũthingu.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>chorus	Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>5.	Mũndũ ũrĩa wĩkanaga uuma-andũ  na akohoranĩra, ũcio no wega onaga,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> o ũrĩa ũtabaragĩra maũndũ make  na kĩhooto.
Amu gũtirĩ hingo angĩenyenyeka;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> mũndũ mũthingu nĩ wa gũtũũra aririkainwo  o kinya tene. 
 
chorus	Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Ndangĩĩtigĩra  ũhoro ũrĩa  angĩigua mũũru; ngoro yake nĩĩkindĩire, ĩgakĩĩhoka o Jehova.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Ngoro yake nĩ nũmie, ndangĩigua guoya, kinya akona  ũrĩa  endete harĩ arĩa me muku nake.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>chorus	Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>9.	Nĩatũire aitangaga, akaheaga arĩa aagi; ũthingu wake ũtũũraga ũrũmĩte o kinya tene; </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>rũhĩa rũake no rũikarage  rũambaraire nĩ ũrĩa ekĩrĩirũo.</s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384>chorus	Gũkena nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Jehova </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO 126"},{Guid:"342tzYuRMUeile00RIEKtw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                           Thaburi 91:1-2,10-11,12-13;14-15(K)15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ũrĩa ũtũire ahithĩtwo ũhitho-inĩ wa Ũrĩa-wĩ-Igũrũ-mũno arĩikaraga kĩĩgunyĩ-inĩ kĩa Mwene-Hinya. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ngũkiuga atĩrĩ, ũhoro wa Mwathani, atĩ, nĩwe irahĩro rĩakwa o gwata gĩikaro gĩakwa kĩirigĩre nĩwe Ngai wakwa, ũrĩa ndĩĩhokete.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Gũtikĩrĩ ũũru o na ũrĩkũ ũgakũnyita, gũtirĩ itũhũhũ rĩngĩthengerera hema yaku.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ gũkorũo  nĩ agaatha araika ake nĩ ũndũ waku, makũmenyagĩrĩre ikĩro-inĩ ciaku ciothe.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Marĩgũkuuaga ndayaya na hĩ ciao, ndũkae gũkahĩngwo kũgũrũ nĩ ihiga.  Ũgakinyĩrĩria mũrũthi,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> o na nduĩra; ngatia ĩrĩa nyanake, o gwata ndamathia-rĩ, ũitereme na magũrũ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Kuona nĩ anyitĩtie wendo harĩ niĩ, tondũ ũcio nĩ ndĩĩmũhatũraga hatĩ-inĩ; ndĩĩmũigaga handũ haraya na igũrũ,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ ũndũ nĩ amenyete rĩĩtwa rĩakwa.  Arĩngayagĩra, na niĩ ngamwamũkĩria; nĩ ndĩrĩikaraga nake hingo ya mĩnyamaro,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> ndĩrĩmũtharaga harĩ yo, na kũmũtĩithia ndĩmũtĩithie.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"wCJmgw1/fEO12+3vXsoqAg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                               Thaburi 100:2; 3; 5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩaku, Mwathani, nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu ciaku</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Tungatĩrai Mwathani mũkenete; ũkai mbere-inĩ yake mũgĩkũngũyagia.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩaku, Mwathani, nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu ciaku</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Menyai atĩ we Mwathani nĩwe Ngai: nĩwe watũũmbire, ithuĩ tũrĩ ake; tũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩake, nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu ciake kwĩrĩithĩria</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩaku, Mwathani, nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu ciaku</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ mwega; ũtugi wake nĩ wa tene na tene, na wĩhokeku wake nĩ wa nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũrĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩaku, Mwathani, nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu ciaku</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"ZB8S6cVmckmdff1xHtETDQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 1:1-2;3;4 na 6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũtatwaranaga  na ũtaaro wa arĩa aaganu, na ndarũgamaga njĩra-inĩ ya arĩa mehagia, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>kana agaikaraga gĩtindo-inĩ kĩa andũ arĩa atendi.  No rĩ’, nĩ kĩrĩra kĩa Mwathani ekenagĩra nĩkĩo;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> na kĩrĩra kĩu gĩake akerurumagia ũhoro wakĩo mũthenya o na ũtukũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Agakĩhaanaga ta mũtĩ wahandirũo mĩtaro-inĩ ya maaĩ, aciaraga maciaro maguo hingo yamo yakinya, mathangũ maguo namo matihohaga; nake, ũndũ o wothe egwĩka, nĩ ũgaacagĩra.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩa aaganu matihaana ũguo; o matariĩ ta mũũngũ ũrĩa ũũmbũragwo nĩ rũhuho.  Amu Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ njĩra ya arĩa athingu oyaine nayo, nayo njĩra ya arĩa aaganu nĩ gũtoma ĩgatoma.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"P9T/XCRI30OYjyNZDPhBkg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                              Thaburi 72: 1;7-8;10-11;12-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ Ngai, he mũthamaki mĩtuĩre yaku, o we mũriũ wa mũthamaki-rĩ, ũkĩmũhe ũthingu waku.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Matukũ make ũrĩa mũthingu nĩ kũhamba arĩhambaga, na gũtũũre na thayũ mũingĩ, nginya  o hingo mweri ũkarindũka.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ agĩe na watho kuuma iria-inĩ rĩmwe o nginya rĩrĩa rĩngĩ, na kuuma rũũĩ-inĩ o nginya ituri cia thĩ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Athamaki a Tarsis na mabũrũri ma iria-inĩ, nĩ mamũrutagĩre maruta; athamaki a Sheba na a Saba o nao nĩ mamũtegagĩre matega.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Ĩĩ-ni, athamaki othe marokĩmũgũĩra thĩ atungatagĩrũo nĩ ndũrĩrĩ ciothe.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ mũndũ mũkĩa aakaya, we nĩ arĩmũteithũraga, gwata ũrĩa mũthĩnĩki, ũtakĩrĩ na wa kũmũteithia.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũcio ũtarĩ na hinya, o ũcio mwagi-rĩ, nĩ arĩmũiguagĩra tha; andũ acio akĩa, akĩhonokie mĩoyo yao.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"lKSryRaMoEGBR6OuNJNS5Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                            Thaburi 131:1;2;3</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Njikaria harĩ we Mwathani na thayũ.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.	Mwathani, ngoro yakwa ti ya kwĩgatha, na maitho makwa ti ma ngũrũ; o na ndihang’agĩra maũndũ marĩa manene, kana mohoro mangĩrũkĩte.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Njikaria harĩ we Mwathani na thayũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Ngoro yakwa nĩ ndĩmĩkirĩtie na ngamĩhoreria; o ta kaana gakuue nĩ nyina, karĩa gatuithĩirio iria, harĩ niĩ ngoro yakwa no ta mwana ũtuĩte iria.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Njikaria harĩ we Mwathani na thayũ.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Ĩ Israeli-ĩ, wĩrĩgagĩrĩre o Mwathani, kuuma rĩu kinya tene na tene.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Njikaria harĩ we Mwathani na thayũ.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"sJOxhxsNNkKSLr8GwVcqoA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                            Thaburi 96:1 na 3;4-5;7-8;9-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.	Ĩ itĩkai kũinĩra Mwathani rũĩmbo rũerũ! Mũinĩre Mwathani, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ, mawĩko make ma magegania mũkĩmaganĩre iruka ciothe cia andũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Nĩ ũndũ Mwathani nĩ mũnene, na nĩ wa kũgoocwo mũno: we nĩ wa gwĩtigĩrũo gũkĩra ngai ciothe.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Thima-rĩ, ngai icio ciothe cia irĩndĩ no indo itarĩ kĩene, ĩndĩ Mwathani nĩwe wombire igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya irĩndĩ, rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e na hinya.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Rahai Mwathani nĩ kũgwetaga riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake: ũkai na ihaki, mũgĩtonye nja-inĩ ciake.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>4.	Tetemekai mwĩ mbere yake, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. Ugai ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; ĩĩ-ni, thĩ nĩ kũrũmio ĩrũmĩtio, ũndũ</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> ĩtangĩenyenyeka; arĩciragĩra irĩndĩ ciakuo o ũrĩa kwerekereire.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"9YBxHnNozU+LK1Q/vPFrsA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                 Thaburi 33: 4-5;6-7;18-19;20,22</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa ethurĩire gĩtwĩke igai rĩake</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, uuge wa Mwathani nĩ mwerekererũ; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>wĩra wake wothe nĩ wa kwĩhokwo.  Ũndũ ũrĩa enda nĩ ũthingu, o na kĩhooto:</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> thĩ ĩiyũire ũtugi wa Mwathani o kũiyũra.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa ethurĩire gũtwĩke igai rĩake</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Kũũmbwo kwa igũrũ, nĩ uuge wa Mwathani warĩũmbire; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>mwaranĩrie wa ũingĩ wothe wakuo ũgĩkĩũmbwo nĩ mũheehũ wa kanua gake.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Maĩ ma iria inene amonganĩtie magaikara ta kĩhumbu;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> marĩa ma kũrĩa kũriku  mũno amekĩrĩte nyũmba  cia kũmaiga mũthithũ.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa ethurĩire gũtwĩke igai rĩake</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, riitho rĩa Mwathani rĩerekeire harĩ arĩa amwĩtigĩri,</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384> rĩgakĩerekera harĩ andũ arĩa merĩgagĩrĩra o ũtugi wake;</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> nĩguo ateithũrage mĩoyo yao gĩkuũ-inĩ, gwata hingo ya ng’aragu amaikaragie na muoyo.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa ethurĩire gũtwĩke igai rĩake</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Mĩoyo itũ-rĩ, ĩkirĩrĩirie yetereire o Mwathani: </s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>we nowe ũteithio witũ o na ngo iitũ. </s>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1384> Ũtugi waku, Mwathani, tũma ũikarage na ithuĩ, </s>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1384>kũringana o na ũrĩa tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire.  </s>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Gũkena nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa ethurĩire gũtwĩke igai rĩake</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"cQiiNB/kDUyFg1M11nI3Ug",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 85:8-9;10-11;12-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ngũthikĩrĩria njigue ũrĩa Mũrungu, o we Mwathani, ekuuga, amu kĩrĩndĩ gĩake,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o acio marĩ ũiguano nake, no ũhoro wa thayũ angĩkĩhe, nakĩo nĩ kĩmenye gĩgacokerera ũrimũ wa mwĩĩro.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Gũtirĩ nganja ũhonokania wake ũikaraga hakuhĩ na arĩa amwĩtigĩri, nĩ getha riri ũtũũre bũrũri witũ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ũtugi na ũhoro-wa-ma ituĩke nĩ icemainie, ũthingu na thayũ-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>igakĩmumunyana; ũhoro-wa-ma ũtuĩke nĩ ũramera ũgĩkunũkaga thĩ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>naguo ũthingu ũgũcũthagĩrĩrie ũrĩ igũrũ matu-inĩ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩĩ-ni Mwathani no aheanage kĩndũ o gĩothe  kĩega, naguo bũrũri ũyũ witũ ũrutage uumithio waguo. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ũthingu-rĩ, nĩguo ũrĩmũthiaga mbere, ũtũmage makinya make matuĩke njĩra ya gũthiagĩrũo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
