Text:"<s1384>1.Kanua gakwa menyithanie kwĩhokeka gwaku nako nginya  njiarũa na njiarũa.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>  Nĩ amu njugĩte atĩrĩ, Ũtugi-rĩ, nĩ gwakwo ũrĩakagwo o nginya mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> wee wĩhokeku waku ũgũtũũra ũrũmĩtie o kũu igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Motugi ma Mwathani nĩ ngũtũũra ndĩmainagĩra o nginya tene. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Niĩ-rĩ, nĩ ndĩkanĩire na mũthurwo wakwa, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ndungata yakwa Davide nĩ kwĩhĩta ndĩĩhĩtĩte ngamĩrĩkĩrĩa atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mbeũ yaku ngũmĩtũũria ĩĩ nũmu o nginya tene na tene,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> ngĩake gĩtĩ gĩaku kĩa ũnene gĩkinyagĩrĩre njiarũa na njiarũa.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Motugi ma Mwathani nĩ ngũtũũra ndĩmainagĩra o nginya tene. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>3.	We arĩĩtanaga na kũrĩ niĩ ta ũũ.  Wee nĩwe awa, na nowe Ngai wakwa,</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> o na ndũmba ya ihiga ĩrĩa nyene ũhonokio wakwa.  Ũtugi wakwa ngũtũũra ndĩmũrũmĩirie kinya o tene, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>nakĩo kĩrĩkanĩro gĩakwa gĩtũũre kĩrĩ o gĩa kwĩhokeka nĩwe.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
