Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani; tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ, ũgakĩaga kũreka thũ ciakwa ingenerere.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Ĩ Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ ũmĩrutĩte thĩ o kwa ngoma; na ũnjikairie na muoyo, ndige gũtonyerera irima.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Inĩrai Mwathani mũmũgooce, inyuĩ mũrĩ ũiguano nake, rĩĩtwa rĩu rĩake rĩamũre mũkĩrĩcokerie ngatho.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>  Amu marakara make no ma kahinda kanini, ĩndĩ mĩtuganĩre yake nĩ ya gũtũũria mũndũ muoyo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Mwathani, igua ũkĩnginyĩrie wega waku: Ĩ Mwathani, ĩtĩkĩra gũtuĩka mũndeithia. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Rĩu nĩ ũngarũranĩirie mũcayo ũcio ndĩrarĩ naguo ũgatuĩka ndũrũhĩ, Ĩ Mwathani, Ngai wakwa-rĩ,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> ngũgĩtũũra ngũcokagĩria ngatho nginya mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
