Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani-rĩ, nĩwe rũaro rũakwa rũa ihiga, nĩ kĩhingo gĩakwa kĩa hinya, o na nowe mũhatũri; </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩwe Mũrungu wakwa, nĩ ndũmba yakwa ya ihiga, ĩrĩa ndahagĩra, ningĩ ngo yakwa, o naruo rũhĩa rũrĩa rũ’honokagia,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> o na nowe rĩangĩro rĩakwa rĩakĩtwo handũ haraya na igũrũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ngayagĩra Mwathani, o ũcio wagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũgoocagwo, ngakĩhonokio harĩ thũ ciakwa.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ndarigicĩirio nĩ mĩgeto ya gĩkuũ, nayo mĩiyũro ya wanangi ĩkandua nda.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani e muoyo; we ndũmba yakwa ya ihiga arogathwo! </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>We Ngai mwene ũhonokio wakwa arotũũra atũũgĩrĩte! Ũhonokio nĩ mũnene, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ũcio aheaga mũthamaki wake; ũcio wake mũitĩrĩrie maguta-rĩ, nĩ gũtuga amũtugaga.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
