Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Ũhũndũraga andũ magacoka gũtuĩka mũthegethege; </s>"},{ID:6,
