Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Gĩtũmenyithie gũtara matukũ maitũ 
nĩ getha tũgĩe na ngoro cia kũũhĩga.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Garũrũka, Jehova; nĩ nginya rĩ? 
gĩcoke kũiguĩra ndungata ciaku tha.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Rũcinĩ ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku; </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>nĩguo tũtũũre tũkũngũyagia o tũgĩkenaga matukũ maitũ mothe.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Wĩko waku ũroonwo kũrĩ ndungata ciaku, 
na ũkaru waku woneke kũrĩ ciana ciacio.</s>"},{ID:9,
