Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ itĩkai kũinĩra Mwathani rũĩmbo rũerũ! Mũinĩre Mwathani, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ.  Inĩrai Mwathani, gathai rĩĩtwa rĩake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Hunjagiai ũhoro wa ũhonokania wake mũthenya o mũthenya.  Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ, mawĩko make ma magegania mũkĩmaganĩre iruka ciothe cia andũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya irĩndĩ, rahai  Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e na hinya. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Rahai Mwathani nĩ kũgwetaga riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake: ũkai na ihaki, mũgĩtonye nja-inĩ ciake.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ gĩthathaiyei Mwathani mũgemete ũgemu ũrĩa wa ũtheru; tetemekai  mwĩ mbere yake, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> Ugai ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ atĩrĩ: Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; arĩciragĩra irĩndĩ ciakuo o ũrĩa kwerekereire.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
