Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ ariũ a Mũrungu, rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e hinya;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> rahai Mwathani mũkĩgane riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake; thathaiyai Mwathani mwĩgemetie na ũgemu ũrĩa wa ũtheru.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ kũgamba ũragamba na kũu iria-inĩ; Mũrungu, ũcio wĩ riri, nĩ hĩndĩ egũkĩruruma,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o we Mwathani akaruruma kũu igũrũ rĩa maaĩ maingĩ.  Mũgambo wa Mwathani wĩna hinya; mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ mũkaru o gũkara.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ ũthingithagia werũ; ũgatũma mĩtitũ ĩhũrũrũke o gũthera; Mwathani-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>o hingo ĩrĩa ya Mũiyũro wa Maaĩ; ĩĩ-ni, Mwathani aikaraga  ho e mũthamaki wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO"},{Guid:"wnmBmb1rFESoIygLwKwZ7Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 16:5,8;9-10;11</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ngitagĩra Ngai, amu nĩ harĩ Wee ndĩgiritĩtie</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩwe rũgai rũrĩa ngaĩte, o na nowe riita rĩa gĩkombe gĩakwa; wee-rĩ, iringa rĩrĩa ningithĩtio, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩwe ũnyitĩrĩire.  Mwathani nĩ ndĩmwĩigĩire mbere yakwa hingo ciothe, na tondũ e guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũrĩo, ndirĩ hĩndĩ ngenyenyeka.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ngitagĩra Ngai, amu nĩ harĩ Wee ndĩgiritĩtie</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, ngoro yakwa nĩ gũkena ĩkenaga, ũrĩa guo riri wakwa ũgagĩcanjamũka, </s>"},{ID:7,
