Text:"<s1384>1.Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ ariũ a Mũrungu, rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e hinya;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> rahai Mwathani mũkĩgane riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake;</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> thathaiyai Mwathani mwĩgemetie na ũgemu ũrĩa wa ũtheru.</s>"},{ID:6,
