Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ kũgamba ũragamba na kũu iria-inĩ; </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mũrungu, ũcio wĩ riri, nĩ hĩndĩ egũkĩruruma, o we Mwathani akaruruma kũu igũrũ rĩa maaĩ maingĩ. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Mũgambo wa Mwathani wĩ na hinya; mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ mũkaru o gũkara.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>(chorus)		
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>3.Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ ũthingithagia werũ; ũgatũma mĩtitũ ĩhũrũrũke o gũthera; </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani-rĩ, o hingo ĩrĩa ya Mũiyũro wa Maaĩ; ĩĩ-ni, Mwathani aikaraga  ho e mũthamaki wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>(chorus)		
Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
