Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ muuma andũ, ningĩ nĩ wa matha maingĩ; ndahiũhaga kũrakara, na e na ũtugi mũnene.  Mwathani-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ekaga andũ othe wega; indo ciothe iria aathondekire gũtirĩ atarĩ tha nakĩo.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mawĩra macio maku mothe, Mwathani, megũtũũra o magũcokagĩria ngatho; nao andũ arĩa maiguaine nawe,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> kũgatha no matũre makũgathaga.  Megũtũũra moigaga ũrĩa ũthamaki waku wĩ riri, o magĩteretaga ũhoro wa ũrĩa wee wĩ na ũhoti.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Maũndũ macio maku ma ũhoti mamamenyithie ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ, o gwata ũthamaki waku, mamere ũrĩa ũkaru waguo  wĩ riri, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ũthamaki waku nĩ ũrĩa wa tene na tene, wathani waku-rĩ, ũtũũraga nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.  </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
