Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Wee nĩwe ndirĩire maitho, o wee ũikaire thĩ kũu igũrũ. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, O ta ũrĩa maitho ma ndungata maroragĩrĩria guoko  kwa mũthuri ũrĩa ũciathaga.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ta ũrĩa maitho ma mũirĩtu ndungata maroragĩrĩria guoko kwa mũtumia mwene,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> no taguo maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ, o nginya agatũkinyĩria wega wake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Tũkinyĩrie wega waku, Mwathani, gĩtũkinyĩrie wega waku, amu tũrĩ ahũnie kĩrario o kũhũnio.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Ngoro ciitũ kũhũna ihũnĩte o mũno ndendwa  cia aria maikaraga o mearaganĩtie, andũ acio a ngũrũ-rĩ, tũgakĩhũna kĩrario kĩao o kũhũna.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
