Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Rĩrĩa Mwathani aagarũrire a Sion arĩa atahe akĩmainũkia-rĩ, twahaanire ta andũ mekũrota. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Tũnua twitũ  hĩndĩ ĩo tũkĩiyũra mĩtheko, nĩmĩ ciitũ igakĩiyũra mũkũngũiyo.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ gũgĩkĩĩranwo atĩrĩ: Mwathani nĩ ekĩire andũ aya maũndũ manene! Ĩĩ-ni, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ maũndũ manene Mwathani aatwĩkĩire, na ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wamo </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ Mwathani, kĩrĩkie kũgarũra atahwo aitũ mainũke, ta ũrĩa njũĩ cia Gũthini icokaga kũiyũra.  Arĩa marahanda na maithori makagetha o magĩkũngũyagia </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mũndũ o na angĩthiĩ akĩrĩraga akuuĩte mbegũ agĩcihandaga, gũcoka agacoka agĩkũngũyagia, e na itĩa ciake cia ngano.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
