Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee Ngai, nĩ tũtaranĩtie magegania ma rũendo rũaku </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>A Israeli ta nĩ moige ũguo, atĩ ũtugi wake nĩ wa tene na tene. Nyũmba ya Haron,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ta nĩ moige ũguo, atĩ ũtugi wake nĩ wa tene na tene.  Andũ arĩa etigĩri Mwathani-rĩ nĩ makiuge ũguo, atĩ ũtugi wake nĩ wa tene na tene. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee Ngai, nĩ tũtaranĩtie magegania ma rũendo rũaku </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ihiga rĩrĩa rĩaregirũo nĩ aaki nĩrĩo rĩtuĩkĩte o rĩrĩa inene rĩa koine.  Ũndũ ũcio uumĩte kwĩ Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ũgũtũgegia tũkĩwona, Mũthenya ũyũ nĩ Mwathani ũtũmĩte ũgĩe; nĩ tũkĩũkenagĩra.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee  Ngai, nĩ tũtaranĩtie magegania ma rũendo rũaku </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ Mwathani, twagũthaitha, tũhonokagie! Ĩ Mwathani, twagũthaitha, tũma tũtũũre o tũgaacĩĩre! Mũrathimwo-rĩ, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũrĩa wa gũũka na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani! Twĩ gũkũ nyũmba ya Mwathani, inyuĩ nĩ twamũrathima.  Mwathani nowe Mũrungu, na nĩ agĩtuonetie ũtheri.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee  Ngai, nĩ tũtaranĩtie magegania ma rũendo rũaku </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
