Kanua gakwa no kaganage ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Wee, Mwathani, nĩwe ndahĩire; ndũkanakĩreke njonoke. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Tondũ wa ũthingu waku-rĩ, ndeithũra, ũkĩhatũre; nyinamĩrĩria gũtũ, uhonokie.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Kanua gakwa no kaganage ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Harĩ niĩ tuĩka ta ndũmba ya ihiga, ya ũtũũro, harĩa ndĩrĩingagĩra hingo ciothe;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> wee nĩ wathĩte atĩ honokagio; nĩ amu rũaro rũakwa rũa ihiga,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> o na kĩhingo gĩakwa kĩa hinya, no wee.  Ĩ Ngai wakwa, hatũra guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩa mwaganu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Kanua gakwa no kaganage ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũkorũo wee, Mwathani Ngai, nowe kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro gĩakwa;</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> ũtũire wĩ mwĩhoko wakwa kuuma ndĩ o mũnyinyi.  Ndũire ndiirĩrĩirũo nĩwe kuuma o ndaciarũo;</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> wee nĩwe wandutire nda ya maitũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Kanua gakwa no kaganage ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ngũũka  ngĩkumagia mawĩko ma ũhoti ma Mwathani Ngai; ũthingu waku nĩguo ndĩrĩgwetaga, o waku wee wiki.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai, nĩwe ũtũire ũndutaga kuuma ndĩ o mũnyinyi,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> na nginya rĩu no nyumbũraga maũndũ ma magegania marĩa waneka.</s>"},{ID:10,
