Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani; tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ, ũgakĩaga kũreka thũ ciakwa ingenerere. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ĩ Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ ũmĩrutĩte thĩ o kwa ngoma; nĩ ũnjikairie na muoyo, ndige gũtonyerera irima.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Inĩrai Mwathani mũmũgooce, inyuĩ mũrĩ ũiguano nake, rĩĩtwa rĩu rĩake rĩamũre mũkĩrĩcokerie ngatho. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Amu marakara make no ma kahinda kanini, ĩndĩ mĩtuganĩre yake nĩ ya gũtũũria  mũndũ muoyo: kĩrĩro no gũũka kũraarĩrĩra hwaĩ-inĩ na rũcinĩ gũkaroka ngemi.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani, igua, ũkĩnginyĩrie  wega waku: Ĩ Mwathani, itĩkĩra gũtuĩka mũndeithia, rĩu nĩ ũngarũranĩirie mũcayo ũcio ndĩrarĩ naguo</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> ũgatuĩka ndũrũhĩ.  Ĩ Mwathani, Ngai wakwa-ĩ, ngũgĩtũũra ngũcokagĩria ngatho nginya mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO "},{Guid:"/FxVWDmVG0u6BYpBjQxWbA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 19:7;9;11-12;13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mawathi ma Mwathani makenagia mũndũ ngoro </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.	Kĩrĩra kĩa Mwathani nĩ gĩkinyanĩrũ, gĩthondekaga muoyo  wa mũndũ;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ũira wa Mwathani nĩ mwĩhokeku, ũũhĩgagia ũrĩa ũtarĩ mũũgĩ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mawathi ma Mwathani makenagia mũndũ ngoro </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Gwĩtigĩra Mwathani nĩ ũndũ mũtheru, ũtũũraga tene na tene; matua ma Mwathani no ma ma, nĩma kĩhooto kũna.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mawathi ma Mwathani makenagia mũndũ ngoro </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Na ningĩ nĩmo ndungata yaku ĩtaarĩkaga nĩmo; Kũmamenyerera kwĩ na uumithio mũnene.  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nũ ũngĩhota gwĩkũũranĩra kũrĩa ahĩtagia? Mahĩtia macio mehĩthaga-rĩ, ndũgakĩmatuage makwa.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mawathi ma Mwathani makenagia mũndũ ngoro </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ningĩ ũgiranagie ndungata yaku na mehia ma mwĩĩro;</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> ndũkanareke njathagwo nĩmo: nĩguo njikarage ndĩ mũkinyanĩru, ngakĩaga wĩhia mũnene.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"I<s1384>COKIA	
Mawathi ma Mwathani makenagia mũndũ ngoro </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
