Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 23:2-3;4;5-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe mũrĩithi wakwa, ndirĩ kĩndũ ingĩaga</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atũmaga njarahe cieni-inĩ iria ii nyeki nduru; andĩithagia ngurumo ya maaĩ o marĩa me na ũhurũko.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ kũriũkia ariũkagia ngoro yakwa, akandongoria na njĩra cia ũthingu nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe mũrĩithi wakwa, ndirĩ kĩndũ ingĩaga</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>O na ingĩtuĩka ndĩrahungurĩra mũkuru wĩ nduma ta ya gĩkuũ, ndirĩ ũgwati ingĩĩtigĩra, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ gũkorũo two hamwe nawe; thiarĩ waku na mũthĩgi, nĩcio igũtũma ‘makũke’.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe mũrĩithi wakwa, ndirĩ kĩndũ ingĩaga</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ũnjarĩire metha harĩa ndĩ, o ũthiũ-inĩ wa thũ ciakwa; nĩ ũnjitĩrĩirie maguta mũtwe;</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> gĩkombe gĩakwa nakĩo nĩ kembembaine. Matuku mothe ma muoyo wakwa,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384> wega na utugi  itirĩ hingo itarĩrũmanagĩrĩra
na niĩ, na ngũtũũra nyũmba ya Mwathani matukũ matarĩ mũthia.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩwe mũrĩithi wakwa, ndirĩ kĩndũ ingĩaga</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>			</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
