Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                            Thaburi 128:1-2;3;4-5</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Kĩrĩa ũnogeire na moko maku, wee nĩ ũrĩkĩrĩaga; gũkena nĩwe ũrĩkenaga, na gũtũũra ũtũũre o na wega.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>2.Mũtumia waku egũikara ta mũthabibũ ũrĩa mũciari mũno e kũu nyũmba yaku thĩinĩ; </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ciana ciaku nacio ituĩke ta mĩtamaiyũ ya mũmerano ĩthiũrũrũkĩirie metha yaku.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>3.Onei, nĩ ta ũguo mũndũ arĩrathimagwo , ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Mwathani, Mwathani arokũrathima arĩ Sion,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> wonage wega wa Jerusalemu matukũ maku mothe ma gũtũũra muoyo.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	:Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
