Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũonie ũtheri wa ũthiũ waku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nyamũkĩria ndakaya, wee Ngai wa ũthingu wakwa; nĩwe wana’he mĩaramano ndagũa hatĩka-inĩ; nginyĩria wega waku, ihoya rĩakwa ũkĩrĩigue.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũonie ũtheri wa ũthiũ waku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Gĩani na guoya, mũtigage kwĩhia; teretagai o mũndũ na ngoro yake arĩ ũrĩrĩ, mũgĩĩkiragĩre. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Nĩ aingĩ maroria atĩrĩ: Nũ ũngĩtuonania  na maũndũ mega? Mwathani, wee-rĩ, gĩtũtiirĩre ũtheri wa gĩthithi gĩaku.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũonie ũtheri wa ũthiũ waku, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Ngũgĩĩkomera ndĩ na thayũ, njũke o ngĩona toro, tondũ wee, </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani, nĩwe ũndũũragia mwamu, ngaikara o ndĩĩgangarĩte.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Tũonie ũtheri wa ũthiũ waku, Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000FF"}}},
