Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                 Thaburi 85:8-9;10-11;12-13</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.Nĩ ngũthikĩrĩria njigue ũrĩa Mwathani, o we Ngai, ekuuga, amu kĩrĩndĩ gĩake, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>o acio marĩ ũiguano nake, no ũhoro wa thayũ angĩkĩhe, </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>amu ũhonokania wake ũikaraga hakuhĩ na arĩa amwĩtigĩri, nĩ getha riri ũtũũre bũrũri witũ.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>2.Ũtugi na ũhoro wa ma nĩ icemanĩtie, ũthingu na thayũ-rĩ igakĩmumunyana.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũhoro wa ma ũtuĩke nĩ ũramera ũgĩkunũkaga thĩ, naguo ũthingu ũgũcũthagĩrĩrie ũrĩ igũrũ matu-inĩ.
  </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>3.Ĩĩ-ni, Mwathani Ngai no aheanage kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩega, naguo bũrũri ũyũ witũ ũrutage uumithio waguo.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>  Ũthingu-rĩ, nĩguo ũrĩmũthiaga mbere, ũtũmage makinya  make matuĩke njĩra ya gũthiagĩrũo.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO "},{Guid:"d/W+koUHDUSc79A24JQyNw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 145:10-11;15-16;17-18</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumbatũragia guoko gwaku Mwathani, kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩĩ muoyo ũgakĩhũnia</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mawĩra macio maku mothe, Mwathani, megũtũũra o magũcokagĩria ngatho;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nao andũ arĩa maiguaine  nawe, kũgatha no matũre makũgathaga.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Megũtũũra moigaga ũrĩa ũthamaki waku wĩ riri, o magĩteretaga ũhoro wa ũrĩa wee wĩ na ũhoti</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumbatũragia guoko gwaku Mwathani, kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩĩ muoyo ũgakĩhũnia</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ othe nowe maroragĩrĩria, nawe ũkamaheaga irio ciao ihinda rĩacio rĩakinya. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Ũkumbatũragia guoko gwaku, kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩĩ muoyo ũgakĩhũnia kĩrĩa gĩkwenda.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumbatũragia guoko gwaku Mwathani, kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩĩ muoyo ũgakĩhũnia</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani ikĩro-inĩ ciake ciothe no mũthingu, maũndũ make mothe amekaga o na ũtugi.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani-rĩ, arĩa othe mamũkayagĩra, akoragwo hakuhĩ nao, o arĩa othe mamũkayagĩra nĩ kũmwĩhoka na ma.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũkumbatũragia guoko gwaku Mwathani, kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩĩ muoyo ũgakĩhũnia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
