Text:"<s1384>tondũ wa ũguo matha maku marĩ maingĩ-rĩ, tharia mehia makwa o gũtharia.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Thambia mũno, waganu wakwa ũ’thire, ‘theria mahĩtia makwa maninũke.</s>"},{ID:6,
