Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Atĩrĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe ũhonokio wakwa, na nĩwe ndĩrĩĩhokaga na ndicoke gwĩtigĩra; Mwathani nĩwe hinya wakwa,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> na nĩwe ndĩrĩinagĩra; nĩwe ũtuĩkĩte ihonokero rĩakwa.  Tondũ ũcio mũgatahaga maaĩ ithima cia ũhonokanio mũkenete.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Gathai Mwathani; hoyagai mũkĩgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩake; ũmburĩrai andũ maũndũ marĩa ekaga, mũkĩmeraga atĩ rĩĩtwa rĩake nĩ itũũgĩrie mũno.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Inĩrai Mwathani, nĩ ũndũ nĩ ekĩte maũndũ me ngumo nene, na mũtũme ũhoro ũcio ũmenyũo thĩ yothe.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Wee ũtũũraga Sion, anĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene ũgũũthũke mũno, nĩ gũkorũo Ũrĩa Mũtheru wa Israeli, o ũcio ũrĩ thĩinĩ wanyu, nĩ mũnene mũno.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
