Text:"<s1384>guoko gwake kwa ũrĩo, gwake mwene, nĩkuo kũmũhonokanĩirie, o kĩo gĩcoka kĩu gĩake gĩtheru.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ aũguũrĩrie ũthingu wake maitho-inĩ ma ndũrĩrĩ</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ atũmĩte ũhonokio wake ũmenyeke wega: ũthingu wake nĩ aũguũrĩirie maitho-inĩ ma ndũrĩrĩ. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Kũririkana nĩ akĩririkanĩte ũtugi wake o na wĩhokeku wake, iria onagia  nyũmba  ya Israeli.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ aũguũrĩrie ũthingu wake maitho-inĩ ma ndũrĩrĩ</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ũhonokania wa Ngai witũ-rĩ, ituri ciothe cia thĩ rĩu nĩ ciwonete.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ, anĩrĩrai Mwathani na gĩkeno; tumũkai, mũkũngũiye; ĩĩ-ni, mũkĩmũgooce na nyĩmbo</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ aũguũrĩirie ũthingu wake maitho-inĩ ma ndũrĩrĩ</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
