Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, hakarũgama Ngatha mwena waku wa ũrĩo</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mwarĩ ũyũ, ta igua, na ũrũmbũiye; inamĩrĩria gũtũ gwaku: atĩrĩ, riganĩrũo nĩ andũ a kwanyu, o na nyũmba ya thoguo.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩrĩo mũthamaki angĩĩrirĩria ũthaka waku: amu nĩwe mwathani waku; nawe no ũmwĩkĩrĩre.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, hakarũgama Ngatha mwena waku wa ũrĩo</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Airĩtu amuumi thutha, arĩa a thiritũ yake, o nao nĩ gwaku mekũrehwo.  Mekũrehwo na gĩkeno na ndũrũhĩ, matonye nyũmba ya mũthamaki.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, hakarũgama Ngatha mwena waku wa ũrĩo</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
