Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ndĩrĩgathaga Mwathani o hingo ciothe; kanua gakwa kũmĩkumia gatirĩ hĩndĩ gatarĩmũkumagia.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nowe ngoro yakwa ĩrĩĩrahagĩra: arĩa ahoreri marĩiguaga ũguo magakena.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ kĩgoocei Mwathani mũmũnenehie mwĩ hamwe na niĩ, tũtũũgĩrie rĩĩtwa rĩake tũrĩ o ũndũ ũmwe. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ndarongoririe Mwathani, nake akĩnyamũkĩria, agĩkĩndeithũra harĩ maũndũ mothe marĩa maanjiguithĩtie guoya.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ aya-rĩ, nĩ maamũrorereirie, makĩarĩrũo nĩ ũtheri, nao mothiũ mao matirĩ hingo makahumbwo nĩ thoni. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Mũthĩnĩki ũyũ aakaire, nake Mwathani akĩmũigua, akĩmũhonokia mĩnyamaro-inĩ yake yothe.</s>"},{ID:11,
