Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Iĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ ndĩrĩgathaga Mwathani o hingo ciothe; Kanua gakwa kũmũkumia gatirĩ hĩndĩ gatarĩmũkumagia.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nowe Ngoro yakwa ĩrĩĩrahagĩra: arĩa ahoreri marĩiguaga ũguo magakena.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Iĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Maitho ma Mwathani merekeire  na kũrĩ arĩa athingu, na matũ make magategerũo kĩrĩro kĩao. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩa mekaga ũũru-rĩ, ũthiũ wa Mwathani nĩ kũmomĩra ũmomĩire, atĩ ang’urie rĩtwa rĩao rĩtikaririkanwo gũkũ thĩ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Iĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩa athingu maakaire, nake Mwathani akĩigua, akĩmateithũra mĩnyamaro-inĩ yao yothe.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ akoragwo hakuhĩ na arĩa athuthĩku ngoro; acio maherete muoyo-rĩ agakĩmahonokia;</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Iĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Maũũru no maingĩ makoraga ũrĩa mũthingu, ĩndĩ, Mwathani nĩ amũteithũraga harĩ mo mothe.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>  Kũmenyerera nĩ amenyagĩrĩra mahĩndĩ make mothe; gũtirĩ o na rĩmwe rĩngiunĩka.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩa aaganu-rĩ, ũũru nĩ kũũraga ũkamoraga; andũ arĩa mathũũraga ũcio  mũthingu nĩ magatuwo ehia. </s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> Mwathani nĩ gũkũũra akũũraga ngoro cia ndungata ciake; arĩa marahagĩra harĩ we gũtirĩ ũngĩtuwo mwĩhia.</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Iĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"u3UAowlDzUiOIJGhZ/McOA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 116:1-2;3-4;5-6;8-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ nyenda Mwathani, tondũ nĩ aiguĩte mũgambo wakwa, agakĩigua ngĩmũthaitha.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>  Kuona nĩ aanyinamĩrĩirie gũtũ-rĩ, tondũ ũcio, matukũ makwa mothe nĩwe ndĩrĩthathayagia.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nderigicĩirio nĩ mĩgeto ya gĩkuũ, nganyitwo nĩ mĩtandiũko ya kwa-ngoma: nĩ ndonire mĩnyamaro o na kĩeha.  </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Ngĩkaĩra rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani, ngiuga atĩrĩ: Ĩ Mwathani, ndagũthaitha, hatũra muoyo wakwa.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ muuma-andũ, na nĩ mũthingu; ĩĩ-ni, Ngai witũ nĩ wa matha maingĩ.  </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ amenyagĩrĩra arĩa matarĩ ogĩ: nĩ kũhinyio ndahinyĩtio, nake agĩkĩ’honokia.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Amu wee, Mwathani, nĩ ũtharĩte muoyo wakwa gwĩ gĩkuũ, ũgaikĩria maitho makwa maithori, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ũgirĩtie magũrũ makwa mahigũrũo.  Nĩ ndiĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani o mabũrũri-inĩ ma arĩa me muoyo.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"sF7dckTfyE2UW+r8Pg9WSw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                   Thaburi 92:1-2;12-13; 14-15</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ wega mũno gũkumia rĩĩtwa rĩaku na rũĩmbo, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1Nĩ wega mũno  gũcokagĩrĩria Mwathani ngatho, o na gũkumia rĩĩtwa rĩaku na rũĩmbo, wee Wĩ-Igũrũ-Mũno;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> nĩ wega kũrokaga kũonania ũhoro wa ũtugi waku o rũcinĩ, na kuonanagia wĩhokeku waku o ũtukũ o ũtukũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ wega mũno gũkumia rĩĩtwa rĩaku na rũĩmbo, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Ũrĩa mũthingu we arĩhambaga ta mũkĩndũ, akũre o ta mũtarakwa wĩ kũrĩa Lebanoni. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Acio ahande nyũmba-inĩ ya Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ kũhamba marĩhambagĩra kũu nja-inĩ cia Ngai witũ.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ wega mũno gũkumia rĩĩtwa rĩaku na rũĩmbo, Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>3.Magatũũra maciaraga maciaro o na marĩ akũrũ; magatũũra maiyũire ngogoyo, maikare marĩ o aruru; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>monanagĩrĩrie atĩ Mwathani nĩ mũrũngĩrĩru, o we ndũmba yakwa ya ihiga, thĩinĩ wake gũtirĩ kaũndũ ka wogogi.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Nĩ wega mũno gũkumia rĩĩtwa rĩaku na rũĩmbo, Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"FnWx/e3tM0iB3/BMmCxhLQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 25:4-5ab,8-9;10-14</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ na kũu igũrũ kũrĩ wee ndĩmĩroretie</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Menyithia njĩra ciaku, Mwathani; ndutaga ikĩro ciaku, ndĩimenye. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ndwaragĩra o ũhoro-inĩ waku wa ma, o ũkĩndutaga; nĩ gũkorũo wee nĩwe Ngai mwene ũhonokio wakwa.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ na kũu igũrũ kũrĩ wee ndĩmĩroretie</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ mwega, o na nĩ mũrũngĩrĩru; tondũ ũcio, arĩa mahĩtĩtie, nĩ arĩmonagĩrĩria njĩra. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Arĩa ahoreri arĩmatwaraga na mĩthiĩre o ĩrĩa ya kĩhooto: acio ahoreri-rĩ, nĩ kũruta arĩmarutaga mũgerere wa njĩra yake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ na kũu igũrũ kũrĩ wee ndĩmĩroretie</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ikĩro ciothe cia Mwathani no cia ũtugi na ũhoro wa ma harĩ arĩa marũmagia’ kĩrĩkanĩro gĩake,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na maũira marĩa make, makamaathĩkĩra.  Ndundu ya Mwathani nĩ ya acio amwĩtigĩri; nĩo arĩmenyithagia kĩrĩkanĩro  gĩake.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ na kũu igũrũ kũrĩ wee ndĩmĩroretie</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"cHAwYiFvPkGvR1T1ziSfeQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                            Thaburi 63:1;2-3;4-5;6-7</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1846>ICOKIA	:Nĩ kũnyota ngoro yakwa ĩkũnyoteire Wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1846>1.	Ĩ Ngai, wee nĩwe Mũrungu wakwa; ngũroka gũkũrongoria na kĩyo; nĩ kũnyota ngoro yakwa ĩkũnyoteire,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1846> na nĩũndũ waku, mwĩrĩ ũkaigua mĩĩto, ndĩ bũrũri ũyũ mũũmũũ na wĩ mĩnoga, ũyũ ũtarĩ maaĩ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1846>ICOKIA	:Nĩ kũnyota ngoro yakwa ĩkũnyoteire Wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1846>2.	Nĩ ta ũguo ndanagũcũthĩrĩria ndĩ handũ harĩa haamũre, atĩ nyone hinya waku, o gwata riri waku.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1846>  Amu ũtugi waku nĩ mwega gũkĩra muoyo; mĩromo yakwa nĩ kũraha ĩrĩkũrahaga.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1846>ICOKIA	:Nĩ kũnyota ngoro yakwa ĩkũnyoteire Wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1846>3.	Hakĩrĩ  ũguo, ngũtũũra ngũgathaga hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yothe ngũikara na muoyo: ngũgĩtũũra ngwaragĩra hĩ o ndĩĩhokete rĩĩtwa rĩu rĩaku. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1846> Ngoro yakwa ĩrĩhũnaga wega ta ĩrĩĩte maguta, Ĩkarĩa ũnoru; nako kanua gakwa nĩ karĩkũgoocaga, mĩromo ĩgĩkũngũyagia.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1846>ICOKIA	:Nĩ kũnyota ngoro yakwa ĩkũnyoteire Wee Mwathani</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1846>4.	Rĩrĩa ngũkĩririkana ndĩ ũrĩrĩ, matuanĩra-inĩ ma camu wa ũtukũ nĩ ũhoro waku ndĩĩrurumagia. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1846> Nĩ gũkorũo nĩwe ũtũire ũndeithagia, na njikaire kĩĩgunyĩ-inĩ kĩa mathagu maku no ngũngũyagie nĩ gũkena</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1846>ICOKIA	:Nĩ kũnyota ngoro yakwa ĩkũnyoteire Wee Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"M9iA9j4Y/0qbPrq1SjAxYA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 128:1-2;3;4-5;6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani arotũrathima, We nĩwe gĩthima kĩa ũtũũro </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Kĩrĩa ũnogeire na moko maku-rĩ, weee nĩ ũrĩkĩrĩaga; gũkena nĩwe ũrĩkenaga, na gũtũũra ũtũũre o na wega.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani arotũrathima, We nĩwe gĩthima kĩa ũtũũro</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Mũtumia waku egũikara ta mũthabibũ ũrĩa mũciari mũno e kũu nyũmba yaku thĩinĩ; </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ciana ciaku nacio ituĩke ta mĩtamaiyũ ya mũmerano ĩthiũrũrũkĩirie metha yaku.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani arotũrathima, We nĩwe gĩthima kĩa ũtũũro</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Onei, nĩta ũguo mũndũ arĩrathimagwo, ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Mwathani.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani arokũrathima arĩ Sion, wonage wega wa Jerusalem matukũ maku mothe ma gũtũũra muoyo.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani arotũrathima, We nĩwe gĩthima kĩa ũtũũro</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩĩ, o na nĩ ũkona ciana cia ciana ciaku. Gwa Israel kũrotũũra o thayũ!</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"nBErb3kQj0WYGj7rvtbw9w",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 90:12-13;14-15;16-17</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku, Mwathani, nĩ getha tũgĩkene </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Gĩtũmenyithie gũtara matukũ maitũ nĩ getha tũgĩe na ngoro cia kũhĩga. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Garũrũka, Mwathani: nĩ nginya rĩ? Gĩcoke kũiguĩra ndungata ciaku tha.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku, Mwathani, nĩ getha tũgĩkene </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Rũcinĩ ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku; nĩguo tũtũũre tũkũngũyagia o tũgĩkenaga matukũ maitũ mothe. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Tũkenie matukũ maiganaine na marĩa ũtuonetie thĩna, ũmaringanie na mĩaka ĩo tuonete ũru.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku, Mwathani, nĩ getha tũgĩkene </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Wĩko waku ũroonowo kũrĩ ndungata ciaku, na ũkaru waku woneke kũrĩ ciana ciacio.  Wega wa Mwathani Ngai witũ ũrokĩgĩa igũrũ riitũ:</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> wĩra wa moko maitũ naguo, wee tũrũmagĩrie; ĩĩ-nĩ, wĩra wa moko maitũ kũrũmia ũkĩũrũmagie.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku, Mwathani, nĩ getha tũgĩkene </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"0WpUSqfXoE2qQQUecWVNcQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                              Thaburi 95:1-2;6-7ab;8-9</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>1.Ũkani, tũkũngũiye Mwathani tũkenete, tũkĩanĩrĩre ndũmba iitũ ya ihiga, yo nyene ũhonokia witũ.  </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ tũkinye ũthiũ-inĩ wake twĩ na ngatho, tũmwanĩrĩre na gĩkeno tũkĩinaga nyĩmbo cia thaburi.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Gĩũkeni, tũmũthathaiye, tũmĩinamĩrĩre; nĩ tũturĩrie Mwathani ndu, o ũcio Mũtũũmbi.  Nĩ gũkorũo we nĩwe Ngai witũ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ithuĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩake kwĩrĩithĩria , nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu iria atungataga na gwoko gwake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Tigai kũũmia ngoro cianyu, ta ũrĩa mwekire kũu Meriba, mũthĩ to ũrĩa mwarĩ Massa, kũu werũ-inĩ; </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maithe manyu maangeririe, makĩndoria, na magĩkĩona wĩko wakwa.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"31+vaZznlE6PdNhiptjfWQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 54:1-2;3;4-6</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ĩ Ngai, honokia na rĩĩtwa rĩaku, tondũ wa ũguo wĩ na ũhoti-rĩ, nduĩra ũhoro wakwa.  Ngai, igua  ihoya rĩakwa; ciugo ici cia kanua gakwa, citegere matũ.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ njũkĩrĩirũo nĩ andũ ageni, muoyo  wakwa nĩ ũracario nĩ andũ marĩ itua-nda: Ngai -rĩ, magakĩrega aikare maitho-inĩ mao.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>No rĩrĩ, Ngai nĩwe mũndeithia; muoyo wakwa nĩ Mwathani  ũrĩ wa kũũtiirĩrĩra. </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ nĩ igongona  ndĩĩkũrutĩra, ndute o ndĩĩendeire; wee Mwathani, nĩ ngatho ndĩĩgĩcokeria rĩĩtwa rĩaku, tondũ nĩ rĩega.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO  "},{Guid:"UKBjKwPuNUeABqAERb6Q2Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                               Thaburi 146:7;8-9a;9b-10</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee ngoro yakwa-rĩ, gooca Mwathani</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>O we ũrĩa ũtuagĩra andũ arĩa agũmĩre matuĩro ma kĩhooto;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> ũrĩa ningĩ ũheaga arĩa ahũtu irio.  Mwathani-rĩ, arĩa ohe nĩ amohoraga.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee ngoro yakwa-rĩ, gooca Mwathani</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani nĩ ahingũraga arĩa atumumu maitho, Mwathani nĩ ainamũraga arĩa mekonotete, </s>"},{ID:6,
