Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Wee ngoro yakwa-rĩ, gooca Mwathani</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Mwana wa ngoriai na mũtumia wa ndigwa, nĩwe ũmanyitagĩrĩra; nayo njĩra ya andũ aaganu nĩ kũmĩhotomia amĩhootomagia. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> Mwathani egũtũũra athamakaga tene na tene.  Ngai waku, wee Sion-rĩ, egũtũũra athamakaga nginya  njiarũa na njiarũa.  Goocai Mwathani!</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
