Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Gwĩtigĩra  Mwathani nĩ ũndũ mũtheru, ũtũũraga tene na tene; matua ma Mwathani no ma ma, nĩ ma kĩhooto kũna.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s>"},{ID:9,
