Text:"<s1384> Ndarongoririe Mwathani, nake akĩnyamũkĩra, agĩkĩndeithũra harĩ maũndũ mothe marĩa manjiguithĩtie guoya.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Iĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Andũ aya-rĩ, nĩ maamũrorereirie, makĩarĩrũo nĩ ũtheri, nao mothiũ mao matirĩ hingo makahumbwo nĩ thoni.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>  Mũthĩnĩki ũyũ aakaire, nake Mwathani akĩmũigua, akĩmũhonokia mĩnyamaro inĩ yake.</s>"},{ID:11,
