Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	Ndũrĩrĩ ciothe nĩ igagũturĩria maru, wee Mwathani </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Matukũ make ũrĩa mũthingu nĩ kũhamba arĩhambaga, na gũtũũre na thayũ mũingĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nginya  o hingo mweri ũkarindũka.  Nĩ agĩe na watho kuuma iria-inĩ rĩmwe o nginya rĩrĩa rĩngĩ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> na kuuma Rũũĩ-inĩ o nginya ituri cia thĩ.</s>"},{ID:6,
