Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani; gwata kĩrĩa o gĩothe gĩĩ thĩinĩ wakwa nĩ kĩgathe rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩamũre. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Ngoro yakwa, kĩgathe Mwathani, na ndũkariganĩrũo nĩ wega o na ũmwe marĩa agwĩkaga.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Arĩ we ũkuohagĩra waganu waku wothe; ndũari ciaku ciothe o nacio nowe mũkũhonia; o we mũkũũri muoyo waku harĩ irima rĩa gĩkuũ, </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>na nowe mũgwĩki maũndũ ma ũtugi na ma  matha maigũ, ta arĩ thũmbĩ aragwĩkĩra ya ũnene.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani, nĩwe mwĩki ciĩko cia ũthingu, arĩa othe agũmĩre agagĩtua matuĩro ma kĩhooto nĩ ũndũ wao.  Mĩthiĩre yake nĩ ciana cia Israeli aakĩonirie.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Mwathani, nĩ wa matha maingĩ na nĩ muuma-andũ-mũno; ndahiũhaga kũrakara, na e na ũtugi  mũingĩ.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Niĩ amu-rĩ, o ũguo matu-inĩ kũhaicĩte o igũrũ rĩa thĩ, no taguo ũtugi wake ũneneheire arĩa amwĩtigĩri.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>ICOKIA	
