Text:"<fArial Black><s1384></s></f><fArial Black><s2769>Wi mukumie kuri atumia othe, ii na Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ii uciari wa nda yaku nake arokumio guku thi na iguru tondu niwe wagituhonokirie.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
