Text:"<s1384>WIMBO WA KATIKATI					                Zab. 96</s>"},{Tag:1,ID:0,
Text:"<s1384>Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>1.	Mwimbieni Mungu, wimbo mpya!
Mwimbieni Mungu, ulimwengu wote!
Mwimbieni Mungu na kulisifu jina lake!</s>"},{Tag:1,ID:0,
Text:"<s1384>Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Tangazeni kila siku habari njema kwamba 
Ametuokoa. Yatangazieni mataifa utukufu wake,
na matendo yake makuu kwa watu wote.(K)</s>"},{Tag:1,ID:0,
Text:"<s1384>Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Mpeni Mungu heshima, enyi jamii zote za watu;
sifuni utukufu na enzi yake.
Lisifuni jina tukufu la Mungu!(K) </s>"},{Tag:1,ID:0,
Text:"<s1384>Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>4.	Leteni sadaka na kuingia Hekaluni
Mwake.  Mwabuduni Mungu anapotokea,
tetemeka mbele yake, ee dunia nzima.(K)</s>"},{Tag:1,ID:0,
Text:"<s1384>Watu wote wakutukuze ee Mungu
Mataifa yote yakusifu</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>5.	Yaambieni mataifa: “Mwenyezi ni Mfalme! 
