Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niguo tugie hinya mweru ma ngoro-ini ,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ukâi, ukai tukamwamukire </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ahaririirie metha ( na ningi ), ni aratwita tukamwamukire,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
