Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uria ukaria mwiri wakwa e na ngoro theru , ngooka thiini wake tuturanagie nake</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ahaririirie metha (na ningi), ni aratwita tukamwamukire,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake uria wothe ukaria Mwiri wa Kristu o na ningi akinyue thakame yake, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndagakua ori ori ni agatura muoyo tondu ari na hinya mweru wa gutoria</s></f>"},{ID:17,
