Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni mpole, ni mwema, ni uzima.</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Waumini (haya) simameni, pole pole, kwa heshima, jongeeni, </s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
