Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ekaristi, ni jina lake, pamoja nasi, Mungu mwenyewe, ndani yetu nasi ndani yake.</s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Waumini (haya) simameni, pole pole, kwa heshima, jongeeni, </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>karamuni, mpate(mpate) kumuonja Mwokozi (Yesu)x2</s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alitoa, jioni ile, kwa kumbukumbu yake milele, tule tunywe wote tuokoke.</s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Waumini (haya) simameni, pole pole, kwa heshima, jongeeni, karamuni, </s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mpate(mpate) kumuonja Mwokozi(Yesu)x2</s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tugeuze, maisha yetu, tukafanane na meza hii, 
