wala jani lake halinyauki;
kila wafanyalo linafanikiwa. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K)	Heri mtu aliyemfanya Bwana kuwa tumaini lake.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Sivyo walivyo waovu!
