Text:"<s1384>Maana Bwana anatunza njia yao waadilifu,
lakini njia ya waovu itapotea. (K)</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>(K)	Heri mtu aliyemfanya Bwana kuwa tumaini lake.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
