Text:"ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA"},{Guid:"fSUXCxYb3kiKIVerZMqEXQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA   		Zaburi 22:8-9, 17-18a, 19-20, 23-24 (K. 2a)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>K. Mungu wangu, Mungu wangu, mbona umeniacha?</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Wote wanaoniona hunicheka;
hunyonga midomo kwa kunidhihaki; na kutikisa vichwa vyao:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>\"Alimwamini Bwana, acha amwokoe;
acha amuopoe, kwa kuwa anapendezwa naye.\" (K)</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>K. Mungu wangu, Mungu wangu, mbona umeniacha?</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa maana mbwa wengi wamenizunguka;
kundi la waovu wananisonga.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Wamenitoboa mikono na miguu
naweza kuhesabu mifupa yangu yote. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>K. Mungu wangu, Mungu wangu, mbona umeniacha?</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Wanagawanya nguo zangu kati yao;
wanaipigia kura kanzu yangu.
Nawe, </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>ee Bwana, usiwe mbali;
ewe msaada wangu, fanya haraka kunisaidia. (K)</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>K. Mungu wangu, Mungu wangu, mbona umeniacha?</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nitawasimulia ndugu zangu jina lako;
Katikati ya mkutano nitakusifu:
\"Enyi watumishi wa Bwana, </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>msifuni!
Enyi wote, wazao wa Yakobo, mtukuzeni;
enyi wote, wana wa Israeli, mtumikieni!\" (K)</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>K. Mungu wangu, Mungu wangu, mbona umeniacha?</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF990000"}}},
