Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 			Zaburi 51:3-4, 12-13, 14-15 (K. 12a)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>K. Uniumbie moyo safi, ee Mungu.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Unihurumie, ee Mungu, kulingana na wema wako;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>kwa kadiri ya huruma yako kuu, uyafute makosa yangu.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Unioshe kabisa na uovu wangu;
unitakase dhambi yangu. (K)</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>K. Uniumbie moyo safi, ee Mungu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Uniumbie moyo safi, ee Mungu
ufanye upya roho thabiti ndani yangu.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Usinitupe mbali na uso wako,
wala usiniondolee roho yako takatifu. (K)</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>K. Uniumbie moyo safi, ee Mungu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Unirudishie furaha ya wokovu wako;
unitegemeze kwa kunijalia roho sikivu</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Nitawafundisha waasi njia zako,
nao wenye dhambi watarudi kwako. (K)</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>K. Uniumbie moyo safi, ee Mungu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
