Text:"<s1384>(K)Wewe waufumbua mkono wako, ee Bwana, na kukidhi hamu yetu.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kazi zako zote zinakutukuza, ee Bwana,wachaji wako wanakusifu.</s>"},{ID:4,
