Text:"<s1384>Wewe waufumbua mkono wako na kukidhi hamu ya kila kilicho hai. (K)</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>(K)Wewe waufumbua mkono wako, ee Bwana, na kukidhi hamu yetu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana ni mwenye haki katika njia zake zote,na mwema kwa kazi zake zote.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana u karibu na wote wakuitao,wote wakuitao kwa uaminifu. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K)Wewe waufumbua mkono wako, ee Bwana, na kukidhi hamu yetu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF006631"}}},
