Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 		            Zab. 89:4-5,16-17,27 na 29 (K. 2a)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>(K) 	Fadhili za Bwana nitaziimba milele</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nimefunga agano na mteule wangu; 
nimemwapia Daudi, mtumishi wangu:</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>nitawasimika wazao wako hata milele, 
nitaimarisha kiti cha ufalme wako kwa vizazi vyote.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>(K) 	Fadhili za Bwana nitaziimba milele</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Heri taifa linalokujua, 
waendao ee Bwana, katika mwanga wako.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Wanafurahiwa na jina lako mchana kutwa;
nao kwa haki yako wanatukuza kwa kushangilia.  (K)</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>(K) 	Fadhili za Bwana nitaziimba milele</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Yeye ataniita, ‘Wewe ni Baba yangu, 
Mungu wangu na mwamba wa wokovu wangu!’ </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Nitamhifadhia fadhili zangu hata milele; 
na agano langu kwake litadumu daima.  (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K) 	Fadhili za Bwana nitaziimba milele</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
