Zaburi 78:3-4,24-25 na 54 
 		</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Bwana aliwapa mkate wa mbinguni.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Mambo tuliyosikia na kuyajua;mambo ambayo baba zetu walituhadithia,</s>"},{ID:4,
