Text:"<s1384>(K) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>BWANA  huyafumbua macho ya vipofu. 
BWANA huwainua waliokandamızwa chini;
BWANA huwapenda wenye haki
BWANA huwalinda wageni. (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Bwana huwategemeza yatima na mjane,
bali huipotosha njia ya waovu
BWANA atatawala milele,
Mungu wako, ee Sioni, kizazi hata kizazi! (K)</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA  "},{Guid:"cmZF/2ksIUSwEESFqnfTNQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika Oktava ya Kuzaliwa Kwake Bwana Yesu
SHEREHE YA BIKIRA MARIA,
MAMA WA MUNGU</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Hesabu</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana alimwambia Musa: “Mwambie Haruni na wanawe:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivi ndivyo mtakavyowabariki wana wa Israeli.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtawaambia:
Bwana akubariki na kukulinda!</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akuangazie uso wake,na kukufadhili!</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akuelekezee uso wake na kukuletea amani!</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waliweke hivyo jina langu juu ya wana wa Israeli,
nami nitawabariki.\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 67:2-3,5,6,8,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu na aturehemu na kutubariki,
atuangazie uso wake.</s></f>"},{ID:10},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Wagalatia 4:41</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu alisema na mababu zetu kwa njia ya manabii.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku hizi za mwisho amesema na sisi kwa njia ya Mwana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Walimkuta Maria na Yosefu, na mtoto mchanga.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zilipotimia siku nane, aliitwa jina lake Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka
Luka 2:16-21</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati huo: [Wachungaji]  Wachunganji walienda kwa haraka Bethlehemu,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamkuta Maria na Yosefu, na mtoto mchanga amelala horini.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walipomnwona, walieleza habari waliyoambiwa juu ya mtoto
huyu.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Wote waliosikia wakayastaajabia maneno waliyoambiwa na
wachungaji.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Naye Maria akatunza mambo hayo yote akiyawaza
moyoni mwake.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Wachungaji wakarudi kwao wakimtukuza na</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kumsifu Mungu kwa yote waliyoyasikia na kuyaona, kama
walivyoambiwa.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zilipotimia siku nane, ndio wakati wa kumtahiri mtoto,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> aliitwa jina
lake Yesu, kama alivyoitwa na malaika kabla ya kutungwa mimba.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njia yake itambulike duniani,
na wokovu wake katika mataifa yote.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mataifa na wafurahi na kushangilia,
kwa kuwa unawatawala kwa haki,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuwaongoza mataifa ya dunia.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu na wakutukuze, ee Mungu,
watu wote na wakutukuze!</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu atatubariki sisi,
na miisho yote ya dunia itamcha Mungu wetu. </s></f>"}],
Text:"SHEREHE YA BIKIRA MARIA MAMA WA MUNGU"},{Guid:"8jMNAtZwvk2aJFgJ0FcT5g",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA  	Zaburi 63:2. 3-4, 5-6, 7-8 (K. 2b)</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Roho yangu inakuonea kiu, ee Bwana, Mungu wangu.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ee Mungu, Mungu wangu, ninakutafuta kwa dhati!
Roho yangu inakuonea kiu;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>mwili wangu unakuonea shauku,
katika nchi kavu, yenye kiu, isiyo na maji. (K)</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Roho yangu inakuonea kiu, ee Bwana, Mungu wangu.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Hivyo nilikutazama katika patakatifu,
nione enzi yako na utukufu wako.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Fadhili zako ni bora kuliko maisha;
kwa hiyo midomo yangu itakutukuza! (K)</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Roho yangu inakuonea kiu, ee Bwana, Mungu wangu.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Nitakusifu pindi niishipo;
kwa jina lako nitaiinua mikono yangu.</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Roho yangu itafurahi kama kwa kushiba mafuta na vinono,
kwa midomo ya furaha, kinywa changu kitakusifu! (K)</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Roho yangu inakuonea kiu, ee Bwana, Mungu wangu.</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Ninapokukumbuka kitandani mwangu,
Vipindi vyote vya usiku ninakufikiria wewe.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Kwa maana umekuwa msaada  wangu,
na uvulini mwa mbawa zako nitashangilia. (K)</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Roho yangu inakuonea kiu, ee Bwana, Mungu wangu.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
Text:"ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA  "},{Guid:"w7HY/nBJPk+1jpVdVFOZpQ",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF490099"}}},
