Text:"<s1384>dunia imejaa viumbe vyako.
Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu! (K)</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1384>(K) Bwana, umtume Roho wako, na uufanye upya  uso wa nchi</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
