Text:"<s1384>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA:
Zab 141:1,2,3 na 8 {K}2a</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>K:  Ee Bwana, sala yangu na ikubalike mbele zako kama ubani. </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Nimekulilia, ee Bwana, unijie hima! Usikie sauti yangu ninapokuita.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Sala yangu ikubalike mbele zako kama ubani;
Niinuapo mikono yangu iwe kama sadaka ya jioni. {K}</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>K:  Ee Bwana,sala yangu na ikubalike mbele zako kama ubani. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Uweke, ee Bwana, mlinzi kinywani pangu;
linda mlango wa midomo yangu!</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Macho yangu yameelekezwa kwako, ee Bwana, Mungu wangu.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>nimekukimbilia wewe; usiiache nafsi yangu. {K}</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>K:  Ee Bwana,sala yangu na ikubalike mbele zako kama ubani. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Shangilio:</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>K: Aleluya</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Nakutukuza, Baba, Bwana wa mbingu na nchi, kwa maana umewafunulia watoto wachanga mafumbo ya ufalme. </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Aleluya.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
